#: After_the_Storm/episode1/characters.cfg:104
msgid ""
"Certain high-level units in this campaign under your control — such as Galas "
"and Elynia — have special <b>After Maximum Level Advancements (AMLAs)</b>. "
"You can learn more about those by right-clicking applicable units and "
"choosing the <b>Unit Advancements</b> option."
msgstr ""
"Algunas unidades de alto nivel bajo tu control en esta campaña —como Galas y "
"Elynia— tienen <b>Mejoras tras el nivel máximo (AMLAs)</b> especiales. "
"Puedes obtener más información sobre ellas haciendo clic derecho en las "
"unidades correspondientes y seleccionando la opción <b>Mejoras de unidad</b>."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:31
msgid "I... fall to the darkness..."
msgstr "Yo... caigo en la oscuridad..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:35
msgid "Elynia... NO!"
msgstr "¡Elynia... NO!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:41
msgid "Our mission has failed."
msgstr "Nuestra misión ha fracasado."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:52
msgid "I... am finished... I’ll finally join Anlindë..."
msgstr "Yo... he terminado... finalmente me reuniré con Anlindë..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:56
msgid "No! You must resist!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡Debes resistir!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:62
msgid "This... this is a curse!"
msgstr "Esto... ¡esto es una maldición!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:73
msgid "Alas, I can finally depart in peace..."
msgstr "Por fin... puedo partir en paz..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:77
msgid "NO! Malin, we need you for this!"
msgstr "¡NO! ¡Malin, te necesitamos para esto!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:81
msgid "It’s too late already..."
msgstr "Ya es demasiado tarde..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:87
msgid "Now we cannot continue without him. Our mission has failed!"
msgstr "Ahora no podemos continuar sin él. ¡Nuestra misión ha fracasado!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:98
msgid "I think it’s the end... for me..."
msgstr "Creo que es el final... para mí..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:110
msgid "Hm. Oh well, waste not, want not."
msgstr "Hmm. Bueno, no se desperdicia nada."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:115
msgid "<i>(glares)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(lo fulmina con la mirada)</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:120
msgid ""
"All right, all right! But you probably want to dispose of the body quickly "
"before his stench alone kills you. The little pest hasn’t bathed in weeks."
msgstr ""
"Está bien, está bien. Pero probablemente quieras deshacerte del cuerpo "
"rápido antes de que su hedor te mate. La pequeña plaga no se ha bañado en "
"semanas."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:125
msgid ""
"That would be your fault for stalking him whenever he wasn’t with us two."
msgstr ""
"Eso sería tu culpa por acecharlo cada vez que no estaba con nosotros dos."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#. Yes, he starts quoting Shakespeare before being interrupted.
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:132
msgid "Alas, poor Igor! <i>(conjures dark magic)</i> I knew him, Elynia—"
msgstr "¡Ay, pobre Igor! <i>(conjura magia oscura)</i> Lo conocía, Elynia—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:137
msgid "Leave his body alone!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡Deja su cuerpo en paz!!!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:152
msgid "Ouch. I fall before accomplishing my mission!"
msgstr "Auch. Caigo antes de cumplir mi misión."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:158
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:250
msgid ""
"The orcs are now leaderless, and won’t want to help us. We cannot continue "
"without their help!"
msgstr ""
"Los orcos están sin líder y no querrán ayudarnos. ¡No podemos continuar sin "
"su ayuda!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:169
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:261
msgid "Alas, it’s the end of the story for me..."
msgstr "Ay... es el fin de la historia para mí..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:175
msgid "We shouldn’t have allowed this to happen."
msgstr "No deberíamos haber permitido que esto sucediera."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:179
msgid ""
"Ah, too bad for the girl. But she was indeed one of the best archers I have "
"seen."
msgstr ""
"Ah, qué pena por la chica. Pero en verdad era una de las mejores arqueras "
"que he visto."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:190
msgid "I wish... I could be with you... now... Galas..."
msgstr "Desearía... poder estar contigo... ahora... Galas..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:200
msgid "No, Elynia! Not you now!"
msgstr "¡No, Elynia! ¡No tú ahora!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:214
msgid ""
"Now it’s up to me to put an end to this madness... I hope I can manage to do "
"it alone..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora depende de mí poner fin a esta locura... Espero poder lograrlo solo..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:227
msgid "I go to join my only true friend... now..."
msgstr "Voy a reunirme con mi único verdadero amigo... ahora..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:233
msgid "How could I let this happen? NO!"
msgstr "¿Cómo pude dejar que esto pasara? ¡NO!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:244
msgid "Ouch. I am done for!"
msgstr "Auch. ¡Estoy acabado!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/deaths.cfg:267
msgid ""
"Ah, too bad for the girl. She was indeed one of the best archers I have seen."
msgstr ""
"Ah, qué pena por la chica. En verdad era una de las mejores arqueras que he "
"visto."

