#. [campaign]: id=After_the_Storm_I
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/menu.cfg:14
msgid ""
"After the Emperor of Chaos was defeated, the free civilizations of the Great "
"Continent hoped that his followers would abandon the ongoing war. Meanwhile, "
"Galas and his unlikely band of heroes head back to the northern lands to "
"request aid for their next journey."
msgstr ""
"Tras la derrota del Emperador del Caos, las civilizaciones libres del Gran "
"Continente esperaban que sus seguidores abandonaran la guerra en curso. "
"Mientras tanto, Galas y su peculiar grupo de héroes regresan a las tierras "
"del norte para solicitar ayuda para su próximo viaje."

