#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:295
msgid "Death of Morzey"
msgstr "Muerte de Morzey"

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:379
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Night falls... The scouts reported at midday that those accursed soldiers of "
"Uria were headed towards our town. It’s going to be a very long night "
"waiting for them to arrive."
msgstr ""
"Cae la noche, y los exploradores informaron al mediodía que esos malditos "
"soldados se dirigían hacia nuestro pueblo."

#. [message]: role=guard_2
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:384
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Assuming they don’t somehow make it here sooner than that. Sigh... It wasn’t "
"enough for them to burn and ransack Tyannes. Damn it, why don’t the elders "
"send us reinforcements?"
msgstr ""
"No les bastó con quemar y saquear Tyannes... Maldición, ¿por qué los "
"ancianos no nos envían refuerzos?"

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:389
msgid ""
"Meh. Ever since this war started they have cared little about safety — not "
"just ours. It’s rumored that the country itself would fare very poorly "
"against another foreign invasion."
msgstr ""
"Bah. Desde que comenzó esta guerra apenas se han preocupado por la seguridad "
"— no solo la nuestra. Se rumorea que el país mismo no resistiría otra "
"invasión extranjera."

#. [message]: role=guard_2
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:393
msgid "Well, I’ve heard that the elves have..."
msgstr "Bueno, he oído que los elfos tienen..."

#. [message]: role=guard_3
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:397
msgid "On guard! Three strangers approach from the southern road!"
msgstr "¡En guardia! ¡Tres extraños se acercan por el camino del sur!"

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:423
msgid "Halt there! Identify yourselves, strangers!"
msgstr "¡Detenganse! ¡Identifiquense, extraños!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:427
msgid ""
"We are travelers. We don’t plan to stay in your town for more than one "
"night. You don’t need to know who we are."
msgstr ""
"Somos viajeros. No planeamos quedarnos en su pueblo más de una noche. No "
"necesitáis saber quiénes somos."

#. [message]: role=guard_2
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:431
msgid ""
"Sorry, but we were ordered not to let anybody... pass... She’s... beautiful."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, pero se nos ordenó no dejar pasar a nadie... Ella es... hermosa."

#. [message]: role=guard_3
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:436
msgid ""
"A faerie? Wh— what’s one of your kind doing so far from the northern lands?"
msgstr ""
"¿Un hada? ¿Q-qué hace alguien de tu especie tan lejos de las tierras del "
"norte?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:440
msgid ""
"As I said, we don’t plan to stay for more than one night. Just let us in."
msgstr ""
"Como dije, no planeamos quedarnos más de una noche. Simplemente déjanos "
"entrar."

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:455
msgid "Who is that? Hey, the cloaked one!"
msgstr "¿Quién es ese? ¡Eh, el de la capa!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:459
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:251
msgid "Eh?"
msgstr "¿Eh?"

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:463
#, fuzzy
msgid "Aaah!! Necromancer!"
msgstr "¡Un nigromante! Un..."

#. [message]: role=guard_3
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:467
msgid "Quick! Alert the—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:471
msgid ""
"You are not alerting the entire town of his presence, are you? Such a "
"handsome man could spend the night doing... more worthwhile things than "
"fighting us..."
msgstr ""
"No estarás alertando a todo el pueblo de su presencia, ¿verdad? Un hombre "
"tan apuesto podría pasar la noche haciendo... cosas más provechosas que "
"peleando con nosotras..."

#. [message]: role=guard_3
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:475
#, fuzzy
msgid "Erm... I..."
msgstr "... Yo..."

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:479
msgid ""
"I don’t know what the hell your purpose here is, but we do have important "
"things to do this night, such as defending the town from your cursed "
"henchmen!"
msgstr ""
"No sé cuál demonios es su propósito aquí, ¡pero tenemos cosas importantes "
"que hacer esta noche, como defender el pueblo de sus malditos esbirros!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:483
#, fuzzy
msgid "Henchmen? Do you see anyone else accompanying us? No? Well, then."
msgstr "¿Esbirros? ¿Acaso ves a alguien más acompañándonos?"

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:490
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Eh! That you don’t <i>seem</i> to bring anyone with you does not mean you "
"cannot somehow summon them later! We heard rumors of the infernal warriors "
"coming to our valley!"
msgstr ""
"¡Eh! ¡Que no <i>parezca</i> que traes a nadie contigo no significa que no "
"puedas invocarlos más tarde! ¡Hemos oído rumores de que los guerreros "
"malditos vienen a nuestro valle!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:495
#, fuzzy
msgid "Infernal, you say?"
msgstr "¿Zhangor, dices?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:507
msgid ""
"Clad in black armor, bearing flags with impaled skulls at the top, and said "
"to smell especially funny?"
msgstr ""
"¿Con armaduras negras, portando banderas con calaveras empaladas en la punta "
"y que, dicen, huelen especialmente mal?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:512
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Those are our enemies as well. We have had many encounters with them before. "
"Perhaps we could be of help, <i>if</i> you would be so kind as to let us "
"into the town."
msgstr ""
"También son nuestros enemigos. Ya hemos tenido algunos encuentros con ellos "
"antes. Quizás podríamos ayudar, <i>si</i> nos permitieran entrar dentro de "
"sus murallas."

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:517
msgid ""
"Let them come in at once! We are in need of all the help we can get if we "
"want to live another day."
msgstr ""
"¡Déjalos entrar de inmediato! Necesitamos toda la ayuda posible si queremos "
"vivir un día más."

#. [message]: role=guard_1
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:522
msgid "Yes, sir! As you command, sir!"
msgstr "¡Sí, señor! ¡Como ordene, señor!"

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:542
msgid ""
"Strangers, please help us. I am sure the gate guards already told you of the "
"situation..."
msgstr ""
"Forasteros, por favor ayúdenos. Estoy seguro de que los guardias de la "
"puerta ya les contaron la situación..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:547
msgid "Yes, they did."
msgstr "Sí, lo hicieron."

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:552
msgid ""
"Well, well. I have heard of necromancers helping the northern country’s "
"cause, so I... suppose you can be trusted. Although, if you turn out to be "
"working for our enemies we would be doomed either way. I beg of you to aid "
"us in this battle; all we have left nowadays is the town militia, for which "
"we can barely afford proper weapons."
msgstr ""
"Vaya, vaya. He oído que algunos nigromantes ayudan a la causa del país del "
"norte, así que... supongo que puedo confiar en ustedes. Aunque si resultan "
"trabajar para nuestros enemigos, estaríamos condenados de todas formas. Les "
"ruego que nos ayuden en esta batalla; lo único que nos queda hoy en día es "
"la milicia del pueblo, y apenas podemos costearles armas decentes."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:557
msgid "We’ll help you. Just don’t ask names."
msgstr "Los ayudaremos. Solo no pregunten nombres."

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:562
msgid "That’s... a very dubious request..."
msgstr "Eso es... una petición muy sospechosa..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:570
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"There is someone else coming with us. I hope you will not mind his presence "
"here as well."
msgstr ""
"Hay alguien más que viene con nosotros también. Estoy seguro de que "
"toleraréis su presencia aquí."

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:575
msgid "Well, I..."
msgstr "Bueno, yo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:616
msgid ""
"Ugh, a goblin? Riding a wolf? You cannot be serious! Your kind is not "
"welcome around these parts after the poultry farmers’ guild incident."
msgstr ""
"¡Ugh, un goblin? ¿Montando un lobo? ¡No puedes hablar en serio! Tu clase no "
"es bienvenida por estos lares después del incidente con el gremio de "
"granjeros avícolas."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:621
msgid ""
"No, no, no! I mean no harm! Just passing by with my friends, that’s all! "
"Willow is also a very well behaved lady, you aren’t even gonna notice her "
"presence."
msgstr ""
"¡No, no, no! ¡No quiero hacer daño! Solo estoy de paso con mis amigos, eso "
"es todo. Willow también es una dama muy bien educada, ni siquiera notarán su "
"presencia."

#. [message]: role=guard_6
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:634
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Sir! We’re receiving reports of enemy forces approaching from the northern "
"hills!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mi señor! ¡Antorchas y tambores de guerra se acercan desde las colinas del "
"norte!"

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:639
msgid ""
"Blast it — we did not anticipate them arriving so soon! Everyone, to arms!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:655
msgid "We failed to protect the town..."
msgstr "Hemos fallado en proteger el pueblo..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:669
msgid "Curse you, heretics! The Iron Council shall punish you for your deeds!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos sean, herejes! ¡El Consejo de Hierro os castigará por vuestras "
"acciones!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:681
msgid "I do not think so."
msgstr "No lo creo."

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:690
msgid ""
"We will be eternally thankful for your help, travelers! If there is anything "
"we can do in return..."
msgstr ""
"¡Estaremos eternamente agradecidos por vuestra ayuda, viajeros! Si hay algo "
"que podamos hacer a cambio..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:695
msgid ""
"No problem; we just need provisions and directions for our journey to the "
"northern country."
msgstr ""
"No hay problema; solo necesitamos provisiones e indicaciones para nuestro "
"viaje al país del norte."

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:700
msgid ""
"Traveling north, eh? There is a mountain pass to the northeast — it used to "
"be a very accessible trading route before the war began. Nowadays it is "
"plagued by dark cultists and their undead minions, and the Grand Council has "
"done nothing to clean it up."
msgstr ""
"¿Viajar al norte, eh? Hay un paso de montaña al noreste; solía ser una ruta "
"comercial muy accesible antes de que comenzara la guerra. Hoy en día está "
"plagada de oscuros cultistas y sus siervos no-muertos, y el Gran Consejo no "
"ha hecho nada para despejarla."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:705
msgid "Thanks for the information, we may as well take that path then."
msgstr "Gracias por la información, entonces quizá tomemos ese camino."

#. [message]: speaker=Morzey
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:710
msgid "Are you sure?"
msgstr "¿Estás seguro?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:715
msgid "We <i>control</i> the dead. We need not worry about them."
msgstr ""
"Nosotros <i>controlamos</i> a los muertos. No necesitamos preocuparnos por "
"ellos."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:739
msgid ""
"Sometimes, your loved ones must be willing to sacrifice their lives for a "
"greater cause."
msgstr ""
"A veces, tus seres queridos deben estar dispuestos a sacrificar sus vidas "
"por una causa mayor."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/01_The_Skirmish.cfg:753
msgid ""
"Their reinforcements are here! There is no way we can keep the town from "
"devastation at this point!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/storytxt.cfg:70
msgid "High Pass"
msgstr "Paso Alto"

#. [side]: id=Mal Ciphan, type=Lich
#. [side]: id=Nyadien, type=Draug
#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:44
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:164
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/07_The_Search_for_the_Past.cfg:87
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:134
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:176
msgid "team_name^Undead"
msgstr "No-muertos"

#. [side]: id=Mal Ciphan, type=Lich
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:87
msgid "Mal Ciphan"
msgstr "Mal Ciphan"

#. [side]: id=Nyadien, type=Draug
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:207
msgid "Nyadien"
msgstr "Nyadien"

#. [event]
#. [event]: type=Orcish Archer, type=Orcish Archer, type=Skeleton, type=Orcish Grunt, type=Revenant, type=Revenant, type=Deathblade, type=Dark Adept, type=Skeleton Archer, type=Orcish Grunt, type=Revenant
#. [scenario]
#. [event]: type=Shaxthal War Drone, type=Shaxthal Enforcer Drone, type=Shaxthal Demolisher Drone, type=Chaos Cataphract, id=Celwyngyr, type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Morol, type=Lich, id=Mal Fyrgwynn, type=Demon Warrior, gender=male, id=Demon Lord Alavys
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:289
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:157
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/08_Fear.cfg:247
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/09_The_Triad_part_1.cfg:887
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:208
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:271
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:232
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:561
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1166
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/02_01_Return_to_Raelthyn.cfg:663
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:531
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:545
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/04_01_Outpost_of_Hell.cfg:660
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/04_01_Outpost_of_Hell.cfg:677
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/05_Pass_of_Sorrows.cfg:636
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1628
msgid "Defeat all enemy leaders"
msgstr "Derrota a todos los líderes enemigos"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:306
msgid ""
"This place gives me chills. Perhaps this path was not a good choice after "
"all."
msgstr ""
"Este lugar me da escalofríos. Quizá este camino no fue una buena elección "
"después de todo."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:312
msgid "Pah. Leave your worries behind, there is nothing to..."
msgstr "Bah. Deja tus preocupaciones atrás, no hay nada que..."

#. [message]: type=Necrophage
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:345
msgid "Groaaar!!!"
msgstr "¡¡Groaaar!!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:350
msgid "... and who called upon you?"
msgstr "... ¿y quién los invocó?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:355
msgid ""
"So it is as the townsfolk warned us — this pass is infested with undead. "
"We’ll have to give them a final rest before we can proceed any further."
msgstr ""
"Así que era como los aldeanos nos advirtieron: este paso está infestado de "
"no-muertos. Tendremos que darles el descanso final antes de poder avanzar."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:360
msgid "Aww, this will be boring."
msgstr "Aww, esto será aburrido."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Ciphan
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:376
msgid ""
"Ahhh, the traitors! Never again will you see the sunlight, for I shall feed "
"your impious souls to Yechnagoth!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahhh, los traidores! ¡Nunca más volveréis a ver la luz del sol, pues "
"alimentaré vuestras impías almas a Yechnagoth!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:381
msgid "The same old tune. These goons should seek a new job or something."
msgstr ""
"La misma cantinela de siempre. Estos matones deberían buscarse un trabajo "
"nuevo o algo así."

#. [message]: speaker=Nyadien
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:390
msgid "You, Galas! You abandoned us in the valley! You left us all to die!"
msgstr ""
"¡Tú, Galas! ¡Nos abandonaste en el valle! ¡Nos dejaste a todos para morir!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:395
msgid "Nyadien? But..."
msgstr "¿Nyadien? Pero..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:400
msgid "Do you know him?"
msgstr "¿Lo conoces?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:405
msgid ""
"He was the leader of the patrol group that replaced mine just before the "
"Chaos Empire invaded our valley."
msgstr ""
"Era el líder del grupo de patrulla que reemplazó al mío justo antes de que "
"el Imperio del Caos invadiera nuestro valle."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:410
msgid ""
"Elf, know that Galas did not have the power to stop that invasion, but the "
"Chaos Empire no longer has a leader. There is nothing that should force you "
"to roam this world anymore!"
msgstr ""
"Elfo, sabe que Galas no tenía el poder para detener esa invasión, pero el "
"Imperio del Caos ya no tiene líder. ¡Nada debería obligarte a vagar por este "
"mundo nunca más!"

#. [message]: speaker=Nyadien
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:415
msgid "I will personally make sure you don’t go unpunished, traitor!"
msgstr "¡Me aseguraré personalmente de que no quedes sin castigo, traidor!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:420
msgid ""
"It is a waste of time to try to deal with this pile of bones. The "
"necromancer who raised him probably used some malign spell to infect his "
"soul with hatred towards every elf who outlived him."
msgstr ""
"Es una pérdida de tiempo intentar razonar con este montón de huesos. El "
"nigromante que lo alzó probablemente usó algún hechizo maligno para infectar "
"su alma con odio hacia cada elfo que sobrevivió."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:547
msgid ""
"It’s beginning to snow... Galas, we probably should avoid spending too long "
"in this pass — it seems like it could easily become a deathtrap, especially "
"with the undead controlling it."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:552
msgid ""
"I agree, the snow could not only hinder us significantly but also turn us "
"into easy prey."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:562
msgid ""
"We are taking too long! We need to hurry up if we don’t want to be buried "
"alive in this place!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:580
msgid ""
"I am vanquished, but I curse your race to never see a day of peace or joy "
"again for the rest of eternity!"
msgstr ""
"Estoy vencido, ¡pero maldigo a vuestra raza a no volver a ver un día de paz "
"o alegría por el resto de la eternidad!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:592
msgid "So many times... I forget how many times they have said that."
msgstr "Tantas veces... Ya he olvidado cuántas veces han dicho eso."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:606
msgid ""
"Honestly, with your fearsome steed you should be more than able to reach "
"your destination without us, Igor."
msgstr ""
"Sinceramente, con tu temible montura deberías ser más que capaz de alcanzar "
"tu destino sin nosotros, Igor."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:611
msgid ""
"You’re kidding, right? There’s no way we’d be able to get past all the "
"smelly skeletons alone! I don’t wanna become one of them zombies while I’m "
"still young!"
msgstr ""
"¿Estás bromeando, verdad? ¡No hay forma de que podamos pasar entre todos "
"esos esqueletos apestosos solos! ¡No quiero convertirme en uno de esos "
"zombis mientras aún soy joven!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:616
msgid ""
"<i>(snicker)</i> I could arrange for you to become a more dignified skeleton "
"warrior if you prefer..."
msgstr ""
"<i>(risita)</i> Podría arreglar para que te conviertas en un guerrero "
"esqueleto más digno si lo prefieres..."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:621
msgid "Eeek!!! No!!!"
msgstr "¡¡Eeek!!! ¡¡¡No!!!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:626
msgid "Will you please stop tormenting him, Malin."
msgstr "¿Puedes dejar de atormentarlo, Malin?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:631
msgid ""
"Fiiiiine. <small>Someone needs a sense of humor... <i>mutter mutter</i>...</"
"small>"
msgstr ""
"Bieeeeen. <small>Alguien necesita sentido del humor... <i>murmura murmura</"
"i>...</small>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:636
msgid "The ears aren’t just for show, you know. We <i>can</i> hear you."
msgstr "Las orejas no son solo de adorno, ¿sabes? <i>Podemos</i> oírte."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:645
#, fuzzy
msgid "It seems like there is a much bigger storm approaching..."
msgstr "Se acerca una tormenta."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/02_High_Pass.cfg:654
msgid ""
"This doesn’t seem good at all — the storm has finally reached this pass and "
"we’ll be buried under the snow. We should not have tarried here for so long!"
msgstr ""
"Esto no pinta nada bien: la tormenta finalmente ha llegado a este paso y "
"quedaremos sepultados bajo la nieve. ¡No deberíamos haber demorado tanto "
"aquí!"

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/storytxt.cfg:90
msgid "Civil War in the North"
msgstr "Guerra Civil en el Norte"

