#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/09_The_Triad_part_2.cfg:1201
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/09_The_Triad_part_3.cfg:207
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/12_Return_to_Wesmere.cfg:519
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/12_Return_to_Wesmere.cfg:792
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/12_Return_to_Wesmere.cfg:894
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/12_Wesmere_Terminus.cfg:507
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/12_Wesmere_Terminus.cfg:968
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/12_Wesmere_Terminus.cfg:2290
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:169
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:414
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/09_New_Hive.cfg:264
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/10_The_Betrayal.cfg:1058
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/10_The_Betrayal.cfg:1354
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/10_The_Betrayal.cfg:1440
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/11_A_Final_Confrontation.cfg:422
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/11_A_Final_Confrontation.cfg:765
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/11_A_Final_Confrontation.cfg:1002
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/11_A_Final_Confrontation.cfg:1409
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/11_A_Final_Confrontation.cfg:1952
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/11_A_Final_Confrontation.cfg:2176
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/05_Pass_of_Sorrows.cfg:278
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/05_Pass_of_Sorrows.cfg:635
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/05_Pass_of_Sorrows.cfg:946
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:631
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:461
msgid "Current Objectives:"
msgstr "Objetivos actuales:"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:300
msgid "Move Galas, Elynia and Mal Keshar to Fort Eldáin"
msgstr "Mueve a Galas, Elynia y Mal Keshar al Fuerte Eldáin"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:316
msgid "I don’t like this... There are signs of a recent battle in this area."
msgstr "No me gusta esto... Hay señales de una batalla reciente en esta zona."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:321
msgid ""
"Quickly, let us investigate what happened here. I hope it’s not too late."
msgstr ""
"Rápido, investiguemos qué sucedió aquí. Espero que no sea demasiado tarde."

#. [message]: type=Bowman
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:402
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Who are you? Why, do you bring your unholy slaves to feast on the remains of "
"our fallen?!"
msgstr ""
"¿Quiénes son ustedes? ¿Por qué traen a sus impíos esclavos a alimentarse de "
"nuestros restos caídos?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:407
msgid ""
"We are sworn allies of the peoples of the Far North, and the undead support "
"us against our enemies."
msgstr ""
"Somos aliados jurados de los pueblos del Lejano Norte, y los no-muertos nos "
"apoyan contra nuestros enemigos."

#. [message]: type=Footpad
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:413
msgid "It is... it is the Lady of Light! I had heard rumors but this is..."
msgstr "¡Es... es la Dama de la Luz! Había escuchado rumores, pero esto es..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:418
msgid ""
"This fortress barely stands. What vile creatures have come to plague the "
"northern country?"
msgstr ""
"Esta fortaleza apenas se mantiene en pie. ¿Qué viles criaturas han venido a "
"asolar el norte?"

#. [message]: type=Bowman
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:424
msgid ""
"The elves, my lady. The elves have gone mad and are attacking each other, "
"laying waste to every settlement in their path. Neither faction is willing "
"to seek a peaceful end to this conflict, and we don’t think we can withstand "
"their siege for much longer. Most of our men have died defending the city "
"walls, and resources are increasingly scarce."
msgstr ""
"Los elfos, mi señora. Los elfos se han vuelto locos y se atacan entre sí, "
"arrasando cada asentamiento en su camino. Ninguna facción está dispuesta a "
"buscar un final pacífico para este conflicto, y no creemos que podamos "
"soportar su asedio por mucho tiempo. La mayoría de nuestros hombres han "
"muerto defendiendo los muros de la ciudad y los recursos son cada vez más "
"escasos."

#. [message]: type=Bowman
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:450
msgid ""
"We cannot continue without help, and the messengers we sent to the Grand "
"Council for reinforcements have not returned yet. I’ll probably hate myself "
"for the rest of my life for asking help from those who deal with dark magic, "
"but..."
msgstr ""
"No podemos continuar sin ayuda, y los mensajeros que enviamos al Gran "
"Consejo para pedir refuerzos aún no han regresado. Probablemente me odiaré "
"el resto de mi vida por pedir ayuda a quienes tratan con magia oscura, "
"pero..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:456
msgid "Pfft, we cannot waste our time here."
msgstr "Pfft, no podemos perder nuestro tiempo aquí."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:465
msgid ""
"We must help these poor people and try to negotiate a deal with our kinsmen. "
"We must not allow another civil war to tear our civilization apart! "
"Otherwise..."
msgstr ""
"Debemos ayudar a esta pobre gente e intentar negociar un acuerdo con "
"nuestros parientes. ¡No podemos permitir que otra guerra civil destroce "
"nuestra civilización! De lo contrario..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:470
msgid "Our sacrifices would have been in vain."
msgstr "Nuestros sacrificios habrán sido en vano."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:475
msgid "We’ll help you defend your fortress until those reinforcements arrive."
msgstr ""
"Los ayudaremos a defender su fortaleza hasta que lleguen esos refuerzos."

#. [message]: type=Bowman
#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:481
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/07x_Resolutions.cfg:176
msgid "Thank you."
msgstr "Gracias."

#. [message]: type=Footpad
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:496
msgid "Lead us, my lord."
msgstr "Guíanos, mi señor."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:563
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:542
msgid ""
"Resist until the Grand Council’s reinforcements arrive at the end of turns"
msgstr ""
"Resiste hasta que los refuerzos del Gran Consejo lleguen al final de los "
"turnos"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:572
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:550
msgid "You will not be able to recall the human defense in later scenarios"
msgstr ""
"No podrás recordar a las unidades humanas de defensa en escenarios "
"posteriores"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:565
msgid "Death of an enemy leader"
msgstr "Muerte de un líder enemigo"

#. [message]: speaker=Unidë
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:587
msgid ""
"Who is it that helps the human sub-people defend their town against the true "
"rulers of the forest?"
msgstr ""
"¿Quién es el que ayuda a los subhumanos a defender su ciudad contra los "
"verdaderos señores del bosque?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:592
msgid ""
"I am Galas, an elf of the Valley of Elynia like you. What is the reason for "
"this unnecessary bloodshed?"
msgstr ""
"Soy Galas, un elfo del Valle de Elynia como tú. ¿Cuál es la razón de este "
"derramamiento de sangre innecesario?"

#. [message]: speaker=Unidë
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:597
msgid ""
"We are at war with those who have taken the life of Lord Inodien and his "
"successor! Are you supporters of their foul cause too?"
msgstr ""
"Estamos en guerra con aquellos que han quitado la vida al Lord Inodien y a "
"su sucesor. ¿También apoyan su causa vil?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:602
msgid ""
"You know me well, Unidë — I would not support anyone, elf or otherwise, who "
"would threaten the life of our leaders and our civilization. However, you "
"are not doing any good by murdering innocent humans and elves."
msgstr ""
"Me conoces bien, Unidë; no apoyaría a nadie, elfo o no, que amenazara la "
"vida de nuestros líderes y nuestra civilización. Sin embargo, no haces "
"ningún bien asesinando a humanos y elfos inocentes."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:607
msgid ""
"There must be a way to solve this problem without resorting to fighting. In "
"these grim times, with war already raging in the outer lands, the last thing "
"we need is conflict between ourselves as well. It will be our definitive "
"doom. The traitors must be judged by elvish law, not by chaos and death."
msgstr ""
"Debe haber una forma de resolver este problema sin recurrir a la lucha. En "
"estos tiempos sombríos, con la guerra ya asolando las tierras exteriores, lo "
"último que necesitamos es un conflicto entre nosotros mismos. Eso sería "
"nuestra perdición definitiva. Los traidores deben ser juzgados por la ley "
"élfica, no por el caos y la muerte."

#. [message]: speaker=Unidë
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:612
msgid ""
"Who do you think you are to give me orders? I am in charge of our people "
"now, and I do not listen to those who ally themselves with this worthless "
"human scum and their foul dark sorcerers."
msgstr ""
"¿Quién te crees para darme órdenes? Ahora estoy a cargo de nuestro pueblo, y "
"no escucho a quienes se alían con esta despreciable escoria humana y sus "
"viles hechiceros oscuros."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:617
msgid ""
"Diplomacy isn’t going to work, of course — this petty elf has a death wish."
msgstr ""
"La diplomacia no va a funcionar, por supuesto; este mezquino elfo tiene un "
"deseo de muerte."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:622
msgid ""
"Avoid killing their leaders at all costs. If we want to solve this conflict, "
"we’ll need the Grand Council to negotiate with the faction leaders, and "
"without them, I fear that their successors may incite an even worse "
"bloodshed. I only wish we could stop our kinsmen without resorting to "
"violence."
msgstr ""
"Eviten matar a sus líderes a toda costa. Si queremos resolver este "
"conflicto, necesitaremos que el Gran Consejo negocie con los líderes de las "
"facciones, y sin ellos, temo que sus sucesores puedan incitar un "
"derramamiento de sangre aún peor. Ojalá pudiéramos detener a nuestros "
"parientes sin recurrir a la violencia."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:627
msgid ""
"As it seems now, there is no other option for us than to hold out against "
"their troops until help arrives. To arms!"
msgstr ""
"Tal como parece ahora, no nos queda otra opción que resistir contra sus "
"tropas hasta que llegue la ayuda. ¡A las armas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Unidë
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:642
msgid ""
"Though our enemies will not die by my hand, my brethren will avenge me! May "
"this be the last day the traitors live to see the light of Naia and Sela!"
msgstr ""
"Aunque mis enemigos no mueran por mi mano, ¡mis hermanos me vengarán! ¡Que "
"este sea el último día que los traidores vean la luz de Naia y Sela!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:654
msgid ""
"We shouldn’t have allowed her to die. Now it will be nigh impossible to put "
"an end to this!"
msgstr ""
"No deberíamos haber permitido que muriera. ¡Ahora será casi imposible poner "
"fin a esto!"

#. [message]: speaker=Celán
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:668
msgid "Alas, I have fallen before putting an end to this conflict."
msgstr "Ay, he caído antes de poner fin a este conflicto."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:680
msgid ""
"We shouldn’t have allowed him to die. Now it will be nigh impossible to put "
"an end to this!"
msgstr ""
"No deberíamos haber permitido que muriera. ¡Ahora será casi imposible poner "
"fin a esto!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:703
msgid "I die... for our people!"
msgstr "Muero... por nuestro pueblo."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:724
msgid "Ahh, great. Now we are killing other elves."
msgstr "Ahh, genial. Ahora estamos matando a otros elfos."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:736
msgid ""
"The situation is not improving. If those reinforcements don’t arrive soon we "
"won’t be able to hold this place for much longer!"
msgstr ""
"La situación no mejora. ¡Si esos refuerzos no llegan pronto, no podremos "
"mantener este lugar por mucho más tiempo!"

#. [unit]: type=Orcish Slurbow, id=Kar-velgan
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:785
msgid "Kar-velgan"
msgstr "Kar-velgan"

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:810
msgid ""
"Elves, stop this brutal bloodshed! You have slaughtered many innocent "
"northerners; humans, orcs, and elves alike. This dreadful display breaches "
"the treaty we signed with Lord Galas!"
msgstr ""
"¡Elfos, detengan este derramamiento de sangre brutal! Han masacrado a muchos "
"inocentes del norte: humanos, orcos y elfos por igual. ¡Esta terrible "
"muestra rompe el tratado que firmamos con el Lord Galas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Unidë
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:815
msgid "We do not listen to human sub-people!"
msgstr "¡No escuchamos a los subhumanos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:820
msgid ""
"Then you shall listen to your own authorities. I came as soon as I could to "
"bring order to this chaos. You have not only disobeyed the will of your "
"former leader, Lord Galas; you also ignored the advice and command of "
"Elynia, the Lady of Light herself."
msgstr ""
"Entonces escucharás a tus propias autoridades. Vine tan pronto como pude "
"para traer orden a este caos. No solo has desobedecido la voluntad de tu "
"antiguo líder, el Lord Galas; también has ignorado el consejo y la orden de "
"Elynia, la propia Dama de la Luz."

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:825
msgid ""
"In light of these events and the terms of the treaty, the Grand Council has "
"decided to banish the elvish kind from the northern country. You shall put "
"an end to your civil war and prepare to leave our territory before five days "
"have passed, or we shall order our own troops to deal with you. We do not "
"want to do this, and you are well aware that you are at a numerical "
"disadvantage."
msgstr ""
"A la luz de estos acontecimientos y los términos del tratado, el Gran "
"Consejo ha decidido desterrar a la raza élfica del norte del país. Pondrán "
"fin a su guerra civil y se prepararán para abandonar nuestro territorio "
"antes de que pasen cinco días, o ordenaremos a nuestras propias tropas "
"encargarse de ustedes. No queremos hacer esto, y ustedes son muy conscientes "
"de que están en desventaja numérica."

#. [message]: speaker=Celán
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:834
msgid ""
"Did one of your kind kill the puny ‘lord’ of these rebels as part of a ruse "
"to banish us from the forests, then?"
msgstr ""
"¿Acaso uno de los tuyos mató al enclenque ‘lord’ de estos rebeldes como "
"parte de un ardid para desterrarnos de los bosques?"

#. [message]: speaker=Kar-velgan
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:839
msgid "Listen, wose-born scum: Inodien was slain by no elf, human or orc!"
msgstr ""
"Escucha, escoria nacida de los woses: ¡Inodien no fue asesinado por ningún "
"elfo, humano u orco!"

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:848
msgid ""
"We have good reasons to think that the Chaos Empire sent forth their "
"mercenaries for the purpose of causing this revolt and sending us all to our "
"doom. But we are not letting that happen, at least not today."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos buenas razones para pensar que el Imperio del Caos envió a sus "
"mercenarios con el propósito de causar esta revuelta y condenarnos a todos. "
"Pero no vamos a permitir que eso suceda, al menos no hoy."

#. [message]: speaker=Unidë
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:853
msgid "This is not fair! Why should we pay for crimes committed by outsiders?"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto no es justo! ¿Por qué deberíamos pagar por crímenes cometidos por "
"forasteros?"

#. [message]: speaker=Kar-velgan
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:858
msgid ""
"Your hands are not clean, elf! How do you even dare to ignore that fact in "
"front of the bearers of the law?"
msgstr ""
"¡Tus manos no están limpias, elfo! ¿Cómo te atreves siquiera a ignorar ese "
"hecho frente a los portadores de la ley?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:867
msgid ""
"It is true. We have spilled much elvish blood with this fight. Galas and I "
"shall leave these lands as soon as we can."
msgstr ""
"Es cierto. Hemos derramado mucha sangre élfica con esta lucha. Galas y yo "
"abandonaremos estas tierras tan pronto como podamos."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:872
msgid "But my lady, how? None of this is your fault..."
msgstr "Pero mi señora, ¿cómo? Nada de esto es culpa suya..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:877
msgid "What? And how are we going to travel to Zocthanol Isle then?"
msgstr "¿Qué? ¿Y cómo vamos a viajar a la Isla Zocthanol entonces?"

#. [message]: speaker=Unidë
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:882
msgid ""
"I swear that my people will never forget this, the most vile of treacheries. "
"I shall withdraw my troops and my people from this accursed country today, "
"but I do intend to return some day to demand proper justice!"
msgstr ""
"Juro que mi pueblo nunca olvidará esta, la más vil de las traiciones. "
"Retiraré mis tropas y a mi gente de este país maldito hoy mismo, pero tengo "
"la intención de volver algún día para exigir justicia adecuada."

#. [message]: speaker=Celán
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:887
msgid ""
"If the Lady of Light is willing to depart from these lands to never return "
"because of our own misdeeds, then we shall abandon the country as well. Come "
"with me, men!"
msgstr ""
"Si la Dama de la Luz está dispuesta a abandonar estas tierras para no volver "
"jamás debido a nuestras propias fechorías, entonces nosotros también "
"abandonaremos el país. ¡Venid conmigo, hombres!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:900
msgid "Elynia? Can you tell us your plan?"
msgstr "Elynia, ¿puedes contarnos tu plan?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:905
msgid ""
"There is a port to the west in the Bay of Tirigaz. It’s controlled by orcs, "
"but perhaps we can find a way to bribe them so they lend us ships and "
"provisions. It is the only port that doesn’t belong to the Aragwaithi "
"nowadays."
msgstr ""
"Hay un puerto al oeste en la Bahía de Tirigaz. Está controlado por orcos, "
"pero quizás podamos encontrar la manera de sobornarlos para que nos presten "
"barcos y provisiones. Es el único puerto que hoy en día no pertenece a los "
"Aragwaithi."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#. Here Mal Keshar is supposed to be about to say something like "this is ridiculous" or such.
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:912
msgid ""
"This is— Pah. We shall go to Tirigaz, then. But how will we determine the "
"location of Zocthanol Isle?"
msgstr ""
"Esto es... Bah. Iremos a Tirigaz, entonces. Pero ¿cómo determinaremos la "
"ubicación de la Isla Zocthanol?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:917
msgid "That will be my job to do."
msgstr "Ese será mi trabajo."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:927
msgid "Then... I suppose this is where it ends."
msgstr "Entonces... Supongo que aquí es donde termina."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:932
msgid ""
"Are you really sure about this, Igor? I thought you would prefer to live "
"among your people in the west instead."
msgstr ""
"¿Estás realmente seguro de esto, Igor? Pensé que preferirías vivir entre los "
"tuyos en el oeste."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:937
msgid ""
"I mean, yes, being with goblins is great! But I’m scared after what happened "
"— you know, the whole Chaos thing? And it seems like the orc chieftains are "
"still bad at guarding the land from invaders from the south. No, I think I’m "
"done being village goblin. I’m gonna become city goblin now!"
msgstr ""
"Quiero decir, sí, ¡estar con los goblins es genial! Pero estoy asustado "
"después de lo que pasó —ya sabes, todo eso del Caos—. Y parece que los "
"caudillos orcos siguen siendo malos para proteger la tierra de los invasores "
"del sur. No, creo que ya terminé de ser un goblin de aldea. ¡Ahora me voy a "
"convertir en goblin de ciudad!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:942
msgid ""
"Hmph. How would a filthy runt like you survive the perils of civilization, I "
"wonder."
msgstr ""
"Hmph. Me pregunto cómo un mocoso sucio como tú podría sobrevivir a los "
"peligros de la civilización."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:947
msgid "Hey, I can do artsy stuff! Haven’t you heard me sing before? Ahem—"
msgstr ""
"¡Oye, puedo hacer cosas artísticas! ¿No me has oído cantar antes? Ejem—"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:952
msgid "If I have to listen to that again, I swear to the Dark Gods—"
msgstr "Si tengo que escuchar eso otra vez, lo juro por los Dioses Oscuros—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:957
msgid ""
"It has been a long journey for you, and we certainly cannot force you to "
"stick around considering all the dangers that await us next. I just hope we "
"will get to see each other again some day. I think I speak for all three of "
"us when I say we are deeply grateful for your help and support, even through "
"the most nightmarish of circumstances."
msgstr ""
"Ha sido un largo viaje para ti, y ciertamente no podemos obligarte a "
"quedarte considerando todos los peligros que nos aguardan ahora. Solo espero "
"que podamos volver a vernos algún día. Creo que hablo por los tres cuando "
"digo que estamos profundamente agradecidos por tu ayuda y apoyo, incluso en "
"las circunstancias más pesadillescas."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:962
msgid "We will miss you greatly. Best of luck, my friend."
msgstr "Te echaremos mucho de menos. Buena suerte, amigo mío."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:967
msgid "Awww, you guys, I’m tearing up... I will miss you too!"
msgstr ""
"Awww, chicos, se me están llenando los ojos de lágrimas... ¡Yo también los "
"voy a extrañar!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/03_Civil_War.cfg:972
msgid "Can we just... please. Let us move on already."
msgstr "¿Podemos simplemente... por favor? Sigamos adelante de una vez."

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/storytxt.cfg:113
msgid "Terror at Dusk"
msgstr "Terror al Anochecer"

#. [side]: id=Darglen, type=Chaos Lorekeeper
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:128
msgid "Darglen"
msgstr "Darglen"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:190
msgid "That is the sound of those blasted creatures!"
msgstr "¡Ese es el sonido de esas malditas criaturas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:199
msgid ""
"Um... that’s unusual. Could they be behind the death of Inodien? But then..."
msgstr ""
"Mmm... eso es extraño. ¿Podrían estar detrás de la muerte de Inodien? Pero "
"entonces..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:204
msgid "... The Chaos Empire must not be in disarray as we thought."
msgstr ""
"... El Imperio del Caos no debe de estar tan desorganizado como pensábamos."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:209
msgid ""
"They shall pay for the senseless destruction and bloodshed they caused. Let "
"us get rid of them before they bring more strife to this country!"
msgstr ""
"Pagarán por la destrucción sin sentido y la masacre que causaron. ¡Acabemos "
"con ellos antes de que traigan más conflictos a este país!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:224
msgid ""
"Don’t die yet, vermin! We want some answers before crushing your useless "
"skull against the rocks!"
msgstr ""
"¡No mueras aún, sabandija! Queremos algunas respuestas antes de aplastar tu "
"inútil cráneo contra las rocas."

#. [message]: speaker=Darglen
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:229
msgid ""
"... And do you really believe I would speak? Heh... you can torture me as "
"much as you want, but you won’t get anything from me!"
msgstr ""
"... ¿Y de verdad crees que hablaré? Heh... puedes torturarme cuanto quieras, "
"pero no obtendrás nada de mí."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:234
msgid "Stupid..."
msgstr "Estúpido..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:239
msgid "Let him."
msgstr "Déjalo."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:255
msgid ""
"That bastard... Hekuba... He and the Iron Triad must be behind this. But "
"what are they trying to accomplish?"
msgstr ""
"Ese bastardo... Hekuba... Él y la Tríada de Hierro deben estar detrás de "
"esto. Pero ¿qué intentan lograr?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:260
msgid ""
"They want to take revenge on us and our kind after Argan’s death, of course. "
"It seems that as long as their cult exists, so will the Chaos Empire."
msgstr ""
"Quieren vengarse de nosotros y de los nuestros tras la muerte de Argan, por "
"supuesto. Parece que mientras su culto exista, también lo hará el Imperio "
"del Caos."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:279
msgid ""
"This was the last one, and it doesn’t seem like there are any more groups "
"coming here."
msgstr ""
"Ese fue el último, y no parece que haya más grupos viniendo hacia aquí."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:284
msgid ""
"Let’s not worry a lot about them. These pathetic weaklings are nothing "
"compared to the hordes we fought before."
msgstr ""
"No nos preocupemos demasiado por ellos. Estos patéticos débiles no son nada "
"comparados con las hordas que enfrentamos antes."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:289
msgid "Let’s proceed to Tirigaz now, quickly."
msgstr "Vayamos a Tirigaz ahora, rápido."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:294
msgid ""
"Why don’t we go after their leaders and put an end to this stupid war "
"<i>now</i>?"
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué no vamos tras sus líderes y ponemos fin a esta estúpida guerra "
"<i>ahora</i>?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:299
msgid ""
"No... That would be a highly reckless choice. We don’t know what kind of "
"enemies we might be facing other than Mal Hekuba — you have not forgotten "
"our last encounter with him, have you? We are at a disadvantage without more "
"information about them — their leaders, their weapons, their plans. This is "
"why we must find Zocthanol first."
msgstr ""
"No... Eso sería una decisión sumamente imprudente. No sabemos qué tipo de "
"enemigos podríamos enfrentar aparte de Mal Hekuba — no has olvidado nuestro "
"último encuentro con él, ¿verdad? Estamos en desventaja sin más información "
"sobre ellos: sus líderes, sus armas, sus planes. Por eso debemos encontrar "
"primero a Zocthanol."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:304
msgid "<i>(sighs)</i> Very well, then."
msgstr "<i>(suspira)</i> Muy bien, entonces."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:313
msgid ""
"We have wasted far too much time dealing with these pests. Look! A large "
"swarm is approaching from the south!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos perdido demasiado tiempo ocupándonos de estas plagas. ¡Mira! ¡Un "
"enorme enjambre se acerca desde el sur!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/04_Terror_at_Dusk.cfg:318
msgid "Indeed. This... this was not a very prudent idea."
msgstr "Ciertamente. Esto... esto no fue una idea muy prudente."

