"posteriores"

#. [value]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:541
msgid "170 gold! It seems it was a trading ship!"
msgstr "¡170 de oro! Parece que era un barco mercante."

#. [value]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:542
msgid "You retrieve 170 pieces of gold."
msgstr "Recoges 170 piezas de oro."

#. [value]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:546
msgid "Bah, only 25 pieces of gold. Better than nothing, I guess."
msgstr "Bah, solo 25 piezas de oro. Mejor que nada, supongo."

#. [value]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:547
msgid "You retrieve 25 pieces of gold."
msgstr "Recoges 25 piezas de oro."

#. [value]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:551
msgid "Two pieces of gold? Damn, this must be a joke!"
msgstr "¿Dos piezas de oro? ¡Maldita sea, esto debe ser una broma!"

#. [value]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:552
msgid "You retrieve two pieces of gold."
msgstr "Recoges dos piezas de oro."

#. [value]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:556
msgid "Well, well, 50 pieces of gold can be put to good use!"
msgstr "Vaya, vaya, 50 piezas de oro pueden ser útiles."

#. [value]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:557
msgid "You retrieve 50 pieces of gold."
msgstr "Recoges 50 piezas de oro."

#. [message]: speaker=Ishkaal
#. The pointy-eared demons here are the elves.
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:646
msgid ""
"You filthy soft-skinned beasts, this is your last opportunity to return our "
"swamps! We are not planning to retreat to the forests of the pointy-eared "
"demons!"
msgstr ""
"¡Asquerosas bestias de piel blanda, esta es su última oportunidad de "
"devolvernos nuestros pantanos! ¡No planeamos retirarnos a los bosques de los "
"demonios orejudos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Tan-Vatar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:651
msgid ""
"We care nothing for your stupid conflicts on the eastern borders. You "
"trespassed our frontiers and broke our treaty, and now you ask from us the "
"very lands you took by force; after raiding our southern garrison, no less! "
"If you believe we will accede now—"
msgstr ""
"No nos importan sus estúpidos conflictos en las fronteras del este. Ustedes "
"cruzaron nuestras fronteras y rompieron nuestro tratado, y ahora nos piden "
"las mismas tierras que tomaron por la fuerza; ¡después de saquear nuestra "
"guarnición del sur, nada menos! Si creen que vamos a ceder ahora—"

#. [message]: speaker=Ishkaal
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:656
msgid ""
"To the Dark Gods with you and your treaty! The words of an orc are no more "
"meaningful than his fetid breath! Maybe you’ll admit your defeat once we "
"have razed every single one of your precious buildings to the ground. Go "
"ahead, Rishix! Teach them a lesson!"
msgstr ""
"¡Al demonio tú y tu tratado! ¡Las palabras de un orco no valen más que su "
"aliento fétido! Quizás admitas tu derrota cuando hayamos arrasado hasta el "
"último de tus preciados edificios. ¡Vamos, Rishix! ¡Enséñales una lección!"

#. [message]: speaker=Rishix
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:661
msgid "We’ll make these puny dirt-dwellers rue the day they were born!"
msgstr ""
"¡Haremos que estos insignificantes habitantes del fango se arrepientan del "
"día en que nacieron!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:718
msgid "That city to the northwest... is it the port of Tirigaz?"
msgstr "Esa ciudad al noroeste... ¿es el puerto de Tirigaz?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:723
msgid ""
"Yes... it wasn’t so well fortified during my time. So many things have "
"changed since then."
msgstr ""
"Sí... no estaba tan bien fortificado en mi tiempo. Han cambiado muchas cosas "
"desde entonces."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#. "Is that smoke I smell?"
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:729
msgid "Is that smoke I— Wait, I hear steps..."
msgstr "¿Es ese humo que—? Espera, escucho pasos..."

#. [unit]: type=Orcish Crossbowman, id=Vuruk
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:746
msgid "Vuruk"
msgstr "Vuruk"

#. [message]: speaker=Vuruk
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:763
msgid "Hello, strangers! Are you loyal to the Grand Council?"
msgstr "¡Hola, forasteros! ¿Son leales al Gran Consejo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:768
msgid "Ehm..."
msgstr "Ehm..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:773
msgid "Yes, we are."
msgstr "Sí, lo somos."

#. [message]: speaker=Vuruk
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:778
msgid ""
"Those vile saurians hold the port of Tirigaz under siege, leaving me unable "
"to reach the city to deliver some important news to our lord. I think I "
"speak for all of us when I say that your help would be very appreciated. I "
"need to get to the city keep, but the journey across isn’t safe while those "
"vermin roam about our lands!"
msgstr ""
"Esos viles saurios mantienen el puerto de Tirigaz bajo asedio, y no puedo "
"llegar a la ciudad para entregar noticias importantes a nuestro señor. Creo "
"hablar por todos cuando digo que su ayuda sería muy apreciada. Debo llegar "
"al castillo de la ciudad, pero el trayecto no es seguro mientras esas "
"alimañas merodean por nuestras tierras."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:783
msgid "The enemies of our friends are our enemies. We can help you."
msgstr ""
"Los enemigos de nuestros amigos son nuestros enemigos. Podemos ayudarte."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:788
msgid ""
"(<i>whispering</i>) I am curious about their motives... Don’t you think your "
"trust in the orcs could be misplaced?"
msgstr ""
"(<i>susurrando</i>) Me intrigan sus motivos... ¿No crees que tu confianza en "
"los orcos podría estar mal puesta?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:793
msgid ""
"We must stop and repel those saurians before they take over Tirigaz or the "
"northern town that provides resources to the port."
msgstr ""
"Debemos detener y rechazar a esos saurios antes de que se apoderen de "
"Tirigaz o de la ciudad del norte que suministra recursos al puerto."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:804
msgid "Vuruk, what is it that you need to report to the lord of Tirigaz?"
msgstr "Vuruk, ¿qué es eso que debes informar al señor de Tirigaz?"

#. [message]: speaker=Vuruk
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:809
msgid ""
"Hmm... I fear it is nothing I’m allowed to share with anyone but Lord Tan-"
"Vatar and his trusted commanders, at least not at this time."
msgstr ""
"Hmm... Me temo que no es nada que pueda compartir con nadie excepto con Lord "
"Tan-Vatar y sus comandantes de confianza, al menos no por ahora."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#. [message]: speaker=Irylean
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:814
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08B_Destiny_part_1.cfg:371
msgid "Fair enough."
msgstr "Está bien."

#. [message]: speaker=Ishkaal
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:830
msgid "Come in aid of your kin, friends from the deep sea!"
msgstr "¡Acudan en ayuda de sus parientes, amigos del mar profundo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:880
msgid ""
"Ah, ha, ha, hah! They have the support of some wild creatures from the "
"ocean! Nothing we cannot handle."
msgstr ""
"¡Ah, ja, ja, ja! ¡Tienen el apoyo de unas criaturas salvajes del océano! "
"Nada que no podamos manejar."

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:944
msgid "Where did all these damned creatures come from?"
msgstr "¿De dónde salieron todas estas malditas criaturas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Ishkaal
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:953
msgid "This is turning out to be much harder than we expected..."
msgstr "Esto está resultando ser mucho más difícil de lo que esperábamos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Vuruk
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1025
msgid ""
"Arthol is being ransacked by the saurians! Now there’s no hope for Tirigaz!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los saurios están saqueando Arthol! ¡Ahora no hay esperanza para Tirigaz!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1046
msgid ""
"Tirigaz has been captured! Our mission has failed, and we won’t be able to "
"reach Zocthanol now!"
msgstr ""
"¡Tirigaz ha sido capturada! Nuestra misión ha fracasado, y ahora no podremos "
"llegar a Zocthanol."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1075
msgid "No! I’ve got to... uuugh..."
msgstr "¡No! Tengo que... uuugh..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1087
msgid ""
"We let the orcish messenger perish on the battlefield! The lord of Tirigaz "
"is not going to like this..."
msgstr ""
"¡Dejamos que el mensajero orco pereciera en el campo de batalla! Al señor de "
"Tirigaz no le va a gustar esto..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1102
msgid "The treacherous ones cannot win! Eeaack..."
msgstr "¡Los traicioneros no pueden ganar! Eeaack..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1126
msgid "Damn you, dirt-dwellers!"
msgstr "¡Malditos sean, habitantes del fango!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1151
msgid ""
"I have been struck down by the damned minions of a lich! This is not fair!"
msgstr ""
"¡He sido abatido por los malditos esbirros de un liche! ¡Esto no es justo!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1170
msgid ""
"Accursed lich! May the Dark Gods smite you down for this atrocity— Eaugh!!!"
msgstr ""
"¡Liche maldito! Que los Dioses Oscuros te destruyan por esta atrocidad— "
"¡Eaugh!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ishkaal
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1189
msgid "Noooooo! You’ll suffer for this atrocity!"
msgstr "¡Noooooo! ¡Pagarán por esta atrocidad!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1209
msgid "Ha, ha, ha! Die, fool!"
msgstr "¡Ja, ja, ja! ¡Muere, necio!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1214
msgid "No! The city will fall... without my leadership... *ack*"
msgstr "¡No! La ciudad caerá... sin mi liderazgo... *ack*"

#. [message]: speaker=Ishkaal
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1219
msgid "Take that, orcish scum! Your leader is dead now, and your city is ours!"
msgstr ""
"¡Tomen eso, escoria orca! Su líder está muerto, y su ciudad es nuestra."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1231
msgid ""
"The commander of the defense of Tirigaz has been slain! The city won’t "
"resist for much longer now..."
msgstr ""
"¡El comandante de la defensa de Tirigaz ha caído! La ciudad no resistirá por "
"mucho más tiempo..."

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1253
msgid "Don’t get any closer to our villages, you vermin!"
msgstr "¡No se acerquen más a nuestras aldeas, alimañas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ishkaal
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1258
msgid "Crush their villages into the ground!"
msgstr "¡Aplasten sus aldeas hasta los cimientos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1292
msgid ""
"These villages belong to the lord of Tirigaz! We must protect them, not "
"capture them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Estas aldeas pertenecen al señor de Tirigaz! Debemos protegerlas, no "
"capturarlas."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1311
msgid ""
"The fountain’s water is overflowing with an unusual energy.\n"
"\n"
"You catch a glimpse of a strange-looking faerie observing you from behind a "
"nearby tree, but by the time you approach it she has seemingly vanished. In "
"the hurry to return to the fray you almost slip on a puddle."
msgstr ""
"El agua de la fuente rebosa con una energía inusual.\n"
"\n"
"Alcanzas a ver a un hada de aspecto extraño que te observa detrás de un "
"árbol cercano, pero cuando te acercas parece haberse desvanecido. En la "
"prisa por volver a la refriega casi resbalas en un charco."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1322
msgid "The fountain’s water continues to overflow with an unusual energy."
msgstr "El agua de la fuente sigue rebosando con una energía inusual."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1346
msgid "(<i>jumps in</i>) Wheeeeeeee!!!"
msgstr "(<i>salta dentro</i>) ¡Wheeeeeeee!"

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1397
msgid "Shimmering Fountain"
msgstr "Fuente Resplandeciente"

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1400
msgid ""
"The Naiad’s spell blesses anyone who takes a swim in the water of this "
"fountain with newfound vim and courage."
msgstr ""
"El hechizo de la Náyade bendice a cualquiera que se bañe en las aguas de "
"esta fuente con renovado vigor y valentía."

#. [unit]: type=Orcish Warrior, id=Vitork
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1427
msgid "Vitork"
msgstr "Vitork"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1438
msgid "Yes! We did it!"
msgstr "¡Sí! ¡Lo logramos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Tan-Vatar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1443
msgid ""
"This is an important battle you’ve helped us win, travelers. The city of "
"Tirigaz shall be eternally thankful for your assistance."
msgstr ""
"Esta es una batalla importante que nos han ayudado a ganar, viajeros. La "
"ciudad de Tirigaz les estará eternamente agradecida por su ayuda."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1448
msgid ""
"It is our duty to assist our allies in these times. However, I believe this "
"soldier has something to tell you..."
msgstr ""
"Es nuestro deber asistir a nuestros aliados en estos tiempos. Sin embargo, "
"creo que este soldado tiene algo que decirle..."

#. [message]: speaker=Vitork
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1453
msgid "Vuruk, brother, you made it! Did you discover anything new?"
msgstr "¡Vuruk, hermano, lo lograste! ¿Descubriste algo nuevo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Vuruk
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1458
msgid ""
"Ha, indeed! I need to talk with you about it later, but now I must report to "
"the chieftains."
msgstr ""
"¡Ja, en efecto! Necesito hablar contigo al respecto más tarde, pero ahora "
"debo informar a los jefes."

#. [message]: speaker=Tan-Vatar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1463
msgid ""
"I see you helped Vuruk return home safe and sound. Well done! So, what can "
"we do for you to repay our debt?"
msgstr ""
"Veo que ayudaron a Vuruk a regresar sano y salvo a casa. ¡Bien hecho! "
"Entonces, ¿qué podemos hacer para saldar nuestra deuda con ustedes?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1468
msgid ""
"Um, we are currently looking for transportation services. We must sail the "
"open ocean to find a certain island..."
msgstr ""
"Eh, actualmente estamos buscando servicios de transporte. Debemos navegar "
"por el océano abierto para encontrar cierta isla..."

#. [message]: speaker=Tan-Vatar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1473
msgid ""
"I mean no offense, but only fools would dare sail the <i>open ocean</i>! "
"Nobody has ventured into farther waters and returned in one piece, ever! "
"Nobody knows exactly what kind of creatures inhabit the Vast Sea! Nobody "
"knows for certain what lies beyond the horizon, but it surely can’t be good, "
"you see! Why would anyone want to travel so far into unknown waters, when "
"there are plenty of safer unexplored lands awaiting back whence you came?"
msgstr ""
"No quiero ofender, pero solo los necios se atreverían a navegar el <i>océano "
"abierto</i>. ¡Nadie se ha aventurado tan lejos y ha regresado entero, jamás! "
"Nadie sabe exactamente qué clase de criaturas habitan en el Mar Inmenso. "
"Nadie sabe con certeza qué hay más allá del horizonte, pero seguro que no es "
"nada bueno, ¿saben? ¿Por qué querría alguien viajar tan lejos por aguas "
"desconocidas, cuando hay muchas tierras inexploradas más seguras esperando "
"atrás, de donde vinieron?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1478
msgid ""
"We have a mission to complete, but much like Vuruk’s, it is not something we "
"should discuss with..."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos una misión que cumplir, pero al igual que la de Vuruk, no es algo "
"que debamos discutir con..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1483
msgid ""
"We know the location of a certain isle where some people who once lived on "
"the Great Continent went to. We need to gather some information from them — "
"as part of a mission for the Grand Council."
msgstr ""
"Conocemos la ubicación de cierta isla a la que fueron algunas personas que "
"una vez vivieron en el Gran Continente. Necesitamos reunir información de "
"ellos como parte de una misión para el Gran Consejo."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1488
msgid "Uh, huh."
msgstr "Ajá."

#. [message]: speaker=Tan-Vatar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/05_Bay_of_Tirigaz.cfg:1493
msgid ""
"The Grand Council? Why didn’t you say so in the first place! We’ll do "
"anything we can to help you in your mission. It’ll be difficult to gather an "
"appropriate crew for you, but at least I can give you one of our fastest "
"transport vessels."
msgstr ""
"¿El Gran Consejo? ¡Por qué no lo dijeron desde el principio! Haremos todo lo "
"posible para ayudarles en su misión. Será difícil reunir una tripulación "
"adecuada para ustedes, pero al menos puedo darles una de nuestras "
"embarcaciones de transporte más rápidas."

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/storytxt.cfg:146
msgid "Quenoth Isle"
msgstr "Isla Quenoth"

#. [side]
#. [side]: id=Gaellis, type=Quenoth Champion
#. [side]: id=Maina, type=Quenoth Sun Sylph
#. [side]: id=Inara, type=Quenoth Ranger, gender=female
#. [side]: id=Lintaen, type=Quenoth Hero
#. [side]: id=Listra, type=Quenoth Sun Singer
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:47
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_02_Elves_of_a_Different_Land.cfg:50
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_02_Elves_of_a_Different_Land.cfg:91
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_02_Elves_of_a_Different_Land.cfg:150
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_02_Elves_of_a_Different_Land.cfg:196
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_02_Elves_of_a_Different_Land.cfg:267
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/07x_Resolutions.cfg:45
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/07x_Resolutions.cfg:63
msgid "team_name^Quenoth"
msgstr "Quenoth"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:94
msgid ""
"This place appears to be abandoned... Are you sure this is the correct "
"island?"
msgstr ""
"Este lugar parece abandonado... ¿Estás segura de que esta es la isla "
"correcta?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:99
msgid ""
"Not completely... but it’s possible that the Quenoth elves just avoid these "
"shores for some reason."
msgstr ""
"No completamente... pero es posible que los elfos quenoth eviten estas "
"costas por alguna razón."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:104
msgid "Let’s explore and try to find them, then."
msgstr "Entonces exploremos e intentemos encontrarlos."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:242
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/06_Divergence.cfg:1333
msgid "Time passes..."
msgstr "El tiempo pasa..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:274
msgid ""
"Maybe we should return to the ship. I’m not really sure about going into the "
"forest at night, it could be dangerous."
msgstr ""
"Quizás deberíamos regresar al barco. No estoy del todo segura de adentrarnos "
"en el bosque de noche, podría ser peligroso."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:279
msgid "Why are you hesitating now?"
msgstr "¿Por qué dudas ahora?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:286
msgid ""
"Do you remember when we almost lost you in the caves beneath Wesmere? I "
"don’t want to risk that occurring again. We don’t know why we haven’t found "
"any elves here and..."
msgstr ""
"¿Recuerdas cuando casi te perdimos en las cavernas bajo Wesmere? No quiero "
"arriesgarme a que eso ocurra de nuevo. No sabemos por qué no hemos "
"encontrado ningún elfo aquí y..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:297
msgid "Is there something you haven’t told me?"
msgstr "¿Hay algo que no me has contado?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:302
msgid "Galas, I—"
msgstr "Galas, yo—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:313
#, fuzzy
msgid "I hear movement among the trees."
msgstr "Oigo algo moviéndose entre los árboles."

#. [event]: type=Quenoth Fighter, id=Nion, type=Quenoth Flanker, id=Valad, type=Quenoth Flanker, id=Hara, type=Quenoth Fighter, id=Yon, type=Quenoth Scout, id=Ladien
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:326
msgid "Nion"
msgstr "Nion"

#. [event]: type=Quenoth Fighter, id=Nion, type=Quenoth Flanker, id=Valad, type=Quenoth Flanker, id=Hara, type=Quenoth Fighter, id=Yon, type=Quenoth Scout, id=Ladien
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:338
msgid "Valad"
msgstr "Valad"

#. [event]: type=Quenoth Fighter, id=Nion, type=Quenoth Flanker, id=Valad, type=Quenoth Flanker, id=Hara, type=Quenoth Fighter, id=Yon, type=Quenoth Scout, id=Ladien
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:348
msgid "Hara"
msgstr "Hara"

#. [event]: type=Quenoth Fighter, id=Nion, type=Quenoth Flanker, id=Valad, type=Quenoth Flanker, id=Hara, type=Quenoth Fighter, id=Yon, type=Quenoth Scout, id=Ladien
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:366
msgid "Yon"
msgstr "Yon"

#. [event]: type=Quenoth Fighter, id=Nion, type=Quenoth Flanker, id=Valad, type=Quenoth Flanker, id=Hara, type=Quenoth Fighter, id=Yon, type=Quenoth Scout, id=Ladien
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:376
msgid "Ladien"
msgstr "Ladien"

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:390
msgid ""
"Who are you and where do you come from? You don’t seem to be of our kin."
msgstr "¿Quiénes son y de dónde vienen? No parecen ser de los nuestros."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:395
msgid ""
"We are elves! There’s no need to point at us with those arrows and swords, "
"either; we’re clearly at a disadvantage here."
msgstr ""
"¡Somos elfos! Y no hay necesidad de apuntarnos con esas flechas y espadas; "
"claramente estamos en desventaja aquí."

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:400
msgid ""
"You do not look or dress like our people. Is this some kind of joke? We are "
"pretty sure we’ve never seen your faces on this island."
msgstr ""
"No se ven ni visten como nuestro pueblo. ¿Es esto algún tipo de broma? "
"Estamos bastante seguros de que nunca hemos visto sus rostros en esta isla."

#. [message]: speaker=Hara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:405
msgid "They are probably impostors sent by Uria to destroy our home!"
msgstr ""
"¡Probablemente son impostores enviados por Uria para destruir nuestro hogar!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:410
msgid "Let us explain..."
msgstr "Déjennos explicar..."

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:415
msgid "Seize them!"
msgstr "¡Captúrenlos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:422
msgid "Stop!"
msgstr "¡Alto!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:437
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"(<i>spreading her wings</i>) How can you <b>not</b> recognize your kin, "
"young girl? Have the Quenoth elves truly forgotten their origins?"
msgstr ""
"(<i>desplegando sus alas</i>) ¿Cómo es posible que <b>no</b> reconozcas a "
"tus ancestros silvanos, jovencita? ¿Han olvidado por completo los elfos "
"quenoth su historia tras todo este tiempo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:448
msgid ""
"(<i>in a calm, sad tone</i>) When did you last see the essence of the forest "
"blazing in the dark?"
msgstr ""
"(<i>con un tono calmado y triste</i>) ¿Cuándo fue la última vez que vieron "
"la esencia del bosque ardiendo en la oscuridad?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:502
msgid ""
"Elynia held a small fire in her hands, illuminating the surroundings with a "
"strong, azure light. The elves stared in awe at her subtle but effective "
"display of the power of Faerie; some of them stepped back, alarmed, "
"uncertain of what to make of the unusual situation."
msgstr ""
"Elynia sostuvo una pequeña llama en sus manos, iluminando los alrededores "
"con una intensa luz azulada. Los elfos la miraron asombrados ante su sutil "
"pero efectivo despliegue del poder del mundo feérico; algunos retrocedieron, "
"alarmados y sin saber cómo reaccionar ante la inusual situación."

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/06_01_Quenoth_Isle.cfg:532
msgid "Come with me."
msgstr "Vengan conmigo."

