#. [side]: type=Chaos Lorekeeper, id=Grulock
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:75
msgid "Grulock"
msgstr "Grulock"

#. [side]: type=Chaos Razerman, id=Zygred
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:121
msgid "Zygred"
msgstr "Zygred"

#. [event]
#. [else]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:207
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:348
msgid "Move Elynia to the top edge of the map"
msgstr "Mueve a Elynia al borde superior del mapa"

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:237
msgid "She hasn’t wanted to talk to us for days. Is our destination...?"
msgstr "No ha querido hablarnos en días. ¿Nuestro destino es...?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:242
msgid ""
"Yes, I gather that her plan is still to strike at Wesmere before the "
"Northlanders have an opportunity to launch a proper offensive or even hear "
"of our situation. Damn, for all I know our messengers and their ship could "
"have been destroyed by the enemy already."
msgstr ""
"Sí, deduzco que su plan sigue siendo atacar Wesmere antes de que los "
"norteños tengan la oportunidad de lanzar una ofensiva adecuada o incluso de "
"enterarse de nuestra situación. Maldición, por lo que sé nuestros mensajeros "
"y su barco ya podrían haber sido destruidos por el enemigo."

#. [message]: speaker=Horo
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:247
msgid ""
"I heard that the Grand Council has been hesitant about pressing on this war "
"ever since your victory in the Empire’s so-called capital. They think "
"they’ve won already."
msgstr ""
"He oído que el Gran Consejo ha dudado en continuar con esta guerra desde tu "
"victoria en la supuesta capital del Imperio. Creen que ya han ganado."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:270
msgid "Is everyone ready for battle?"
msgstr "¿Todos están listos para la batalla?"

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:276
msgid "Er, battle?"
msgstr "¿Eh... batalla?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:281
msgid ""
"Our scouts didn’t go unnoticed, and they found a couple of well-armed enemy "
"outposts ahead. This will most certainly not be a safe journey across the "
"dry remains of Wesmere."
msgstr ""
"Nuestros exploradores no pasaron desapercibidos y encontraron un par de "
"puestos avanzados enemigos bien armados más adelante. Este sin duda no será "
"un viaje seguro a través de los restos secos de Wesmere."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:309
msgid ""
"Has it even occurred to you that our little struggle in their headquarters "
"on that accursed peninsula has put their forces in motion again to protect "
"what little remains of Yechnagoth?"
msgstr ""
"¿Acaso se te ha ocurrido que nuestra pequeña lucha en su cuartel general en "
"esa maldita península ha puesto de nuevo a sus fuerzas en movimiento para "
"proteger lo poco que queda de Yechnagoth?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:316
msgid ""
"Of course it has. But there’s no time to discuss this now. Let’s move out."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que sí. Pero no hay tiempo para discutir esto ahora. Movámonos."

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:327
msgid "These disgusting demons are vanquished at last!"
msgstr "¡Estos asquerosos demonios han sido finalmente derrotados!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:332
msgid ""
"Yes, but we must proceed quickly and cautiously to the northeast "
"nevertheless. More troops will come if we give them the opportunity to "
"regroup."
msgstr ""
"Sí, pero debemos avanzar rápidamente y con cautela hacia el noreste de todos "
"modos. Vendrán más tropas si les damos la oportunidad de reagruparse."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:376
msgid "Onwards we go, now!"
msgstr "¡Adelante, ahora mismo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:400
msgid "We cannot advance without securing our path first!"
msgstr "¡No podemos avanzar sin asegurar primero nuestro camino!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:414
msgid ""
"It’s still my opinion that we are running a large risk with your current "
"plan."
msgstr "Sigo opinando que estamos corriendo un gran riesgo con tu plan actual."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:419
msgid "Was it any better to not take risks at all in that fortress, though?"
msgstr "¿Pero fue mejor no arriesgarse nada en esa fortaleza?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:428
msgid ""
"I don’t know what you are trying to imply, but I may as well remind you that "
"I wasn’t the only one to hesitate and that <i>he</i> would not have survived "
"the attempt without his lower half like I did. It was <i>your</i> assigned "
"task to practice that spell beforehand and <i>you</i> failed to do so — "
"don’t involve me in <i>your</i> mistakes."
msgstr ""
"No sé qué intentas insinuar, pero también te recuerdo que no fui el único "
"que dudó y que <i>él</i> no habría sobrevivido al intento sin su parte "
"inferior como yo. Era <i>tu</i> tarea practicar ese hechizo antes y "
"<i>fallaste</i> en hacerlo — no me involucres en <i>tus</i> errores."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:433
msgid "<i>(glaring at Mal Keshar)</i> ..."
msgstr "<i>(mirando fijamente a Mal Keshar)</i> ..."

#. [message]: speaker=Horo
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/10_Tears.cfg:439
msgid "Pagh, let’s get on with this, everybody! We haven’t got much time!"
msgstr "¡Pagh, sigamos con esto, todos! ¡No tenemos mucho tiempo!"

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/storytxt.cfg:338
msgid "Ambush at the Gates"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Chaos Cataphract, id=Mendryr
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:100
msgid "Mendryr"
msgstr "Mendryr"

#. [side]: type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Haldaran
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:128
msgid "Haldaran"
msgstr "Haldaran"

#. [side]: type=Hell Guardian, id=Elgamal
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:144
msgid "team_name^Wesmere Defense"
msgstr "Defensa de Wesmere"

#. [side]: type=Hell Guardian, id=Elgamal
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:154
msgid "Elgamal"
msgstr "Elgamal"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:282
msgid ""
"Due to the Wesmere curse, the time of day is always chaotic during this "
"scenario"
msgstr ""
"Debido a la maldición de Wesmere, la hora del día siempre es caótica durante "
"este escenario"

#. [message]: speaker=Horo
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:291
msgid ""
"There’s an alarming amount of movement in the southern hills. It would seem "
"an entire battalion has been following our steps since we left Kalari "
"Peninsula."
msgstr ""
"Hay una cantidad alarmante de movimiento en las colinas del sur. Parece que "
"un batallón entero nos ha estado siguiendo desde que salimos de la Península "
"Kalari."

#. [message]: speaker=Mendryr
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:305
msgid ""
"The Council was right in their assessment of the situation. The elf witch "
"and the lich have amassed an army of orcs and undead mercenaries to raid "
"Fort Ænthal. It seems we arrived in the nick of time. To arms!"
msgstr ""
"El Consejo tenía razón en su evaluación de la situación. La bruja elfa y el "
"lich han reunido un ejército de orcos y mercenarios no-muertos para asaltar "
"el Fuerte Ænthal. Parece que llegamos justo a tiempo. ¡A las armas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Haldaran
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:310
msgid "To arms! For the Dark Lady!"
msgstr "¡A las armas! ¡Por la Dama Oscura!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:323
msgid ""
"I sort of expected that. It might prove tricky to advance with those "
"buffoons on our heels. On the other hand, the fortress ahead doesn’t seem to "
"be very well guarded."
msgstr ""
"Más o menos lo esperaba. Puede ser difícil avanzar con esos tontos "
"pisándonos los talones. Por otro lado, la fortaleza adelante no parece estar "
"muy bien protegida."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:328
msgid "Very well, then. Let’s take them down."
msgstr "Muy bien, entonces. Derribémoslos."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:333
msgid ""
"I do feel something is amiss, though. We should be cautious... especially "
"since our leader appears to be giving us commands without thinking things "
"through."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, siento que algo anda mal. Debemos ser cautelosos... "
"especialmente porque nuestro líder parece dar órdenes sin pensar bien las "
"cosas."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:338
msgid "If you think <i>you</i> could do a better job at leading the orcs..."
msgstr ""
"Si crees que <i>tú</i> podrías hacer un mejor trabajo liderando a los "
"orcos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:343
msgid ""
"It’s not my intention to have <i>anything</i> to do with them at all. I just "
"want to make sure you keep your feet on the ground — well, whenever that is "
"an appropriate thing to do, anyway."
msgstr ""
"No es mi intención tener <i>nada</i> que ver con ellos. Solo quiero "
"asegurarme de que mantengas los pies en la tierra — bueno, siempre que eso "
"sea apropiado, claro."

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:351
msgid "What did you say about the fortress not being well guarded, lich?"
msgstr "¿Qué dijiste sobre que la fortaleza no estaba bien protegida, lich?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:356
msgid "I stand corrected. We <i>may</i> need a better strategy."
msgstr "Reconozco mi error. <i>Quizás</i> necesitemos una mejor estrategia."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:368
msgid "We have failed... H— how? *Ugh*"
msgstr "Hemos fracasado... ¿C-cómo? *Ugh*"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:380
msgid "Forgive us, Lady..."
msgstr "Perdónanos, Señora..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:392
msgid "You are about to find out that Yechnagoth is no more, fool."
msgstr "Estás a punto de descubrir que Yechnagoth ya no existe, tonto."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:408
msgid "I depart from this world to embrace the power of Uria..."
msgstr "Me aparto de este mundo para abrazar el poder de Uria..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:413
msgid ""
"Not likely, but you will certainly embrace the cold touch of death on the "
"other side, heh, heh."
msgstr ""
"No lo creo, pero seguramente abrazarás el frío toque de la muerte del otro "
"lado, je, je."

#. [message]: speaker=Elgamal
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:418
msgid ""
"You... You haven’t seen the full extent of her power... You haven’t seen the "
"great things she’s done for us... You understand nothing... Nothing... at "
"all..."
msgstr ""
"Tú... No has visto el alcance completo de su poder... No has visto las "
"grandes cosas que ha hecho por nosotros... No entiendes nada... Nada... en "
"absoluto..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:430
msgid ""
"Now that you’re dead, all that has suddenly become irrelevant, hasn’t it?"
msgstr ""
"Ahora que estás muerto, todo eso de repente se volvió irrelevante, ¿no es "
"así?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:462
msgid ""
"It’s over now, fiends. Flee while you can, and make sure the Triad hears of "
"your shameful defeat at our hands."
msgstr ""
"Se acabó ahora, demonios. Huid mientras podáis, y aseguraos de que la Tríada "
"escuche de vuestra vergonzosa derrota a manos nuestras."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:468
msgid ""
"It’s over now. There’s nobody left to obstruct our path but those artificial "
"abominations."
msgstr ""
"Se acabó ahora. No queda nadie que obstruya nuestro camino salvo esas "
"abominaciones artificiales."

#. [message]: speaker=Horo
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:475
msgid "<i>(snicker)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(risita)</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:480
msgid "So, Wesmere is just ahead. What are you going to do now, lass?"
msgstr "Así que Wesmere está justo adelante. ¿Qué vas a hacer ahora, muchacha?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates.cfg:485
msgid ""
"I want to discuss some plans with the three of you right now, in fact. Come "
"with me."
msgstr ""
"De hecho, quiero discutir algunos planes con ustedes tres ahora mismo. Venid "
"conmigo."

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/storytxt.cfg:338
msgid "Departure"
msgstr "Partida"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:60
msgid ""
"You seem even more upset than usual, Elynia. What would the matter be this "
"time?"
msgstr ""
"Pareces más alterada de lo habitual, Elynia. ¿Cuál es el problema esta vez?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:69
msgid ""
"I don’t think I could bear more losses after what happened to Galas. My plan "
"was not to <i>fight</i> in enemy lands, but rather to <i>infiltrate</i>. "
"This battle was not part of the plan — we were to part ways right before "
"reaching this fort."
msgstr ""
"No creo que pueda soportar más pérdidas después de lo que le pasó a Galas. "
"Mi plan no era <i>luchar</i> en tierras enemigas, sino <i>infiltrarme</i>. "
"Esta batalla no formaba parte del plan — debíamos separarnos justo antes de "
"llegar a este fuerte."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:74
msgid ""
"Wait... You planned to enter the hive on your own, without us? That’s "
"just... stupid! You don’t know for sure what lurks beneath besides the "
"Shaxthal creatures we have encountered so far! What if that woman or Mal "
"Hekuba are awaiting there?!"
msgstr ""
"Espera... ¿Planeaste entrar en la colmena sola, sin nosotros? Eso es... "
"estúpido. ¡No sabes con certeza qué se oculta allí abajo aparte de las "
"criaturas Shaxthal que hemos encontrado hasta ahora! ¿Y si esa mujer o Mal "
"Hekuba están esperando allá?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:79
msgid ""
"I was hoping you could provide me with a few of your best undead warriors, "
"in fact."
msgstr ""
"De hecho, esperaba que pudieras proporcionarme algunos de tus mejores "
"guerreros no-muertos."

#. [message]: speaker=Horo
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:84
msgid ""
"Lady, that’s suicidal! From what we’ve heard, <i>nobody</i> could survive a "
"confrontation with those horrors without support! Allow us to protect you "
"until you reach the entrance to the caves at the very least!"
msgstr ""
"Señora, ¡eso es suicida! Según lo que hemos oído, <i>nadie</i> podría "
"sobrevivir a un enfrentamiento con esos horrores sin apoyo. ¡Permítenos "
"protegerte al menos hasta que llegues a la entrada de las cuevas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:89
msgid ""
"I refuse to send any undead down there unless you allow me to go with you."
msgstr ""
"Me niego a enviar no-muertos allá abajo a menos que me permitas acompañarte."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:110
msgid ""
"What’s your motivation, Malin? What makes you want to accompany me now that "
"neither Galas nor Anlindë exist in this world?"
msgstr ""
"¿Cuál es tu motivación, Malin? ¿Qué te hace querer acompañarme ahora que ni "
"Galas ni Anlindë existen en este mundo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:119
msgid ""
"I have been tempted to ask you the same question for a while, actually. I "
"know you cared about the boy much like you cared about Argan, and I have "
"sensed your grief following his death. And yet, somehow you have been in "
"denial about it — perhaps <i>afraid</i> to admit that losing him had a "
"greater effect on your self than losing Argan. I suppose it could just be a "
"matter of time, seeing as how Argan disappeared from your life much longer "
"ago."
msgstr ""
"De hecho, he estado tentado a hacerte la misma pregunta por un tiempo. Sé "
"que te importaba el chico tanto como te importaba Argan, y he percibido tu "
"dolor tras su muerte. Y, sin embargo, de algún modo lo has negado — quizá "
"tengas <i>miedo</i> de admitir que perderlo te afectó más que perder a "
"Argan. Supongo que solo es cuestión de tiempo, dado que Argan desapareció de "
"tu vida hace mucho más tiempo."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:124
msgid ""
"But even though you want to pretend none of this is the truth, your demeanor "
"makes it all evident to us. Now you seem to seek vengeance against Uria’s "
"followers, especially Elyssa. What’s the point of wasting the gift of "
"eternal life to pursue such an ephemeral goal, I ask?"
msgstr ""
"Pero aunque quieras fingir que nada de esto es verdad, tu actitud nos lo "
"hace evidente. Ahora pareces buscar venganza contra los seguidores de Uria, "
"especialmente contra Elyssa. ¿Cuál es el sentido de desperdiciar el don de "
"la vida eterna para perseguir un objetivo tan efímero, te pregunto?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:133
msgid "You have not answered... my question..."
msgstr "No has respondido... a mi pregunta..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:138
msgid ""
"Probably because I don’t need to. I don’t have a motive to do anything "
"anymore. My foolish mission to erase the orcish species from Irdya failed "
"too long ago!"
msgstr ""
"Probablemente porque no necesito hacerlo. Ya no tengo motivo para hacer "
"nada. ¡Mi tonta misión de borrar a la especie orca de Irdya fracasó hace "
"demasiado tiempo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:143
msgid "Is it redemption that you seek?"
msgstr "¿Es redención lo que buscas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:148
msgid "I don’t know! That’s what you asked when I first met you, remember?"
msgstr "¡No lo sé! Eso fue lo que me preguntaste cuando te conocí, ¿recuerdas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:159
msgid "We aren’t accomplishing anything. My lady, please reconsider—"
msgstr "No estamos logrando nada. Mi señora, por favor reconsidera—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:164
msgid ""
"We’ll secure the hive entrance together, but from that point onwards it will "
"be only Mal Keshar and I, and whoever wants to go with us except for you two."
msgstr ""
"Aseguraremos la entrada de la colmena juntos, pero a partir de ese momento "
"solo estaremos Mal Keshar y yo, y quien quiera acompañarnos excepto ustedes "
"dos."

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:170
msgid "Wh— Why would that be, my lady?"
msgstr "¿P-Por qué sería eso, mi señora?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:175
msgid ""
"We are going to need some capable soldiers alive to alert the Grand Council "
"if neither we nor our messengers make it back. I want you to immediately "
"head back to the Far North should we not return to the surface within one "
"day."
msgstr ""
"Vamos a necesitar algunos soldados capaces con vida para alertar al Gran "
"Consejo si ni nosotros ni nuestros mensajeros regresamos. Quiero que se "
"dirijan inmediatamente al Lejano Norte si no volvemos a la superficie en un "
"día."

#. [message]: speaker=Horo
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:180
msgid ""
"Very well, then. I am... unsure about what strategy — if any at all — you "
"have in mind to defeat or destroy whatever you are going to face in that "
"place, but... Your quest is noble. I wish you the best of luck to complete "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Muy bien, entonces. No estoy... segura de qué estrategia — si es que tienes "
"alguna — tienes en mente para derrotar o destruir lo que sea que vayas a "
"enfrentar allí, pero... Tu misión es noble. Te deseo la mejor de las suertes "
"para completarla."

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:185
msgid ""
"If I ever return to our island, I’ll make sure our people hear of your "
"bravery and your many sacrifices. I am sure you’ll succeed in this last "
"mission, my lady."
msgstr ""
"Si alguna vez regreso a nuestra isla, me aseguraré de que nuestro pueblo "
"escuche sobre tu valentía y tus muchos sacrificios. Estoy segura de que "
"triunfarás en esta última misión, mi señora."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode1/scenarios/11_Ambush_at_the_Gates_cutscene.cfg:196
msgid "Thank you... It really means a lot to me."
msgstr "Gracias... Realmente significa mucho para mí."

