#: After_the_Storm/episode2/characters.cfg:172
msgid ""
"As a high-level unit under your control, Elynia has special <b>After Maximum "
"Level Advancements (AMLAs)</b>. You can learn more about those by right-"
"clicking her and choosing the <b>Unit Advancements</b> option."
msgstr ""
"Como unidad de alto nivel bajo tu control, Elynia tiene <b>Mejoras tras el "
"nivel máximo (AMLAs)</b> especiales. Puedes obtener más información sobre "
"ellas haciendo clic derecho en la unidad correspondiente y seleccionando la "
"opción <b>Mejoras de unidad</b>."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/deaths.cfg:26
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/deaths.cfg:67
msgid "I... fall to the darkness."
msgstr "Yo... caigo en la oscuridad."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/deaths.cfg:37
msgid "No! My mission isn’t over yet!"
msgstr "¡No! Mi misión aún no ha terminado."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/deaths.cfg:48
msgid "Augh! Elynia, save me—"
msgstr "¡Augh! Elynia, sálvame—"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/deaths.cfg:59
msgid "I’ve fallen before completing my mission. Forgive me..."
msgstr "He caído antes de completar mi misión. Perdóname..."

#. [campaign]: id=After_the_Storm_II
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/menu.cfg:7
msgid "AtS-2"
msgstr "AtS-2"

#. [campaign]: id=After_the_Storm_II
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/menu.cfg:9
msgid "Episode II: Fate"
msgstr "Episodio II: Destino"

#. [campaign]: id=After_the_Storm_II
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/menu.cfg:14
msgid ""
"Time passes, and the Chaos Empire still manages to make a stand against its "
"enemies. While the Grand Council is preoccupied with more pressing matters, "
"the fragile alliance of the peoples of the Far North is threatened by a new, "
"mysterious leader who seeks to invade their defenseless lands."
msgstr ""
"El tiempo pasa, y el Imperio del Caos aún logra resistir frente a sus "
"enemigos. Mientras el Gran Consejo está ocupado con asuntos más urgentes, la "
"frágil alianza de los pueblos del Lejano Norte se ve amenazada por un nuevo "
"y misterioso líder que busca invadir sus tierras indefensas."

#. [campaign]: id=After_the_Storm_II
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/menu.cfg:19
msgid "difficulty_menu^Footpad"
msgstr "Patrullero"

#. [campaign]: id=After_the_Storm_II
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/menu.cfg:20
msgid "difficulty_menu^Trapper"
msgstr "Trampero"

#. [campaign]: id=After_the_Storm_II
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/menu.cfg:21
msgid "difficulty_menu^Highwayman"
msgstr "Bandolero"

#. [scenario]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/00_Transience.cfg:4
msgid "Transience"
msgstr "Transitoriedad"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/00_Transience.cfg:125
msgid ""
"I remember hearing of the mandate issued to destroy the Sceptre of Fire back "
"in the day..."
msgstr ""
"Recuerdo haber oído hablar del mandato emitido para destruir el Cetro de "
"Fuego en aquellos tiempos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/00_Transience.cfg:134
msgid ""
"I’m curious about why you decided to betray your people by keeping the "
"Sceptre’s core to yourself, Elynia."
msgstr ""
"Tengo curiosidad por saber por qué decidiste traicionar a tu gente "
"quedándote con el núcleo del Cetro, Elynia."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/00_Transience.cfg:139
msgid "That’s nothing of your concern."
msgstr "Eso no es asunto tuyo."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/00_Transience.cfg:144
msgid ""
"It is not, really? Because to me, it seems that you carry with you a "
"dangerous artifact that these people <i>need</i> for some vaguely-defined "
"purpose that will most certainly bring no good to this world! Destroying it "
"would be the most logical choice right now."
msgstr ""
"¿Ah, no lo es? Porque a mí me parece que llevas contigo un artefacto "
"peligroso que esta gente <i>necesita</i> para algún propósito vagamente "
"definido que con toda seguridad no traerá nada bueno a este mundo. "
"¡Destruirlo sería la elección más lógica en este momento!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/00_Transience.cfg:149
msgid ""
"... I beg to differ, but with the Union gone it may well be the only great "
"power remaining on Irdya that we could use to fight Uria and the Iron Triad, "
"unless you know something I am not aware of — which I find unlikely."
msgstr ""
"... Permíteme discrepar, pero con la Unión desaparecida bien podría ser el "
"único gran poder que queda en Irdya que podríamos usar para luchar contra "
"Uria y la Tríada de Hierro, a menos que sepas algo de lo que no esté "
"enterada — lo cual me parece poco probable."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/00_Transience.cfg:154
msgid "This isn’t the best moment to argue over this."
msgstr "Este no es el mejor momento para discutir sobre esto."

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/storytxt.cfg:59
msgid "By the Moonlight"
msgstr "A la luz de la luna"

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:62
msgid "team_name^Humans"
msgstr "team_name^Humanos"

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:76
msgid "Aethyr"
msgstr "Aethyr"

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:78
msgid "Devon"
msgstr "Devon"

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:113
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:128
msgid "team_name^Animals"
msgstr "team_name^Animales"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:170
msgid "Find a friendly unit"
msgstr "Encuentra una unidad aliada"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:183
msgid ""
"There seem to be some hostile animals ahead. I’d better move carefully..."
msgstr ""
"Parece que hay algunos animales hostiles más adelante. Será mejor que me "
"mueva con cuidado..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:191
msgid "I think I can see a village to the northeast..."
msgstr "Creo que puedo ver una aldea al noreste..."

#. [unit]: type=Huntsman, id=Luddry
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:294
msgid "Luddry"
msgstr "Luddry"

#. [unit]: type=Lich, id=Daent
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:322
msgid "Daent"
msgstr "Daent"

#. [message]: speaker=Aethyr
#. [message]: speaker=Lord Durstrang
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:350
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:279
msgid "Halt! Who goes there?"
msgstr "¡Alto! ¿Quién va ahí?"

#. [message]: speaker=Devon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:355
msgid ""
"Don’t pay any attention to that — it’s just another of those disgusting "
"forest creatures."
msgstr ""
"No le prestes atención: es solo otra de esas asquerosas criaturas del bosque."

#. [message]: speaker=Aethyr
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:360
msgid "But she’s injured—"
msgstr "Pero está herida…"

#. [message]: speaker=Devon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:365
msgid ""
"It’s a trick! They lure you into the dark to do whatever they please with "
"your dead body—"
msgstr ""
"¡Es una trampa! Te atraen hacia la oscuridad para hacer lo que quieran con "
"tu cadáver…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:370
msgid "... I need help. Could any of you please—"
msgstr "... Necesito ayuda. ¿Alguno de ustedes podría…?"

#. [message]: speaker=Devon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:375
msgid "Begone, unless you want us to slice your throat open!"
msgstr "¡Lárgate, a menos que quieras que te cortemos la garganta!"

#. [message]: speaker=Luddry
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:382
msgid "What’s going on here?"
msgstr "¿Qué está pasando aquí?"

#. [message]: speaker=Aethyr
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:387
msgid "Chief, this lass here, she—"
msgstr "Jefe, esta muchacha aquí, ella…"

#. [message]: speaker=Luddry
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:392
msgid "You look oddly familiar. What’s your name?"
msgstr "Pareces extrañamente familiar. ¿Cuál es tu nombre?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:397
msgid "I am Elynia, the—"
msgstr "Soy Elynia, la…"

#. [message]: speaker=Luddry
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:402
msgid ""
"The Lady of Light, as I recall. You weren’t of much help to us in the "
"country."
msgstr ""
"La Dama de la Luz, según recuerdo. No fuiste de mucha ayuda para nosotros en "
"el campo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:407
msgid "... Excuse me? I don’t know you."
msgstr "... ¿Disculpa? No te conozco."

#. [message]: speaker=Luddry
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:414
msgid ""
"Of course you don’t know me, because you and your friends were too busy "
"battling the dark soldiers to help us civilians in Ardgam. That was my "
"hometown, and my family was trapped, helpless, amidst the fire. What’s your "
"purpose here, and why should we help you??"
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que no me conoces, porque tú y tus amigos estaban demasiado "
"ocupados luchando contra los soldados oscuros para ayudarnos a los civiles "
"en Ardgam. Ese era mi pueblo natal, y mi familia quedó atrapada, indefensa, "
"en medio del fuego. ¿Cuál es tu propósito aquí y por qué deberíamos ayudarte?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:421
msgid ""
"I would like to know where I am, and if it would be possible, I’d also like "
"some help to get to the Grand Council. This is a matter of the utmost "
"importance..."
msgstr ""
"Me gustaría saber dónde estoy y, si fuera posible, también quisiera algo de "
"ayuda para llegar al Gran Consejo. Es un asunto de suma importancia…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:430
msgid "—Are you even listening to me?!"
msgstr "¿¡Me están escuchando siquiera!?"

#. [message]: speaker=Luddry
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:435
msgid ""
"I don’t feel particularly inclined to help you — at least not right now. If "
"you really need to get to those useless elders, you are on your own. We "
"don’t have any time for this nonsense, as we need to defend <i>our</i> town "
"by our own means right now."
msgstr ""
"No me siento particularmente inclinado a ayudarte… al menos no ahora. Si "
"realmente necesitas llegar hasta esos inútiles ancianos, tendrás que "
"arreglártelas sola. No tenemos tiempo para estas tonterías, ya que debemos "
"defender <i>nuestro</i> pueblo por nuestros propios medios en este momento."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:452
msgid "It feels like I’ve been in a similar situation before..."
msgstr "Siento que he estado en una situación similar antes…"

#. [message]: speaker=Aethyr
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:461
msgid ""
"Can you help us? I know our leader appears to be very resentful of you, but "
"it’s said that the evil mage Daent has returned from the land of the dead to "
"get his revenge upon us, for banishing him from the village. The rumors of "
"the power he has amassed since then are terrifying."
msgstr ""
"¿Puedes ayudarnos? Sé que nuestro líder parece guardar mucho resentimiento "
"hacia ti, pero se dice que el malvado mago Daent ha regresado de la tierra "
"de los muertos para vengarse de nosotros por haberlo desterrado del pueblo. "
"Los rumores sobre el poder que ha acumulado desde entonces son aterradores."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:466
msgid ""
"Hm... Well, I may be able to provide you with my assistance if you would "
"help me in exchange. Really, I’m not asking for much. "
msgstr ""
"Hm… Bien, tal vez pueda ofrecerles mi ayuda si ustedes me ayudan a cambio. "
"Realmente no estoy pidiendo mucho."

#. [message]: speaker=Devon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:471
msgid ""
"We can’t make any promises, faerie. Our leader isn’t that kind of person — "
"you’ll have to figure out how to solve your problems on your own."
msgstr ""
"No podemos hacer ninguna promesa, hada. Nuestro líder no es ese tipo de "
"persona: tendrás que averiguar cómo resolver tus problemas por tu cuenta."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:480
msgid "So be it, then."
msgstr "Que así sea, entonces."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:525
msgid "Death of Luddry"
msgstr "Muerte de Luddry"

#. [message]: speaker=Luddry
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:551
msgid "Argh! I’m done for."
msgstr "¡Argh! Estoy acabado."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:563
msgid ""
"I don’t suppose these people would want to help me now that they are "
"leaderless..."
msgstr ""
"No creo que esta gente quiera ayudarme ahora que se han quedado sin líder…"

#. [message]: speaker=Devon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:568
msgid "<i>Thanks</i> for your absolutely <i>useless</i> help, faerie."
msgstr "<i>Gracias</i> por tu ayuda absolutamente <i>inútil</i>, hada."

#. [message]: speaker=Daent
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:584
msgid "Arise! Arise once again, fallen warriors of times long past! Arise!"
msgstr ""
"¡Levantense! ¡Levantense una vez más, guerreros caídos de tiempos pasados! "
"¡Levantense!"

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:590
msgid "I don’t like the sound of that... not at all..."
msgstr "No me gusta cómo suena eso… para nada…"

#. [message]: speaker=Daent
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:615
msgid "Ah, you have been sent by my brother to destroy me, isn’t that right?"
msgstr "Ah, te ha enviado mi hermano para destruirme, ¿verdad?"

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:621
msgid "Your brother?"
msgstr "¿Tu hermano?"

#. [message]: speaker=Daent
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:626
msgid ""
"Well, less chatter and more action, I say! You all shall embrace undeath "
"soon, no matter whether you want or not!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bien, menos charla y más acción, digo yo! ¡Todos ustedes abrazarán la no-"
"muerte muy pronto, lo queran o no!"

#. [message]: speaker=Daent
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:641
msgid "Ahhh, you think you can destroy me, don’t you? Well—"
msgstr "Ahhh, crees que puedes destruirme, ¿verdad? Pues…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:646
msgid "Enough of this."
msgstr "Basta de esto."

#. [message]: speaker=Daent
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:672
msgid ""
"Ahhh, you think you can destroy me, don’t you? Well, a few have already "
"tried to vanquish me before to no avail... What makes you think it will be "
"different this time? MWAHAHAHAHA!"
msgstr ""
"Ahhh, crees que puedes destruirme, ¿verdad? Pues, unos cuantos ya han "
"intentado derrotarme antes sin éxito… ¿Qué te hace pensar que será diferente "
"esta vez? ¡MWAHAHAHAHA!"

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:690
msgid "He’s gone!"
msgstr "¡Se ha ido!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:711
msgid "That wasn’t too hard."
msgstr "No fue tan difícil."

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:723
msgid "Our village is saved!"
msgstr "¡Nuestro pueblo está a salvo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Devon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:728
msgid ""
"Heh. I admit I didn’t expect this to work out with a faerie leading those "
"impressionable fools."
msgstr ""
"Heh. Admito que no esperaba que esto funcionara con un hada liderando a esos "
"ingenuos."

#. [message]: speaker=Luddry
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:733
msgid ""
"Well done, everybody. As for you, faerie... What is it that you needed from "
"us again?"
msgstr ""
"Bien hecho, todos. Y en cuanto a ti, hada… ¿Qué era eso que necesitabas de "
"nosotros?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:738
msgid "I also have a name, as I told you before."
msgstr "También tengo un nombre, como te dije antes."

#. [message]: speaker=Luddry
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:743
msgid "I suggest that you get to the point before I change my mind."
msgstr "Te sugiero que vayas al grano antes de que cambie de opinión."

#. [message]: speaker=Aethyr
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:748
msgid "But sir, her help in defeating the undead was..."
msgstr "Pero señor, su ayuda para derrotar a los no-muertos fue…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:753
msgid ""
"I need to know exactly where I am, and I must also meet with the Grand "
"Council of the Northern Peoples as soon as I may, for which I could need "
"some help depending on our location."
msgstr ""
"Necesito saber exactamente dónde estoy, y también debo reunirme con el Gran "
"Consejo de los Pueblos del Norte lo antes posible; para ello podría "
"necesitar algo de ayuda según nuestra ubicación."

#. [message]: speaker=Luddry
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:758
msgid ""
"I see. Well, we also need to arrange a meeting with the Council for our own "
"purposes. Sending some of our most capable hunters with you along with our "
"messengers might not be a bad idea after all, as you seem to excel in the "
"arts of healing and the northern forests are not particularly safe nowadays."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo. Bueno, nosotros también necesitamos organizar una reunión con el "
"Consejo para nuestros propios fines. Enviar a algunos de nuestros cazadores "
"más capaces contigo junto con nuestros mensajeros podría no ser una mala "
"idea después de todo, ya que pareces destacar en las artes curativas y los "
"bosques del norte no son particularmente seguros en estos días."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#. "But where am I?"
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:764
msgid "I’d be very grateful if you provided me with such help, then. But—"
msgstr "Estaría muy agradecida si me ofrecieran esa ayuda, entonces. Pero…"

#. [message]: speaker=Luddry
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/01_By_the_Moonlight.cfg:769
msgid "And welcome to the Heart Forest."
msgstr "Y bienvenida al Bosque Corazón."

