#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:476
msgid "Death of Durvan"
msgstr "Muerte de Durvan"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:188
msgid ""
"Frankly, when the village chief said ‘capable’ I was expecting something "
"better."
msgstr ""
"Francamente, cuando el jefe de la aldea dijo «capaces», esperaba algo mejor."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:193
msgid ""
"It’d be a grave mistake to underestimate us, lass. Life ’round here ain’t "
"easy these days, and we have to be prepared to deal with anything."
msgstr ""
"Sería un grave error subestimarnos, muchacha. La vida por aquí no es fácil "
"en estos días, y debemos estar preparados para enfrentar cualquier cosa."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:198
msgid ""
"I’m well aware of that, having lived in the wilderness myself before, but "
"these are mostly novices and untrained youths!"
msgstr ""
"Soy muy consciente de ello, ya que yo misma viví en la naturaleza antes, "
"¡pero estos son en su mayoría novatos y jóvenes sin entrenamiento!"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:203
msgid ""
"The chief wouldn’t want to send off veterans on the chance that our home is "
"attacked again. Anyway, we’d better get going. Look out for the trolls that "
"control this road — they hunt unwary travelers and eat them alive."
msgstr ""
"El jefe no querría enviar a los veteranos por si acaso nuestro hogar es "
"atacado de nuevo. En fin, será mejor que sigamos adelante. Cuidado con los "
"trolls que dominan este camino: cazan a los viajeros incautos y se los comen "
"vivos."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:214
msgid "Blast! I wasn’t counting on this happening!"
msgstr "¡Maldita sea! ¡No contaba con que esto pasara!"

#. [message]: speaker=Reck
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:235
msgid "Reck don’t like humans on his base. We smash them!"
msgstr "A Reck no le gustan los humanos en su territorio. ¡Los aplastamos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Reck
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:247
msgid "Reck dying... and don’t know why."
msgstr "Reck se muere... y no sabe por qué."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:262
#, fuzzy
msgid "That big troll was hoarding quite a decent sum of gold in these ruins."
msgstr ""
"Ese gran troll estaba acumulando una considerable cantidad de oro en estas "
"ruinas."

#. [unit]: id=Dremorran, type=Fugitive
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:293
msgid "Dremorran"
msgstr "Dremorran"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:353
msgid "Cic"
msgstr "Cic"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:354
msgid "Glynvan"
msgstr "Glynvan"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:355
msgid "Quorren"
msgstr "Quorren"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:356
msgid "Caror"
msgstr "Caror"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:357
msgid "Danon"
msgstr "Danon"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:380
msgid "I hear some commotion ahead..."
msgstr "Oigo alboroto más adelante..."

#. [message]: speaker=Quorren
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:395
msgid ""
"Drop everything you’re carrying with you gal, and we <i>may</i> spare your "
"pretty neck!"
msgstr ""
"¡Suelta todo lo que llevas, chica, y <i>quizás</i> te perdonemos ese bonito "
"cuello!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:400
msgid "We don’t have time for this—"
msgstr "No tenemos tiempo para esto—"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:405
msgid "We can’t just leave that poor girl at their mercy! We must help her!"
msgstr "¡No podemos dejar a esa pobre chica a su merced! ¡Debemos ayudarla!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:410
msgid "(<i>sigh</i>) Of course, that’s what I was planning to do anyway."
msgstr ""
"(<i>suspiro</i>) Por supuesto, eso era lo que planeaba hacer de todos modos."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:415
msgid "Save Allyna from the bandits"
msgstr "Salva a Allyna de los bandidos"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:419
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:579
msgid "Death of Allyna"
msgstr "Muerte de Allyna"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:432
msgid "Alas! I never got a chance to see the great towers of the capital!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ay! Nunca tuve la oportunidad de ver las grandes torres de la capital."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:437
msgid "We shouldn’t have let this happen!"
msgstr "¡No deberíamos haber dejado que esto pasara!"

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:494
msgid ""
"Oh, thank you for saving my life, sir, I’ll be forever grateful! Is there "
"anything I could do to repay you?"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, gracias por salvarme la vida, señor, estaré eternamente agradecida! "
"¿Hay algo que pueda hacer para recompensarte?"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:499
msgid "Hm, actually, it is this lass here who is leading us..."
msgstr "Mmm, en realidad es esta joven la que nos está guiando..."

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:513
msgid "She’s the legendary Lady of Light!"
msgstr "¡Ella es la legendaria Dama de la Luz!"

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:518
msgid "Oh, I see! I beg your pardon, my lady."
msgstr "¡Ah, ya veo! Le pido disculpas, mi señora."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:523
msgid ""
"May I ask what business brings a young girl like you to such a dangerous "
"location alone? What’s your name, anyway?"
msgstr ""
"¿Puedo preguntar qué asuntos traen a una joven como tú a un lugar tan "
"peligroso sola? ¿Cuál es tu nombre, por cierto?"

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:528
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I’m Allyna of Dalbloom, from the eastern border. It’s a very tiny village, "
"so you may not have heard of it before. I was sent on a mission to deliver "
"an important message to the Grand Council."
msgstr ""
"Soy Allyna de Dalbloom, de la frontera oriental. Es un pueblo muy pequeño, "
"así que quizá no hayas oído hablar de él. Me enviaron en una misión para "
"entregar un mensaje importante al Gran Consejo de—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:533
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hm, I see. We happen to be on a similar mission ourselves. I would strongly "
"suggest that you join us — it’s a miracle that you have made it this far "
"through these uncivilized lands in one piece. What do you think?"
msgstr ""
"Claro, nosotros también necesitamos entregar nuestros propios mensajes. Te "
"sugiero firmemente que te unas a nosotros — es un milagro que hayas llegado "
"tan lejos a través de estas tierras incivilizadas ilesa. ¿Qué opinas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:538
msgid ""
"Yes! —I mean, if it doesn’t bother you, of course. Sure it is uncivilized "
"around here — I don’t think I have ever seen a town get ransacked like that "
"before..."
msgstr ""
"¡Sí! —quiero decir, si no te molesta, claro. Sí, es incivilizado por aquí — "
"no creo haber visto nunca un pueblo saqueado así antes..."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:546
msgid "What are you talking about?"
msgstr "¿De qué hablas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:551
msgid ""
"The bridge town ahead was captured by a large armed band. I turned back as "
"soon as I could, but some of their brutes chased me, and then I found you!"
msgstr ""
"El pueblo del puente más adelante fue capturado por una gran banda armada. "
"Me di la vuelta tan pronto como pude, pero algunos de sus brutos me "
"persiguieron, y entonces los encontré a ustedes."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:556
msgid ""
"Sounds like we may have to cleanse the town a bit before proceeding, then."
msgstr ""
"Parece que tendremos que limpiar un poco el pueblo antes de continuar, "
"entonces."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:561
msgid "Good plan. Gods, I never thought Talwyn would fall like that..."
msgstr "Buen plan. Dioses, nunca pensé que Talwyn caería así..."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:575
msgid "Defeat the bandit leader in Talwyn"
msgstr "Derrota al líder bandido en Talwyn"

#. [message]: speaker=Dremorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:595
msgid "No! All our efforts have been in vain!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡Todos nuestros esfuerzos han sido en vano!"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:617
msgid "Onwards we go, to the capital!"
msgstr "¡Adelante, vamos hacia la capital!"

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/02_The_Heart_Forest.cfg:622
msgid ""
"So are you truly the Lady of Light? I’ve heard many amazing stories about "
"you! Do you mind if I ask you some questions?"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces eres realmente la Dama de la Luz? ¡He oído muchas historias "
"increíbles sobre ti! ¿Te importa si te hago algunas preguntas?"

