#. [label]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:145
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/02_01_Return_to_Raelthyn.cfg:459
msgid "Tower of Silence"
msgstr "Torre del Silencio"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:239
msgid "Darren"
msgstr "Darren"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:245
msgid "Aethyncyn"
msgstr "Aethyncyn"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:262
msgid ""
"Finally, the walls of Raelthyn! It’s a pity it’s too dark to see the glory "
"of the capital city!"
msgstr ""
"¡Finalmente, las murallas de Raelthyn! Es una lástima que esté demasiado "
"oscuro para ver la gloria de la ciudad capital."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:267
msgid "I have been here before. Now, let’s move."
msgstr "He estado aquí antes. Ahora, avancemos."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:284
msgid ""
"I’m a humble messenger from the small village of Suthwood in the Heart "
"Forest. We came here to meet with the Grand Council."
msgstr ""
"Soy un humilde mensajero de la pequeña aldea de Suthwood en el Bosque del "
"Corazón. Venimos aquí para reunirnos con el Gran Consejo."

#. [message]: speaker=Lord Durstrang
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:289
msgid "You and who else?"
msgstr "¿Tú y quién más?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lord Durstrang
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:305
msgid "Seize the traitor!"
msgstr "¡Capturen al traidor!"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:310
msgid "Traitor? Who?"
msgstr "¿Traidor? ¿Quién?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:318
msgid "Exactly what in the world is going on here?"
msgstr "¿Qué demonios está pasando aquí?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lord Durstrang
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:323
msgid ""
"You, faerie, are accused of betraying the Alliance of the Peoples of the Far "
"North, leading an elvish faction found to be collaborating with our enemies "
"in times of war, and disclosing vital tactical information which jeopardizes "
"the safety of the Aragwaith country and our allies."
msgstr ""
"Tú, hada, estás acusada de traicionar la Alianza de los Pueblos del Lejano "
"Norte, liderar una facción élfica que ha sido encontrada colaborando con "
"nuestros enemigos en tiempos de guerra, y de revelar información táctica "
"vital que pone en peligro la seguridad del país Aragwaith y de nuestros "
"aliados."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:332
msgid ""
"Certainly, this must be some kind of misunderstanding... I would never shift "
"my allegiances against what’s best for the free civilizations of Irdya!"
msgstr ""
"Ciertamente, esto debe ser algún tipo de malentendido... ¡Nunca cambiaría "
"mis lealtades en contra de lo que es mejor para las civilizaciones libres de "
"Irdya!"

#. [message]: speaker=Torancyn
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:344
msgid ""
"Imprisoning her will not be necessary. Allow her to come to the Grand "
"Council."
msgstr "No será necesario encarcelarla. Permítanle acudir al Gran Consejo."

#. [message]: speaker=Lord Durstrang
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:349
msgid "But, my lord..."
msgstr "Pero, mi señor..."

#. [message]: speaker=Valen
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:365
msgid "A trial won’t be required either. She’s been framed by the enemy."
msgstr "Tampoco se requerirá un juicio. Ha sido incriminada por el enemigo."

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:370
msgid ""
"Elynia, we have been eagerly awaiting your return. It’s been a long time..."
msgstr ""
"Elynia, hemos estado esperando ansiosamente tu regreso. Ha pasado mucho "
"tiempo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:375
msgid ""
"Lord Arnesius, it’s good to see you again. Something terrible has happened..."
msgstr "Lord Arnesius, es bueno verte de nuevo. Algo terrible ha ocurrido..."

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:380
msgid ""
"Yes, yes... Valen has told us everything, and there’s more you need to know "
"as well. Come with us."
msgstr ""
"Sí, sí... Valen nos ha contado todo, y hay más que necesitas saber también. "
"Ven con nosotros."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:385
msgid ""
"My Lord, I— our messengers were promised an audience with the Council as "
"well..."
msgstr ""
"Mi Señor, yo— a nuestros mensajeros también se les prometió una audiencia "
"con el Consejo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:390
msgid ""
"That will have to wait while we discuss some war matters, but since you have "
"come from so far protecting her, you may also come and listen."
msgstr ""
"Eso tendrá que esperar mientras discutimos algunos asuntos de guerra, pero "
"dado que han venido de tan lejos protegiéndola, también pueden venir y "
"escuchar."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_01_Unrest_in_Raelthyn.cfg:395
msgid "Very well, my lord."
msgstr "Muy bien, mi señor."

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/storytxt.cfg:93
msgid "Revelations"
msgstr "Revelaciones"

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:103
msgid ""
"We’d like to start by apologizing for our actions, or more accurately, our "
"lack thereof. Had we understood the importance of your mission to Zocthanol "
"we’d have sent a whole fleet with you, and Galas’ demise could have surely "
"been avoided."
msgstr ""
"Nos gustaría comenzar disculpándonos por nuestras acciones, o más "
"precisamente, por la falta de ellas. Si hubiéramos entendido la importancia "
"de tu misión a Zocthanol, habríamos enviado toda una flota contigo, y la "
"muerte de Galas seguramente se podría haber evitado."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:108
msgid ""
"I... I don’t think that would have made a great difference. The storm that "
"caught us was a trap set up by our enemies."
msgstr ""
"Yo... no creo que eso hubiera hecho gran diferencia. La tormenta que nos "
"atrapó fue una trampa tendida por nuestros enemigos."

#. [message]: speaker=Torancyn
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:113
msgid ""
"As soon as we got word of your plan to assault the Wesmere hive on your own, "
"we sent a platoon in your aid, but their path was obstructed by those "
"Shaxthal creatures, who took over the Bay of Glamdrol to the south-west."
msgstr ""
"En cuanto recibimos noticias de tu plan de asaltar la colmena de Wesmere por "
"tu cuenta, enviamos un pelotón en tu ayuda, pero su camino fue obstruido por "
"esas criaturas Shaxthal, que tomaron la Bahía de Glamdrol al suroeste."

#. [message]: speaker=Torancyn
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:118
msgid ""
"By the time the soldiers arrived, it was already too late. Not only did we "
"not find you or the lich Mal Keshar, but the plains had completely "
"disappeared."
msgstr ""
"Para cuando llegaron los soldados, ya era demasiado tarde. No sólo no te "
"encontramos a ti ni al lich Mal Keshar, sino que las llanuras habían "
"desaparecido por completo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:127
msgid "But... disappeared?"
msgstr "¿Pero... desaparecidas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:132
msgid ""
"Everything vanished at the center of the explosion from which you escaped. "
"The hive, the rocks, the clouds — everything had completely disappeared, "
"according to the reports we got. The area surrounding the massive crater "
"turned into a vast ashy desert devoid of any traces of life, artificial or "
"otherwise. They also said the air itself had turned thin as in the tallest "
"peaks of the Heart Mountains. We could only assume you had also been caught "
"in the explosion and were destroyed along with the necromancer."
msgstr ""
"Todo desapareció en el centro de la explosión de la que escapaste. La "
"colmena, las rocas, las nubes — todo había desaparecido por completo, según "
"los informes que recibimos. El área alrededor del enorme cráter se convirtió "
"en un vasto desierto ceniciento sin ningún rastro de vida, artificial o de "
"otro tipo. También dijeron que el aire mismo se volvió tan delgado como en "
"las cumbres más altas de las Montañas del Corazón. Sólo podemos suponer que "
"también fuiste atrapada en la explosión y destruida junto con el nigromante."

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:137
msgid ""
"With the ongoing war, we couldn’t spend much time or resources in searching "
"for you, so we decided to seek assistance from a seer who could tell us what "
"happened and why. That’s when we found Valen, who has been of great help to "
"us this past year."
msgstr ""
"Con la guerra en curso, no pudimos dedicar mucho tiempo ni recursos a "
"buscarte, así que decidimos buscar ayuda de una vidente que pudiera decirnos "
"qué pasó y por qué. Fue entonces cuando encontramos a Valen, que nos ha sido "
"de gran ayuda durante este último año."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:146
msgid "Hold on..."
msgstr "Espera..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:155
msgid ""
"That isn’t possible! A year? But— it has been— it has been less than a month!"
msgstr "¡Eso no es posible! ¿Un año? Pero— ha sido— ha sido menos de un mes."

#. [message]: speaker=Valen
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:164
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For you, my lady, time only continued to flow after the point you reappeared "
"in our country’s borders, but for us, time has gone by as usual. It’s been a "
"little over a year since the destruction of Wesmere."
msgstr ""
"Para ti, mi señora, el tiempo sólo continuó fluyendo después del momento en "
"que reapareciste en las fronteras de nuestro país, pero para nosotros, el "
"tiempo ha pasado como siempre. Ha pasado un poco más de un año desde la "
"destrucción de Wesmere."

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:169
msgid ""
"We suspect you were at the very center of the explosion, which may have "
"caused an anomaly that brought you forward in time."
msgstr ""
"Sospechamos que estabas en el mismo centro de la explosión, lo que pudo "
"haber causado una anomalía que te llevó hacia adelante en el tiempo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:178
msgid ""
"... Actually, it may be my own fault. I used a teleportation spell I had "
"just learned, without mastering it first, just as I felt as though my very "
"existence had come to an end..."
msgstr ""
"... En realidad, puede ser culpa mía. Usé un hechizo de teletransporte que "
"acababa de aprender, sin dominarlo antes, justo cuando sentí como si mi "
"propia existencia hubiera llegado a su fin..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:187
msgid ""
"But the entire place vanishing doesn’t make sense... How could that happen?"
msgstr ""
"Pero que todo el lugar desapareciera no tiene sentido... ¿Cómo pudo pasar "
"eso?"

#. [message]: speaker=Torancyn
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:192
msgid ""
"There are many things we still haven’t learned about our enemies that are, "
"perhaps, essential for putting an end to this war."
msgstr ""
"Hay muchas cosas que aún no sabemos sobre nuestros enemigos que quizás sean "
"esenciales para poner fin a esta guerra."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:197
msgid ""
"Where’s Kyara? And Horo? We sent them to you after securing the Chaos "
"outpost in Wesmere!"
msgstr ""
"¿Dónde están Kyara? ¿Y Horo? ¡Los enviamos a ustedes después de asegurar el "
"puesto avanzado del Caos en Wesmere!"

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:202
msgid "I fear we have never heard those names before."
msgstr "Me temo que nunca hemos oído esos nombres antes."

#. [message]: speaker=Torancyn
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:207
msgid ""
"Assuming they stumbled upon the same class and number of enemies as our men "
"did, it’s very likely they didn’t make it."
msgstr ""
"Asumiendo que se encontraron con la misma clase y número de enemigos que "
"nuestros hombres, es muy probable que no lo lograran."

#. [message]: speaker=Valen
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:216
msgid ""
"If you can provide me with more information, I may be able to find out what "
"occurred to them, but it will take time."
msgstr ""
"Si puedes proporcionarme más información, tal vez pueda averiguar qué les "
"ocurrió, pero llevará tiempo."

#. [message]: speaker=Torancyn
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:221
msgid ""
"While Valen was trying to determine your whereabouts, new riots took place "
"between the elves in the lands to the east. There are rumors of a certain "
"rose-haired faerie allying herself with the leaders of the Chaos Empire, "
"which is why you and your people have become rather unpopular amongst our "
"peers."
msgstr ""
"Mientras Valen intentaba determinar tu paradero, estallaron nuevos "
"disturbios entre los elfos en las tierras del este. Hay rumores de que "
"cierta hada de cabello rosado se ha aliado con los líderes del Imperio del "
"Caos, por lo que tú y tu gente se han vuelto bastante impopulares entre "
"nuestros pares."

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:226
msgid ""
"The elves are once again divided and fighting their own kinsmen on the "
"eastern border of our country, but one of the factions is clearly at an "
"advantage thanks to their alliance with the Empire. We suspect they may be "
"planning to invade us next, taking advantage of the tight situation on the "
"southern borders."
msgstr ""
"Los elfos están nuevamente divididos y luchando contra sus propios parientes "
"en la frontera este de nuestro país, pero una de las facciones tiene "
"claramente la ventaja gracias a su alianza con el Imperio. Sospechamos que "
"podrían estar planeando invadirnos a nosotros a continuación, aprovechando "
"la delicada situación en las fronteras del sur."

#. [message]: speaker=Torancyn
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:231
msgid ""
"Furthermore, it is said a great explosion took place in Glamdrol a few days "
"ago. We haven’t received any confirmation yet, but we fear it’s of a similar "
"nature to the one which destroyed Wesmere. If that’s true, then we have just "
"lost our largest western garrison."
msgstr ""
"Además, se dice que hace unos días ocurrió una gran explosión en Glamdrol. "
"Aún no hemos recibido confirmación, pero tememos que sea de naturaleza "
"similar a la que destruyó Wesmere. Si eso es cierto, entonces acabamos de "
"perder nuestra guarnición occidental más grande."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:236
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:272
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2921
msgid "I see..."
msgstr "Ya veo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:241
msgid ""
"It’s of utmost importance that the situation in the east is cleared up. The "
"friendly elvish faction has asked us for aid, but as it is now we are unable "
"to gather the complete Council to come to an agreement. We currently don’t "
"have many men to spare, so it has been suggested that you could lead a "
"militia in order to assist them, and hopefully discover the identity of this "
"mysterious impersonator."
msgstr ""
"Es de suma importancia que se esclarezca la situación en el este. La facción "
"élfica amiga nos ha pedido ayuda, pero en este momento no podemos reunir al "
"Consejo completo para llegar a un acuerdo. Actualmente no tenemos muchos "
"hombres disponibles, por lo que se ha sugerido que tú puedas liderar una "
"milicia para asistirlos y, con suerte, descubrir la identidad de este "
"misterioso impostor."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:246
msgid ""
"I think I’ve had enough experience with leading militiamen in the forests "
"for my liking, and I highly doubt they could stand a chance against those "
"demons and biomechanical creatures."
msgstr ""
"Creo que ya he tenido suficiente experiencia liderando milicianos en los "
"bosques para mi gusto, y dudo mucho que puedan tener alguna oportunidad "
"contra esos demonios y criaturas biomecánicas."

#. [message]: speaker=Torancyn
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:256
msgid ""
"It was never our intention to send you alone with barely-trained fighters. "
"Amongst your messengers was one of Mal Keshar’s very own disciples, a woman "
"by the name of Zynara. She’s willing to assist by leading a new undead horde "
"against our enemies for you."
msgstr ""
"Nunca fue nuestra intención enviarte solo con combatientes apenas "
"entrenados. Entre tus mensajeros estaba una de las propias discípulas de Mal "
"Keshar, una mujer llamada Zynara. Ella está dispuesta a ayudar liderando una "
"nueva horda de no-muertos contra nuestros enemigos para ti."

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:261
msgid ""
"If you agree to help us, we will also make sure to keep you informed of any "
"important events from the main battle front, sending you messages through "
"Valen. You’ll also be able to communicate with us this way."
msgstr ""
"Si aceptas ayudarnos, también nos aseguraremos de mantenerte informado de "
"cualquier evento importante en el frente principal, enviándote mensajes a "
"través de Valen. También podrás comunicarte con nosotros de esta manera."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:270
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"There’s a very important journal we retrieved from the Chaos capital, and "
"Mal Keshar told me before his destruction that he passed it to Kyara, the "
"desert elf, in case neither of us would make it back from the hive. It is my "
"hope that she and Horo are still alive somewhere, or that at the very least "
"they passed the journal to another person. I will agree to lead the "
"expedition on the condition that you also do your best to locate it."
msgstr ""
"Hay un diario muy importante que recuperamos de la capital del Caos, y Mal "
"Keshar me dijo antes de su destrucción que se lo entregó a Kyara, la elfa "
"del desierto, en caso de que ninguno de los dos regresáramos de la colmena. "
"Espero que ella y Horo sigan vivos en algún lugar, o que al menos hayan "
"pasado el diario a otra persona de confianza. Aceptaré liderar la expedición "
"con la condición de que también hagan todo lo posible por localizarlo."

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:275
msgid ""
"That’s a fair deal, although I would first like to know what this journal "
"contains that makes it such a great priority for you, over your reputation "
"and people."
msgstr ""
"Es un trato justo, aunque primero me gustaría saber qué contiene este diario "
"que lo hace tan prioritario para ti, por encima de tu reputación y tu gente."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:280
msgid ""
"Mal Keshar didn’t get a chance to talk with me about the contents of the "
"journal besides the location of the hive, where the heart of Yechnagoth was "
"supposedly stored. Before his destruction, he referred to “a greater cause, "
"one that transcends the fate of Irdya” — I have a feeling that it’s about "
"something he read in it. The journal was written by the Chaos Emperor "
"himself, so the information within should be accurate and relevant for our "
"purposes."
msgstr ""
"Mal Keshar no tuvo oportunidad de hablar conmigo sobre el contenido del "
"diario, salvo por la ubicación de la colmena, donde supuestamente se "
"almacenaba el corazón de Yechnagoth. Antes de su destrucción, se refirió a "
"“una causa mayor, que trasciende el destino de Irdya” — tengo la sensación "
"de que se trata de algo que leyó en él. El diario fue escrito por el propio "
"Emperador del Caos, por lo que la información que contiene debería ser "
"precisa y relevante para nuestros propósitos."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:289
msgid ""
"That is, assuming the heart of the colossal creature we destroyed in Wesmere "
"was truly Yechnagoth’s."
msgstr ""
"Eso es, asumiendo que el corazón de la criatura colosal que destruimos en "
"Wesmere fuera realmente el de Yechnagoth."

#. [message]: speaker=Valen
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:294
msgid "I’ll do whatever it takes to find out about that journal, my lady."
msgstr "Haré lo que sea necesario para averiguar sobre ese diario, mi señora."

#. [message]: speaker=Arnesius
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/03_02_Revelations.cfg:299
msgid ""
"Very well, then. Tomorrow we’ll provide you with further instructions for "
"your mission. We’ll talk with the messengers from Suthwood now."
msgstr ""
"Muy bien, entonces. Mañana te daremos más instrucciones para tu misión. "
"Ahora hablaremos con los mensajeros de Suthwood."

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/storytxt.cfg:108
msgid "Shifting Allegiances"
msgstr "Cambio de Lealtades"

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:51
msgid "team_name^Demons"
msgstr "Demonios"

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:94
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:117
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:199
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:247
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:258
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:271
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:353
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/12_Destiny_part_3.cfg:55
msgid "team_name^Shaxthals"
msgstr "Shaxthals"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:179
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:816
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:237
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:282
msgid "Death of Zynara"
msgstr "Muerte de Zynara"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:266
msgid "It’s really been a long trip. Are we there yet?"
msgstr "Ha sido un viaje muy largo. ¿Ya llegamos?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:271
msgid ""
"No, but we should reach Dalbloom in the middle of the night if we keep our "
"pace and don’t stop to rest."
msgstr ""
"No, pero deberíamos llegar a Dalbloom a medianoche si mantenemos el ritmo y "
"no paramos a descansar."

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:276
msgid ""
"Ah, if you only knew how to use the Ruby’s power to its full extent, we "
"could have avoided all this."
msgstr ""
"Ah, si supieras usar el poder del Rubí en toda su magnitud, podríamos haber "
"evitado todo esto."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:281
msgid "Right. But—"
msgstr "Cierto. Pero—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:290
msgid ""
"<i>(disconcerted)</i> You can’t possibly know about the Ruby of Fire! Who "
"are you?"
msgstr ""
"<i>(desconcertada)</i> ¡No puedes saber nada sobre el Rubí de Fuego! ¿Quién "
"eres?"

#. [message]: speaker=Allyna
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:297
msgid ""
"I’m sorry for lying to you. I really like you, but... I needed you to come "
"here."
msgstr ""
"Perdóname por haberte mentido. Realmente me gustas, pero... necesitaba que "
"vinieras aquí."

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:331
msgid "An impostor!"
msgstr "¡Un impostor!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:336
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I needed to disguise myself as a helpless human girl so I’d be allowed to "
"travel with you and guide you to this place. I beg you to listen to what he "
"has to say, please."
msgstr ""
"No, simplemente necesitaba disfrazarme de una indefensa chica humana para "
"que me permitieran viajar con ustedes y guiarlos hasta aquí."

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:469
msgid "The Lady of Light."
msgstr "La Dama de la Luz."

#. [message]: speaker=Tara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:474
msgid "It is an honor to meet you."
msgstr "Es un honor conocerte."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:479
msgid "What do you want from us?"
msgstr "¿Qué quieren de nosotros?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:484
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Let me be clear: we do not seek an armed confrontation with you and your "
"forces. We just want your staff, or to be more specific, the gem decorating "
"its top: the Ruby of Fire."
msgstr ""
"Solo queremos tu bastón, o para ser más específicos, la gema que adorna su "
"extremo: el Rubí de Fuego."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:489
msgid ""
"You already tried this once and didn’t succeed; what makes you think this "
"time will be any different?"
msgstr ""
"Ya intentaste esto una vez y no tuviste éxito; ¿qué te hace pensar que esta "
"vez será diferente?"

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:494
msgid ""
"My lady, we are wasting precious time here! Let us purge the Northlands of "
"this blight!"
msgstr ""
"Mi señora, ¡estamos perdiendo tiempo valioso aquí! ¡Purguemos las Tierras "
"del Norte de esta plaga!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:499
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The power of the Ruby of Fire is too great and too evil for it to fall into "
"the wrong hands. You fiends shall not obtain it as long as I live. I refuse "
"to listen to any more of your drivel."
msgstr ""
"El poder del Rubí de Fuego es demasiado grande y malvado para que caiga en "
"las manos equivocadas. ¡No lo obtendrán mientras yo viva!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:504
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I was hoping to achieve something with a more civilized approach, but I "
"guess diplomacy has become a thing of the past on this world as well."
msgstr ""
"Así sea entonces. Esperaba lograr algo con un enfoque más civilizado, pero "
"supongo que la diplomacia también se ha vuelto cosa del pasado en este mundo."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:535
msgid "I’m truly sorry. It wasn’t my intention for things to come to this."
msgstr "Lo siento mucho. No era mi intención que las cosas llegaran a esto."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:552
msgid "What... was that?"
msgstr "¿Qué... fue eso?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:557
msgid ""
"I’m not sure. There’s something very... unusual about these demons, aside "
"from the fact that there are two faerie beings allied with them."
msgstr ""
"No estoy segura. Hay algo muy... inusual en estos demonios, aparte del hecho "
"de que hay dos seres feéricos aliados con ellos."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:566
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can now recruit undead units.\n"
"\n"
"However, because Zynara is not as powerful as Mal Keshar, her abilities have "
"certain restrictions: you cannot recruit Vampire Bats, and you may only "
"control a limited number of units from the <b>Ghost</b> line at a time "
"(units in your recall list count towards the limit)."
msgstr ""
"Ahora puedes reclutar unidades no-muertas.\n"
"\n"
"Sin embargo, debido a que Zynara no es tan poderosa como Mal Keshar, sus "
"habilidades tienen ciertas restricciones:\n"
"• No puedes reclutar Murciélagos Vampiro.\n"
"• Zynara solo puede controlar hasta <b>$player_ghost_limit</b> unidades de "
"la línea <b>Fantasma</b> a la vez.\n"
"• Si intentas reclutar un Fantasma adicional, perderás <b>permanentemente</"
"b> el control de una unidad aleatoria de la línea Fantasma y no podrás "
"reclutar —pero sí recordar— más por el resto del escenario.\n"
"• Las unidades de la línea Fantasma en tu lista de recuerdo también cuentan "
"para el límite."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:597
msgid "Did you all hear that?"
msgstr "¿Escucharon eso?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:602
msgid "That’s the sound of bad news — Shaxthal creatures are approaching."
msgstr ""
"Es la señal de malas noticias — Las criaturas Shaxthal se están acercando."

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:684
msgid "They have arrived!"
msgstr "¡Han llegado!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:689
msgid "Curse Uria! They have found us!"
msgstr "¡Maldita sea Uria! ¡Nos han encontrado!"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:700
msgid ""
"Those metallic beasts don’t seem interested in us as much as they are "
"interested in our foes, but why?"
msgstr ""
"Esas bestias metálicas parecen interesarse más por nuestros enemigos que por "
"nosotros, ¿pero por qué?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:705
msgid ""
"Lady of Light, I’d like to call a truce. These creatures are our enemies "
"too, and we don’t really want to get involved in a slaughter."
msgstr ""
"Dama de la Luz, me gustaría proponer una tregua. Estas criaturas también son "
"nuestras enemigas, y realmente no queremos involucrarnos en una masacre."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:710
msgid "Why should my side accede? Don’t you all work for Uria?"
msgstr "¿Por qué debería mi bando acceder? ¿Acaso no trabajan todos para Uria?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:715
msgid "We don’t! We are struggling <i>against</i> her!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡Estamos luchando <i>contra</i> ella!"

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:720
msgid ""
"My lady, those demons cannot be trusted! They must be staging a trap, posing "
"as enemies of Uria!"
msgstr ""
"Mi señora, ¡no se puede confiar en esos demonios! ¡Deben estar tendiendo una "
"trampa, fingiendo ser enemigos de Uria!"

#. [message]: role=doubtful faerie
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:754
msgid ""
"I don’t know, they do seem to have a few of us amongst them. I am fairly "
"sure our kind wouldn’t ally with demons without a very good reason."
msgstr ""
"No lo sé, parece que hay algunos de los nuestros entre ellos. Estoy bastante "
"segura de que nuestra raza no se aliaría con demonios sin una muy buena "
"razón."

#. [message]: role=suspecting human
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:759
msgid "And what if that reason is destroying us? Your kind can’t be trusted!"
msgstr "¿Y si esa razón es destruirnos? ¡No se puede confiar en los tuyos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:766
msgid "My lady?"
msgstr "¿Mi señora?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. This line corresponds to Elynia's thoughts.
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:774
#, fuzzy
msgid "<i>What would Galas and Anlindë have done in this situation?</i>"
msgstr "¿Qué habrían hecho Galas y Anlindë en esta situación?"

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:779
msgid "My lady, you must decide now!"
msgstr "Mi señora, ¡debe decidir ahora!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:788
msgid ""
"Let us cooperate with these strange demons and repel the Shaxthal incursion "
"before they infest the countryside. We’ll decide what to do about them later."
msgstr ""
"Cooperemos con estos extraños demonios y repelamos la incursión Shaxthal "
"antes de que infesten el campo. Decidiremos qué hacer con ellos después."

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:793
msgid ""
"This is ridiculous! My master must have overestimated your ability to "
"command!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto es ridículo! ¡Mi maestro debe haber sobreestimado tu capacidad de "
"mando!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:798
msgid ""
"Your master would have been destroyed if Galas and Anlindë hadn’t been at "
"the command of the elvish troops. They gave him a chance to redeem himself. "
"If it weren’t for that, none of us would be here today discussing this."
msgstr ""
"Tu maestro habría sido destruido si Galas y Anlindë no hubieran estado al "
"mando de las tropas élficas. Le dieron una oportunidad de redimirse. Si no "
"fuera por eso, ninguno de nosotros estaría aquí hoy discutiendo esto."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:803
msgid "Very well, let’s do this!"
msgstr "Muy bien, ¡hagámoslo!"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:812
msgid "Repel the Shaxthal incursion"
msgstr "Repeler la incursión Shaxthal"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:817
msgid "Death of Elorran"
msgstr "Muerte de Elorran"

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:834
msgid ""
"My people! Now that Uria knows we are plotting against her, they are doomed "
"without my guidance!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mi gente! Ahora que Uria sabe que estamos conspirando contra ella, están "
"condenados sin mi guía."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:855
msgid "Fort Dalbloom"
msgstr "Fuerte Dalbloom"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:874
msgid "Yes! We did it! We did it together!"
msgstr "¡Sí! ¡Lo logramos! ¡Lo hicimos juntos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:879
msgid ""
"Am I right in assuming that the village of Dalbloom doesn’t truly exist "
"anymore, and it’s just the name of an ancient stronghold from the times "
"before the Fall?"
msgstr ""
"¿Estoy en lo cierto al suponer que la aldea Dalbloom ya no existe realmente, "
"y que es solo el nombre de una antigua fortaleza de los tiempos anteriores a "
"la Caída?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:884
msgid ""
"That’s right. We needed you to come here, away from the Alliance’s troops, "
"and away from the Chaos forces. Or at least, we <i>thought</i> they would "
"not be roaming around these parts. It’s alarming that their war beasts have "
"come this far within the human country."
msgstr ""
"Así es. Necesitábamos que vinieras aquí, lejos de las tropas de la Alianza y "
"de las fuerzas del Caos. O al menos <i>pensábamos</i> que no deambularían "
"por estos territorios. Es alarmante que sus bestias de guerra hayan llegado "
"tan lejos dentro del territorio humano."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:896
msgid ""
"May I know why you believe acquiring the Ruby of Fire will do good to your "
"cause, whatever it is?"
msgstr ""
"¿Puedo saber por qué creen que adquirir el Rubí de Fuego beneficiará su "
"causa, sea cual sea?"

#. [message]: speaker=Tara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:901
msgid ""
"My lady, Elorran is one of the few demon lords who refused to heed Uria’s "
"call to war against the good peoples of Irdya. He came to me seeking support "
"for his mission. Our intention was to contact you and destroy that artifact "
"you hold."
msgstr ""
"Mi señora, Elorran es uno de los pocos señores demonio que se negó a atender "
"el llamado de Uria a la guerra contra los pueblos justos de Irdya. Vino a mí "
"buscando apoyo para su misión. Nuestra intención era contactarte y destruir "
"ese artefacto que posees."

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:906
msgid ""
"According to what Anya heard, you set foot in the Kalari stronghold once, "
"and confronted the Iron Council."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:911
msgid "More like they decided to bring us there against our will. Go on."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:921
msgid ""
"The many Gatekeepers were created from the ancient Guardian of Secrets, "
"Uria’s sister. They were assigned to different locations to protect them "
"from external interference, preventing anything from entering or leaving "
"Inferno. Uria has figured this out, and she wants the Ruby of Fire to create "
"a path to allow her to enter and invade a world much like yours, called "
"Ethea. We do not know yet what her motives are — there may be something "
"there which she could use against the few remaining gods who may oppose her."
msgstr ""
"Los muchos Guardianes de la Puerta fueron creados a partir del antiguo "
"Guardián de los Secretos, la hermana de Uria. Fueron asignados a diferentes "
"lugares para protegerlos de interferencias externas, impidiendo que algo "
"entrara o saliera del Infierno. Uria se ha dado cuenta de esto y quiere el "
"Rubí de Fuego para crear un camino que le permita entrar e invadir un mundo "
"muy parecido al tuyo, llamado Ethea. Aún no sabemos cuáles son sus motivos; "
"puede que haya algo allí que pueda usar contra los pocos dioses restantes "
"que podrían oponerse a ella."

#. [message]: speaker=Tara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:926
msgid ""
"To that end she is using Irdya to test her forces and breed a massive army "
"of biomechanical creatures for use against those who will defend Ethea."
msgstr ""
"Para ello está usando Irdya para probar sus fuerzas y criar un ejército "
"masivo de criaturas biomecánicas para usar contra quienes defiendan Ethea."

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:931
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Although some of us think the right being <i>could</i> use the power of the "
"Ruby to destroy or incapacitate Uria, nobody wants to risk delivering such a "
"precious asset to her by failing in a suicidal mission. Hence we want to "
"destroy it."
msgstr ""
"Aunque algunos de nosotros creen que el ser correcto <i>podría</i> usar el "
"poder del Rubí para destruir o incapacitar a Uria, nadie quiere correr el "
"riesgo y entregar inconscientemente el artefacto a ella al fracasar en una "
"misión tan suicida. Por eso queremos destruirlo."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:936
msgid "We really need your help..."
msgstr "Realmente necesitamos tu ayuda..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:945
msgid ""
"The Ruby of Fire— this staff, originally owned by my master, the Great "
"Sorceress Niryone... it belongs to me. I have sacrificed much keeping it "
"away from those who could threaten the future of the peoples of Irdya. "
"Surely we can thwart Uria’s plans in a different way."
msgstr ""
"El Rubí de Fuego — este bastón, originalmente perteneciente a mi maestra, la "
"Gran Hechicera Niryone... me pertenece a mí. He sacrificado mucho para "
"mantenerlo alejado de quienes podrían amenazar el futuro de los pueblos de "
"Irdya. Seguramente podemos frustrar los planes de Uria de otra manera."

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:950
msgid ""
"We aren’t the only group that has stood against her rule, but we are one of "
"the few to survive to this day. We’ve seen her real power, and only the "
"wielder of the Union could possibly stand a chance against her — if only "
"that power hadn’t fallen into her hands following your short incursion into "
"her territory."
msgstr ""
"No somos el único grupo que se ha opuesto a su dominio, pero somos de los "
"pocos que han sobrevivido hasta hoy. Hemos visto su verdadero poder, y solo "
"el portador de la Unión podría tener alguna oportunidad contra ella — si es "
"que ese poder no hubiera caído en sus manos después de tu breve incursión en "
"su territorio."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:955
msgid "What do you mean— she cannot use that power, right?"
msgstr "¿Qué quieres decir — que ella no puede usar ese poder, verdad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:960
msgid "Not yet..."
msgstr "Todavía no..."

#. [message]: speaker=Tara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:965
msgid ""
"What she expects to find on Ethea may be another artifact that could enable "
"her to wield the Union."
msgstr ""
"Lo que espera encontrar en Ethea podría ser otro artefacto que le permita "
"empuñar la Unión."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:970
msgid ""
"I’m not convinced destroying the Ruby is the solution. What if there’s an "
"equivalent somewhere else on Irdya, or on another world?"
msgstr ""
"No estoy convencida de que destruir el Rubí sea la solución. ¿Y si hay un "
"equivalente en otro lugar de Irdya, o en otro mundo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:975
msgid ""
"That’s a risk we’ll have to take. As things stand right now, Uria <i>is</i> "
"more likely to obtain the Ruby than any other alternative in order to "
"accelerate her plans."
msgstr ""
"Es un riesgo que tendremos que correr. Tal como están las cosas ahora, Uria "
"<i>es</i> más probable que obtenga el Rubí que cualquier otra alternativa "
"para acelerar sus planes."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:984
msgid ""
"The elves... the people whom I swore to protect ages ago need me at this "
"very moment. Let me use the power of the Ruby once more, and then we’ll make "
"sure it will never be used again."
msgstr ""
"Los elfos... el pueblo al que juré proteger hace siglos me necesita en este "
"mismo momento. Déjenme usar el poder del Rubí una vez más, y luego nos "
"aseguraremos de que nunca se use de nuevo."

#. [message]: speaker=Tara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:993
#, fuzzy
msgid "Elorran, I fear we won’t be able to convince her."
msgstr "Señor, no podremos convencerla de hacer lo contrario."

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:998
msgid ""
"<i>(sighs)</i> Your tenacity has not gone unnoticed, Lady of Light. Uria "
"knows you are a formidable enemy, albeit notably foolish at times. Do what "
"you feel is right, and then come back to us as soon as you may so we can put "
"an end to her plans together. Anya will go with you; her necklace will allow "
"you to find us, no matter the distance or the time."
msgstr ""
"<i>(suspira)</i> Tu tenacidad no ha pasado desapercibida, Dama de la Luz. "
"Uria sabe que eres una enemiga formidable, aunque a veces bastante "
"imprudente. Haz lo que creas correcto, y luego regresa con nosotros tan "
"pronto como puedas para poner fin a sus planes juntos. Anya irá contigo; su "
"collar te permitirá encontrarnos, sin importar la distancia o el tiempo."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:1003
msgid "I will... go with her? Yes! I mean... if that’s not a problem."
msgstr "¿Iré... con ella? ¡Sí! Quiero decir... si eso no es un problema."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:1008
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We are heading towards a war zone and we welcome the support of every man or "
"woman who can wield a weapon, cast a spell, or tend to the injured. However, "
"I am... unsure about allowing such a young girl to accompany us."
msgstr ""
"Nos dirigimos hacia una zona de guerra y damos la bienvenida al apoyo de "
"todo hombre o mujer que pueda empuñar un arma, lanzar un hechizo o atender a "
"los heridos. Sin embargo, no estoy... segura de permitir que una joven como "
"Anya nos acompañe."

#. [message]: speaker=Tara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:1013
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You might underestimate her now because making use of her magic before would "
"have blown her cover, but I assure you, she is a most excellent spellcaster, "
"even better than me."
msgstr ""
"Podrías subestimarla ahora porque usar su magia antes habría descubierto su "
"disfraz, pero te aseguro que es una excelente hechicera bajo las "
"circunstancias adecuadas."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:1018
msgid ""
"(<i>blushing</i>) Ahhhh, don’t say that! I’m not that impressive, especially "
"compared to her..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:1023
msgid ""
"Very well, Lord Elorran. I swear I will do my best to keep the Ruby away "
"from our enemies."
msgstr ""
"Muy bien, Lord Elorran. Juro que haré todo lo posible para mantener el Rubí "
"lejos de nuestros enemigos."

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:1028
msgid "Dealing with demons... (<i>sigh</i>) This can’t end well..."
msgstr "Tratar con demonios... (<i>suspira</i>) Esto no puede terminar bien..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:1033
msgid ""
"I would like to keep our pact a secret between us. Even if the Grand Council "
"understood, there seems to be a fair chance they could fall and provide "
"Uria’s henchmen with information about our plans. No-one should speak of "
"this."
msgstr ""
"Me gustaría mantener nuestro pacto en secreto entre nosotros. Incluso si el "
"Gran Consejo lo entendiera, hay una buena posibilidad de que caigan y "
"proporcionen a los secuaces de Uria información sobre nuestros planes. Nadie "
"debería hablar de esto."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:1038
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:374
msgid "Understood, my lady."
msgstr "Entendido, mi señora."

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:1043
msgid "Understood..."
msgstr "Entendido..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:1048
msgid ""
"Well, let’s continue onwards. Hopefully we won’t come across any more "
"interruptions."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, continuemos. Espero que no nos encontremos con más interrupciones."

#. [message]: speaker=Elorran
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/04_Shifting_Allegiances.cfg:1082
msgid ""
"There is an army of hostile elves approaching... Things would have worked "
"out much better if this Lady of Light had not turned out to be such a "
"dreadful disappointment as a leader and a tactician."
msgstr ""
"Se acerca un ejército de elfos hostiles... Las cosas habrían ido mucho mejor "
"si esta Dama de la Luz no hubiera resultado ser una decepción tan terrible "
"como líder y táctica."

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/storytxt.cfg:131
msgid "The Eastern Front"
msgstr "El Frente Oriental"

