#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1169
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/02_01_Return_to_Raelthyn.cfg:671
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:534
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/04_01_Outpost_of_Hell.cfg:663
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/05_Pass_of_Sorrows.cfg:282
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/05_Pass_of_Sorrows.cfg:639
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/05_Pass_of_Sorrows.cfg:950
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:635
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1630
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08B_Destiny_part_1.cfg:291
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08B_Destiny_part_1.cfg:690
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08B_Destiny_part_1.cfg:1216
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:475
msgid "Death of Anya"
msgstr "Muerte de Anya"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:267
msgid "There are so many different flowers in this field! It’s beautiful!"
msgstr "¡Hay tantas flores diferentes en este campo! ¡Es hermoso!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:272
msgid "Indeed it is."
msgstr "Así es."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:291
msgid ""
"My lady, there are encampments ahead, apparently occupied by elves! This "
"doesn’t look right!"
msgstr ""
"Mi señora, hay campamentos más adelante, ¡aparentemente ocupados por elfos! "
"Esto no parece correcto."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:326
msgid ""
"Certainly not — they shouldn’t be this close to Aragwaithi territory, so I "
"presume they belong to the hostile faction. Everyone prepare for battle, and "
"let’s hope for the best."
msgstr ""
"Ciertamente no deberían estar tan cerca del territorio Aragwaithi, así que "
"supongo que pertenecen a la facción hostil. Todos prepárense para la batalla "
"y esperemos lo mejor."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:351
msgid "May the Lords of Light protect us..."
msgstr "Que los Señores de la Luz nos protejan..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:361
msgid "They have assembled an army!"
msgstr "¡Han reunido un ejército!"

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:371
msgid ""
"Not just that, but they also have support from the metallic creatures of "
"Uria!"
msgstr ""
"¡Y no solo eso, sino que también cuentan con el apoyo de las criaturas "
"metálicas de Uria!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:381
msgid "My lady, what do you suggest we do?"
msgstr "Mi señora, ¿qué sugiere que hagamos?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:386
msgid ""
"I wish we could just entirely avoid casualties, but that’s not going to "
"happen."
msgstr ""
"Ojalá pudiéramos evitar por completo las bajas, pero eso no va a suceder."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:395
msgid ""
"I fear for the fate of the elves who sent that call for help to the "
"Council..."
msgstr ""
"Temo por el destino de los elfos que enviaron esa petición de ayuda al "
"Consejo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Telan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:407
msgid "Who is it that dares defy the power of the Lady of Light?"
msgstr "¿Quién se atreve a desafiar el poder de la Dama de la Luz?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:412
msgid ""
"You, I presume. I am the only Lady of Light that there is on Irdya, and you "
"have been deceived into fighting against me and the Grand Council of the "
"Northern Peoples in favor of a dark cause, one that betrays the memory of "
"our civilization and our leaders."
msgstr ""
"Tú, supongo. Soy la única Dama de la Luz que existe en Irdya, y has sido "
"engañada para luchar contra mí y contra el Gran Consejo de los Pueblos del "
"Norte en favor de una causa oscura, una que traiciona la memoria de nuestra "
"civilización y de nuestros líderes."

#. [message]: speaker=Telan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:417
msgid ""
"You are nothing but a blatant impostor working for the human bastards — a "
"dirty, treacherous impostor!"
msgstr ""
"¡No eres más que una descarada impostora que trabaja para esos malditos "
"humanos: una impostora sucia y traidora!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:422
msgid "Take her back to the encampment! I need to ask a few questions..."
msgstr "¡Llévenla de vuelta al campamento! Necesito hacer algunas preguntas..."

#. [message]: speaker=Telan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:427
msgid "I refuse to answer to the likes of you!"
msgstr "¡Me niego a responderle a alguien como tú!"

#. [message]: speaker=Unidë
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:449
msgid "The traitors... they have slain me..."
msgstr "Los traidores... me han asesinado..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:461
msgid ""
"Those elves who willingly choose to support the forces that seek to destroy "
"our world don’t deserve to live."
msgstr ""
"Los elfos que eligen apoyar voluntariamente a las fuerzas que buscan "
"destruir nuestro mundo no merecen vivir."

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:466
msgid "(<i>mumbling</i>) That seems rather hypocritical coming from you."
msgstr "(<i>murmurando</i>) Eso suena bastante hipócrita viniendo de ti."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:471
msgid "I can hear you, Zynara."
msgstr "Puedo oírte, Zynara."

#. [message]: speaker=Ethanin-Adrael
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:487
msgid "I shall not fall today!"
msgstr "¡Hoy no caeré!"

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:501
msgid "He’s escaping!"
msgstr "¡Está escapando!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:625
msgid "How do you do that, girl?"
msgstr "¿Cómo haces eso, niña?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:630
msgid "Do what?"
msgstr "¿Hacer qué?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:635
msgid ""
"You seem able to heal your own wounds without any effort. I haven’t heard of "
"other faeries of the deep forest having that power."
msgstr ""
"Parece que puedes sanar tus propias heridas sin ningún esfuerzo. No he oído "
"de otras hadas del bosque profundo con ese poder."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:640
msgid "Ah. Well, I have had this ability for as long as I can remember."
msgstr "Ah. Bueno, he tenido esta habilidad desde que tengo memoria."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:660
msgid ""
"This conflict didn’t begin just now. When Galas and I last visited the "
"northern country, a civil war was already raging due to Inodien’s death. The "
"rumors pointed at the Iron Council’s intrusion in our lands and affairs, but "
"we didn’t have the opportunity to confirm anything."
msgstr ""
"Este conflicto no comenzó recién ahora. Cuando Galas y yo visitamos por "
"última vez el país del norte, ya se libraba una guerra civil debido a la "
"muerte de Inodien. Los rumores apuntaban a la intrusión del Consejo de "
"Hierro en nuestras tierras y asuntos, pero no tuvimos la oportunidad de "
"confirmar nada."

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:665
msgid ""
"Ah, the struggle that resulted in the banishment of the elves from the "
"country. I remember that."
msgstr ""
"Ah, la lucha que resultó en el destierro de los elfos del país. Lo recuerdo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:670
msgid ""
"Much elvish blood has been shed today. I swear that whoever is behind this "
"shall pay with their own life — no matter what it takes."
msgstr ""
"Hoy se ha derramado mucha sangre élfica. Juro que quien esté detrás de esto "
"pagará con su propia vida, cueste lo que cueste."

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:756
msgid "Elynia! I’m so glad to see you again after so long..."
msgstr "¡Elynia! Me alegra tanto verte de nuevo después de tanto tiempo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:761
msgid ""
"Unarye, what happened? We were heading towards the eastern forest to meet "
"with you when we stumbled upon this incursion. How could our enemies advance "
"this far?"
msgstr ""
"Unarye, ¿qué ocurrió? Íbamos hacia el bosque oriental para reunirnos contigo "
"cuando nos topamos con esta incursión. ¿Cómo pudieron nuestros enemigos "
"avanzar tanto?"

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:766
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Indeed we owe you a few explanations, and I apologize for arriving late, but "
"our forces have been severely weakened. Come with me, and I’ll explain all."
msgstr ""
"Ciertamente te debemos unas cuantas explicaciones, y lamento no haber podido "
"llegar antes, pero nuestras fuerzas han quedado severamente debilitadas. Ven "
"conmigo y te lo explicaré todo."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:771
msgid "My lady, do you know this elf?"
msgstr "Mi señora, ¿conoce a esta elfa?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:776
msgid ""
"She is one of Galas’ friends, Unarye, and she’s been collaborating with the "
"Grand Council ever since we left to infiltrate the Empire. I know she can be "
"trusted. Now, let’s go."
msgstr ""
"Es una de las amigas de Galas, Unarye, y ha estado colaborando con el Gran "
"Consejo desde que partimos a infiltrarnos en el Imperio. Sé que es de "
"confianza. Ahora, vamos."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:786
msgid ""
"My lady, I’ve just heard rumors that the elves are already advancing towards "
"Raelthyn."
msgstr ""
"Mi señora, acabo de oír rumores de que los elfos ya están avanzando hacia "
"Raelthyn."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front.cfg:791
msgid ""
"That explains why they haven’t crushed us yet despite our poor performance. "
"This was a foolish move. It’s best that we fall back to aid in the defense "
"of the central region, quickly."
msgstr ""
"Eso explica por qué no nos han aplastado aún, pese a nuestro pobre "
"desempeño. Ha sido un movimiento insensato. Lo mejor será retroceder para "
"ayudar en la defensa de la región central, rápidamente."

#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/storytxt.cfg:131
msgid "The Plan"
msgstr "El Plan"

#. [unit]: type=Elvish Lord, id=Lord Ardamién
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:77
msgid "Lord Ardamién"
msgstr "Lord Ardamién"

#. [unit]: type=Elvish Shyde, id=Miryath
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:90
msgid "Miryath"
msgstr "Miryath"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:133
msgid ""
"Everyone here is restless, and the elvish leader is nowhere to be seen..."
msgstr ""
"Todos aquí están inquietos, y la líder élfica no aparece por ninguna parte..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:138
msgid "Ah, here she comes!"
msgstr "¡Ah, ahí viene!"

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:157
msgid "I apologize once again for keeping you all waiting."
msgstr "Les pido disculpas una vez más por haberlos hecho esperar."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:162
msgid "It’s no problem, really."
msgstr "No hay problema, en serio."

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:167
msgid ""
"The reason we moved out of the way to the Aragwaith country is that we "
"originally thought our fallen kin would chase us and leave the humans alone. "
"As we all just saw, of course, we were mistaken. Our own people have managed "
"to retrieve some valuable information from the enemy settlements, though. "
"Listen carefully..."
msgstr ""
"La razón por la que nos apartamos hacia el país de los Aragwaithi fue que "
"originalmente pensamos que nuestros parientes caídos nos perseguirían y "
"dejarían a los humanos en paz. Como acabamos de ver, por supuesto, estábamos "
"equivocados. Sin embargo, nuestra gente ha logrado obtener información "
"valiosa de los asentamientos enemigos. Escuchen con atención..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:172
msgid "We are listening, my friend."
msgstr "Te escuchamos, amiga mía."

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:177
msgid ""
"The impostor who calls herself the Lady of Light has amassed a varied army "
"of elves, humans, barbarians and Shaxthal creatures, apparently as part of a "
"plan to reorganize the Chaos forces and strike the human country from the "
"east while keeping their troops busy in the west. Not only have they gotten "
"support from Inodien’s successors, but they have also made contact with "
"elvish and human barbarians from lands farther to the east — peoples whose "
"existence was unknown to us thus far."
msgstr ""
"La impostora que se hace llamar la Dama de la Luz ha reunido un ejército "
"variado de elfos, humanos, bárbaros y criaturas Shaxthal, aparentemente como "
"parte de un plan para reorganizar las fuerzas del Caos y atacar el país "
"humano desde el este mientras mantienen sus tropas ocupadas en el oeste. No "
"solo han conseguido el apoyo de los sucesores de Inodien, sino que también "
"han establecido contacto con bárbaros élficos y humanos de tierras más "
"orientales, pueblos cuya existencia desconocíamos hasta ahora."

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:182
msgid ""
"Their base of operations is said to be located in Telchior’s Hold in the "
"Valley of Elynia — the very place whence we fled under Galas’ command "
"following the Chaos invasion. Something deeply wrong must have occurred "
"there after our departure. As I recall, the last time we met you mentioned "
"that Lord Lédinor was possessed by Uria."
msgstr ""
"Se dice que su base de operaciones se encuentra en el Bastión de Telchior, "
"en el Valle de Elynia: el mismo lugar del que huimos bajo el mando de Galas "
"tras la invasión del Caos. Algo muy grave debe de haber ocurrido allí "
"después de nuestra partida. Según recuerdo, la última vez que nos vimos "
"mencionaste que el Lord Lédinor estaba poseído por Uria."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:187
msgid "That’s correct, indeed."
msgstr "Así es, en efecto."

#. [message]: speaker=Lord Ardamién
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:192
msgid ""
"The information we have could be a fabrication intended to mislead us into "
"thinking the valley has some relevance in the greater scheme of things, but "
"it’s not possible to disregard the danger this foul new alliance poses. If "
"the northern lands fall now, the Chaos Empire will have won the war even "
"without their Emperor or capital."
msgstr ""
"La información que tenemos podría ser una farsa destinada a engañarnos para "
"que pensemos que el valle tiene alguna relevancia en el esquema mayor de las "
"cosas, pero no es posible ignorar el peligro que representa esta vil nueva "
"alianza. Si las tierras del norte caen ahora, el Imperio del Caos habrá "
"ganado la guerra aun sin su Emperador ni su capital."

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:197
msgid ""
"We are in the middle of restructuring our forces to protect the eastern "
"front for as long as we can, even if the Grand Council isn’t available to "
"coordinate efforts with us."
msgstr ""
"Estamos en medio de la reestructuración de nuestras fuerzas para proteger el "
"frente oriental tanto tiempo como podamos, incluso si el Gran Consejo no "
"está disponible para coordinar esfuerzos con nosotros."

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:202
msgid ""
"Elynia, you lead many capable warriors and you have the support of the "
"undead. If you could infiltrate the valley in the meantime and vanquish the "
"impostor, we could put an end to the war on this front."
msgstr ""
"Elynia, diriges a muchos guerreros capaces y cuentas con el apoyo de los no-"
"muertos. Si pudieras infiltrarte en el valle mientras tanto y derrotar a la "
"impostora, podríamos poner fin a la guerra en este frente."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:207
msgid ""
"But... I know nothing of the valley other than that it lies in the middle of "
"the desert — fighting in such an environment could be disastrous!"
msgstr ""
"Pero... no sé nada del valle, salvo que está en medio del desierto. "
"¡Combatir en un entorno así podría ser desastroso!"

#. [message]: speaker=Miryath
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:212
msgid ""
"The impersonator is a coward and she isn’t going to lead her minions on the "
"front line. If anything can be done about her, it’ll have to be at her base."
msgstr ""
"La suplantadora es una cobarde y no va a liderar a sus secuaces en la línea "
"del frente. Si puede hacerse algo contra ella, tendrá que ser en su base."

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:217
msgid ""
"You are a powerful warrior and you have more experience in these matters "
"than any of us present. You helped Galas and Mal Keshar infiltrate the Chaos "
"Empire before. I’m sure you will be successful in this task."
msgstr ""
"Eres una guerrera poderosa y tienes más experiencia en estos asuntos que "
"cualquiera de los presentes. Antes ayudaste a Galas y Mal Keshar a "
"infiltrarse en el Imperio del Caos. Estoy segura de que tendrás éxito en "
"esta tarea."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:226
msgid ""
"Very well. We’ll travel to your old home to purge this plague and strike "
"down the false Lady of Light."
msgstr ""
"Muy bien. Viajaremos a tu antiguo hogar para purgar esta plaga y derrotar a "
"la falsa Dama de la Luz."

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:231
msgid ""
"Thank you, Elynia — thank you all. I’m sure that under your command the "
"mission will be a success. Now, I must go to discuss our plans with our "
"field commanders."
msgstr ""
"Gracias, Elynia. Gracias a todos. Estoy segura de que bajo tu mando la "
"misión será un éxito. Ahora debo irme a discutir nuestros planes con los "
"comandantes de campo."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:253
msgid "But, my lady, the Ruby! What if it’s a trap?"
msgstr "Pero, mi señora, ¡el Rubí! ¿Y si es una trampa?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:258
msgid ""
"We’ll have to deal with the trap if that’s the case. This is more important!"
msgstr ""
"Tendremos que lidiar con la trampa si ese es el caso. ¡Esto es más "
"importante!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:263
msgid "But Elorran is waiting for us!"
msgstr "¡Pero Elorran nos está esperando!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:268
msgid "Please inform him of our next mission and convince him to be patient."
msgstr ""
"Por favor, infórmale de nuestra próxima misión y convéncelo de ser paciente."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/05_The_Eastern_Front_cutscene.cfg:273
msgid "... Very well, then..."
msgstr "... Está bien, entonces..."

#. [scenario]: type=Errant Soul
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/storytxt.cfg:160
msgid "The Voyage Home"
msgstr "El Viaje a Casa"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Pigork
#. [side]: type=Orcish Slayer, id=Bratar
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:41
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:67
msgid "team_name^Orcs"
msgstr "Orcos"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Pigork
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:55
msgid "Pigork"
msgstr "Pigork"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Slayer, id=Bratar
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:81
msgid "Bratar"
msgstr "Bratar"

#. [unit]: type=Goblin Rouser, id=Vultraz
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:91
msgid "Vultraz"
msgstr "Vultraz"

#. [unit]: type=Goblin Impaler, id=Gargaz
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:105
msgid "Gargaz"
msgstr "Gargaz"

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:119
msgid "team_name^Desert Creatures"
msgstr "Criaturas del desierto"

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:176
msgid "team_name^Desert Spirits"
msgstr "Espíritus del desierto"

#. [label]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:195
msgid "Mount Boombadil"
msgstr "Monte Boombadil"

#. [label]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:200
msgid "Fort Gralseth"
msgstr "Fuerte Gralseth"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:277
msgid ""
"Secure the orcish settlement to the southeast by defeating all enemy leaders"
msgstr ""
"Asegura el asentamiento orco al sureste derrotando a todos los líderes "
"enemigos"

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:301
msgid "The desert... I never thought I’d have to see it again."
msgstr "El desierto... Nunca pensé que tendría que verlo otra vez."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:306
msgid "Ugh. I feel unwell in these dry and bright lands."
msgstr "Ugh. Me siento mal en estas tierras secas y luminosas."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:311
msgid ""
"It can’t be helped. Dark faeries are frail creatures that revel in the "
"shadows of the greatest and densest forests. Really, the desert is no place "
"for you. I am sorry for dragging you along."
msgstr ""
"No hay remedio. Las hadas oscuras son criaturas frágiles que disfrutan de "
"las sombras de los bosques más grandes y densos. En realidad, el desierto no "
"es un lugar para ti. Lamento haberte arrastrado hasta aquí."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:316
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh, my lady, it’s not like I’m going to melt away from a little excess "
"sunlight. I just need some time to adapt to this environment, that’s all."
msgstr ""
"Oh, mi señora, no se preocupe por mí. Solo necesito algo de tiempo para "
"adaptarme a este entorno, nada más."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:321
msgid ""
"My lady, if you’ll allow me to complain... we can’t just march across the "
"desert without stopping to rest!"
msgstr ""
"Mi señora, si me permite quejarme... ¡no podemos simplemente atravesar el "
"desierto sin detenernos a descansar!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:333
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The scouts reported the presence of orcs bearing the Chaos banner in a "
"settlement ahead to the southeast, in the Gralseth region. Stopping to rest "
"here would be very risky with those fools around, but perhaps we could force "
"them out and replenish our supplies."
msgstr ""
"Los exploradores informaron sobre la presencia de orcos portando la bandera "
"del Caos en un asentamiento al sureste, en la región de Gralseth. Detenernos "
"a descansar aquí sería muy arriesgado con esos insensatos cerca, pero tal "
"vez podríamos asegurar su asentamiento y reponer provisiones."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:338
msgid "Excellent!"
msgstr "¡Excelente!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:343
msgid ""
"A word of caution, though. Ever since the Fall, the many victims of the "
"disasters which devastated Irdya have been endlessly wandering across lands "
"like this, preying on the souls of the living."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, una advertencia: desde la Caída, las muchas víctimas de los "
"desastres que devastaron Irdya han estado vagando sin descanso por tierras "
"como esta, acechando las almas de los vivos."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:365
msgid ""
"They are particularly weak by themselves and our arcane fire should be "
"enough to banish them from our world. However, our less experienced fighters "
"should not take their chances fighting them alone."
msgstr ""
"Son especialmente débiles por sí mismos, y nuestro fuego arcano debería ser "
"suficiente para expulsarlos de nuestro mundo. Sin embargo, nuestros "
"combatientes menos experimentados no deberían arriesgarse a enfrentarlos "
"solos."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:379
msgid "Time to get moving."
msgstr "Es hora de avanzar."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:414
msgid "I banish you from this world! Go now to your deserved rest!"
msgstr "¡Te destierro de este mundo! Ve ahora a tu merecido descanso."

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:420
msgid "Begone, wandering spirit!"
msgstr "¡Fuera, espíritu errante!"

#. [floating_text]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:447
msgid "banished"
msgstr "desterrado"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:466
msgid ""
"Oooooh, gryphon eggs! If we take them and let them hatch, do you think we "
"would be able to train gryphon mounts so we can take them to battle? I heard "
"that a famous prince in the Golden Age did that and then won against the "
"evil queen while riding the largest gryphon ever seen!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:471
msgid ""
"I think the desert heat is getting to your head, girl. Perhaps you should "
"refresh yourself at the river for a bit?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:476
msgid "B— but... I swear it’s true!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:495
msgid ""
"Ahhhh... There’s no feeling like putting my feet under refreshing, flowing "
"water... I miss the northern forests..."
msgstr ""
"Ahhhh... No hay nada como poner los pies en agua fresca y corriente... "
"Extraño los bosques del norte..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:500
msgid ""
"Where do you come from, anyway? You couldn’t have spent your whole life "
"traveling with Elorran and Tara."
msgstr ""
"¿De dónde vienes, por cierto? No pudiste haber pasado toda tu vida viajando "
"con Elorran y Tara."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:511
msgid "Oh... Of course not. It’s just... it’s complicated."
msgstr "Oh... Por supuesto que no. Es solo que... es complicado."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:522
msgid ""
"If you don’t feel like telling me more about yourself right now, I can "
"understand — I’m just curious, that’s all."
msgstr ""
"Si no tienes ganas de contarme más sobre ti ahora, lo entiendo; solo tengo "
"curiosidad, nada más."

#. [message]: speaker=Bratar
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:530
msgid ""
"Chief! The faerie! The faerie and her pets are approaching from the "
"northwest!"
msgstr "¡Jefe! ¡El hada! ¡El hada y sus mascotas se acercan desde el noroeste!"

#. [message]: speaker=Pigork
#. "Necromancer" should be translated in a gender neutral fashion
#. if possible to keep their identity ambiguous (there are two
#. necromancers in the Iron Council, one is female (Mal Kendria)
#. and the other is male (Mal Hekuba).
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:539
msgid ""
"Ah, just as the necromancer told us. Excellent news. More meat for our "
"wolves!"
msgstr ""
"Ah, tal como nos dijo el nigromante. Excelentes noticias. ¡Más carne para "
"nuestros lobos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Vultraz
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:545
msgid "Yes, more meat for our pigs! Er— I mean wolves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sí, más carne para nuestros cerdos! Er... quiero decir, ¡para nuestros "
"lobos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:595
msgid "A sandstorm! We won’t be able to continue marching like this!"
msgstr "¡Una tormenta de arena! ¡No podremos seguir avanzando así!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:600
msgid "This small inconvenience shall not stop us! Onwards!"
msgstr "¡Esta pequeña molestia no nos detendrá! ¡Adelante!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:608
msgid "My lady, are you sure this is a good plan?"
msgstr "Mi señora, ¿está segura de que este es un buen plan?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:613
msgid ""
"It’s better than tarrying here for too long, so it’s good enough for me!"
msgstr ""
"Es mejor que quedarnos aquí demasiado tiempo, así que para mí es suficiente."

#. [message]: speaker=Vultraz
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:626
msgid "Eaaaagh..."
msgstr "¡Eaaaagh...!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gargaz
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:638
msgid "Argh! No!"
msgstr "¡Argh! ¡No!"

#. [message]: speaker=Bratar
#. "Send our messenger back to the valley, immediately!"
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:651
msgid "They are more than we expected! Send our messenger back to—"
msgstr ""
"¡Son más de los que esperábamos! ¡Envía a nuestro mensajero de vuelta a—!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:672
msgid "Blast it! Their messenger escaped!"
msgstr "¡Maldición! ¡Su mensajero escapó!"

#. [message]: speaker=Pigork
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:684
msgid "... useless... insects..."
msgstr "... inútiles... insectos..."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:699
#, fuzzy
msgid "You retrieve 104 pieces of gold."
msgstr "Recoges 170 piezas de oro."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:717
msgid "Maybe this wasn’t such a good idea after all."
msgstr "Quizás, después de todo, no fue tan buena idea."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:722
msgid ""
"I wasn’t counting on that messenger and his swift mount. Regardless, our "
"presence here was both predicted and awaited — this decidedly spells bad "
"news."
msgstr ""
"No contaba con ese mensajero y su veloz montura. De todos modos, nuestra "
"presencia aquí fue prevista y esperada; esto sin duda trae malas noticias."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:727
msgid "But I told you so!"
msgstr "¡Pero se lo advertí!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:732
msgid ""
"I <i>did</i> expect a trap from the very beginning too, girl. We— I have "
"been in situations like this before..."
msgstr ""
"Yo también <i>esperaba</i> una trampa desde el principio, niña. Yo... he "
"estado en situaciones así antes..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:737
msgid "But this time I won’t let them succeed."
msgstr "Pero esta vez no permitiré que tengan éxito."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/06_The_Voyage_Home.cfg:745
msgid ""
"Valen just informed me that the impostor’s forces are advancing towards "
"Raelthyn. That can only mean Unarye and her troops fell in battle. This is "
"hopeless."
msgstr ""
"Valen acaba de informarme que las fuerzas de la impostora avanzan hacia "
"Raelthyn. Eso solo puede significar que Unarye y sus tropas cayeron en "
"combate. Esto no tiene esperanza."

#. [scenario]: id=Elynia
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/storytxt.cfg:180
msgid "Proximus"
msgstr "Proximus"

#. [side]
#. [side]: type=Chocobone, id=General Lorelath
#. [side]: type=Elvish Hero, id=Cithraldin
#. [side]: type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Gerumanen
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:72
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:92
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:131
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:165
msgid "team_name^Northern Defense Line"
msgstr "Línea de defensa norte"

#. [side]: type=Chocobone, id=General Lorelath
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:109
msgid "General Lorelath"
msgstr "General Lorelath"

#. [side]: type=Elvish Hero, id=Cithraldin
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:148
msgid "Cithraldin"
msgstr "Cithraldin"

#. [side]: type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Gerumanen
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:182
msgid "Gerumanen"
msgstr "Gerumanen"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:242
msgid "According to the map Unarye gave us, the valley entrance is just ahead."
msgstr ""
"Según el mapa que nos dio Unarye, la entrada al valle está justo delante."

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:247
msgid "Good."
msgstr "Bien."

#. [message]: speaker=Zynara
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:258
msgid "Don’t you think it is unsafe to be here all alone, though?"
msgstr "¿No crees que es peligroso estar aquí solas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:263
msgid ""
"There’s nothing suspicious around here, so... No, I don’t think so. We are "
"both capable of defending ourselves against desert animals."
msgstr ""
"No hay nada sospechoso por aquí, así que... No, no lo creo. Ambas somos "
"capaces de defendernos de los animales del desierto."

#. [unit]: type=Lich, id=Mal Zynavu, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:298
msgid "Mal Zynavu"
msgstr "Mal Zynavu"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:319
msgid "Well, let’s see how you fare on your own against <i>me</i>!"
msgstr "¡Bien, veamos cómo te las arreglas sola contra <i>mí</i>!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:327
msgid "Wh—"
msgstr "¡Qu—!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:360
msgid "—<b>Who</b> are you in truth? <b>ANSWER!</b>"
msgstr "—<b>¿Quién</b> eres en realidad? ¡<b>RESPONDE</b>!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:365
msgid ""
"It saddens me to admit that my master was a very misguided person — his "
"destruction was only a matter of time. Uria’s power is the greatest force "
"that’s ever graced us. We could avoid wasting so many lives all over the "
"continent if everyone accepted her offer and joined her cause."
msgstr ""
"Me entristece admitir que mi maestro era una persona muy equivocada; su "
"destrucción era solo cuestión de tiempo. El poder de Uria es la fuerza más "
"grande que nos ha bendecido jamás. Podríamos evitar desperdiciar tantas "
"vidas en todo el continente si todos aceptaran su oferta y se unieran a su "
"causa."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:370
msgid ""
"So <b>you</b> were in the country working for the Triad all this time? "
"<b>YOU BETRAYED US!</b>"
msgstr ""
"¿Así que <b>tú</b> estabas en el país trabajando para la Tríada todo este "
"tiempo? ¡<b>NOS TRAICIONASTE</b>!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:375
msgid ""
"I am not the only one! Even those pitiful northerners have grown weary of "
"this pointless war and seek easier alternatives. Now, give me that staff. "
"Oh, and don’t forget you are not in possession of godlike powers anymore — I "
"can and will kill you if you don’t concede."
msgstr ""
"¡No soy la única! Incluso esos patéticos norteños se han cansado de esta "
"guerra sin sentido y buscan alternativas más fáciles. Ahora, dame ese "
"bastón. Y no olvides que ya no posees poderes divinos: puedo matarte y lo "
"haré si no cedes."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:418
msgid "<i>They</i> are also willing to help..."
msgstr "<i>Ellos</i> también están dispuestos a ayudar..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:482
msgid "—GAH!"
msgstr "—¡AGH!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:526
msgid "Anya! Durvan! How did you know? I—"
msgstr "¡Anya! ¡Durvan! ¿Cómo lo supieron? Yo—"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:531
msgid ""
"My lady, we’d never leave you alone in the darkness. After all, it <i>is</i> "
"our element!"
msgstr ""
"Mi señora, nunca la dejaríamos sola en la oscuridad. Después de todo, <i>es</"
"i> nuestro elemento."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:536
msgid ""
"There’s a lot of movement in the hills to the south, my lady. The northern "
"defense line is preparing for battle, and so should we!"
msgstr ""
"Hay mucho movimiento en las colinas al sur, mi señora. La línea defensiva "
"del norte se está preparando para la batalla, ¡y nosotros también deberíamos "
"hacerlo!"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:560
msgid "Elynia must destroy Mal Zynavu by herself"
msgstr "Elynia debe destruir a Mal Zynavu por sí sola"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:571
msgid "You may attack Mal Zynavu only with Elynia"
msgstr "Solo puedes atacar a Mal Zynavu con Elynia"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:607
msgid ""
"I didn’t come from so far to the former home of my people to be defeated by "
"a traitor and coward."
msgstr ""
"No he venido tan lejos al antiguo hogar de mi pueblo para ser derrotada por "
"una traidora y cobarde."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#. The truncated word is "Elynia".
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:628
msgid "El— my lady?!"
msgstr "¡El— mi señora?!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:633
msgid ""
"I <i>have</i> done this before, thanks to Argan and Malin. Although I am not "
"as good as them with spirits, unfortunately..."
msgstr ""
"Esto ya lo he hecho antes, gracias a Argan y Malin. Aunque no soy tan buena "
"con los espíritus como ellos, desafortunadamente..."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:638
msgid "Your staff... the Ruby’s glowing!"
msgstr "Tu bastón... ¡el Rubí está brillando!"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:661
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Elynia can no longer recruit <b>Ghosts</b>.\n"
"\n"
"However, she still has access to any Ghost line units already present in her "
"recall list, and she is now able to recruit <b>Vampire Bats</b>."
msgstr ""
"Elynia ya no puede reclutar Fantasmas.\n"
"\n"
"Sin embargo, aún tiene acceso a las unidades de la línea Fantasma que quedan "
"en su lista de reclamos, y ahora puede reclutar Murciélagos Vampiro."

#. [message]: speaker=Gerumanen
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:677
msgid "I can see her friends there... he, he..."
msgstr "Puedo ver a sus amigos ahí... je, je..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:682
msgid "Ignore them — strike down the faerie first!"
msgstr "Ignóralos — ¡derriba primero a la hada!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:694
msgid ""
"Who is your leader? Who is awaiting us in the valley and who is my "
"impersonator?"
msgstr ""
"¿Quién es tu líder? ¿Quién nos espera en el valle y quién es mi suplantadora?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Zynavu
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:699
msgid "I work for the Iron Council! I have no idea who—"
msgstr "¡Trabajo para el Consejo de Hierro! No tengo idea quién—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:704
msgid "You... are... <b>LYING</b>!"
msgstr "¡Tú... estás... <b>MENTIENDO</b>!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:775
msgid "How could you..."
msgstr "¿Cómo pudiste..."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:788
msgid "It’s over now."
msgstr "Ya terminó."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:797
msgid "My lady..."
msgstr "Mi señora..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:806
msgid "Just ‘Elynia’ will do, friends."
msgstr "Solo ‘Elynia’ está bien, amigos."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:815
msgid "What should we do now?"
msgstr "¿Qué hacemos ahora?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:820
msgid ""
"There is no turning back, and the impostor must be preparing to confront us "
"or flee from the valley. Whichever is the case, I am going to find her and "
"burn her to ashes. You must contact Elorran immediately to notify him of "
"Zynara’s betrayal. It’s very probable that he is in danger."
msgstr ""
"No hay vuelta atrás, y la impostora debe estar preparando enfrentarnos o "
"huir del valle. Sea cual sea el caso, voy a encontrarla y reducirla a "
"cenizas. Deben contactar a Elorran de inmediato para informarle sobre la "
"traición de Zynara. Probablemente esté en peligro."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:825
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:392
msgid "Very well!"
msgstr "¡Muy bien!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:830
msgid "Everyone else, prepare for what I hope will be our last battle."
msgstr ""
"Todos los demás, prepárense para lo que espero sea nuestra última batalla."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:835
msgid "Yes, my lady!"
msgstr "Sí, mi señora."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/07_Proximus.cfg:843
msgid "The main troops are coming..."
msgstr "Las tropas principales están llegando..."

