msgstr "Paso de Alenaril"

#. [label]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:295
msgid "River Toldrin"
msgstr "Río Toldrin"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:340
msgid "Elynia must defeat the false Lady of Light by herself"
msgstr "Elynia debe derrotar a la falsa Dama de la Luz por sí misma"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:341
msgid "Defeat all other enemy leaders"
msgstr "Derrotar a todos los demás líderes enemigos"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:343
msgid "The false Lady of Light gets killed by a different unit"
msgstr "La falsa Dama de la Luz es eliminada por una unidad diferente"

#. [message]: speaker=Adel
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:369
msgid ""
"Sirs, the impostor has arrived with her army! The northern defense line is—"
msgstr ""
"Señores, ¡la impostora ha llegado con su ejército! La línea de defensa norte "
"está—"

#. [message]: speaker=Kaerus-Aganan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:374
msgid ""
"Ha! Ha! That is no army. I thought the northern elves would be more kind to "
"their so-called savior! Ha!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! ¡Ja! Eso no es un ejército. ¡Pensé que los elfos del norte serían más "
"amables con su llamada salvadora! ¡Ja!"

#. [message]: speaker=Lady of Light
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:379
msgid ""
"Behold, the usurper arrived to challenge us in our own headquarters. What a "
"pitiful effort! To arms! Take her down and bring me her head and the staff "
"she stole from me!"
msgstr ""
"He aquí, la usurpadora llegó a retarnos en nuestra propia base. ¡Qué "
"esfuerzo tan lamentable! ¡A las armas! ¡Derrótenla y tráiganme su cabeza y "
"el bastón que me robó!"

#. [message]: speaker=Kethael
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:384
msgid "Yes, my lady."
msgstr "Sí, mi señora."

#. [message]: speaker=Midnolan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:389
msgid "As you command, my lady!"
msgstr "¡Como mande, mi señora!"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:404
msgid "They seem quite loyal to her despite the state of their home."
msgstr "Parece que le son bastante leales a pesar del estado de su hogar."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:409
msgid ""
"Indeed, something is seriously amiss about these elves. If only we could "
"prove she is the impostor, perhaps they would then listen to reason."
msgstr ""
"De hecho, algo anda muy mal con estos elfos. Si pudiéramos demostrar que "
"ella es la impostora, quizás entonces escucharan la razón."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:414
msgid "What do you suggest, my lady... Elynia?"
msgstr "¿Qué sugieres, mi señora... Elynia?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:419
msgid "Stay clear of her and allow me to confront her by myself."
msgstr "Mantente alejada de ella y déjame enfrentarla yo sola."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:424
msgid "Very well..."
msgstr "Muy bien..."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:444
msgid ""
"Dedicated to Elynia-Thanadria of Wesmere, Lady of Light and Protector of the "
"Elves of Irdya."
msgstr ""
"Dedicado a Elynia-Thanadria de Wesmere, Dama de la Luz y Protectora de los "
"Elfos de Irdya."

#. [message]: speaker=Kaerus-Aganan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:456
msgid "Protect the Lady of Light! Argh—"
msgstr "¡Protejan a la Dama de la Luz! ¡Argh—"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:471
msgid "I— the Lady of Light... why..."
msgstr "Y—yo, la Dama de la Luz... ¿por qué...?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:502
msgid "The impostor escaped!"
msgstr "¡La impostora escapó!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:507
msgid ""
"This isn’t good. Since we couldn’t unmask her in front of her subjects, they "
"will summon reinforcements and fight us to the death. We must retreat "
"immediately!"
msgstr ""
"Esto no es bueno. Como no pudimos desenmascararla frente a sus súbditos, "
"convocarán refuerzos y lucharán hasta la muerte. ¡Debemos retirarnos de "
"inmediato!"

#. [message]: speaker=Lady of Light
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:557
msgid "I shall never be defeated by vile impostors like you!"
msgstr "¡Nunca seré derrotada por vil impostores como tú!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:562
msgid ""
"Do you truly believe your own lies? Why don’t you show these elves what you "
"are capable of? Your great powers as the Lady of Light? <i>Who</i> are you, "
"and why are you posing as me?"
msgstr ""
"¿De verdad crees tus propias mentiras? ¿Por qué no les muestras a estos "
"elfos de qué eres capaz? ¿Tus grandes poderes como la Dama de la Luz? "
"<i>¿Quién</i> eres, y por qué te haces pasar por mí?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lady of Light
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:567
msgid "Your end is at hand. I shall not answer. Guards! Kill her!"
msgstr "Tu fin está cerca. No responderé. ¡Guardias! ¡Mátenla!"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:591
msgid "Anariel"
msgstr "Anariel"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:592
msgid "Eldulas"
msgstr "Eldulas"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:593
msgid "Vinon"
msgstr "Vinon"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:642
msgid "Back, you fools!"
msgstr "¡Retrocedan, necios!"

#. [message]: speaker=Eldulas
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:722
msgid "What is this? She emanates such a radiant light!"
msgstr "¿Qué es esto? ¡Ella emana una luz tan radiante!"

#. [message]: speaker=Vinon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:732
msgid "... Wha— What are we doing?"
msgstr "... ¿Qué— qué estamos haciendo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lady of Light
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:737
msgid "Do not hesitate! Kill her! <b>Now!</b>"
msgstr "¡No duden! ¡Mátenla! <b>¡Ahora!</b>"

#. [message]: speaker=Vinon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:746
msgid "Who... Who should we trust?"
msgstr "¿Quién... en quién deberíamos confiar?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anariel
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:751
msgid "My lady... Elynia! The Lady of Light! I remember you!"
msgstr "Mi señora... ¡Elynia! ¡La Dama de la Luz! ¡Te recuerdo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Lady of Light
#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:760
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08B_Destiny_part_1.cfg:1943
msgid "No..."
msgstr "No..."

#. [message]: speaker=Eldulas
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:765
msgid "... We have been deceived..."
msgstr "... Hemos sido engañados..."

#. [message]: speaker=Vinon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:833
msgid "What have we done?"
msgstr "¿Qué hemos hecho?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lady of Light
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:861
msgid "This is <i>not</i> over yet!"
msgstr "¡Esto <i>no</i> ha terminado aún!"

#. [message]: race=elf
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:891
msgid "The false Lady of Light has escaped!"
msgstr "¡La falsa Dama de la Luz ha escapado!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:919
msgid "We still need to defeat the other commanders!"
msgstr "¡Todavía necesitamos derrotar a los otros comandantes!"

#. [else]
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:923
msgid "Defeat all remaining enemy leaders"
msgstr "Derrotar a todos los líderes enemigos restantes"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:941
msgid ""
"Their reinforcements have arrived and they have surrounded the valley! This "
"is hopeless!"
msgstr ""
"¡Han llegado sus refuerzos y han rodeado el valle! ¡Esto es desesperado!"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:954
msgid "That fiend retreated into the Shaxthal hive."
msgstr "Ese demonio se retiró a la colmena Shaxthal."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:959
msgid ""
"Her crimes against the unity of the elvish civilization must not go "
"unpunished. I shall pursue her underground if need be."
msgstr ""
"Sus crímenes contra la unidad de la civilización élfica no deben quedar "
"impunes. La perseguiré bajo tierra si es necesario."

#. [message]: speaker=Anariel
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:964
msgid ""
"My lady, we cannot let you go underground alone! It’s become an exceedingly "
"dangerous place since the new hive was completed."
msgstr ""
"Mi señora, ¡no podemos dejar que vaya sola bajo tierra! Se ha vuelto un "
"lugar sumamente peligroso desde que la nueva colmena fue completada."

#. [message]: speaker=Eldulas
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:969
msgid ""
"We haven’t seen him or her ourselves yet, but the humans have been spreading "
"rumors of the arrival of a powerful ally of the impostor! They might be "
"awaiting you!"
msgstr ""
"Aún no lo hemos visto ni visto, pero los humanos han estado difundiendo "
"rumores sobre la llegada de un poderoso aliado del impostor. ¡Podrían estar "
"esperándote!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:974
msgid "My lady, I— I mean Elynia, let us go with you, please!"
msgstr "Mi señora, yo— quiero decir Elynia, ¡permítenos ir contigo, por favor!"

#. [message]: speaker=Vinon
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:983
msgid "If there’s anything else we can do to try to amend our grave mistake..."
msgstr ""
"Si hay algo más que podamos hacer para intentar enmendar nuestro grave "
"error..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode2/scenarios/08_And_then_there_was_Chaos.cfg:988
msgid "Let’s go together."
msgstr "Vayamos juntos."

