#. [message]: speaker=Eluclya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:345
msgid ""
"My lady, since you are returning to the Far North we thought we should let "
"you know you can count on our help. Should you need fighters or a healer..."
msgstr ""
"Mi señora, ya que va a regresar al Lejano Norte pensamos que deberíamos "
"informarle que puede contar con nuestra ayuda. Si necesita combatientes o un "
"sanador..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:350
msgid "I appreciate your offer, and you can come with us if you wish."
msgstr "Agradezco su oferta, y pueden venir con nosotros si lo desean."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:356
msgid ""
"These three loyal elves—Eluclya, Nalan and Crendil—will be available for you "
"to recall from now on."
msgstr ""
"Estos tres leales elfos —Eluclya, Nalan y Crendil— estarán disponibles para "
"que los llame desde ahora."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:361
msgid ""
"Elynia, I’m not sure leaving most of our men behind is actually a good idea."
msgstr ""
"Elynia, no estoy seguro de que dejar a la mayoría de nuestros hombres atrás "
"sea realmente una buena idea."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:366
msgid ""
"I prefer that they stay here to investigate the ruins for us and assist the "
"elves should the Empire send more troops back here. Anya can teleport them "
"back to us later if necessary. We don’t have much time and we have already "
"tarried here for too long because of my incompetence."
msgstr ""
"Prefiero que se queden aquí para investigar las ruinas por nosotros y ayudar "
"a los elfos en caso de que el Imperio envíe más tropas. Anya puede traerlos "
"de vuelta más tarde si es necesario. No tenemos mucho tiempo y ya hemos "
"demorado demasiado aquí por mi incompetencia."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:371
msgid ""
"Don’t say such things — it’s not your fault! Teleportation is a very "
"complicated and dangerous skill to learn for those who weren’t born with the "
"ability!"
msgstr ""
"¡No diga esas cosas! ¡No es su culpa! La teletransportación es una habilidad "
"muy complicada y peligrosa de aprender para quienes no nacieron con esa "
"capacidad."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:378
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you say so, girl. (<i>smiling</i>) I suppose it’s not my place to argue "
"with a creature of the dark."
msgstr ""
"Si tú lo dices, niña. (<i>sonriendo</i>) Supongo que no me corresponde "
"discutir con una criatura de la oscuridad."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:387
msgid "Let’s return."
msgstr "Volvamos."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:567
msgid "Where are we? Where is everyone?"
msgstr "¿Dónde estamos? ¿Dónde está todos?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:576
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"While Anya and Durvan contemplated their surroundings, Elynia spotted and "
"picked up a necklace identical to Anya’s, covered in blood."
msgstr ""
"Mientras Anya y Durvan contemplan su entorno, Elynia recoge un collar "
"idéntico al de Anya, cubierto de sangre."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:586
msgid "This does not bode well."
msgstr "Esto no es un buen presagio."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:591
msgid "That trail... No..."
msgstr "Ese rastro... No..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:605
msgid "Please tell me they’re not..."
msgstr "Por favor, dime que no están..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:661
msgid "... May the Lords of Light have mercy..."
msgstr "... Que los Señores de la Luz tengan misericordia..."

