msgid "Kyanala"
msgstr "Kyanala"

#. [hidden_unit]: type=Demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1010
msgid "Shergal"
msgstr "Shergal"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1027
msgid "This... is quite the bloody mess..."
msgstr "Esto... es un desastre sangriento..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1037
msgid "Anya... I..."
msgstr "Anya... yo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1047
msgid "... I— I advise you don’t come outside—"
msgstr "... A— Aconsejo que no salgas—"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1103
msgid "(<i>crying</i>) No..."
msgstr "(<i>llorando</i>) No..."

#. [message]: speaker=General Ramzal
#. The full title is "The Fist of Uria", and is male, but this is supposed
#. to be unclear at this point in order to mess with Elynia's head.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1122
msgid ""
"There they are! Just like the Fist told us, they would turn up soon looking "
"for their fallen friends. Would that our pets had lingered around for long "
"enough. But I’m rambling — let’s end this once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahí están! Tal como nos dijo el Puño, vendrían pronto buscando a sus amigos "
"caídos. Ojalá nuestras mascotas se hubieran quedado más tiempo. Pero estoy "
"divagando: ¡acabemos con esto de una vez por todas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1127
msgid ""
"Search the settlement for survivors, gather any living humans from the "
"nearby villages, and try to locate Elorran and Tara’s remains."
msgstr ""
"Registrad el asentamiento en busca de sobrevivientes, reunid a cualquier "
"humano con vida de las aldeas cercanas y tratad de localizar los restos de "
"Elorran y Tara."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1132
msgid "Elynia...? What’s your plan?"
msgstr "¿Elynia...? ¿Cuál es tu plan?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1137
msgid ""
"We will make the demons pay for this atrocity. That is all I know and care "
"about for the moment."
msgstr ""
"Haremos que los demonios paguen por esta atrocidad. Eso es lo único que sé y "
"me importa por ahora."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1174
msgid ""
"Player units which start their turn on forest tiles on fire will take 8 "
"<b>fire</b> damage"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1175
msgid "Forest fire damage will kill a unit if it drops below 1 HP"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1190
msgid "Anya... I’m truly sorry for all this. It all has been my fault..."
msgstr "Anya... Lamento mucho todo esto. Todo ha sido culpa mía..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1200
msgid ""
"(<i>still crying</i>) Don’t blame yourself. This... we knew it would happen. "
"It would happen sooner or later."
msgstr ""
"(<i>aún llorando</i>) No te culpes. Esto... sabíamos que pasaría. Pasaría "
"tarde o temprano."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1206
msgid ""
"I just... I just hoped I’d have a chance to say goodbye to them. They... "
"they took care of me for so long, ever since I was abandoned... as a child."
msgstr ""
"Yo solo... solo esperaba tener la oportunidad de despedirme de ellos. "
"Ellos... me cuidaron tanto tiempo, desde que fui abandonada... de niña."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1215
msgid ""
"I could never understand. I had heard stories about your kind... And then I "
"met you, and I saw you and that elvish lady, and the other elves... You have "
"such a different perception of those who ascend to faeriedom... You look "
"upon them with awe and respect. Humans don’t share the sentiment with those "
"born from faerie and demonkind like me."
msgstr ""
"Nunca pude entenderlo. Había escuchado historias sobre los de tu clase... Y "
"luego te conocí a ti, y vi a esa dama élfica y a los otros elfos... Tenéis "
"una percepción tan diferente de aquellos que ascienden a la condición "
"feérica... Los contempláis con asombro y respeto. Los humanos no comparten "
"ese sentimiento hacia los nacidos de las hadas y los demonios como yo."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1221
msgid ""
"They hate us. Perhaps out of fear, or out of ignorance. Or simply because we "
"are not like them."
msgstr ""
"Nos odian. Quizás por miedo, o por ignorancia. O simplemente porque no somos "
"como ellos."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1227
msgid ""
"Thirteen years ago, Tara found me in the forest. I was cold, starving, and "
"frightened. She brought me to Elorran, and together they raised me since "
"then, all despite the dangers of their mission. The rational option for them "
"should have been to leave me behind so I wouldn’t hinder them, and yet..."
msgstr ""
"Hace trece años, Tara me encontró en el bosque. Estaba fría, hambrienta y "
"asustada. Me llevó con Elorran, y juntos me criaron desde entonces, a pesar "
"de los peligros de su misión. La opción racional para ellos habría sido "
"dejarme atrás para no entorpecerlos y, aun así..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1256
msgid "... They taught me many things. But most importantly..."
msgstr "... Me enseñaron muchas cosas. Pero lo más importante..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1285
msgid "They taught me to smile."
msgstr "Me enseñaron a sonreír."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1294
msgid ""
"My mission failed. I brought you back, but we don’t have the Ruby, and "
"Elorran and Tara can’t help us anymore. But... I’m sure all this had to "
"happen for a reason, even if it often feels like a cruel and pointless game "
"of life and death."
msgstr ""
"Mi misión fracasó. Te traje de vuelta, pero no tenemos el Rubí, y Elorran y "
"Tara ya no pueden ayudarnos. Pero... estoy segura de que todo esto tuvo que "
"suceder por una razón, aunque a menudo parezca un cruel e inútil juego de "
"vida y muerte."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1300
msgid "If we are still alive, it must mean something..."
msgstr "Si aún estamos vivos, debe significar algo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1309
msgid "It must mean our purpose in this game hasn’t been fulfilled yet."
msgstr ""
"Debe significar que nuestro propósito en este juego aún no se ha cumplido."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1318
msgid "I will follow you until the end... what else is there for me to do."
msgstr "Te seguiré hasta el final... ¿qué otra cosa me queda por hacer?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1332
msgid "You are all I have now."
msgstr "Ahora eres todo lo que tengo."

#. [message]: speaker=General Ramzal
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1354
msgid ""
"I’ve been eagerly awaiting the opportunity to behold the Lady of Light’s "
"impaled torso, but that won’t happen now, for my presence is required in "
"Kalari. But please, go on without me; just make sure to leave a trophy for "
"me to claim."
msgstr ""
"He estado esperando con ansias la oportunidad de contemplar el torso "
"empalado de la Dama de la Luz, pero eso no sucederá ahora, pues se requiere "
"mi presencia en Kalari. Pero por favor, continúen sin mí; solo asegúrense de "
"dejarme un trofeo para reclamar."

#. [unit]: type=Chaos Razerman, id=Glorderon
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1385
msgid "Glorderon"
msgstr "Glorderon"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1417
msgid "What was that explosion? The volcano?"
msgstr "¿Qué fue esa explosión? ¿El volcán?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1422
msgid "No. It was much farther from this region..."
msgstr "No. Fue mucho más lejos de esta región..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1432
msgid ""
"The explosion definitely came from Raelthyn. There’s an enormous cloud of "
"smoke coming from that direction. This... I suppose this explains why I "
"couldn’t contact Valen yesterday."
msgstr ""
"La explosión vino claramente de Raelthyn. Hay una enorme nube de humo "
"viniendo de esa dirección. Esto... supongo que explica por qué no pude "
"contactar con Valen ayer."

#. [message]: speaker=Glorderon
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1444
msgid "This... isn’t po—"
msgstr "Esto... no es po—"

#. [message]: speaker=Sibul
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1456
msgid "Damn you, creatures— Grargh!!!"
msgstr "Malditas criaturas— ¡Grargh!"

#. [message]: speaker=Vrenmark
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1468
msgid "Ah, yes, you can kill me now, but at the end of the day—"
msgstr "Ah, sí, pueden matarme ahora, pero al final del día—"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1484
msgid "Elynia, can I talk to you for a moment?"
msgstr "Elynia, ¿puedo hablar contigo un momento?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1489
msgid "You mean... Well, yes, of course."
msgstr "¿Te refieres a…? Bueno, sí, por supuesto."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1494
msgid ""
"(<i>aside</i>) We found a witness. He claims a demon and a faerie were "
"amongst the many victims of a number of mechanical birds who descended from "
"the sky, killing and devouring everybody in their path, making sure to leave "
"no whole corpses behind. Elorran and Tara..."
msgstr ""
"(<i>aparte</i>) Encontramos un testigo. Afirma que un demonio y un hada "
"estaban entre las muchas víctimas de unas aves mecánicas que descendieron "
"del cielo, matando y devorando a todos en su camino, asegurándose de no "
"dejar cadáveres enteros atrás. Elorran y Tara..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1499
msgid ""
"(<i>aside</i>) I understand. Why... Why did it have to end like this...? "
"Just when I thought we had a chance to rally demonkind against Uria..."
msgstr ""
"(<i>aparte</i>) Entiendo. ¿Por qué...? ¿Por qué tuvo que terminar así...? "
"Justo cuando pensé que teníamos una oportunidad de unir a los demonios "
"contra Uria..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1510
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/11_After_the_Storm.cfg:383
msgid "Elynia?"
msgstr "¿Elynia?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1515
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/06_Divergence.cfg:1053
msgid "Yes?"
msgstr "¿Sí?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1529
msgid ""
"I don’t know anymore. If Raelthyn has fallen, then all hope is lost; the "
"Chaos Empire has won the war, and Uria is now able to do whatever she wants "
"with Irdya and her next target with that artifact in her possession. We "
"might be able to survive the upcoming onslaught for a while if we go back "
"with Unarye, assuming they haven’t also been crushed by these relentless "
"hordes coming out of damned nowhere..."
msgstr ""
"Ya no lo sé. Si Raelthyn ha caído, entonces toda esperanza está perdida; el "
"Imperio del Caos ha ganado la guerra, y Uria ahora puede hacer lo que quiera "
"con Irdya y con su próximo objetivo teniendo ese artefacto en su poder. Tal "
"vez podamos sobrevivir un tiempo más a la embestida que se avecina si "
"regresamos con Unarye, suponiendo que ellos no hayan sido aplastados también "
"por estas hordas implacables que salen de maldito ningún lado..."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1534
msgid "What if we left the Great Continent instead?"
msgstr "¿Y si dejamos el Gran Continente en su lugar?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1539
msgid ""
"The elves in Zocthanol Isle told us their merfolk allies had evidence that "
"only the Great Northern Ice Plains remain besides this continent. We would "
"quickly perish there, so that’s not an option. And what would the point be "
"if Uria presumably has the power to destroy Irdya itself?"
msgstr ""
"Los elfos de la Isla Zocthanol nos dijeron que sus aliados tritones tenían "
"pruebas de que solo las Grandes Llanuras Heladas del Norte quedan además de "
"este continente. Allí pereceríamos rápidamente, así que no es una opción. ¿Y "
"cuál sería el sentido si Uria presumiblemente tiene el poder de destruir la "
"propia Irdya?"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1544
msgid "You aren’t suggesting we just sit here and do nothing, are you?"
msgstr "No estarás sugiriendo que nos sentemos aquí sin hacer nada, ¿verdad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1558
msgid "... guess I am."
msgstr "... supongo que sí."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1567
msgid "Elynia, please! Just... let’s go back to Raelthyn."
msgstr "¡Elynia, por favor! Solo... regresemos a Raelthyn."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1572
msgid ""
"To see more of this? Do you really want to see more senseless destruction? "
"Do you really want me to lead you to another devastated battlefield littered "
"with dismembered corpses?"
msgstr ""
"¿Para ver más de esto? ¿De verdad quieres ver más destrucción sin sentido? "
"¿De verdad quieres que te lleve a otro campo de batalla devastado y lleno de "
"cadáveres despedazados?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/01_Beyond_her_Smile.cfg:1577
msgid "I feel this is not over yet. Let’s go back. Please..."
msgstr "Siento que esto aún no ha terminado. Regresemos. Por favor..."

