msgstr ""
"La Fortaleza de Adavyan comprende la fortaleza inicial y las casillas de "
"castillo donde está Torancyn"

#. [scenario]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/02_01_Return_to_Raelthyn.cfg:683
msgid ""
"Keep in mind Demolisher Drones destroy and kill everything within a one-hex "
"radius when slain; you will need to sacrifice units to achieve your goals"
msgstr ""
