#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:547
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/04_01_Outpost_of_Hell.cfg:679
msgid "Death of General Bardyl"
msgstr "Muerte del General Bardyl"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:555
msgid ""
"You’ll continue to control General Bardyl and his troops until the end of "
"the next scenario"
msgstr ""
"Seguirás controlando al General Bardyl y sus tropas hasta el final del "
"próximo escenario."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:566
msgid "This is taking too long — I begin to worry for Elynia..."
msgstr "Esto está tardando demasiado… Empiezo a preocuparme por Elynia..."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:573
msgid "Nah, there she comes."
msgstr "Nah, ahí viene."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:603
msgid "Elynia, you are back! Is that... the journal?"
msgstr "¡Elynia, has vuelto! ¿Ese es… el diario?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:608
msgid "That’s correct."
msgstr "Así es."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:613
msgid ""
"So, is that General Bardyl fellow going to help us assault Aran-Balgur then?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿ese tal General Bardyl nos ayudará a asaltar Aran-Balgur?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:618
msgid ""
"Indeed he is, but not specifically because of my advice; he was already "
"giving consideration to the idea because of a rumor that’s been running "
"through his troops as of late. It appears someone successfully "
"‘interrogated’ a captured enemy soldier and got some information about the "
"source of the local raids and the ongoing invasion. What they know suggests "
"that there is indeed a portal in Aran-Balgur."
msgstr ""
"Así es, pero no específicamente por mi consejo; ya estaba considerando la "
"idea debido a un rumor que ha estado circulando entre sus tropas "
"últimamente. Al parecer, alguien ‘interrogó’ con éxito a un soldado enemigo "
"capturado y obtuvo información sobre el origen de las incursiones locales y "
"la invasión en curso. Lo que saben sugiere que, en efecto, hay un portal en "
"Aran-Balgur."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:623
msgid ""
"I shudder to wonder exactly how this information was obtained. I know from "
"experience that the men in the service of the Empire are either completely "
"ignorant of their superiors’ plans, or instructed to commit suicide before "
"being captured, and the sorcerers and demons are too powerful to contain."
msgstr ""
"Me estremece pensar en cómo se obtuvo exactamente esa información. Sé por "
"experiencia que los hombres al servicio del Imperio o bien son completamente "
"ignorantes de los planes de sus superiores, o están instruidos para "
"suicidarse antes de ser capturados; y los hechiceros y demonios son "
"demasiado poderosos para ser contenidos."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:628
msgid "I guess now we should all advance towards Aran-Balgur?"
msgstr "¿Supongo que ahora todos debemos avanzar hacia Aran-Balgur?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:633
msgid "Exactly. And we should be careful."
msgstr "Exacto. Y debemos tener cuidado."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:650
msgid ""
"The road to the south leading to Aran-Balgur is said to be well protected by "
"powerful demons, and there’s also an enemy guard post obstructing our path. "
"Furthermore, we may stumble upon their main invasion army at some point. The "
"only reason Fort Astar still stands is that they don’t perceive Bardyl’s "
"forces as a threat stationed here. However, the moment they see his little "
"army marching towards their territory, they will not be as merciful."
msgstr ""
"Se dice que el camino hacia el sur que conduce a Aran-Balgur está bien "
"protegido por poderosos demonios, y también hay un puesto de guardia enemigo "
"que obstruye nuestro paso. Además, podríamos toparnos con su ejército "
"principal de invasión en algún momento. La única razón por la que el Fuerte "
"Astar sigue en pie es que no consideran a las fuerzas de Bardyl como una "
"amenaza mientras permanecen aquí. Sin embargo, en el momento en que vean a "
"su pequeño ejército marchar hacia su territorio, no serán tan "
"misericordiosos."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:655
msgid "So it rests on us and our followers, I take it."
msgstr "Entonces depende de nosotros y de nuestros seguidores, ¿no es así?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:660
msgid "Exactly."
msgstr "Exacto."

#. [message]: speaker=General Bardyl
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:693
msgid "And so, it begins."
msgstr "Y así comienza."

#. [message]: speaker=Kyara
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:701
msgid "If you don’t mind me asking, sir, are you sure about this?"
msgstr "Si no le molesta que pregunte, señor, ¿está seguro de esto?"

#. [message]: speaker=General Bardyl
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:706
msgid ""
"Of course I am. The Grand Council has neglected us for long enough, and "
"those damned bastards from hell are getting increasingly bored of playing "
"with us. As much as I find her kind disgusting, if the faerie’s troops and "
"power are as impressive as she promised we’ll recover Aran-Balgur before "
"long. And if there’s a portal in there and we can destroy it, we’ll regain "
"the Council’s blessing as well."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que sí. El Gran Consejo nos ha ignorado durante demasiado "
"tiempo, y esos malditos bastardos del infierno están cada vez más aburridos "
"de jugar con nosotros. Por muy repugnante que me resulte su especie, si las "
"tropas y el poder de la hada son tan impresionantes como prometió, "
"recuperaremos Aran-Balgur en poco tiempo. Y si hay un portal allí y podemos "
"destruirlo, también recuperaremos la bendición del Consejo."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:724
msgid ""
"Time to tear those evil creatures to bits! We will make them pay, oh yes..."
msgstr ""
"¡Es hora de despedazar a esas malvadas criaturas! Les haremos pagar, oh sí…"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:729
msgid "This goblin fellow seems really invested into this, doesn’t he?"
msgstr "Este goblin parece realmente involucrado en esto, ¿no?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:734
msgid ""
"Apparently he was close friends with Lord Galas and Mal Keshar, and also "
"someone else... Elynia hasn’t told me much about that woman in particular, "
"which is saying something considering how difficult it is to get her to talk "
"about the others in the first place."
msgstr ""
"Al parecer era muy amigo del Lord Galas y de Mal Keshar, y también de "
"alguien más… Elynia no me ha contado mucho sobre esa mujer en particular, lo "
"cual ya es decir considerando lo difícil que es lograr que hable de los "
"demás."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:739
msgid ""
"Are you sure you should be prying that much, though? It sounds like a very "
"personal subject for her."
msgstr ""
"¿Estás segura de que deberías indagar tanto? Parece un tema muy personal "
"para ella."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:744
msgid ""
"I know, I know... I just wish she would open up and not shoulder so much "
"grief alone when we are all in this together. But perhaps you are right, "
"it’s not my place to intrude."
msgstr ""
"Lo sé, lo sé… Solo desearía que se abriera un poco y no cargara con tanto "
"dolor sola cuando todos estamos en esto juntos. Pero quizá tengas razón, no "
"me corresponde entrometerme."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:806
msgid "Lord Nar-hamoth demands the blood of the northern scum! Charge!"
msgstr ""
"¡El Señor Nar-hamoth exige la sangre de la escoria del norte! ¡Al ataque!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:821
msgid ""
"I remember that name — I believe it’s one of the fiends of the Iron Triad."
msgstr ""
"Recuerdo ese nombre… Creo que es uno de los demonios de la Tríada de Hierro."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:826
msgid ""
"So the rumors Elorran heard are true? That guy is said to be the least "
"competent Demon Lord of all, and yet Uria trusts him over most for some "
"reason."
msgstr ""
"¿Así que los rumores que escuchó Elorran son ciertos? Dicen que ese sujeto "
"es el Señor Demonio menos competente de todos, y aun así Uria confía en él "
"más que en la mayoría por alguna razón."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:831
msgid "We’ll soon see how competent he is on the battlefield, then."
msgstr "Pronto veremos cuán competente es en el campo de batalla, entonces."

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:907
msgid ""
"So you finally decided to challenge me directly? Hopefully this will be an "
"entertaining fight! For the glory of the mother of Urvatha!"
msgstr ""
"¿Así que finalmente decidieron desafiarme directamente? ¡Espero que esta sea "
"una pelea entretenida! ¡Por la gloria de la madre de Urvatha!"

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:924
msgid "Die, pathetic Irdyan rats! DIE!"
msgstr "¡Muéranse, ratas patéticas de Irdya! ¡MUÉRANSE!"

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1017
msgid ""
"Ha! Not bad, but I was just warming up! Now, let us see if you can handle "
"THIS!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! No está mal, pero solo estaba calentando. ¡Ahora veamos si pueden "
"soportar ESTO!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1047
msgid "Oh, come on! That’s just cheating!"
msgstr "¡Vamos! ¡Eso es hacer trampa!"

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1058
msgid ""
"You do not tire of combat easily, eh? I’m impressed! Shall we have a third "
"round then?"
msgstr ""
"No se cansan fácilmente del combate, ¿eh? ¡Estoy impresionado! ¿Tendremos "
"una tercera ronda entonces?"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1064
msgid "Will you stop doing that, you fiend?!"
msgstr "¿¡Vas a dejar de hacer eso, demonio!?"

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1073
msgid ""
"Ha! Your strength and resourcefulness have not gone unnoticed by the "
"Guardian of Life! I too can respect an enemy that perseveres against "
"impossible odds, Elynia-Thanadria."
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! Tu fuerza y astucia no han pasado desapercibidas para el Guardián de la "
"Vida. Yo también puedo respetar a un enemigo que persevera contra "
"probabilidades imposibles, Elynia-Thanadria."

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1099
msgid "Alas, that stubbornness of yours shall be your and your kind’s undoing!"
msgstr "¡Pero esa terquedad tuya será la perdición de ti y de los tuyos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1114
msgid ""
"Hm. Very impressive, indeed. Despite being such lowly rats, you sure seem to "
"be capable of grand feats when given the right motivation. Ahh, yes, as that "
"hapless bastard Argan found out the hard way. Would that we had not met each "
"other as enemies in a never-ending war, don’t you agree? It is just as "
"unfortunate that my presence is currently required elsewhere..."
msgstr ""
"Hm. Muy impresionante, de hecho. A pesar de ser ratas tan miserables, parece "
"que son capaces de grandes hazañas cuando se les da la motivación adecuada. "
"Ahh, sí, como aquel pobre bastardo de Argan descubrió por las malas. Ojalá "
"no nos hubiéramos encontrado como enemigos en una guerra interminable, ¿no "
"crees? Es igual de lamentable que mi presencia sea requerida en otro lugar "
"ahora mismo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1119
msgid "Stop him before he escapes!"
msgstr "¡Deténganlo antes de que escape!"

#. [message]: speaker=Nar-hamoth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1124
msgid "I shall eagerly await the day we meet again!"
msgstr "¡Esperaré con ansias el día en que nos volvamos a encontrar!"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1151
msgid "Come back here, you coward!"
msgstr "¡Vuelve aquí, cobarde!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1156
msgid ""
"... Fleeing the battlefield seems a conventional tactic for the highest-"
"ranking servants of Uria. Mal Hekuba did so in both of our previous face-to-"
"face encounters as well. I don’t think we ever got a taste of his true might "
"before he decided to fuse his own putrid body with those artifacts."
msgstr ""
"... Huir del campo de batalla parece una táctica convencional para los "
"sirvientes de más alto rango de Uria. Mal Hekuba hizo lo mismo en nuestros "
"dos encuentros anteriores cara a cara. No creo que hayamos llegado a conocer "
"su verdadero poder antes de que decidiera fusionar su putrido cuerpo con "
"aquellos artefactos."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1161
msgid "That may have been for the best, though."
msgstr "Aunque puede que eso haya sido lo mejor."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1166
msgid ""
"Perhaps. Still, I would be grateful if I never had to deal with their "
"limitless arrogance again."
msgstr ""
"Quizás. Aun así, estaría agradecida si nunca más tuviera que lidiar con su "
"arrogancia sin límites."

#. [message]: speaker=General Bardyl
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1184
msgid ""
"This operation was a disastrous mistake. Their shock troops are heading here "
"now, and the faerie’s reinforcements are all but useless. Perhaps if we "
"surrender they’ll at least spare our lives."
msgstr ""
"Esta operación fue un error desastroso. Sus tropas de choque se dirigen "
"hacia aquí ahora, y los refuerzos de la hada son prácticamente inútiles. "
"Quizá si nos rendimos al menos nos perdonen la vida."

#. [message]: speaker=General Bardyl
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1214
msgid ""
"Well played, faerie. Not only you deliberately misled us about your numbers, "
"but you also omitted the fact that you consort with necromancers. This "
"changes everything."
msgstr ""
"Bien jugado, hada. No solo nos engañaste deliberadamente sobre tus números, "
"sino que además omitiste el hecho de que te relacionas con nigromantes. Esto "
"lo cambia todo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1219
msgid ""
"Not necessarily. Today’s events would indicate that together we can build a "
"formidable opposition force. Is this not what you wanted? An opportunity to "
"retake Aran-Balgur, your former home? Is it not what your men desire as "
"well? Or would you prefer to stay here and defend Astar against an enemy "
"with a plan? Tell me, how many soldiers have deserted since the Glamdrol "
"incident?"
msgstr ""
"No necesariamente. Los eventos de hoy indicarían que juntos podemos "
"construir una fuerza de oposición formidable. ¿No es esto lo que querías? "
"¿Una oportunidad para recuperar Aran-Balgur, tu antiguo hogar? ¿No es "
"también lo que desean tus hombres? ¿O prefieres quedarte aquí y defender "
"Astar contra un enemigo con un plan? Dime, ¿cuántos soldados han desertado "
"desde el incidente de Glamdrol?"

#. [message]: speaker=General Bardyl
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1224
msgid ""
"I specifically pointed out your deception; I did not say I would retract, "
"and that’s not an option at this point unless I were looking for a mutiny. "
"I’m done speaking to you for now."
msgstr ""
"He señalado específicamente tu engaño; no dije que me retiraría, y no es una "
"opción a estas alturas a menos que quiera provocar un motín. He terminado de "
"hablar contigo por ahora."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1233
msgid ""
"Elynia, are you sure about this? You did admit before that your judgment "
"might not be—"
msgstr ""
"Elynia, ¿estás segura de esto? Antes admitiste que tu juicio podría no ser—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/03_Amidst_the_Ruins_of_Glamdrol.cfg:1238
msgid ""
"I’m not really heeding my judgment anymore, girl. It’s just a hunch I "
"have... I have to return to Kalari and find this Demon Lord of the Storms, "
"if it’s the last thing I do."
msgstr ""
"Ya no estoy siguiendo realmente mi juicio, chica. Es solo una corazonada que "
"tengo... Debo regresar a Kalari y encontrar a ese Señor Demonio de las "
"Tormentas, aunque sea lo último que haga."

