#. [scenario]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:845
msgid "You can only have up to eight allies on the map simultaneously"
msgstr "Solo puedes tener hasta ocho aliados en el mapa al mismo tiempo"

#. [message]: speaker=Teremor
#. [message]: speaker=memory!Elyssa
#. [message]: speaker=Aradellys
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:871
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2851
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/13_Epilogue.cfg:487
msgid "What brings you here?"
msgstr "¿Qué te trae por aquí?"

#. [message]: speaker=Vyrelyam
#. "The Fire of Uria" refers to Elyssa.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:877
msgid "A message from the Demon Lord of the Storms, for the Fire of Uria."
msgstr "Un mensaje del Señor Demonio de las Tormentas, para el Fuego de Uria."

#. [message]: speaker=Ryghel
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:882
msgid ""
"The captain said we are not supposed to let anyone in for now! You’ll have "
"to wait until he comes back from his inspection."
msgstr ""
"¡El capitán dijo que no debemos dejar entrar a nadie por ahora! Tendrás que "
"esperar hasta que regrese de su inspección."

#. [message]: speaker=Vyrelyam
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:887
msgid ""
"Time is of the essence. Do you really wish to anger your masters by making "
"them wait more than is absolutely necessary?"
msgstr ""
"El tiempo es esencial. ¿Realmente quieres enfadar a tus amos haciéndolos "
"esperar más de lo absolutamente necesario?"

#. [message]: speaker=Teremor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:892
msgid ""
"Look, wench, our masters can go to hell for all I care. You can either "
"deliver your damn message to the captain and convince him to let you pass, "
"or just forget about it. Unless you would prefer to entertain us for a while "
"in exchange for letting you pass, heh heh."
msgstr ""
"Mira, mocosa, que nuestros amos se vayan al infierno por lo que me importa. "
"O entregas tu maldito mensaje al capitán y lo convences de dejarte pasar, o "
"simplemente olvídalo. A menos que prefieras entretenernos un rato a cambio "
"de dejarte pasar, je je."

#. [message]: speaker=Vyrelyam
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:897
msgid "I want to speak to your captain. Where is he?"
msgstr "Quiero hablar con tu capitán. ¿Dónde está?"

#. [message]: speaker=Ryghel
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:906
msgid ""
"He’s probably in the storerooms right now. Go to your right and turn at the "
"last passage down the corridor."
msgstr ""
"Probablemente esté en las despensas ahora mismo. Ve a tu derecha y gira en "
"el último pasillo al final del corredor."

