#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/12_Destiny_part_3.cfg:1028
msgid "Current Objective:"
msgstr "Objetivo actual:"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:923
msgid "Talk to the guard captain"
msgstr "Habla con el capitán de la guardia"

#. [message]: speaker=Captain Verathorn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:954
msgid "Who goes there?"
msgstr "¿Quién va ahí?"

#. [message]: speaker=Vyrelyam
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:966
msgid ""
"Sir, I have been sent by the Demon Lord of the Storms to bring a message to—"
msgstr ""
"Señor, he sido enviado por el Señor Demonio de las Tormentas para entregar "
"un mensaje a—"

#. [message]: speaker=Captain Verathorn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:971
msgid "Is it anything you aren’t allowed to pass on to me?"
msgstr "¿Es algo que no estás autorizada a comunicarme?"

#. [message]: speaker=Vyrelyam
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:976
msgid "... Yes, quite so. I would prefer to talk to the Fire in pe—"
msgstr "... Sí, así es. Preferiría hablar con el Fuego en pe—"

#. [message]: speaker=Captain Verathorn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:981
msgid ""
"The Fire does not want to see anyone right now in her chamber, or anywhere "
"else for that matter. She said so herself: “I don’t want anyone coming into "
"this fortress tonight”. Maybe those deaf sluggards at the main gate need a "
"lesson or two...?"
msgstr ""
"El Fuego no quiere ver a nadie ahora mismo en su cámara, ni en ningún otro "
"lugar. Ella misma lo dijo: “No quiero que nadie entre en esta fortaleza esta "
"noche”. Quizá esos zopencos sordos en la puerta principal necesiten una "
"lección o dos...?"

#. [message]: speaker=Captain Verathorn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:990
msgid "What’s your name, girl?"
msgstr "¿Cuál es tu nombre, chica?"

#. [message]: speaker=Vyrelyam
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:995
msgid "Vyrelyam, sir."
msgstr "Vyrelyam, señor."

#. [message]: speaker=Captain Verathorn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1000
msgid ""
"I hadn’t seen your face around before. But there’s something oddly familiar "
"about it..."
msgstr ""
"No había visto tu rostro antes por aquí. Pero tiene algo extrañamente "
"familiar..."

#. [message]: speaker=Vyrelyam
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1005
msgid "Is that so? ... Perhaps you may also recall torturing an elf or two..."
msgstr ""
"¿Es así? ... Quizá también recuerdes haber torturado a uno o dos elfos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Captain Verathorn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1014
msgid "YOU—"
msgstr "TÚ—"

#. [message]: speaker=Vyrelyam
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1030
msgid ""
"Well... that didn’t work as planned. We must find a way to open that gate by "
"ourselves."
msgstr ""
"Bueno... eso no salió como planeábamos. Debemos encontrar la forma de abrir "
"esa puerta por nuestra cuenta."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1033
msgid "Melor"
msgstr "Melor"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1034
msgid "Irumia"
msgstr "Irumia"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1035
msgid "Harakas"
msgstr "Harakas"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1040
msgid "Move your leader back to the entrance chamber"
msgstr "Mueve a tu líder de regreso a la cámara de entrada"

#. [message]: speaker=Irumia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1068
msgid "There she is!"
msgstr "¡Ahí está ella!"

#. [message]: speaker=Melor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1073
msgid "Your illusions can’t deceive me, faerie witch!"
msgstr "¡Tus ilusiones no pueden engañarme, bruja feérica!"

#. [message]: speaker=Teremor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1106
msgid "Seize her, quickly!"
msgstr "¡Captúrala, rápido!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1111
msgid "There goes our infiltration plan. To arms!"
msgstr "Se acabó nuestro plan de infiltración. ¡A las armas!"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1150
msgid "Find a way to open the main access gate"
msgstr "Encuentra la forma de abrir la puerta principal de acceso"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1188
msgid "Proceed through the main access gate"
msgstr "Avanza a través de la puerta principal de acceso"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1221
msgid ""
"And thus I descend into the darkness of Uria’s key stronghold on Irdya..."
msgstr "Y así desciendo a la oscuridad del bastión clave de Uria en Irdya..."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1223
msgid ""
"Ergea’s words were clear: we do not have a chance to win this war and purge "
"the corrupted goddess’ influence from this earth; not without the power "
"hidden beneath Kalari."
msgstr ""
"Las palabras de Ergea fueron claras: no tenemos oportunidad de ganar esta "
"guerra y purgar la influencia de la diosa corrupta de esta tierra; no sin el "
"poder oculto bajo Kalari."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1225
msgid ""
"I do not intend to stand watching while she turns our ruined world into "
"breeding grounds for her invasion army. Neither could I bear to live knowing "
"that it is in her plans to tear another world apart and threaten our very "
"reality to quench her dreadful thirst for power. I have to do something to "
"prevent that."
msgstr ""
"No pienso quedarme mirando mientras convierte nuestro mundo arruinado en "
"criadero para su ejército invasor. Tampoco podría soportar vivir sabiendo "
"que planea destrozar otro mundo y amenazar nuestra propia realidad para "
"saciar su terrible sed de poder. Tengo que hacer algo para evitarlo."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1227
msgid "No matter the cost."
msgstr "Cueste lo que cueste."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1313
msgid ""
"elynia^This is not the right corridor. We must find a way leading to the "
"transport room."
msgstr ""
"Este no es el pasillo correcto. Debemos encontrar un camino que lleve a la "
"sala de transporte."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1319
msgid ""
"elynia^That is not the right corridor. We must find a way leading to the "
"transport room."
msgstr ""
"Ese no es el pasillo correcto. Debemos encontrar un camino que lleve a la "
"sala de transporte."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1343
msgid ""
"Just a bunch of gold coins. Too bad that they are rather weighty and we have "
"no use for them at this time."
msgstr ""
"Solo un montón de monedas de oro. Lástima que sean bastante pesadas y no les "
"demos uso por ahora."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1364
msgid "There’s nothing in this chest."
msgstr "No hay nada en este cofre."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1400
msgid ""
"This potion flask seems important. Let the Lady of Light come to examine it."
msgstr ""
"Esta botella de poción parece importante. Que la Dama de la Luz venga a "
"examinarla."

#. [object]: id=potion_of_life
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1458
msgid "Potion of Life"
msgstr "Poción de vida"

#. [object]: id=potion_of_life
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1459
msgid ""
"This potion grants the Regenerates ability, allowing the unit to heal itself "
"8 HP per turn or remove the poison effect."
msgstr ""
"Esta poción otorga la habilidad de Regeneración, permitiendo que la unidad "
"se cure 8 puntos de vida por turno o elimine el efecto de veneno."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1470
msgid "Hm, this might prove useful later."
msgstr "Hmm, esto podría ser útil más adelante."

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1495
msgid "Potion of Magnificent Taste"
msgstr "Poción de Sabor Magnífico"

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1498
msgid ""
"The potion’s stupendous and reinvigorating taste heals the unit by 1 HP."
msgstr ""
"El sabor estupendo y revitalizante de la poción cura a la unidad 1 de PS."

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1548
msgid "Legendary Sword"
msgstr "Espada Legendaria"

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1550
msgid ""
"This sword, forgotten by time, once belonged to a legendary hero who "
"presumably died in a glorious and dignified fashion like real heroes are "
"wont to do. Unfortunately, since then it has rusted beyond use, and as the "
"unit picks it up it snaps in half. The sword is now only marginally better "
"than a small rock in combat — not that Elynia has any units that are trained "
"in sword-fighting anyway."
msgstr ""
"Esta espada, olvidada por el tiempo, perteneció a un héroe legendario que "
"presumiblemente murió de manera gloriosa y digna, como suelen hacerlo los "
"verdaderos héroes. Desafortunadamente, desde entonces se ha oxidado hasta "
"volverse inutilizable, y cuando la unidad la recoge se parte por la mitad. "
"Ahora la espada es apenas mejor que una pequeña piedra en combate — aunque "
"Elynia no tiene unidades entrenadas en esgrima de todos modos."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1597
msgid "Should this unit take it?"
msgstr "¿Debería esta unidad tomarlo?"

#. [option]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1599
msgid "Take it."
msgstr "Tomarlo."

#. [option]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1611
msgid "Leave it."
msgstr "Déjalo."

#. [scenario]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1639
msgid ""
"This small axe is not particularly suitable for combat at close quarters, "
"but it may come in handy as a throwable weapon."
msgstr ""
"Esta pequeña hacha no es particularmente adecuada para combate cuerpo a "
"cuerpo, pero puede ser útil como arma arrojadiza."

#. [scenario]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1640
msgid ""
"This small axe could be useful in the hands of a trained man or demon "
"fighter."
msgstr ""
"Esta pequeña hacha podría ser útil en manos de un combatiente humano o "
"demoníaco entrenado."

#. [object]: id=throwing_axe
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1645
msgid "Small Axe"
msgstr "Hacha Pequeña"

#. [object]: id=throwing_axe
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1646
msgid ""
"The unit wielding this weapon may use it for long range combat to inflict "
"some considerable blade damage."
msgstr ""
"La unidad que empuñe esta arma puede usarla para combate a larga distancia e "
"infligir un daño considerable con la hoja."

#. [effect]: type=blade
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1656
msgid "throwing axe"
msgstr "hacha arrojadiza"

#. [scenario]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1705
msgid ""
"The poison in the jar could be poured on claws or weapons and used against "
"living opponents in melee combat to increase attack efficiency through its "
"devastating effects on their health."
msgstr ""
"El veneno del frasco puede ser vertido en garras o armas y usado contra "
"oponentes vivos en combate cuerpo a cuerpo para aumentar la efectividad del "
"ataque mediante sus devastadores efectos en la salud."

#. [scenario]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1706
msgid ""
"This large jar contains poison that could be poured on claws or weapons and "
"used against living opponents by a trained melee fighter or a staff-wielding "
"magic user."
msgstr ""
"Este gran frasco contiene veneno que puede ser vertido en garras o armas y "
"usado contra oponentes vivos por un luchador cuerpo a cuerpo entrenado o un "
"usuario de magia con bastón."

#. [object]: id=poison_jar
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1711
msgid "Poison Jar"
msgstr "Frasco de Veneno"

#. [object]: id=poison_jar
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1712
msgid ""
"The unit employing this foul-smelling death catalyst can poison living "
"opponents by dealing damage with its melee attacks."
msgstr ""
"La unidad que use este catalizador de muerte maloliente puede envenenar a "
"los oponentes vivos al infligir daño con sus ataques cuerpo a cuerpo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1780
msgid ""
"We must all enter the transport room together — nobody should be left behind."
msgstr ""
"Debemos entrar todos juntos en la sala de transporte — nadie debe quedarse "
"atrás."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1786
msgid "Gather all your on-map units in the transport room"
msgstr "Reúne todas tus unidades en el mapa dentro de la sala de transporte"

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:1925
msgid "Now what?"
msgstr "¿Y ahora qué?"

#. [unit]: type=Lumeril Guard, id=Agathylas
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2006
msgid "Agathylas"
msgstr "Agathylas"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2100
msgid "Mal Boras"
msgstr "Mal Boras"

#. [unit]: type=Lich, id=Mal Gulgolet
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2107
msgid "Mal Gulgolet"
msgstr "Mal Gulgolet"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2179
msgid "Council Chamber"
msgstr "Cámara del Consejo"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2180
msgid "Abandoned Council Chamber"
msgstr "Cámara del Consejo Abandonada"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2221
msgid "The transporter abruptly stops."
msgstr "El transportador se detiene bruscamente."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2257
msgid "I recognize this corridor. Onwards!"
msgstr "Reconozco este pasillo. ¡Adelante!"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2263
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:123
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:398
msgid "Proceed further underground"
msgstr "Avanza más en las profundidades"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Gulgolet
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2334
msgid ""
"The Lady of Light and her foolish new cohorts, eh? We should have known that "
"Ergea and her kind couldn’t be trusted. Hopefully you enjoy their company, "
"for we intend to send you all to the abyss together, and not precisely to "
"die..."
msgstr ""
"¿La Dama de la Luz y sus necios nuevos compañeros, eh? Deberíamos haber "
"sabido que Ergea y los suyos no eran de fiar. Espero que disfruten su "
"compañía, porque planeamos enviarles a todos juntos al abismo… y no "
"precisamente a morir..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Gulgolet
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2340
msgid ""
"The Lady of Light, eh? We should have known that Ergea and her kind couldn’t "
"be trusted. Too bad that your cohorts didn’t make it; we wanted to send you "
"all to the abyss together, and not precisely to die..."
msgstr ""
"¿La Dama de la Luz, eh? Deberíamos haber sabido que Ergea y los suyos no "
"eran de fiar. Lástima que tus compañeros no lo lograron; queríamos enviarles "
"a todos juntos al abismo… y no precisamente a morir..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#. 'Master' here in feminine, referring to Elyssa (the 'Fire').
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2348
msgid ""
"Save your boasting for later — it will not help you win the battle on the "
"surface and we are well accustomed to it at this point. Where is your master?"
msgstr ""
"Guarda tus fanfarronadas para más tarde: no te ayudarán a ganar la batalla "
"en la superficie, y ya estamos bien acostumbrados a ellas a estas alturas. "
"¿Dónde está tu ama?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Gulgolet
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2353
msgid ""
"Our <i>masters</i> are busy with their own inscrutable plans, and the "
"fortress defenses are already disposing of your pathetic allies above. But "
"it is not <i>your</i> place to ask questions here. Now..."
msgstr ""
"Nuestros <i>amos</i> están ocupados con sus propios e inescrutables planes, "
"y las defensas de la fortaleza ya se están encargando de tus patéticos "
"aliados arriba. Pero aquí no es <i>tu</i> lugar para hacer preguntas. Ahora…"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Gulgolet
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2362
msgid ""
"Would you prefer to go down fighting, or surrender and let us take you to "
"the Fire?"
msgstr ""
"¿Prefieres caer luchando o rendirte y permitir que te llevemos al Fuego?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2371
msgid "I’ll let you have a guess."
msgstr "Te dejaré adivinarlo."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Gulgolet
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2386
msgid "... heh. The Fire was right... about you..."
msgstr "... jeh. El Fuego tenía razón… sobre ti..."

#. [unit]: type=Demon Spelldancer, id=Talia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2403
msgid "Talia"
msgstr "Talia"

#. [unit]: type=Chaos Lorekeeper, id=Mal Arachgeas
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2484
msgid "Mal Arachgeas"
msgstr "Mal Arachgeas"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2581
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3327
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:963
msgid "Is that..."
msgstr "¿Es eso..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2624
msgid "Those passages appear to lead somewhere."
msgstr "Esos pasajes parecen conducir a algún lugar."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2720
msgid ""
"A secret passage. Not particularly ingenious. Although... it might lead to "
"the cave Ergea mentioned."
msgstr ""
"Un pasaje secreto. No es particularmente ingenioso. Aunque… podría conducir "
"a la cueva que mencionó Ergea."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2743
msgid "Wait. There’s someone else in here..."
msgstr "Espera. Hay alguien más aquí dentro..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2831
msgid ""
"It’s the other necromancer, member of the Iron Triad. Perhaps, if we take "
"her down... we might be able to force her to give us some directions."
msgstr ""
"Es la otra nigromante, miembro de la Tríada de Hierro. Quizás, si la "
"derrotamos… podamos obligarla a darnos algunas indicaciones."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2837
msgid ""
"It’s the other necromancer, member of the Iron Triad. Perhaps, if I take her "
"down... I might be able to force her to give me some directions."
msgstr ""
"Es la otra nigromante, miembro de la Tríada de Hierro. Quizás, si la "
"derroto… pueda obligarla a darme algunas indicaciones."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2849
msgid "Defeat Mal Kendria"
msgstr "Derrota a Mal Kendria"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2872
msgid ""
"You are the other necromancer from the Iron Triad, aren’t you? Where is your "
"master hiding? Where is the Ruby of Fire?"
msgstr ""
"Eres la otra nigromante de la Tríada de Hierro, ¿no es así? ¿Dónde se "
"esconde tu maestra? ¿Dónde está el Rubí de Fuego?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2886
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3190
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/storytxt.cfg:67
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/storytxt.cfg:73
msgid "(<i>silence</i>)"
msgstr "(<i>silencio</i>)"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2895
msgid "Are you going to answer?"
msgstr "¿Vas a responder?"

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2908
msgid "There is something wrong about her eyes..."
msgstr "Hay algo extraño en sus ojos…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2913
msgid "I don’t have time for this."
msgstr "No tengo tiempo para esto."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2940
msgid ""
"Devoid of her own will... and turned into a living puppet... Suddenly, "
"defeating her does not seem to be much of an achievement. I don’t think I "
"saw anything like this the last time I was here. Why would they do this to "
"her, though?"
msgstr ""
"Privada de su propia voluntad… y convertida en una marioneta viviente… De "
"repente, derrotarla no parece ser un gran logro. No creo haber visto nada "
"así la última vez que estuve aquí. ¿Por qué le harían esto?"

#. [message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2950
msgid ""
"My lady, we should proceed onwards, quickly. We don’t have much more time, "
"and the Fire of Uria will not take kindly to all these casualties."
msgstr ""
"Mi señora, debemos avanzar rápidamente. No tenemos mucho más tiempo, y el "
"Fuego de Uria no se tomará bien todas estas bajas."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2955
msgid ""
"Indeed, let us continue down this passage. If Ergea’s instructions are "
"correct, there is a large stone chamber ahead."
msgstr ""
"En efecto, continuemos por este pasaje. Si las instrucciones de Ergea son "
"correctas, hay una gran cámara de piedra más adelante."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:2961
msgid ""
"I should just continue down this passage. If Ergea’s instructions are "
"correct, there is a large stone chamber ahead."
msgstr ""
"Debo seguir por este pasaje. Si las instrucciones de Ergea son correctas, "
"hay una gran cámara de piedra más adelante."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3000
msgid "Move Elynia into the chamber"
msgstr "Mueve a Elynia a la cámara"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3140
msgid "We are trapped in this chamber..."
msgstr "Estamos atrapados en esta cámara…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3146
msgid "I am trapped in this chamber..."
msgstr "Estoy atrapada en esta cámara…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3170
msgid ""
"(<i>chuckles</i>) That’s were you want us to go. Isn’t that correct... "
"Elyssa?"
msgstr "(<i>risita</i>) Ahí es donde quieres que vayamos. ¿No es así… Elyssa?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3176
msgid ""
"(<i>chuckles</i>) That’s were you want me to go. Isn’t that correct... "
"Elyssa?"
msgstr "(<i>risita</i>) Ahí es donde quieres que vaya. ¿No es así… Elyssa?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3199
msgid "You could have opened the gate for me, at the very least."
msgstr "Podrías haber abierto la puerta para mí, al menos."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3209
msgid "Find a way to open the chamber exit gate to proceed"
msgstr ""
"Encuentra la forma de abrir la puerta de salida de la cámara para continuar"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3264
msgid ""
"Elynia already has the glyph’s spell. Move her next to the chamber exit to "
"open it."
msgstr ""
"Elynia ya tiene el hechizo del glifo. Muévela junto a la salida de la cámara "
"para abrirla."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3271
msgid "Elynia should be the one to investigate this glyph."
msgstr "Elynia debería ser quien investigue este glifo."

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3286
msgid "Barrier Spell"
msgstr "Hechizo de Barrera"

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3289
msgid ""
"This spell allows the unit to open any barriers that were originally sealed "
"with the same spell."
msgstr ""
"Este hechizo permite a la unidad abrir cualquier barrera que haya sido "
"sellada originalmente con el mismo hechizo."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3302
msgid "Move Elynia next to the chamber exit gate to proceed"
msgstr "Mueve a Elynia junto a la puerta de salida de la cámara para continuar"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3400
msgid "... So you want me to proceed alone. Very well, then."
msgstr "... Así que quieres que continúe sola. Muy bien, entonces."

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_1.cfg:3630
msgid ""
"You have eight allies on the map already. You cannot recruit additional "
"units at this time!"
msgstr ""
"Ya tienes ocho aliados en el mapa. ¡No puedes reclutar más unidades por el "
"momento!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:227
msgid "I will be truly disappointed if you aren’t waiting behind that gate..."
msgstr ""
"Me sentiré verdaderamente decepcionada si no me esperas detrás de esa "
"puerta..."

#. [scenario]: id=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:260
#, fuzzy
msgid "Elyssa, the Guardian of Darkness"
msgstr "Guardiana de la Oscuridad"

#. [scenario]: id=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:260
msgid "Heiress to the Eater of Soul’s Legacy"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:316
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr "Hm..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:325
msgid ""
"I have been awaiting this moment for so long, Elyssa. Or should I call you "
"Yechnagoth?"
msgstr ""
"He esperado este momento por tanto tiempo, Elyssa. ¿O debería llamarte "
"Yechnagoth?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:336
msgid "Yechnagoth is no more."
msgstr "Yechnagoth ya no existe."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:370
msgid "Vanquish Elyssa"
msgstr "Derrota a Elyssa"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:539
msgid "Do you truly believe that such cheap tricks can stop me?"
msgstr "¿De verdad crees que esos trucos baratos pueden detenerme?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:683
msgid ""
"I suppose I may as well call you an impostor then. I have read Argan’s "
"journal — you weren’t destined to possess those powers."
msgstr ""
"Supongo que debería llamarte impostora entonces. He leído el diario de "
"Argan: no estabas destinada a poseer esos poderes."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:688
msgid ""
"It was never my choice, dear. And even if it were the case, I have never "
"actually <i>claimed</i> to be Merthiaal."
msgstr ""
"Nunca fue mi elección, querida. Y aunque lo fuera, en realidad nunca <i>he "
"afirmado</i> ser Merthiaal."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:697
msgid "I have to admit that you are quite agile for a winged faerie."
msgstr "Debo admitir que eres bastante ágil para ser un hada alada."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:706
msgid "Alas, that will not be sufficient to defeat me."
msgstr "Pero eso no será suficiente para derrotarme."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:715
msgid "I had hoped you would have learned new tricks since we last met."
msgstr ""
"Esperaba que hubieras aprendido nuevos trucos desde la última vez que nos "
"vimos."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:724
msgid "As much as I would not mind to keep doing this forever..."
msgstr "Por mucho que no me importaría seguir haciendo esto por siempre..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:729
msgid ""
"You purposefully misled us by removing any references to the final "
"whereabouts of Yechnagoth’s heart from Argan’s journal, didn’t you?"
msgstr ""
"Nos engañaste a propósito al eliminar cualquier referencia sobre el paradero "
"final del corazón de Yechnagoth del diario de Argan, ¿verdad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:734
msgid ""
"I admit that I took some pages from Argan’s journal some time before you "
"acquired it from him, yes; I also changed a few other things for your "
"<i>convenience</i>."
msgstr ""
"Admito que tomé algunas páginas del diario de Argan un tiempo antes de que "
"tú lo consiguieras de él, sí; también cambié algunas otras cosas para tu "
"<i>comodidad</i>."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:739
msgid ""
"You killed Galas before my very eyes. You are responsible for Mal Keshar’s "
"destruction. And for the deaths of millions."
msgstr ""
"Mataste a Galas ante mis propios ojos. Eres responsable de la destrucción de "
"Mal Keshar. Y de la muerte de millones."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:744
msgid ""
"(<i>chuckles</i>) It was all part of the plan! All those deaths were "
"necessary to appease Uria and prepare our vast stage for this day — the vast "
"stage we normally call ‘Irdya’. My business with that elf you secretly loved "
"was not personal."
msgstr ""
"(<i>risas</i>) ¡Todo era parte del plan! Todas esas muertes fueron "
"necesarias para apaciguar a Uria y preparar nuestro gran escenario para este "
"día, el vasto escenario que normalmente llamamos ‘Irdya’. Mis asuntos con "
"ese elfo que amabas en secreto no fueron personales."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:754
msgid ""
"Those who can harness the Aspect of Darkness can read into the minds of "
"weaker creatures at will. Did you not know this?"
msgstr ""
"Aquellos que dominan el Aspecto de la Oscuridad pueden leer las mentes de "
"criaturas más débiles a voluntad. ¿No lo sabías?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:763
msgid ""
"Of course you didn’t. You have wasted your entire life pursuing the most "
"banal objectives. You never bothered to try to understand that power you "
"had. Argan and you could have done great things if you had learned what the "
"Union truly entails."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que no. Has desperdiciado toda tu vida persiguiendo los "
"objetivos más banales. Nunca te molestaste en tratar de comprender ese poder "
"que poseías. Argan y tú podrían haber hecho grandes cosas si hubieran "
"aprendido lo que la Unión realmente implica."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:772
msgid ""
"You have lived awake for over eight hundred years, and yet... you are still "
"an incompetent little brat. Such is the curse of eternal youth, I guess?"
msgstr ""
"Has vivido despierta durante más de ochocientos años y aun así... sigues "
"siendo una mocosa incompetente. Tal vez esa sea la maldición de la juventud "
"eterna, ¿eh?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:782
msgid ""
"Are you not exhausted already? You sure are persistent. I could end you with "
"a single strike if I wanted..."
msgstr ""
"¿Acaso no estás ya agotada? Eres realmente persistente. Podría acabar "
"contigo de un solo golpe si quisiera..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:787
msgid "THEN WHY DON’T YOU DO IT?!"
msgstr "¡ENTONCES, ¿POR QUÉ NO LO HACES?!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:792
msgid "Is that what you truly want, then? Do you seek the cold touch of death?"
msgstr "¿Es eso lo que realmente deseas? ¿Buscas el frío toque de la muerte?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:801
msgid ""
"And yet, you fear it. You haven’t been able to bring yourself to put an end "
"to this, but why?"
msgstr ""
"Y aun así, la temes. No has sido capaz de ponerle fin a todo esto, pero ¿por "
"qué?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:810
msgid ""
"Is it that you are unable to assume responsibility for your own decisions "
"anymore?"
msgstr ""
"¿Será que ya no puedes asumir la responsabilidad de tus propias decisiones?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:824
msgid ""
"I see. Frankly, this is quite disappointing. I thought Argan and Galas saw "
"<i>something</i> in you besides your pretty face and hair."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo. Francamente, esto es bastante decepcionante. Pensé que Argan y Galas "
"veían <i>algo</i> en ti además de tu bonita cara y tu cabello."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:834
msgid ""
"Oh, my bad. I forgot to mention that... You really want to know, don’t you? "
"Yes, Galas <i>did</i> want to reciprocate your feelings, but he never did "
"so... because you were too busy grieving over Argan’s death like a little "
"girl."
msgstr ""
"Oh, mi error. Olvidé mencionar que… Realmente quieres saberlo, ¿verdad? Sí, "
"Galas <i>sí</i> quería corresponder a tus sentimientos, pero nunca lo hizo… "
"porque estabas demasiado ocupada llorando la muerte de Argan como una niñita."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:844
msgid ""
"Perhaps, if you were not so stupid and ignorant of your own power... you "
"would have been able to save Argan in the first place. Don’t you think?"
msgstr ""
"Quizás, si no fueras tan estúpida e ignorante de tu propio poder… habrías "
"podido salvar a Argan en primer lugar. ¿No lo crees?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:853
msgid "Shut..."
msgstr "Cáll..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:862
msgid "UP!!!"
msgstr "¡ATE!!!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:952
msgid "... What—"
msgstr "… ¿Qué—?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:957
msgid "Heh, heh, heh..."
msgstr "Je, je, je…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:966
msgid "Good..."
msgstr "Bien..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1019
msgid "But still not sufficient to defeat a Guardian of Darkness, my dear."
msgstr ""
"Pero aún no es suficiente para derrotar a una Guardiana de la Oscuridad, "
"querida."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1046
msgid ""
"I had thought that this would be a fair fight, but in the end it was merely "
"a foolish hope. What do you think?"
msgstr ""
"Pensé que esto sería un combate justo, pero al final no fue más que una "
"tonta esperanza. ¿Qué opinas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1055
msgid ""
"On the other hand, you are still alive and able to stand. I am impressed."
msgstr "Por otro lado, sigues viva y en pie. Estoy impresionada."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1060
msgid "What... are you... waiting for..."
msgstr "¿Qué… estás… esperando…?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1065
msgid "Heh."
msgstr "Je."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07A_Dark_Fire_part_2.cfg:1074
msgid "Sweet dreams, my dear."
msgstr "Dulces sueños, querida."

