#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08B_Destiny_part_1.cfg:295
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08B_Destiny_part_1.cfg:694
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08B_Destiny_part_1.cfg:1220
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:479
msgid "Death of Cron"
msgstr "Muerte de Cron"

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:653
msgid ""
"My scouts have just informed me that the bulk of the region’s defenses are "
"already in motion and heading for our present location. They shall be here "
"in just a few hours. It is possible that someone betrayed us, or..."
msgstr ""
"Mis exploradores me han informado que la mayor parte de las defensas de la "
"región ya están en movimiento y se dirigen hacia nuestra ubicación. Llegarán "
"en pocas horas. Es posible que alguien nos haya traicionado, o..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:662
msgid "... She is not coming back, is she?"
msgstr "... No va a regresar, ¿verdad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:667
msgid "I thought we were all gonna fight together..."
msgstr "Pensé que íbamos a luchar todos juntos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Irylean
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:672
msgid ""
"She must have had a good reason for leaving us like this, Anya. Well... I "
"hope so, anyway. My lady, what about those reinforcements?"
msgstr ""
"Debe haber tenido una buena razón para dejarnos así, Anya. Bueno... al menos "
"eso espero. Mi señora, ¿qué hay de esos refuerzos?"

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:684
msgid ""
"The old fort near the river city guards a second portal leading to the "
"northern lands whence you came. I had arranged for your allies to arrive "
"through it at dawn, but... this unexpected development jeopardizes the "
"success of the entire operation."
msgstr ""
"El viejo fuerte cerca de la ciudad junto al río protege un segundo portal "
"que conduce a las tierras del norte de donde ustedes vinieron. Había "
"organizado que sus aliados llegaran por allí al amanecer, pero... este "
"imprevisto pone en peligro el éxito de toda la operación."

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:690
msgid ""
"We must secure that fort as swiftly as we may. It is only a few hours before "
"dawn breaks. If we manage to distract our enemies for long enough, Elynia "
"might have an opportunity to succeed in her mission."
msgstr ""
"Debemos asegurar ese fuerte lo más rápido posible. Solo faltan unas pocas "
"horas para el amanecer. Si logramos distraer a nuestros enemigos el tiempo "
"suficiente, Elynia podría tener una oportunidad de cumplir su misión."

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:700
msgid ""
"The inhabitants of these lands are not too satisfied with the Iron Triad’s "
"management. I advise that we try to gain their support and stir up a "
"revolution — their numbers and resources may prove essential for what has "
"yet to come."
msgstr ""
"Los habitantes de estas tierras no están muy satisfechos con la gestión de "
"la Tríada de Hierro. Aconsejo que intentemos ganarnos su apoyo y provocar "
"una revolución; sus números y recursos podrían resultar esenciales para lo "
"que está por venir."

#. [message]: speaker=Irylean
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:705
msgid "Let us get moving then. Anya shall lead the way!"
msgstr "Entonces pongámonos en marcha. ¡Anya liderará el camino!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:710
msgid "I... shall?"
msgstr "¿Yo... lideraré?"

#. [message]: speaker=Irylean
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:715
msgid ""
"That’s what Elynia said in that note, did she not? But you don’t need to "
"worry about the management aspect — we can help you with that. Your darkness "
"powers and teleportation should be advantageous in the front line, but it’s "
"more important that these men are led by someone with whom they are already "
"well familiarized besides Elynia herself — another <i>someone</i> they can "
"relate to, if you catch my drift."
msgstr ""
"Eso es lo que Elynia dijo en esa nota, ¿no es así? Pero no tienes que "
"preocuparte por la gestión; podemos ayudarte con eso. Tus poderes de "
"oscuridad y teletransportación serán ventajosos en la línea del frente, pero "
"es más importante que estos hombres sean liderados por alguien con quien ya "
"estén bien familiarizados además de Elynia, <i>alguien</i> con quien puedan "
"identificarse, si entiendes lo que quiero decir."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:720
msgid "... Wait... you mean..."
msgstr "... Espera... ¿quieres decir..."

#. [message]: speaker=Irylean
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:725
msgid "Yes!"
msgstr "¡Sí!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:730
msgid ""
"(<i>annoyed</i>) Your rationale seems rather perverse, and it’s slightly "
"offensive considering I have never... unlike... Ack! How about... we just... "
"move on?!"
msgstr ""
"(<i>molesta</i>) Tu razonamiento parece bastante perverso, y es un poco "
"ofensivo considerando que yo nunca... a diferencia de... ¡Argh! ¿Qué tal "
"si... simplemente seguimos?!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:735
msgid "I support the motion. This is no time for such frivolous chatter."
msgstr "Apoyo la moción. No es momento para conversaciones tan frívolas."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:739
msgid ""
"As part of the agreement Elynia reached with the Demon Lord Ergea, you are "
"now able to recruit <b>Demons</b>, <b>Saurians</b>, and <b>Trolls</b>."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Jarayavel
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:755
msgid "So bold— argh..."
msgstr "Tan audaz... argh..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mereldyan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:767
msgid "The Fist shall not tolerate your intrusion..."
msgstr "El Puño no tolerará su intromisión..."

#. [message]: speaker=Zaraphor
#. The 'Fist' is a yet unseen male demon.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:780
msgid "The Fist knows... He knows everything... Flee while you can..."
msgstr "El Puño lo sabe... Lo sabe todo... Huyan mientras puedan..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elesmeera
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:792
msgid ""
"No, n— please no! My fair lady of the Storms, I— I did not have a choice! "
"The Fist— I— I—"
msgstr ""
"¡No, n— por favor no! Mi hermosa dama de las Tormentas, yo... yo no tenía "
"elección. El Puño... yo... yo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:797
msgid ""
"You betrayed me and my people. There is only one possible punishment for "
"such a grave misdeed under my rule and you are well aware what it is."
msgstr ""
"Traicionaste a mi pueblo y a mí. Solo hay un castigo posible para un acto "
"tan grave bajo mi mandato y sabes muy bien cuál es."

#. [message]: speaker=Elesmeera
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:802
msgid "No! I beg you—"
msgstr "¡No! Te lo suplico—"

#. [unit]: id=Theneryr, type=Bowman
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:828
msgid "Theneryr"
msgstr "Theneryr"

#. [unit]: id=Maergon, type=Bowman
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:843
msgid "Maergon"
msgstr "Maergon"

#. [unit]: id=Sergalyr, type=Spearman
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:858
msgid "Sergalyr"
msgstr "Sergalyr"

#. [unit]: id=Muthel, type=Thief, gender=male
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:873
msgid "Muthel"
msgstr "Muthel"

#. [unit]: id=Cyrelean, type=Thief, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:890
msgid "Cyrelean"
msgstr "Cyrelean"

#. [message]: speaker=Cyrelean
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:904
msgid ""
"The old order is coming to an end at last, and in time, freedom will be ours!"
msgstr ""
"¡El viejo orden llega finalmente a su fin, y con el tiempo, la libertad será "
"nuestra!"

#. [message]: speaker=Sergalyr
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:909
msgid ""
"Let us purge the foul worshipers of Uria and reclaim our ancestors’ lands!"
msgstr ""
"¡Purgaremos a los repugnantes adoradores de Uria y reclamaremos las tierras "
"de nuestros ancestros!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:936
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1251
msgid "Both playing teams retrieve $temp_gold_retrieval_amount pieces of gold."
msgstr ""
"Ambos equipos jugadores recuperan $temp_gold_retrieval_amount piezas de oro."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:972
msgid "I don’t understand... It should be dawn already!"
msgstr "No lo entiendo... ¡Ya debería haber amanecido!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:977
msgid "The... day of the Longest Night... This does not bode well."
msgstr "El... día de la Noche Más Larga... Esto no es buen presagio."

#. [message]: speaker=Irylean
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:999
msgid ""
"We failed to secure that portal in time! Without those reinforcements we "
"will never make it! Retreat!"
msgstr ""
"¡No aseguramos ese portal a tiempo! ¡Sin esos refuerzos no lo lograremos! "
"¡Retirada!"

#. [event]: type=Shaxthal War Drone, type=Shaxthal Enforcer Drone, type=Shaxthal Demolisher Drone, type=Chaos Cataphract, id=Celwyngyr, type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Morol, type=Lich, id=Mal Fyrgwynn, type=Demon Warrior, gender=male, id=Demon Lord Alavys
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1235
msgid "Celwyngyr"
msgstr "Celwyngyr"

#. [event]: type=Shaxthal War Drone, type=Shaxthal Enforcer Drone, type=Shaxthal Demolisher Drone, type=Chaos Cataphract, id=Celwyngyr, type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Morol, type=Lich, id=Mal Fyrgwynn, type=Demon Warrior, gender=male, id=Demon Lord Alavys
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1253
msgid "Morol"
msgstr "Morol"

#. [event]: type=Shaxthal War Drone, type=Shaxthal Enforcer Drone, type=Shaxthal Demolisher Drone, type=Chaos Cataphract, id=Celwyngyr, type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Morol, type=Lich, id=Mal Fyrgwynn, type=Demon Warrior, gender=male, id=Demon Lord Alavys
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1271
msgid "Mal Fyrgwynn"
msgstr "Mal Fyrgwynn"

#. [event]: type=Shaxthal War Drone, type=Shaxthal Enforcer Drone, type=Shaxthal Demolisher Drone, type=Chaos Cataphract, id=Celwyngyr, type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Morol, type=Lich, id=Mal Fyrgwynn, type=Demon Warrior, gender=male, id=Demon Lord Alavys
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1321
msgid "Demon Lord Alavys"
msgstr "Señor Demonio Alavys"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1529
msgid "Uh... It seems we arrived just in time."
msgstr "Uh... Parece que llegamos justo a tiempo."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1560
msgid "Archer guy!"
msgstr "¡Tirador!"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1565
msgid "Oh no. Er, I mean, hail!"
msgstr "Oh no. Eh, quiero decir, ¡saludos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1572
msgid "Durvan! I thought you would be on your way back home by now!"
msgstr "¡Durvan! ¡Pensé que ya estarías de camino a casa!"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1577
msgid ""
"I changed my mind, I guess? I can’t shake off the feeling that I’ll regret "
"this later, though. Where is Elynia?"
msgstr ""
"¿Cambié de opinión, supongo? Aunque no puedo quitarme de encima la sensación "
"de que me arrepentiré más tarde. ¿Dónde está Elynia?"

#. [message]: speaker=Irylean
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1582
msgid "We don’t know."
msgstr "No lo sabemos."

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1590
msgid ""
"You may discuss that at a later time. For now, it is of utmost importance "
"that we distract or take down Kalari’s military. I am confident that the "
"Alliance troops Sir Durvan has amassed shall serve us well for this mission."
msgstr ""
"Podrán hablar de eso más tarde. Por ahora, es de suma importancia que "
"distraígamos o eliminemos al ejército de Kalari. Estoy segura de que las "
"tropas de la Alianza que ha reunido el señor Durvan nos servirán bien en "
"esta misión."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1595
msgid ""
"It’s really General Bardyl and Elynia who should get the credit, not me. I "
"merely asked him to lend us a hand, and he gladly acceded, most likely in "
"return for Elynia’s support during the siege of Aran-Balgur. And "
"incidentally, I’m no Sir."
msgstr ""
"En realidad, el mérito es del general Bardyl y Elynia, no mío. Yo sólo le "
"pedí que nos echara una mano, y accedió de buena gana, probablemente a "
"cambio del apoyo de Elynia durante el asedio de Aran-Balgur. Y, por cierto, "
"no soy ningún señor."

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1601
msgid ""
"You may discuss that at a later time. For now, it is of utmost importance "
"that we distract or take down Kalari’s military. However, I expected Sir "
"Durvan to provide us with more numerous troops than this."
msgstr ""
"Podrán hablar de eso más tarde. Por ahora, es de suma importancia que "
"distraígamos o eliminemos al ejército de Kalari. Sin embargo, esperaba que "
"el señor Durvan nos proporcionara tropas más numerosas que estas."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1606
msgid ""
"General Bardyl wouldn’t accede to spending more lives on a pointless mission "
"after Elynia decided to part ways with him before they could properly "
"reclaim Aran-Balgur. So, I had to make do with low-ranking militiamen and "
"some orcish mercenaries. And incidentally, I’m no Sir."
msgstr ""
"El general Bardyl no quiso sacrificar más vidas en una misión sin sentido "
"después de que Elynia decidiera separarse de él antes de que pudieran "
"recuperar Aran-Balgur. Así que tuve que arreglármelas con milicianos de bajo "
"rango y algunos mercenarios orcos. Y, por cierto, no soy ningún señor."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1613
msgid ""
"Time is of the essence, Durvan. We need to get moving while the darkness can "
"provide us with an advantage."
msgstr ""
"El tiempo apremia, Durvan. Debemos avanzar mientras la oscuridad aún nos da "
"ventaja."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1618
msgid ""
"Sure, these men and women thirst for the blood of these fiends. Lead the way!"
msgstr ""
"Claro, estos hombres y mujeres ansían la sangre de esos engendros. ¡Guía el "
"camino!"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1651
msgid ""
"So, Elynia went on a mission to infiltrate the Iron Council’s citadel? What "
"kind of nonsense is that?"
msgstr ""
"¿Así que Elynia se fue en una misión para infiltrarse en la ciudadela del "
"Consejo de Hierro? ¿Qué clase de disparate es ese?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1656
msgid ""
"According to Ergea she went to locate some kind of weapon buried beneath "
"Kalari. I am really worried for her. She just left during the night without "
"telling anyone about her plans. What are we supposed to do now? I mean, "
"other than perpetuating this bloodshed. Ergea says it’s important and that "
"it might be her only chance to succeed. But who knows what kind of "
"abominations await in that place."
msgstr ""
"Según Ergea, se fue a buscar algún tipo de arma enterrada bajo Kalari. Estoy "
"muy preocupada por ella. Se marchó durante la noche sin contarle a nadie sus "
"planes. ¿Qué se supone que hagamos ahora? Quiero decir, aparte de perpetuar "
"esta masacre. Ergea dice que es importante y que podría ser su única "
"oportunidad de triunfar. Pero, ¿quién sabe qué clase de abominaciones la "
"esperan en ese lugar?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1665
msgid ""
"And then there is this inexplicable unending darkness. It <i>is</i> our "
"element, yet I can’t help but find all this dreadfully unnatural and "
"foreboding."
msgstr ""
"Y luego está esta inexplicable oscuridad interminable. <i>Es</i> nuestro "
"elemento, pero no puedo evitar encontrar todo esto terriblemente antinatural "
"y siniestro."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1670
msgid ""
"Yes... yes, it is. Maybe I shouldn’t have allowed Ergea to convince me to "
"come here."
msgstr ""
"Sí... sí, lo es. Quizá no debería haber dejado que Ergea me convenciera de "
"venir aquí."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1675
msgid "Ah, so you came back to us because she asked you to?"
msgstr "Ah, ¿así que volviste con nosotros porque ella te lo pidió?."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#. The first 'you' is singular; the second 'you' is plural.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1682
msgid ""
"Er... well, I admit that before she asked me I already wanted to see whether "
"you were all right... I mean, you people."
msgstr ""
"Eh... bueno, admito que antes de que ella me lo pidiera ya quería ver si "
"estabas bien... quiero decir, si ustedes estaban bien."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1687
msgid "Hm. I see."
msgstr "Hm. Ya veo."

#. [message]: speaker=Cron
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1702
msgid "Cron likes the sound of bones breaking under his hammer."
msgstr "A Cron le gusta el sonido de los huesos rompiéndose bajo su martillo."

#. [message]: speaker=Cron
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1717
msgid "Cron enjoys crushing insolent vermin to death."
msgstr "A Cron le gusta aplastar a las alimañas insolentes hasta matarlas."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1722
msgid "Get away from me, you beast!"
msgstr "¡Aléjate de mí, bestia!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1752
msgid ""
"Into the fountain of courage.\n"
"\n"
"Down the river of fear.\n"
"\n"
"A light in the darkness she patiently awaits."
msgstr ""
"En la fuente del valor.\n"
"\n"
"Por el río del miedo.\n"
"\n"
"Una luz en la oscuridad aguarda pacientemente."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1782
msgid ""
"A mysterious nymph sits on the rocks, contemplating the dark and restless "
"ocean in front of her with a blank expression.\n"
"\n"
"She seems completely uninterested in the creature’s presence as well. When "
"approached, the nymph does not make eye contact and instead conjures a "
"number of bubbles out of thin air. They seem far more deserving of her "
"attention than even the carnage currently taking place not too far away on "
"the riverside.\n"
"\n"
"Perhaps she is waiting for someone."
msgstr ""
"Una misteriosa ninfa está sentada sobre las rocas, contemplando el oscuro e "
"inquieto océano frente a ella con una expresión vacía.\n"
"\n"
"Parece completamente desinteresada en la presencia de la criatura. Al "
"acercarse, la ninfa no establece contacto visual y en su lugar conjura un "
"número de burbujas de la nada. Parecen mucho más dignas de su atención que "
"incluso la carnicería que tiene lugar no muy lejos en la ribera.\n"
"\n"
"Quizá esté esperando a alguien."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1795
msgid ""
"The water nymph continues to play with her bubbles.\n"
"\n"
"Perhaps she is waiting for someone."
msgstr ""
"La ninfa acuática sigue jugando con sus burbujas.\n"
"\n"
"Quizá esté esperando a alguien."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1858
msgid "Ummm... Hello?"
msgstr "Ejem... ¿Hola?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1867
msgid ""
"I was wondering if you are a Naiad? I was told by Tara that your kind are "
"hardly ever seen by anyone at all..."
msgstr ""
"Me preguntaba si eres una náyade. Tara me dijo que vuestra clase rara vez es "
"vista por nadie..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1876
msgid ""
"Uhhh... yes... the ocean. It looks really ominous here at night, doesn’t "
"it?..."
msgstr ""
"Ehhh... sí... el océano. Se ve realmente amenazador aquí de noche, ¿no "
"crees?..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1893
msgid ""
"<i>(sighs)</i> I’m sorry, I should not have bothered you. I guess I will "
"leave you to... whatever it is you are doing..."
msgstr ""
"<i>(suspira)</i> Lo siento, no debería haberte molestado. Supongo que te "
"dejaré con... lo que sea que estés haciendo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1908
msgid ""
"You truly are a curious creature, Anya, daughter of Mintha. I had never "
"heard before of one born of faerie and demonkind. I suppose it’s only "
"natural that both rarely mingle due to their innate hatred of each other. "
"Although it makes you wonder... because in the very beginning all of us, "
"even humans, were considered ‘demons’ anyway, were we not? We were the "
"spirits brought to life by the Tree."
msgstr ""
"En verdad eres una criatura curiosa, Anya, hija de Mintha. Nunca antes había "
"oído de alguien nacido de hada y demonio. Supongo que es natural que ambos "
"rara vez se mezclen debido a su odio innato. Aunque te hace pensar... porque "
"al principio todos nosotros, incluso los humanos, éramos considerados "
"‘demonios’, ¿no es así? Éramos los espíritus traídos a la vida por el Árbol."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1925
msgid ""
"That name... how can you possibly know that name? I don’t... I don’t "
"understand—"
msgstr ""
"Ese nombre... ¿cómo es posible que sepas ese nombre? Yo no... no lo entiendo—"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1933
msgid ""
"I have been keeping an eye on the Lady of Light and her allies for longer "
"than even the Demon Lord and you have. I have seen her rise from the very "
"depths of Irdya, do battle against unfathomable foes hailing from a time and "
"place beyond the Veil, make her way through the accursed hordes of the "
"Mother of Urvatha with the help of the most improbable allies, and carry out "
"her sworn duty despite it taking the heaviest toll of all."
msgstr ""
"He estado observando a la Dama de la Luz y sus aliados durante más tiempo "
"del que incluso tú y el Señor Demonio llevan existiendo. La he visto "
"ascender desde las mismas profundidades de Irdya, luchar contra enemigos "
"insondables procedentes de un tiempo y lugar más allá del Velo, abrirse paso "
"entre las hordas malditas de la Madre de Urvatha con la ayuda de los aliados "
"más improbables, y cumplir con su deber jurado pese al precio tan alto que "
"ello le ha costado."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1941
msgid ""
"Accordingly, I provided one of her faeriekind allies with a small gift as a "
"reward for the fortitude of mind and body they displayed in battle."
msgstr ""
"En consecuencia, ofrecí a uno de sus aliados feéricos un pequeño regalo como "
"recompensa por la fortaleza de mente y cuerpo que demostró en combate."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1949
msgid ""
"I guided you towards a relic from the Golden Age as a reward for your "
"unfaltering optimism in the face of adversity."
msgstr ""
"Te guié hasta una reliquia de la Edad Dorada como recompensa por tu "
"inquebrantable optimismo frente a la adversidad."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1954
msgid "It doesn’t do anything, though. Elynia said there’s no magic in it."
msgstr "Pero no hace nada. Elynia dijo que no hay magia en ella."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1959
msgid ""
"But does it need to be magic to feel precious to you? Does every experience "
"along your journey need to be viscerally gratifying in order for you to "
"build an emotional attachment to those memories?"
msgstr ""
"¿Acaso necesita ser mágica para resultarte preciosa? ¿Todas las experiencias "
"de tu viaje deben ser visceralmente gratificantes para que formes un vínculo "
"emocional con esos recuerdos?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1964
msgid ""
"I... suppose you are right. It reminds me so much of her somehow... Oh gods, "
"I hope she is all right..."
msgstr ""
"Yo... supongo que tienes razón. De algún modo me recuerda tanto a ella... Oh "
"dioses, espero que esté bien..."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1971
msgid ""
"The only thing left for me to do is to assist you in this upcoming battle "
"however I can so that you may see the light of day again. I must warn you "
"first, though, the power that was conferred upon me by the Goddess is very "
"limited, and time is running short. I can give you the answer to one "
"question about the past, and a last blessing."
msgstr ""
"Lo único que me queda por hacer es ayudarte en la próxima batalla como "
"pueda, para que puedas ver la luz del día nuevamente. Pero debo advertirte: "
"el poder que me confirió la Diosa es muy limitado y el tiempo se agota. "
"Puedo darte la respuesta a una pregunta sobre el pasado y una última "
"bendición."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1976
msgid "One question?"
msgstr "¿Una pregunta?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1991
msgid "This is so unexpected... I don’t know what I should ask..."
msgstr "Esto es tan inesperado... No sé qué debería preguntar..."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:1996
msgid "What does your heart tell you?"
msgstr "¿Qué te dice tu corazón?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2011
msgid "I want to know..."
msgstr "Quiero saber..."

#. [option]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2014
msgid "Who are my real parents?"
msgstr "¿Quiénes son mis verdaderos padres?"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#. The Nameless Shapeshifter's pronouns are they/them. They are non-binary. I understand that this doesn't
#. work well for certain languages, but I have deliberately chosen not to suggest an alternative for those,
#. unlike the translator's notes I've left for terms like "Warlord" and "Demon Lord" and other instances of
#. vague or unspecified gender. You are on your own here. Do your research.
#. Also note that Daeira uses "the Demon Lord Foo" to refer to each Demon Lord, instead of "Lord Foo" (used
#. by infernal underlings as well as the Chaos Empire's forces) or even just "Foo" (used by everyone else).
#. This is intentional.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2033
msgid ""
"Nineteen years ago, a Nameless Shapeshifter broke free from a lifetime of "
"servitude under the Demon Lord Nar-hamoth during one of his visits to Irdya. "
"Lacking any practical knowledge of this world and with nothing on their side "
"but their species’ natural endurance, they made their way north along the "
"Great Continent’s perilous seaboard. Defectors are not treated well by the "
"threats within Uria’s domain, but the dark of the night proved a faithful "
"ally to the Nameless One, allowing them to escape most of the obstacles they "
"found on their way North."
msgstr ""
"Hace diecinueve años, un Cambiante Sin Nombre logró liberarse de toda una "
"vida de servidumbre bajo el Demonio Nar-hamoth durante una de sus visitas a "
"Irdya. Sin ningún conocimiento práctico de este mundo y con nada a su favor "
"salvo la resistencia natural de su especie, emprendió el camino hacia el "
"norte por la peligrosa costa del Gran Continente. Los desertores no son bien "
"tratados por las amenazas del dominio de Uria, pero la oscuridad de la noche "
"resultó un aliado fiel para el Sin Nombre, permitiéndole escapar de la "
"mayoría de los obstáculos que encontró en su ruta hacia el norte."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2038
msgid ""
"Their long and grueling journey eventually led them to the great eucalyptus "
"forests of Glamdrol. There it is that they finally found shelter from the "
"scourge of Uria — but not before exhausting all their remaining energy. "
"Shapeshifters may be durable creatures, but that does not make them "
"immortal. On the contrary, constant punishment under their masters only "
"makes them weaker and more prone to diseases specific to their kind. The "
"Nameless One was no exception in this regard."
msgstr ""
"Su largo y agotador viaje finalmente los llevó a los grandes bosques de "
"eucaliptos de Glamdrol. Allí encontraron por fin refugio del azote de Uria, "
"pero no antes de haber agotado todas sus energías restantes. Los cambiantes "
"pueden ser criaturas resistentes, pero eso no los hace inmortales. Por el "
"contrario, el castigo constante bajo sus amos solo los debilita y los hace "
"más propensos a enfermedades propias de su clase. El Sin Nombre no fue una "
"excepción en este aspecto."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2043
msgid ""
"Despite their unfamiliarity with the peoples of Irdya, the Nameless One "
"intuitively knew that the natives would be quick to recognize them as a "
"creature hailing from the Chaos Empire, simply from observing their behavior "
"and way of speaking. Attempting to obtain help could only result in an even "
"more painful death at best, and a return to subjugation at worst.\n"
"\n"
"As the suns departed for the Long Dark, they decided that dying on their own "
"terms as a free soul was a far more preferable fate to any of the "
"alternatives. They were at peace."
msgstr ""
"A pesar de su desconocimiento de los pueblos de Irdya, el Sin Nombre sabía "
"de forma intuitiva que los nativos no tardarían en reconocerlo como una "
"criatura proveniente del Imperio del Caos, solo con observar su "
"comportamiento y forma de hablar. Intentar obtener ayuda solo podría "
"resultar, en el mejor de los casos, en una muerte aún más dolorosa y, en el "
"peor, en un regreso a la subyugación.\n"
"\n"
"Cuando los soles se marcharon hacia la Larga Oscuridad, decidió que morir en "
"sus propios términos como un alma libre era un destino mucho más preferible "
"a cualquiera de las alternativas. Estaba en paz."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2050
msgid ""
"Ready for their eternal rest, the demon collapsed on the cold forest ground "
"next to a spearmint patch, hopeful that the soothing aroma would ease the "
"pain that was yet to come. They closed their eyes, and the world "
"disappeared. The cold slowly subsided and gave way to a comforting warmth. "
"Never in their life had the Nameless One imagined that the embrace of death "
"could feel so welcoming compared to anything else they experienced."
msgstr ""
"Preparado para su descanso eterno, el demonio se desplomó en el suelo frío "
"del bosque, junto a un parche de menta, con la esperanza de que el aroma "
"calmante aliviara el dolor que aún estaba por venir. Cerró los ojos y el "
"mundo desapareció. El frío lentamente cedió y dio paso a un calor "
"reconfortante. Nunca en su vida el Sin Nombre había imaginado que el abrazo "
"de la muerte pudiera sentirse tan acogedor en comparación con cualquier otra "
"cosa que hubiera experimentado."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2055
msgid ""
"Then they felt the tender kiss of spearmint leaves on their lips.\n"
"\n"
"All their physical afflictions were gone in an instant, and they were once "
"again able to open their eyes — and so they saw that the plant had somehow "
"come to life and assumed the shape of a beautiful woman as if by a divine "
"blessing."
msgstr ""
"Entonces sintió el tierno beso de hojas de menta en sus labios.\n"
"\n"
"Todas sus aflicciones físicas desaparecieron al instante y pudo abrir los "
"ojos nuevamente; y así vio que la planta de algún modo había cobrado vida y "
"asumido la forma de una hermosa mujer, como si fuera una bendición divina."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2062
msgid ""
"The Nameless One was just as stunned by the beauty of the eventide nymph as "
"she was by theirs. They wondered what her story was — what circumstances "
"could possibly have brought her to a remote place like that, away from any "
"manner of civilization? And why would she, the free daughter of an untainted "
"world, decide to take pity on a creature who existed only for the purpose of "
"meting out punishment in the name of a goddess of death?\n"
"\n"
"Unfortunately for them, she would never be able to answer those questions, "
"for the gift that allowed her to give that one special person a second "
"chance came with the complete inability to utter a sound. Not even her birth "
"name was known to anyone in existence — “Mintha” was the first thing that "
"came to the shapeshifter’s mind, and she seemed fond of it."
msgstr ""
"El Sin Nombre quedó tan asombrado por la belleza de la ninfa del crepúsculo "
"como ella por la suya. Se preguntó cuál sería su historia: ¿qué "
"circunstancias podrían haberla llevado a un lugar tan remoto como ese, lejos "
"de cualquier vestigio de civilización? ¿Y por qué ella, la hija libre de un "
"mundo inmaculado, decidiría apiadarse de una criatura que existía solo para "
"infligir castigo en nombre de una diosa de la muerte?\n"
"\n"
"Lamentablemente para él, ella nunca podría responder a esas preguntas, pues "
"el don que le permitió darle a esa persona especial una segunda oportunidad "
"vino acompañado de la total incapacidad de pronunciar palabra. Ni siquiera "
"su nombre de nacimiento era conocido por nadie: “Mintha” fue lo primero que "
"le vino a la mente al cambiante, y a ella pareció agradarle."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2069
msgid ""
"The language barrier did little to stop the pair from finding a common "
"ground. The shapeshifter figured out soon enough that Mintha had her own "
"particular ways to communicate with others, and she was eager to be around "
"someone who did not avoid her just because of who she was. While she could "
"not tell them her own story, she was happy to listen to the Nameless One "
"tell her all about the vast unknown that lay far beyond Irdya. And she in "
"turn showed them Irdya as it was, and as it is — a world of endless strife, "
"yet also endless beauty."
msgstr ""
"La barrera del lenguaje hizo poco para impedir que la pareja encontrara un "
"terreno común. El cambiante pronto descubrió que Mintha tenía sus propios "
"modos particulares de comunicarse con otros, y ella estaba ansiosa por estar "
"cerca de alguien que no la evitara solo por lo que era. Aunque no podía "
"contarle su propia historia, se sentía feliz de escuchar al Sin Nombre "
"hablarle sobre lo vasto y desconocido que había más allá de Irdya. Y ella, a "
"su vez, le mostró cómo era y cómo es Irdya: un mundo de luchas "
"interminables, pero también de belleza infinita."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2074
msgid ""
"In time, the shapeshifter and the nymph grew enamored of each other. To the "
"Nameless One, the notion of having a child of their own volition was "
"completely alien, for their kind only bred when required to do so by the "
"Demon Lords, and only with each other. Nevertheless, they promptly found "
"themselves acquiescing to Mintha’s heart desire, and her body would be the "
"one to carry the creature born from their love."
msgstr ""
"Con el tiempo, el cambiante y la ninfa se enamoraron el uno del otro. Para "
"el Sin Nombre, la idea de tener un hijo por su propia voluntad era "
"completamente ajena, pues su clase solo se reproducía cuando los Señores "
"Demonio lo requerían, y solo entre ellos. Sin embargo, pronto se encontró "
"cediendo al deseo del corazón de Mintha, y su cuerpo sería el que llevaría a "
"la criatura nacida de su amor."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2083
msgid "What happened next?"
msgstr "¿Qué pasó después?"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2088
msgid ""
"I apologize. Like I said, I can only answer one question about the past."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento. Como dije, solo puedo responder una pregunta sobre el pasado."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2093
msgid ""
"Well, excuse me if I don’t believe you right now! Surely your goddess must "
"have imparted the full story to you!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bueno, discúlpame si no te creo ahora mismo! ¡Seguramente tu diosa debe "
"haberte contado la historia completa!"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#. She is not saying "no". This becomes relevant later.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2099
msgid "I am just a medium and your particular question is already answered."
msgstr "Solo soy un medio y tu pregunta en particular ya ha sido respondida."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2109
msgid ""
"If you must hear the whole story I am afraid you are going to have to ask "
"the Goddess for the rest."
msgstr ""
"Si quieres escuchar la historia completa, me temo que tendrás que "
"preguntarle el resto a la Diosa."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2114
msgid "Well, I would if I knew who she is or how to communicate with her!!!"
msgstr "¡Bueno, lo haría si supiera quién es o cómo comunicarme con ella!"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2119
msgid ""
"Our kind knows her as Xia’el. Her true name is known by only a counted few, "
"and her domain lies somewhere completely beyond our reach."
msgstr ""
"Los de nuestra clase la conocemos como Xia’el. Su verdadero nombre solo lo "
"conocen unos pocos, y su dominio está en algún lugar completamente fuera de "
"nuestro alcance."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2124
msgid ""
"If that is so then how am I supposed to get there and punch her in the face "
"for telling me an incomplete story?!"
msgstr ""
"Si es así, ¿cómo se supone que llegue allí y le dé un puñetazo en la cara "
"por contarme una historia incompleta?"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2129
msgid "Everything is possible if you set your mind to it!"
msgstr "¡Todo es posible si te lo propones!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2134
msgid ""
"Don’t you <i>dare</i> be all sarcastic like some kind of ancient mythical... "
"water faerie... that knows better than a child like me... Argh! I just... I "
"don’t need this right now. I’m sorry for sounding so frustrated. It’s all "
"just... a lot for me to handle."
msgstr ""
"¡No te <i>atrevas</i> a ser sarcástica como una especie de hada acuática "
"mítica antigua... que sabe más que una niña como yo... ¡Argh! Solo... no "
"necesito esto ahora mismo. Perdón por sonar tan frustrada. Todo esto es... "
"demasiado para mí."

#. [option]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2146
msgid "Did Elynia ever love anyone besides Argan?"
msgstr "¿Elynia amó alguna vez a alguien que no fuera Argan?"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2151
msgid ""
"Of all the questions you could have asked, are you absolutely sure that is "
"the one you want answered?"
msgstr ""
"De todas las preguntas que podrías haber hecho, ¿estás absolutamente segura "
"de que esa es la que quieres que responda?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2156
msgid ""
"I... Well... That just came to mind, that’s all. Should I ask something else—"
msgstr ""
"Yo... Bueno... Solo se me ocurrió, eso es todo. ¿Debería preguntar otra cosa—"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2161
msgid ""
"One question, not two. You already asked the question, and so I must deliver "
"the answer."
msgstr ""
"Una pregunta, no dos. Ya hiciste la pregunta, y por lo tanto debo darte la "
"respuesta."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2166
msgid ""
"Elynia-Thanadria did have all kinds of lovers back during the Golden Age, "
"both before and after meeting Argan. Her first lover was a young human by "
"the name of—"
msgstr ""
"Elynia-Thanadria tuvo todo tipo de amantes durante la Edad Dorada, tanto "
"antes como después de conocer a Argan. Su primer amante fue un joven humano "
"llamado—"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2171
msgid ""
"NO! Stop! I changed my mind, I don’t want to know. That’s not what I really "
"meant to ask specifically anyway."
msgstr ""
"¡NO! ¡Detente! Cambié de opinión, no quiero saberlo. De todos modos, esa no "
"era exactamente la pregunta que quería hacer."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2176
msgid "I know the answer to your real question though."
msgstr "Sin embargo, conozco la respuesta a tu verdadera pregunta."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2188
msgid ""
"You wanted to know if she ever had a more intimate relationship with other "
"faeries, did you not?"
msgstr ""
"Querías saber si alguna vez tuvo una relación más íntima con otras hadas, "
"¿no es así?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2193
msgid ""
"AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAHHHHHH!!! Look over there, it’s one of those... "
"demolisher monsters! It’s very, veeeeery slowly heading towards us!"
msgstr ""
"¡¡¡AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAHHHHHH!!! ¡Mira allí, es uno de esos... monstruos "
"demoledores! ¡Está viniendo hacia nosotros muuuuuy lentamente!"

#. [option]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2201
msgid "Was Zhangor responsible for the Great Fall?"
msgstr "¿Fue Zhangor responsable de la Gran Caída?"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2206
msgid ""
"That is an interesting question for you ask. I did not take you for someone "
"who would be interested in the history of this world."
msgstr ""
"Esa es una pregunta interesante para que la hagas. No te tenía por alguien "
"que se interesara en la historia de este mundo."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2211
msgid "... Look, I know I’m more than a bit dumb at times—"
msgstr "... Mira, sé que a veces soy más que un poco tonta—"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2216
msgid ""
"What I mean is you are an <i>outsider</i>. You may have been born on Irdya, "
"but you do not feel as though you belong here, do you?"
msgstr ""
"Lo que quiero decir es que eres una <i>forastera</i>. Puede que hayas nacido "
"en Irdya, pero no sientes que pertenezcas aquí, ¿verdad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2221
msgid ""
"... I guess I really... don’t. How can you read me so well? I mean, besides "
"the whole business with you spying on us."
msgstr ""
"... Supongo que realmente... no. ¿Cómo puedes leerme tan bien? Quiero decir, "
"además de todo ese asunto de que nos espías."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2226
msgid ""
"There is something surprisingly relatable about you, even though my life so "
"far has been one of complete solitude and yours the opposite. Perhaps it is "
"the fact that we are both daughters of Darkness in some way. Water and Earth "
"have got to meet each other at some point, after all. But I digress."
msgstr ""
"Hay algo sorprendentemente familiar en ti, aunque mi vida hasta ahora ha "
"sido de completa soledad y la tuya todo lo contrario. Quizás sea el hecho de "
"que ambas somos hijas de la Oscuridad de algún modo. Después de todo, el "
"Agua y la Tierra tienen que encontrarse en algún momento. Pero me desvío del "
"tema."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2231
msgid ""
"The Demon Lord Zhangor may be many things, but a patient schemer he is not. "
"He was provided information about a pivotal event by a source that "
"transcends time, and he did as he saw fit with that information. His thirst "
"for power led him to establish his cult in Wesmere, but he was largely "
"ignorant of what he was doing beyond attempting to become something he is "
"not and will likely never become: a god. So, the answer to your question is "
"no."
msgstr ""
"El Señor Demonio Zhangor puede ser muchas cosas, pero un conspirador "
"paciente no es. Recibió información sobre un evento crucial de una fuente "
"que trasciende el tiempo, e hizo con esa información lo que consideró "
"oportuno. Su sed de poder lo llevó a establecer su culto en Wesmere, pero en "
"gran medida era ignorante de lo que estaba haciendo, más allá de intentar "
"convertirse en algo que no es y que probablemente nunca será: un dios. Así "
"que, la respuesta a tu pregunta es no."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2236
msgid ""
"But who was responsible then? It all seems so contrived — both the creation "
"of the second sun and the Fall of the third. The Wesnothians could not "
"possibly have figured it out all on their own, could they?"
msgstr ""
"¿Pero entonces quién fue el responsable? Todo parece tan artificioso: tanto "
"la creación del segundo sol como la Caída del tercero. Los wesnothianos no "
"pudieron haberlo descubierto por sí mismos, ¿o sí?"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2241
msgid "One question, one answer."
msgstr "Una pregunta, una respuesta."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2246
msgid "Oh, come on!"
msgstr "¡Oh, vamos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2251
msgid ""
"This may be worth pondering, though. Some believe their lives are entirely "
"their own doing, that destiny does not exist and that our reality is merely "
"the product of happenstance. The possibility of an unseen force with many "
"hands and eyes having the power to weave the threads of fate into something "
"larger would be too terrifying to consider for mere mortals, after all."
msgstr ""
"Aunque puede valer la pena reflexionar sobre esto. Algunos creen que sus "
"vidas son enteramente obra suya, que el destino no existe y que nuestra "
"realidad es solo el producto del azar. Después de todo, la posibilidad de "
"una fuerza invisible con muchas manos y ojos capaz de tejer los hilos del "
"destino en algo más grande sería demasiado aterradora de considerar para "
"simples mortales."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2256
msgid ""
"I’m not sure I understand what you are suggesting... That all events as they "
"have come to pass were preordained by an entity with a will of its own?"
msgstr ""
"No estoy segura de entender lo que estás sugiriendo... ¿Que todos los "
"acontecimientos tal como han sucedido fueron predestinados por una entidad "
"con voluntad propia?"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2261
msgid ""
"But even if you consider the existence of such a being, is there anyone who "
"can tell you for certain that this hypothetical agent is not being "
"manipulated by a higher entity themselves?"
msgstr ""
"Pero incluso si consideras la existencia de un ser así, ¿hay alguien que "
"pueda decirte con certeza que este agente hipotético no está siendo "
"manipulado a su vez por una entidad superior?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2266
msgid ""
"... This is seriously messing with my head. Can we <i>please</i> stop now? I "
"don’t want to go into battle with a migraine."
msgstr ""
"... Esto me está revolviendo la cabeza en serio. ¿Podemos <i>por favor</i> "
"parar ya? No quiero ir a la batalla con una migraña."

#. [option]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2274
msgid "Is there cake in the Iron Council’s citadel?"
msgstr "¿Hay pastel en la ciudadela del Consejo de Hierro?"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2303
msgid ""
"... There has been cake in the citadel countless times, so I would venture "
"to say there may be some in there right now."
msgstr ""
"... Ha habido pastel en la ciudadela infinidad de veces, así que me "
"atrevería a decir que tal vez haya uno allí ahora mismo."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2308
msgid "YES!"
msgstr "¡SÍ!"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2322
msgid ""
"It is time, then. The Demon Lord Ergea has already informed you of what you "
"must do next. I shall do my part."
msgstr ""
"Es hora, entonces. La Señora Demonio Ergea ya te ha informado de lo que "
"debes hacer a continuación. Yo cumpliré con mi parte."

#. [then]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2335
msgid ""
"All faeries you currently control on the map or your recall list now have "
"the <b>kindled</b> trait, which allows them to ignore time of day penalties, "
"increases their hitpoints by 15%, and their resistance to non-arcane damage "
"by 5%."
msgstr ""
"Todas las hadas que controlas actualmente en el mapa o en tu lista de "
"reservas ahora tienen el rasgo <b>encendidas</b>, que les permite ignorar "
"las penalizaciones por la hora del día, aumenta sus puntos de vida en un 15% "
"y su resistencia al daño no arcano en un 5%."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2344
msgid ""
"Old allies want to support you in the upcoming battle. They may struggle on "
"land, but the Iron Council’s citadel is built on the riverside. You may be "
"able to use this to your advantage later."
msgstr ""
"Viejos aliados quieren apoyarte en la batalla que se avecina. Tal vez tengan "
"dificultades en tierra, pero la ciudadela del Consejo de Hierro está "
"construida a la orilla del río. Quizá puedas aprovechar esto más adelante."

#. [then]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2355
msgid "Promien"
msgstr "Promien"

#. [then]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2358
msgid "Thyon"
msgstr "Thyon"

#. [then]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2361
msgid "Charon"
msgstr "Charon"

#. [then]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2364
msgid "Cadmus"
msgstr "Cadmus"

#. [then]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2367
msgid "Electra"
msgstr "Electra"

#. [then]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2371
msgid "Luna"
msgstr "Luna"

#. [then]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2374
msgid "Merope"
msgstr "Merope"

#. [then]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2378
msgid "Orion"
msgstr "Orion"

#. [message]: speaker=Orion
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2383
msgid "The reckoning with these monsters is at hand, brothers and sisters!"
msgstr ""
"¡El ajuste de cuentas con estos monstruos está cerca, hermanos y hermanas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Luna
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2388
msgid ""
"Purge the unholy beasts from our waters and help the northerners seize "
"Uria’s dark citadel!"
msgstr ""
"¡Purguen a las bestias impías de nuestras aguas y ayuden a los norteños a "
"tomar la oscura ciudadela de Uria!"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2414
msgid "And now, I shall fight alongside you."
msgstr "Y ahora, lucharé a tu lado."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2419
msgid "Oh! We would be honored to have you by our side... er..."
msgstr "¡Oh! Sería un honor tenerte a nuestro lado... eh..."

#. [modify_unit]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2426
msgid "Daeira"
msgstr "Daeira"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2431
msgid ""
"Daeira. Few creatures on this world have ever heard my name and even fewer "
"have lived to tell others of my existence."
msgstr ""
"Daeira. Pocas criaturas en este mundo han oído mi nombre y aún menos han "
"vivido para contarle a otros sobre mi existencia."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2436
msgid ""
"Um... all right! I think I’ve kept Ergea and the others waiting long enough, "
"so... time to go, I think."
msgstr ""
"Eh... ¡de acuerdo! Creo que ya he hecho esperar bastante a Ergea y a los "
"demás, así que... es hora de partir, creo."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2442
msgid ""
"And now, I must leave. Farewell, Anya, and may Xia’el’s blessings accompany "
"you on this fight."
msgstr ""
"Y ahora debo marcharme. Adiós, Anya, y que las bendiciones de Xia’el te "
"acompañen en esta lucha."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2465
msgid "... I think I’ve kept Ergea and the others waiting long enough."
msgstr "... Creo que ya he hecho esperar bastante a Ergea y a los demás."

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2491
msgid ""
"Taking their river settlements, vanquishing their leaders, and leaving their "
"troops in utter disarray ought to be enough to keep the Iron Council "
"distracted for a short interval. It is time to take the fight to the citadel "
"itself."
msgstr ""
"Tomar sus asentamientos fluviales, vencer a sus líderes y dejar a sus tropas "
"en un completo caos debería bastar para mantener distraído al Consejo de "
"Hierro durante un breve intervalo. Es hora de llevar la lucha a la propia "
"ciudadela."

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/07B_Dark_Sea.cfg:2502
msgid ""
"The situation is not as favorable as I wished. We ought to take the fight "
"closer to the Iron Council’s citadel if we want to keep their attention away "
"from Elynia."
msgstr ""
"La situación no es tan favorable como desearía. Debemos llevar la lucha más "
"cerca de la ciudadela del Consejo de Hierro si queremos mantener su atención "
"lejos de Elynia."

#. [transient_message]
#. [scenario]
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:325
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/storytxt.cfg:382
msgid "Interim"
msgstr "Interino"

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:74
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:88
msgid "team_name^Neutral"
msgstr "Neutral"

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:102
msgid "team_name^Gatekeeper"
msgstr "Guardián de la Puerta"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. The narrator refers to Elyssa in second person throughout
#. this scenario.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:355
msgid ""
"That is not entirely accurate. Of course you do have more specific goals in "
"mind tonight, the longest of nights on Irdya.\n"
"\n"
"Ever since you were brought back to life by the man who once was Uria’s "
"first, you have done nothing but comply with the wishes of those responsible "
"for your prolonged lifespan.\n"
"\n"
"Such is the price of cheating death, you think to yourself."
msgstr ""
"Eso no es del todo exacto. Por supuesto, tienes objetivos más específicos en "
"mente esta noche, la más larga de todas en Irdya.\n"
"\n"
"Desde que fuiste devuelta a la vida por el hombre que una vez fue el primero "
"de Uria, no has hecho más que cumplir los deseos de quienes son responsables "
"de tu prolongada existencia.\n"
"\n"
"Tal es el precio de engañar a la muerte, piensas para ti misma."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. The 'Seer' is female, and no, she is not Valen.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:366
msgid ""
"But the Seer told you about things to come. Things that did not make much "
"sense to you at the time; things you promptly disregarded as long-winded "
"prophetic nonsense, of the kind that necessitates a very specific mindset to "
"digest and interpret correctly. Even after over three hundred years, you "
"cannot understand half of her ramblings, and have forgotten most of the rest."
msgstr ""
"Pero la Vidente te habló de cosas por venir. Cosas que en su momento no "
"tuvieron mucho sentido para ti; cosas que rápidamente descartaste como "
"sinsentidos proféticos interminables, del tipo que requiere una mentalidad "
"muy específica para digerir e interpretar correctamente. Incluso después de "
"más de trescientos años, no puedes entender ni la mitad de sus desvaríos, y "
"has olvidado la mayor parte del resto."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:372
msgid ""
"Yet she sometimes does provide you clear instructions to follow. Darkness "
"and its association with the matters of the mind are well understood by her, "
"as the descendant of Delethia she claims to be, and she willingly allows you "
"to exploit that aspect and gnaw at her thick mental barrier when the "
"situation calls for it. But instructions are all you ever find in the vast "
"void of her thoughts.\n"
"\n"
"Executing commands as the machine you are is all you ever do. But you were "
"promised a change. You have a couple of contracts to fulfill first, "
"however.\n"
"\n"
"What will you do?"
msgstr ""
"Y sin embargo, a veces te proporciona instrucciones claras a seguir. La "
"Oscuridad y su asociación con los asuntos de la mente son bien comprendidos "
"por ella, como la descendiente de Delethia que dice ser, y te permite de "
"buena gana explotar ese aspecto y roer su gruesa barrera mental cuando la "
"situación lo requiere. Pero instrucciones es lo único que encuentras en el "
"vasto vacío de sus pensamientos.\n"
"\n"
"Ejecutar órdenes como la máquina que eres es lo único que siempre haces. "
"Pero se te prometió un cambio. Sin embargo, primero tienes un par de "
"contratos que cumplir.\n"
"\n"
"¿Qué harás?"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:396
msgid "Proceed to the meeting chamber"
msgstr "Dirígete a la cámara de reunión"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:424
msgid ""
"There is nothing of interest whence you came. You should really get moving "
"now."
msgstr ""
"No hay nada de interés por donde viniste. Deberías ponerte en marcha de una "
"vez."

#. [literal]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:437
msgid ""
"You have a very specific objective in mind at this particular time, and you "
"are not really the type that gets distracted this easily. What were you "
"thinking?\n"
"\n"
"You purposefully turn around and get back to business."
msgstr ""
"Tienes un objetivo muy específico en mente en este momento, y no eres "
"precisamente del tipo que se distrae con facilidad. ¿En qué estabas "
"pensando?\n"
"\n"
"Te das la vuelta deliberadamente y vuelves al asunto."

#. [literal]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:442
msgid ""
"This is not where you should be heading right now, and you know it. Still, "
"you cannot resist the urge to take a glance at this striking scenery. Who "
"ever knew that ancient ruins could look this good? Truly, nature itself is "
"the best architect there is."
msgstr ""
"No es hacia aquí donde deberías dirigirte ahora mismo, y lo sabes. Aun así, "
"no puedes resistir la tentación de echar un vistazo a este paisaje tan "
"impresionante. ¿Quién hubiera pensado que las ruinas antiguas podrían verse "
"tan bien? Sin duda, la naturaleza es el mejor arquitecto que existe."

#. [literal]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:445
msgid ""
"You take a glance at the wondrous carving on the enchanted gate. It is "
"largely rusted and you can barely make out the details, and yet, your eyes "
"are affixed.\n"
"\n"
"Perhaps you should get back to whatever you were doing."
msgstr ""
"Echas un vistazo a la maravillosa talla en la puerta encantada. Está en su "
"mayor parte oxidada y apenas puedes distinguir los detalles, y aun así, no "
"puedes apartar la vista.\n"
"\n"
"Quizá deberías volver a lo que estabas haciendo."

#. [literal]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:450
msgid ""
"It is an old enchanted gate, of course. You are not completely sure why you "
"bothered casting these spells on most of the gates on this level, actually, "
"but you are prone to wasting your time on frivolous activities like that on "
"occasion, while nobody is around. Then again, the faint glow on it is "
"unusually mesmerizing.\n"
"\n"
"Time to go back to doing something productive."
msgstr ""
"Es una vieja puerta encantada, por supuesto. No estás del todo segura de por "
"qué te molestaste en lanzar estos hechizos sobre la mayoría de las puertas "
"de este nivel, pero tiendes a perder el tiempo en actividades frívolas como "
"esa de vez en cuando, cuando nadie te observa. Aun así, el tenue resplandor "
"sobre ella resulta extrañamente hipnótico.\n"
"\n"
"Es hora de volver a hacer algo productivo."

#. [literal]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:455
msgid ""
"As much as you wish you had the ability, you cannot stop time, and destiny "
"needs a helping hand to ensure that the events foretold for this night take "
"place. You are that helping hand, and you really ought to stop staring at "
"the enchanted gate and get back to your mission."
msgstr ""
"Por mucho que desearías tener esa habilidad, no puedes detener el tiempo, y "
"el destino necesita una mano amiga para asegurar que los eventos predichos "
"para esta noche se cumplan. Tú eres esa mano amiga, y realmente deberías "
"dejar de mirar la puerta encantada y volver a tu misión."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:581
msgid "Activate the communicator"
msgstr "Activa el comunicador"

#. [scenario]
#. The Seer of Uria is female.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:607
msgid "“The Seer”"
msgstr "«La Vidente»"

#. [scenario]
#. The Mother is Uria herself.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:610
msgid "“The Mother”"
msgstr "«La Madre»"

#. [scenario]
#. The Fist is Zhangor.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:613
msgid "“The Fist”"
msgstr "«El Puño»"

#. [scenario]
#. The Shadow is Nar-hamoth.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:616
msgid "“The Shadow”"
msgstr "«La Sombra»"

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:809
msgid "Ah, it is you."
msgstr "Ah, eres tú."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:814
msgid "I believe you wanted to see me, my lady."
msgstr "Creo que deseabas verme, mi señora."

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:819
msgid ""
"That is correct. Have the preparations for my arrival on Ethea been "
"completed yet? I believe there is a certain nuisance remaining to be "
"eliminated."
msgstr ""
"Es correcto. ¿Se han completado ya los preparativos para mi llegada a Ethea? "
"Creo que aún queda cierta molestia por eliminar."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:824
msgid "I have been awaiting your order to destroy the Gatekeeper, my lady."
msgstr "He estado esperando tu orden para destruir al Guardián, mi señora."

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:829
msgid ""
"Hm, hm, I appreciate your obedience, but in this case I would have preferred "
"if you did it as soon as the breach was opened."
msgstr ""
"Hm, hm, aprecio tu obediencia, pero en este caso habría preferido que lo "
"hicieras en cuanto se abrió la brecha."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:834
msgid ""
"I assumed you would wait until you gathered further information on the "
"Guardian of Water, my lady. Is he not..."
msgstr ""
"Asumí que esperarías hasta reunir más información sobre el Guardián del "
"Agua, mi señora. ¿Acaso no está él..."

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:839
msgid "Yes. He is already there."
msgstr "Sí. Él ya está allí."

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:849
msgid ""
"But he is not cognizant of our schemes, is he? His people never noticed the "
"supplies and equipment we stole from their world, so I am free to advance my "
"plans while they are preoccupied with other matters. Do not forget that I "
"need to find the missing piece of that damned puzzle."
msgstr ""
"Pero no está al tanto de nuestros planes, ¿verdad? Su gente nunca notó los "
"suministros y el equipo que robamos de su mundo, así que soy libre de "
"avanzar mis planes mientras ellos están ocupados con otros asuntos. No "
"olvides que necesito encontrar la pieza que falta de ese maldito "
"rompecabezas."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#. The Body of the Union
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:855
msgid "... the Body..."
msgstr "... el Cuerpo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:860
msgid ""
"Will you please stop wasting everyone’s time and destroy that hideous thing "
"at once? And... once you are done, come back to me."
msgstr ""
"¿Podrías dejar de hacer perder el tiempo a todos y destruir esa abominación "
"de una vez? Y... cuando hayas terminado, vuelve a mí."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:865
msgid "Yes. As you command, my lady."
msgstr "Sí. Como ordenes, mi señora."

#. [unit]: type=Lumeril Guard, id=Halbadrel
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:911
msgid "Halbadrel"
msgstr "Halbadrel"

#. [unit]: type=Demon Zephyr, gender=female, id=Sheelevrea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:926
msgid "Sheelevrea"
msgstr "Sheelevrea"

#. [unit]: type=Gutwrencher Imp, id=Kraador
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:940
msgid "Kraador"
msgstr "Kraador"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:958
msgid ""
"You guess it cannot be helped. Things are going to get more complicated than "
"you wanted. As usual."
msgstr ""
"Supone que no hay nada que hacer. Las cosas se van a complicar más de lo que "
"querías. Como siempre."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:989
msgid ""
"These security measures are inconvenient at times. If that stupid faerie and "
"her accomplices did not have access to teleport spells, you would be able to "
"instantly go to the breach site and deal with your target. But it cannot be "
"helped.\n"
"\n"
"The transport glyph awaits. You really hope to not stumble upon any "
"undesirable vermin along the way."
msgstr ""
"Estas medidas de seguridad resultan molestas a veces. Si esa estúpida hada y "
"sus cómplices no tuvieran acceso a hechizos de teletransporte, podrías ir al "
"sitio de la brecha al instante y encargarte de tu objetivo. Pero no hay nada "
"que hacer.\n"
"\n"
"El glifo de transporte te espera. De verdad esperas no encontrarte con "
"ninguna alimaña indeseable en el camino."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1035
msgid "Of course, you are not <i>too</i> concerned about it."
msgstr "Por supuesto, no estás <i>demasiado</i> preocupado por ello."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1043
msgid "Proceed to the transport glyph"
msgstr "Dirígete al glifo de transporte"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1070
msgid ""
"Your mission now is to slay the Gatekeeper. Bothering Uria again before you "
"are done would be absurdly reckless."
msgstr ""
"Tu misión ahora es eliminar al Guardián. Molestar a Uria otra vez antes de "
"terminar sería absurdamente imprudente."

#. [message]: speaker=Sheelevrea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1089
msgid "Hahahaha! Look, it is Uria’s little pet! Isn’t she adorable?"
msgstr "¡Jajajaja! Mira, es la mascota de Uria. ¿No es adorable?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1094
msgid "You are obstructing the way. Get out."
msgstr "Estás bloqueando el paso. Fuera."

#. [message]: speaker=Halbadrel
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1099
msgid "As you wish."
msgstr "Como desees."

#. [message]: speaker=Sheelevrea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1106
msgid "Hee hee hee!"
msgstr "¡Je je je!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1144
msgid ""
"An old, rusted ring with no special powers whatsoever. It is absolutely "
"useless to you."
msgstr ""
"Un viejo anillo oxidado sin ningún poder especial. Es absolutamente inútil "
"para ti."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1161
msgid "Just an old crate. There is nothing of value in it."
msgstr "Solo una vieja caja. No hay nada de valor dentro."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1361
msgid "The unnatural air in this place makes you feel uneasy."
msgstr "El aire antinatural de este lugar te hace sentir incómodo."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1377
msgid "On the other side of the breach, the Gatekeeper on Ethea awaits..."
msgstr "Al otro lado de la brecha, el Guardián en Ethea te espera..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1408
msgid "... There is no going back now..."
msgstr "... Ya no hay vuelta atrás..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1452
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:1388
msgid "...!"
msgstr "¡...!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1462
msgid "<i>Have you forgotten who you are?</i>"
msgstr "<i>¿Has olvidado quién eres?</i>"

#. [event]
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1469
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4754
msgid "Ethealim"
msgstr "Ethealim"

#. [message]: speaker=Ethealim
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1481
msgid "Are you deceiving yourself?"
msgstr "¿Te estás engañando a ti misma?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1497
msgid ""
"I asked the question first. I was told Gatekeepers are not sentient "
"creatures."
msgstr ""
"Yo hice la pregunta primero. Me dijeron que los Guardianes no son criaturas "
"conscientes."

#. [message]: speaker=Ethealim
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1503
msgid ""
"You let yourself be deceived by appearances in spite of the aspect you "
"control. Why is that?"
msgstr ""
"Te dejas engañar por las apariencias a pesar del aspecto que controlas. ¿Por "
"qué es eso?"

#. [message]: speaker=Ethealim
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1550
msgid ""
"As the child of Uria and heiress of Merthiaal you are, you harbor great "
"potential."
msgstr "Como hija de Uria y heredera de Merthiaal, albergas un gran potencial."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1555
msgid "You are mistaken. I am neither thing."
msgstr "Te equivocas. No soy ninguna de las dos cosas."

#. [message]: speaker=Ethealim
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1561
msgid "Are you not human? All humans everywhere are children of Uria."
msgstr ""
"¿Acaso no eres humana? Todos los humanos, en cualquier lugar, son hijos de "
"Uria."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1566
msgid "I am not human. Not anymore."
msgstr "No soy humana. Ya no más."

#. [message]: speaker=Ethealim
#. 'designed' is used here in the sense of 'planned', 'intended', etc.
#. The sentence here is supposed to imply the existence of one or more deities
#. weaving every character's fate since before they were even born.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1579
msgid ""
"The heart of Merthiaal lies within you as designed, but that does not change "
"your true self."
msgstr ""
"El corazón de Merthiaal yace en tu interior, tal como estaba previsto, pero "
"eso no cambia tu verdadero ser."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1588
msgid ""
"I was not destined by the Tree to inherit Darkness... but that’s irrelevant "
"either way. I have transcended the definition of a ‘human’ and become "
"something different."
msgstr ""
"El Árbol no me destinó a heredar la Oscuridad... pero eso es irrelevante de "
"todos modos. He trascendido la definición de ‘humana’ y me he convertido en "
"algo distinto."

#. [message]: speaker=Ethealim
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1594
msgid "Have you? What does your heart tell you?"
msgstr "¿Ah, sí? ¿Qué te dice tu corazón?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1599
msgid "My... heart...?"
msgstr "¿Mi... corazón...?"

#. [message]: speaker=Ethealim
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1605
msgid ""
"The path of Darkness is a convoluted and deceptive one. Whereas your "
"predecessor placed an excessive emphasis on her feelings to the detriment of "
"rationality, you are doing the exact opposite. A true Guardian of Light or "
"Darkness needs to establish a balance between both facets. You, however..."
msgstr ""
"El camino de la Oscuridad es enrevesado y engañoso. Mientras que tu "
"predecesora dio un énfasis excesivo a sus sentimientos en detrimento de la "
"razón, tú haces exactamente lo contrario. Un verdadero Guardián de la Luz o "
"la Oscuridad debe establecer un equilibrio entre ambas facetas. Tú, sin "
"embargo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Ethealim
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1611
msgid "... you have allowed others to <i>distort</i> your identity..."
msgstr "... has permitido que otros <i>distorsionen</i> tu identidad..."

#. [message]: speaker=Ethealim
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1619
msgid ""
"Uria’s corrupting influence is hampering your personal growth and tearing "
"your being apart, just as she wants."
msgstr ""
"La influencia corruptora de Uria está frenando tu crecimiento personal y "
"desgarrando tu ser, tal como ella desea."

#. [message]: speaker=Ethealim
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1629
msgid ""
"Tearing souls apart is what a corrupted Guardian of Life does best. But... "
"can <i>you</i> escape her influence?"
msgstr ""
"Desgarrar almas es lo que mejor hace un Guardián de la Vida corrompido. "
"Pero... ¿puedes <i>tú</i> escapar de su influencia?"

#. [message]: speaker=Ethealim
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1639
msgid "Can you escape her destructive grasp..."
msgstr "¿Puedes escapar de su destructivo abrazo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Ethealim
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1649
msgid ""
"... before she utterly destroys your soul and seizes Darkness through your "
"empty shell?"
msgstr ""
"... antes de que destruya por completo tu alma y se apodere de la Oscuridad "
"a través de tu carcasa vacía?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1667
msgid ""
"(<i>frantic</i>) Bind the soul to stone— turn the memories to dust— erase "
"the spirit— shed the hollow SHELL!"
msgstr ""
"(<i>desesperada</i>) ¡Atad el alma a la piedra— convertid los recuerdos en "
"polvo— borrad el espíritu— despojad la carcasa VACÍA!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1774
msgid "Damn you, Zhangor. Damn you and your stinking lies."
msgstr "Maldito seas, Zhangor. Maldito tú y tus apestosas mentiras."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1915
msgid ""
"Of course, she was not counting on the spell Uria taught you for the "
"mission. Or was she?"
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto, ella no contaba con el hechizo que Uria te enseñó para la "
"misión. ¿O sí?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1921
msgid ""
"You have not felt so stupid in a long time. Zhangor’s ruse was simply too "
"obvious to fall for — Uria would not have asked you to destroy the "
"Gatekeeper yourself if she did not fear her for some reason. Perhaps if she "
"had such an introspective conversation with the Gatekeeper, things would "
"have changed to some degree. Perhaps...\n"
"\n"
"But no. You are well familiarized with the demoness and her childlike "
"stubbornness. Whatever advice the Gatekeeper might have had for her would "
"have gone unheeded. That is, assuming Uria would have given her a chance to "
"speak in the first place."
msgstr ""
"Hace mucho que no te sentías tan estúpida. La artimaña de Zhangor era "
"demasiado obvia para caer en ella: Uria no te habría pedido que destruyeras "
"a la Guardiana si no le temiera por alguna razón. Tal vez, si ella hubiera "
"tenido una conversación introspectiva con la Guardiana, las cosas habrían "
"cambiado en cierto grado. Tal vez...\n"
"\n"
"Pero no. Conoces bien a la demoníaca y su terquedad infantil. Cualquier "
"consejo que la Guardiana pudiera haberle dado habría caído en saco roto. "
"Eso, asumiendo que Uria le hubiera dado siquiera la oportunidad de hablar."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1929
msgid ""
"Maybe you were too hasty in disposing of the creature, though. She seemed to "
"be genuinely trying to help you for some reason. The illusion she cast on "
"you seemed as real as it was intensely painful — not that you are are "
"unaccustomed to pain yourself, but... you admit that you were afraid for a "
"moment."
msgstr ""
"Aunque quizá fuiste demasiado apresurada al deshacerte de la criatura. Por "
"alguna razón, parecía estar intentando ayudarte sinceramente. La ilusión que "
"proyectó sobre ti se sintió tan real como intensamente dolorosa… no es que "
"no estés acostumbrada al dolor, pero… admites que por un momento sentiste "
"miedo."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1935
msgid ""
"Regardless of the intentions of Delethia’s offspring, she managed to stir up "
"uncomfortable thoughts in your mind with her meddling. You decide to sweep "
"them aside, if only for a brief interval while you go to report back to your "
"oppressive overseer."
msgstr ""
"Independientemente de las intenciones de la descendiente de Delethia, logró "
"agitar pensamientos incómodos en tu mente con su intromisión. Decides "
"apartarlos, aunque solo sea por un breve momento mientras vas a informar a "
"tu opresiva supervisora."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1944
msgid "Report to Uria in the meeting chamber again"
msgstr "Informa a Uria en la cámara de reuniones otra vez"

#. [message]: speaker=Sheelevrea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1990
msgid "Ahahahaha! Hey, hey! Did you have fun down there? Hahahahaha!"
msgstr "¡Ahahahaha! ¡Eh, eh! ¿Te divertiste ahí abajo? ¡Hahahahaha!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:1995
msgid ""
"Not really. There was only one Gatekeeper and I was prepared to perform many "
"more soul bind spells tonight."
msgstr ""
"No mucho. Solo había una Guardiana y yo estaba preparada para realizar "
"muchos más hechizos de atadura de almas esta noche."

#. [message]: speaker=Halbadrel
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2000
msgid ""
"That seems rather wasteful and improbable. Lord Zhangor said you needed "
"Uria’s help to cast those."
msgstr ""
"Eso parece bastante desperdiciado e improbable. El Lord Zhangor dijo que "
"necesitabas la ayuda de Uria para lanzar esos hechizos."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2005
msgid "Zhangor, you say?"
msgstr "¿Zhangor, dices?"

#. [message]: speaker=Sheelevrea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2010
msgid "Hahahahaha!"
msgstr "¡Hahahahaha!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2015
msgid ""
"Ah, I see. Good to know it was he who sent you here, but I fear you have "
"been misinformed about the power I wield. Regardless, I have to wonder: why "
"here, in my domain?"
msgstr ""
"Ah, ya veo. Es bueno saber que fue él quien los envió aquí, pero me temo que "
"les han malinformado sobre el poder que manejo. Aun así, me pregunto: ¿por "
"qué aquí, en mi dominio?"

#. [message]: speaker=Halbadrel
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2020
msgid ""
"Lord Zhangor wanted us to keep you in check, naturally. There are various "
"disturbing rumors running around surrounding your habits and plans, you see."
msgstr ""
"El Lord Zhangor quería que te mantuviéramos vigilada, naturalmente. Circulan "
"varios rumores inquietantes sobre tus hábitos y planes, ¿sabes?"

#. [message]: speaker=Sheelevrea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2025
msgid ""
"Some say you like inviting people to dine in your cell. They say... that you "
"invite humans and demons... to eat their succulent flesh when you are... "
"hungry! Hahahahaha!"
msgstr ""
"Algunos dicen que te gusta invitar a la gente a cenar en tu celda. Dicen... "
"que invitas a humanos y demonios... para devorar su suculenta carne cuando "
"tienes... hambre. ¡Hahahahaha!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2030
msgid ""
"(<i>monotone</i>) Ha, ha, ha. I can see why some of you might believe such a "
"thing. But trust me, I am not the one who revels in chaos, destruction, and "
"depravity. Perhaps you should be watching <i>him</i> instead. Nonetheless..."
msgstr ""
"(<i>monótono</i>) Ja, ja, ja. Puedo entender por qué algunos de ustedes "
"podrían creer tal cosa. Pero créanme, no soy yo quien se regodea en el caos, "
"la destrucción y la depravación. Quizá deberían vigilar mejor a <i>él</i>. "
"Aun así…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2058
msgid "I absolutely <i>detest</i> your obnoxious laugh, girl."
msgstr "Absolutamente <i>detesto</i> tu risita insoportable, chica."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2130
msgid ""
"You grab the crystal orb containing the soul of your nameless victim and "
"fling it against the wall, shattering it; the irregular shards are scattered "
"over the floor.\n"
"\n"
"... At least you <i>believe</i> she did not have a name."
msgstr ""
"Tomas la esfera de cristal que contiene el alma de tu víctima sin nombre y "
"la lanzas contra la pared, haciéndola añicos; las astillas irregulares se "
"esparcen por el suelo.\n"
"\n"
"... Al menos <i>crees</i> que no tenía nombre."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2153
msgid ""
"Their leader seems quite impressed by your little demonstration and orders "
"his minion to pick up the shards. Hopefully he will choose to leave you "
"alone, you think — that spell is quite physically and mentally taxing, and "
"displaying weakness before Zhangor’s minions would not be a good idea."
msgstr ""
"Su líder parece bastante impresionado por tu pequeña demostración y ordena a "
"su esbirro que recoja las astillas. Esperas que decida dejarte en paz, "
"piensas — ese hechizo es bastante agotador física y mentalmente, y mostrar "
"debilidad ante los esbirros de Zhangor no sería buena idea."

#. [message]: speaker=Halbadrel
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2162
msgid "Lord Zhangor will hear of this."
msgstr "El Lord Zhangor sabrá de esto."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#. 'however' is used here in the sense of "in whatever manner/fashion/form".
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2168
msgid ""
"(<i>monotone</i>) Oh, excellent, however should I express my gratitude! I "
"was actually worried for a moment that I would have to send him the shards "
"all by myself, wasting Uria’s invaluable time by making her wait much longer "
"for my report."
msgstr ""
"(<i>monótono</i>) Oh, excelente, ¡qué manera tan adecuada de expresar mi "
"gratitud! Por un momento estuve preocupada de que tendría que enviarle yo "
"misma las astillas, desperdiciando el tiempo invaluable de Uria haciéndola "
"esperar mucho más por mi informe."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2175
msgid "Please, <i>do</i> send him my regards."
msgstr "Por favor, <i>hazle</i> llegar mis saludos."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2292
msgid ""
"The Gatekeeper on Ethea is no more, my lady. The breach from Urvatha is now "
"clear for you to cross."
msgstr ""
"La Guardiana de Ethea ya no existe, mi señora. La brecha desde Urvatha está "
"ahora despejada para que pueda cruzar."

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2301
msgid ""
"Hm, hm, I see. Well done, my Fire. Your success pleases me... greatly. Hm... "
"I have a question for you."
msgstr ""
"Hm, hm, ya veo. Bien hecho, mi Fuego. Tu éxito me complace... enormemente. "
"Hm... Tengo una pregunta para ti."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2306
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2347
msgid "Yes, my lady?"
msgstr "¿Sí, mi señora?"

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2311
msgid ""
"Lord Zhangor informed me earlier of a... <i>revolt</i> organized by the "
"stormkind witch. But from what he said I gather that the once-blessed faerie "
"is directly involved as well. What do you know about this?"
msgstr ""
"El Lord Zhangor me informó antes de una... <i>revuelta</i> organizada por la "
"bruja de la tormenta. Pero, por lo que dijo, entiendo que la antaño "
"bendecida hada también está involucrada directamente. ¿Qué sabes sobre esto?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2316
msgid ""
"The faerie was supposed to lead the Irdyan troops from the North but "
"abandoned her duty on the surface before their arrival. She made it to the "
"ruined training chamber and confronted me."
msgstr ""
"El hada se suponía que lideraría a las tropas irdyanas desde el norte, pero "
"abandonó su deber en la superficie antes de su llegada. Llegó hasta la "
"cámara de entrenamiento en ruinas y me enfrentó."

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2321
msgid ""
"Ah, hm, yes. Everyone had been looking forward to that confrontation ever "
"since it was foretold by the Seer — it was an inevitability. Well, I assume "
"you made her pay dearly for her meddling. Is she..."
msgstr ""
"Ah, hm, sí. Todos habían estado esperando ese enfrentamiento desde que fue "
"profetizado por la Vidente: era una inevitabilidad. Bien, supongo que la "
"hiciste pagar caro por su intromisión. ¿Está ella...?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2327
msgid ""
"I killed her just as you wished, my lady. (<i>smirking</i>) Hekuba’s "
"necrophages took care of the rest for me. I would have loved to present you "
"with her corpse, but it appears that our decrepit traitor still manages to "
"interfere even after his soul ceased to exist. A pity too, since I really "
"liked her hair."
msgstr ""
"La maté tal como deseaba, mi señora. (<i>sonriendo</i>) Los necrófagos de "
"Hekuba se encargaron del resto por mí. Me habría encantado presentarle su "
"cadáver, pero parece que nuestro decrépito traidor aún logra interferir "
"incluso después de que su alma dejó de existir. Una lástima también, ya que "
"realmente me gustaba su cabello."

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2332
msgid ""
"No! I would not tolerate you wearing the scalp of that wretched creature "
"anywhere near me; not to mention that some of your followers could get the "
"wrong idea... Do you not think Ergea’s betrayal has caused us enough trouble "
"already?"
msgstr ""
"¡No! No toleraría que usaras el cuero cabelludo de esa miserable criatura "
"cerca de mí; sin mencionar que algunos de tus seguidores podrían hacerse una "
"idea equivocada... ¿No crees que la traición de Ergea ya nos ha causado "
"bastantes problemas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2337
msgid "My apologies, my lady."
msgstr "Mis disculpas, mi señora."

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2342
msgid "Moving on..."
msgstr "Sigamos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2352
msgid ""
"I have transferred Irdya’s control to Lord Zhangor. You are relieved from "
"your duty as my Fire."
msgstr ""
"He transferido el control de Irdya al Lord Zhangor. Quedas relevada de tu "
"deber como mi Fuego."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2361
msgid "M— my lady?"
msgstr "¿M— mi señora?"

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2366
msgid ""
"I refuse to acknowledge your reaction as one of surprise, Elyssa. Did you "
"truly think I would ask you to lend him the bulk of the Triad’s troops "
"without an ulterior reason? This is all part of a plan that is now mostly "
"irrelevant to you. Your duty now is to serve him just as you have served me "
"all these years."
msgstr ""
"Me niego a considerar tu reacción como una de sorpresa, Elyssa. ¿Acaso "
"creíste de verdad que te pediría cederle la mayor parte de las tropas de la "
"Tríada sin un motivo ulterior? Todo esto forma parte de un plan que ahora es "
"mayormente irrelevante para ti. Tu deber ahora es servirle a él tal como me "
"has servido a mí todos estos años."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2371
msgid ""
"But you promised that Irdya would be under my control soon... Zhangor would "
"assist you on Ethea!"
msgstr ""
"Pero prometió que Irdya estaría bajo mi control pronto... ¡Zhangor la "
"asistiría en Ethea!"

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2376
msgid ""
"You ought to watch your tone, girl — do not forget that I can end your life "
"and destroy your soul at any time I please. If you want the ball of dirt you "
"call Irdya, you will have to strike a bargain with your new lord. Do you "
"understand?"
msgstr ""
"Deberías cuidar tu tono, niña: no olvides que puedo acabar con tu vida y "
"destruir tu alma en cualquier momento que me plazca. Si quieres la bola de "
"tierra a la que llamas Irdya, tendrás que llegar a un acuerdo con tu nuevo "
"señor. ¿Lo entiendes?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2381
msgid "I... understand, my lady."
msgstr "Lo... entiendo, mi señora."

#. [message]: speaker=Uria
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2386
msgid ""
"Excellent then. Hm, hm, I am sure Zhangor will be as pleased as I to count "
"on your assistance with exterminating the vermin brought by the faerie. We "
"will meet again in the future, <i>perhaps</i>. Ha, ha, ha, ha!"
msgstr ""
"Excelente entonces. Hm, hm, estoy segura de que Zhangor estará tan "
"complacido como yo de contar con tu ayuda para exterminar a la escoria "
"traída por el hada. Nos volveremos a encontrar en el futuro, <i>quizás</i>. "
"¡Ja, ja, ja, ja!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2440
msgid ""
"That damned shapeshifter scum should have stayed half-dead in that putrid "
"pit. Stupid Uria and her irritating obsession with the bastard. You can only "
"wonder what other machinations they have been brewing behind your back.\n"
"\n"
"This unexpected development changes many things. Your plans need some urgent "
"adjustments before those two perform their next move."
msgstr ""
"Esa maldita escoria cambiaformas debería haberse quedado medio muerta en esa "
"fosa pútrida. Estúpida Uria y su irritante obsesión con el bastardo. Solo "
"puedes preguntarte qué otras maquinaciones han estado tramando a tus "
"espaldas.\n"
"\n"
"Este desarrollo inesperado cambia muchas cosas. Tus planes necesitan ajustes "
"urgentes antes de que esos dos realicen su próximo movimiento."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. This line refers to Elynia as a 'piece', but it'd be nice to keep the gender
#. ambiguous whenever possible.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2450
msgid ""
"Time to check on your pivotal piece in the ruined laboratory. Maybe you "
"should try to remember a few things along the way; open some of those rusty "
"gates in your memory and look inside.\n"
"\n"
"You just know you will need all the hints you can gather from this "
"stronghold for your next course of action."
msgstr ""
"Es hora de revisar tu pieza clave en el laboratorio en ruinas. Tal vez "
"deberías intentar recordar algunas cosas en el camino; abrir algunas de esas "
"oxidadas compuertas en tu memoria y mirar dentro.\n"
"\n"
"Sabes bien que necesitarás todas las pistas que puedas reunir en esta "
"fortaleza para tu próximo curso de acción."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2495
msgid "Enter the ruined laboratory"
msgstr "Entrar en el laboratorio en ruinas"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2534
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"There is no use in attempting to activate the communicator at this time. "
"Uria has probably left her fortress on Urvatha already, Zhangor is busy "
"plotting in his lair, Nar-hamoth is missing in action, and the Seer does not "
"really use these artifacts on account of her inability to move around "
"unassisted — plus, you have nothing left to discuss with any of them."
msgstr ""
"No tiene sentido intentar activar el comunicador en este momento. "
"Probablemente Uria ya haya abandonado su fortaleza en Urvatha, Zhangor está "
"ocupado tramando en su guarida, Nar-hamoth está desaparecido en acción, y la "
"Vidente realmente no usa estos artefactos debido a su incapacidad para "
"desplazarse sin asistencia. Tampoco tienes nada que discutir con ninguno de "
"ellos por ahora."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2561
msgid "Touchplate triggered. A road rises from the depths."
msgstr "Placa de presión activada. Un camino surge de las profundidades."

#. [item_choice_dialog]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2584
msgid "The Original Ten"
msgstr "Los Diez Originales"

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2587
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:232
msgid "Life"
msgstr "Vida"

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2588
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:233
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The force that governs the birth of all creatures in our reality. Incarnated "
"by the Guardian of Life, also known as <b>Uria</b>, Guardian of the Legacy "
"and the Void, Mistress of the Void, Goddess of Life."
msgstr ""
"La fuerza que gobierna el nacimiento de todas las criaturas en nuestra "
"realidad. Encarnada por la Guardiana de la Vida, también conocida como Uria, "
"Guardiana del Legado y el Vacío, Señora del Vacío, Diosa de la Vida."

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2592
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:236
msgid "Water"
msgstr "Agua"

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2593
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:237
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The element common to the origins of all life in our reality, as well as its "
"sustainment and destruction. Incarnated by the Guardian of Water, also known "
"as <b>Valdir</b>, Guardian of Water and Destruction, the Beast, God of War."
msgstr ""
"El elemento común a los orígenes de toda la vida en nuestra realidad, así "
"como a su sustento y destrucción. Encarnado por el Guardián del Agua, "
"también conocido como Valdir, Guardián del Agua y la Destrucción, la Bestia, "
"Dios de la Guerra."

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2597
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:240
msgid "Thunder"
msgstr "Trueno"

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2598
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:241
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The spark that keeps life in motion, the arbiter in a chaotic reality doomed "
"to an ephemeral eternity of strife. Incarnated by the Guardian of Thunder, "
"also known as <b>Kaarul</b>, Guardian of Thunder, Harbinger of Judgment, and "
"God of Storms."
msgstr ""
"La chispa que mantiene la vida en movimiento, el árbitro en una realidad "
"caótica condenada a una efímera eternidad de conflictos. Encarnado por el "
"Guardián del Trueno, también conocido como Kaarul, Guardián del Trueno, "
"Heraldo del Juicio, y Dios de las Tormentas."

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2602
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:244
msgid "Earth"
msgstr "Tierra"

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2603
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:245
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The shelter that harbors the promise of life, the energy that kindles the "
"mystic in a dying reality. Incarnated by the Guardian of Earth, also known "
"as <b>Xia’el</b>, Guardian of the Arcane Flame and Earth, Goddess of the "
"Forests, Protector of Peace."
msgstr ""
"El refugio que alberga la promesa de vida, la energía que enciende lo "
"místico en una realidad moribunda. Encarnada por la Guardiana de la Tierra, "
"también conocida como Xia’el, Guardiana de la Llama Arcana y la Tierra, "
"Diosa de los Bosques, Protectora de la Paz."

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2607
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:248
msgid "Fire"
msgstr "Fuego"

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2608
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:249
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The aspect that fuels life through love, the flame that sustains the forge "
"of knowledge in a reality where ignorance has ensnared its hopeless "
"dwellers. Incarnated by the Guardian of Fire, also known as <b>Shardia</b>, "
"Guardian of Fire and Knowledge, the Fire of Hope, Goddess of Love."
msgstr ""
"El aspecto que alimenta la vida a través del amor, la llama que sostiene la "
"fragua del conocimiento en una realidad donde la ignorancia ha atrapado a "
"sus desesperanzados habitantes. Encarnada por la Guardiana del Fuego, "
"también conocida como Shardia, Guardiana del Fuego y el Conocimiento, el "
"Fuego de la Esperanza, Diosa del Amor."

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2612
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:252
msgid "Darkness"
msgstr "Oscuridad"

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2613
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:253
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The aspect of the free will necessary for life to progress, the precursor "
"and successor of light in a reality devoid of ultimate intent. Incarnated by "
"the Guardian of Darkness, also known as <b>Merthiaal</b>, Guardian of "
"Darkness and Shadows, Eater of Souls, Goddess of Free Will."
msgstr ""
"El aspecto del libre albedrío necesario para que la vida progrese, el "
"precursor y sucesor de la luz en una realidad carente de propósito último. "
"Encarnada por la Guardiana de la Oscuridad, también conocida como Merthiaal, "
"Guardiana de la Oscuridad y las Sombras, Devoradora de Almas, Diosa del "
"Libre Albedrío."

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2617
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:256
msgid "Light"
msgstr "Luz"

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2618
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:257
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The aspect of the constancy from which life springs, the successor and "
"precursor of darkness in a reality unprepared for its end. Incarnated by the "
"Guardian of Light, also known as <b>Luceith’el</b>, Guardian of Light and "
"Metal, Star of the Morning, Healer of Souls."
msgstr ""
"El aspecto de la constancia del que surge la vida, el sucesor y precursor de "
"la oscuridad en una realidad no preparada para su fin. Encarnado por el "
"Guardián de la Luz, también conocido como Luceith’el, Guardián de la Luz y "
"el Metal, Estrella de la Mañana, Sanador de Almas."

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2622
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:261
msgid "Air"
msgstr "Aire"

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2624
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:262
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The aspect of the kiss that insufflates life, the breath that preserves life "
"in a decaying reality. Incarnated by the Guardian of Air, also known as "
"<b>Kazith</b>, Guardian of Air and Breath, Lady of the Skies, Messenger of "
"the Ether."
msgstr ""
"El aspecto del beso que insufla vida, el aliento que preserva la vida en una "
"realidad decadente. Encarnada por la Guardiana del Aire, también conocida "
"como Kazith, Guardiana del Aire y el Aliento, Señora de los Cielos, "
"Mensajera del Éter."

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2628
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:265
msgid "Ice"
msgstr "Hielo"

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2629
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:266
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The aspect that is the cold touch that ends life, the substance that holds "
"treasures for those daring to explore the confines of a shrinking reality. "
"Incarnated by the Guardian of Ice, also known as <b>Yukiria</b>, Guardian of "
"Ice and Mirrors, Queen of the White Expanse, Keeper of Death."
msgstr ""
"El aspecto que es el toque frío que termina con la vida, la sustancia que "
"guarda tesoros para aquellos que se atreven a explorar los confines de una "
"realidad menguante. Encarnada por la Guardiana del Hielo, también conocida "
"como Yukiria, Guardiana del Hielo y los Espejos, Reina de la Blanca Expanse, "
"Guardiana de la Muerte."

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2633
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:269
msgid "Existence"
msgstr "Existencia"

#. [option]
#. [world_entry]: id=the_ten_guardians
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2634
#: After_the_Storm/journey/world.cfg:270
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The aspect that binds all life together, the empty canvas from which a "
"corrupted reality was created. Incarnated by the Guardian of Existence, also "
"known as <b>Delethia</b>, Guardian of Secrets and Time, the Faceless Woman, "
"Seer of the Tree."
msgstr ""
"El aspecto que une toda la vida, el lienzo vacío del que se creó una "
"realidad corrompida. Encarnada por la Guardiana de la Existencia, también "
"conocida como Delethia, Guardiana de los Secretos y el Tiempo, la Mujer Sin "
"Rostro, Vidente del Árbol."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2719
msgid "Biomechanical Engineering Laboratory 03"
msgstr "Laboratorio de Ingeniería Biomecánica 03"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2720
msgid ""
"FACILITY CONDEMNED\n"
"\n"
"NO ENTRY WITHOUT PERMISSION FROM LIFEFORM RESEARCH TEAM LEAD MAL SI’AH"
msgstr ""
"INSTALACIÓN CONDENADA\n"
"\n"
"PROHIBIDA LA ENTRADA SIN PERMISO DEL JEFE DEL EQUIPO DE INVESTIGACIÓN DE "
"FORMAS DE VIDA MAL SI’AH"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08A_Interim.cfg:2788
msgid ""
"A particularly irksome disadvantage of living forever is that you very "
"easily forget things that happened over a century ago if you do not take "
"care to exercise your memory regularly. You are worried that this will "
"become even harder over time, assuming you last long enough for that.\n"
"\n"
"While you prepare your next move you decide to refresh your memory about "
"some things. You make an effort to remember..."
msgstr ""
"Una desventaja particularmente molesta de vivir para siempre es que muy "
"fácilmente olvidas cosas que sucedieron hace más de un siglo si no te "
"esfuerzas por ejercitar tu memoria regularmente. Te preocupa que esto se "
"vuelva aún más difícil con el tiempo, asumiendo que vivas lo suficiente para "
"ello.\n"
"\n"
"Mientras preparas tu próximo movimiento decides refrescar tu memoria sobre "
"algunas cosas. Haces un esfuerzo por recordar..."

