"Destroy Mal Ba’arth, the last Iron Council member, and move Anya to the "
"citadel"
msgstr ""
"Destruye a Mal Ba’arth, el último miembro del Consejo de Hierro, y mueve a "
"Anya a la ciudadela"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:464
msgid "Defeat the Storm Sisters (Vrylla, Grylla, and Aethengrya)"
msgstr "Derrota a las Hermanas de la Tormenta (Vrylla, Grylla y Aethengrya)"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:466
msgid "Move Anya to the citadel"
msgstr "Mueve a Anya a la ciudadela"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:485
msgid ""
"The citadel comprises the starting location for Mal Ba’arth and the "
"immediately adjacent keep (not castle) hexes at (50, 18)"
msgstr ""
"La ciudadela comprende la ubicación inicial de Mal Ba’arth y las casillas de "
"fortaleza adyacentes (no castillos) en (50, 18)"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:486
msgid ""
"It could prove advantageous to defeat other enemy leaders and move Anya or "
"Ergea to their keeps before destroying Mal Ba’arth"
msgstr ""
"Podría ser ventajoso derrotar a otros líderes enemigos y mover a Anya o "
"Ergea a sus fortalezas antes de destruir a Mal Ba’arth"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:487
msgid "Avoid stationing units on the Shaxthal hives nearby"
msgstr "Evita posicionar unidades sobre las colmenas Shaxthal cercanas"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:488
msgid "Do not waste your Goblin Pillagers"
msgstr "No desperdicies a tus Saqueadores Goblin"

