#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:739
msgid ""
"For the last time, Durvan, I am <b>not</b> a goddess! This is ridiculous!"
msgstr "Por última vez, ¡Durvan, <b>no</b> soy una diosa! ¡Esto es ridículo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:744
msgid ""
"Well... there’s not much you can do about it at this point, anyway. Everyone "
"saw the darkness stuff you did with the remaining monsters, and rumors "
"spread like—"
msgstr ""
"Bueno... a estas alturas no puedes hacer mucho al respecto. Todos vieron las "
"cosas oscuras que hiciste con los monstruos restantes, y los rumores se "
"esparcen como—"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:749
msgid ""
"A disease! I do not even know what I actually did! I only want to leave this "
"dreadful place and rest!"
msgstr ""
"¡Una plaga! ¡Ni siquiera sé lo que hice realmente! ¡Solo quiero salir de "
"este horrible lugar y descansar!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:754
msgid ""
"This is the most auspicious moment to storm the citadel if that is what you "
"want to do. And if you play the part you may be able to obtain support from "
"Uria’s converts. Once they realize that the Fist and the Iron Council have "
"been lying to them, the Chaos Empire’s social structure shall shatter. But "
"we ought to plant the seed of distrust now, while Elynia and the Fire "
"prepare to vanquish the usurper."
msgstr ""
"Este es el momento más propicio para asaltar la ciudadela, si eso es lo que "
"quieres hacer. Y si interpretas bien el papel, tal vez logres obtener el "
"apoyo de los conversos de Uria. Una vez que se den cuenta de que el Puño y "
"el Consejo de Hierro les han mentido, la estructura social del Imperio del "
"Caos se desmoronará. Pero debemos sembrar la desconfianza ahora, mientras "
"Elynia y el Fuego se preparan para derrotar al usurpador."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:759
msgid "... Assuming they are even alive."
msgstr "... Suponiendo que sigan vivos."

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:764
msgid "Is that what you want?"
msgstr "¿Es eso lo que deseas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:769
msgid "... Yes."
msgstr "... Sí."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:772
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I want to see her once again. I want to talk to her, smile with her. She "
"promised..."
msgstr ""
"Quiero verla una vez más. Quiero sonreír con ella, hablar con ella. Ella lo "
"prometió..."

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:776
msgid ""
"Then, please, help us. Help us storm the citadel. Help us uproot Uria’s evil "
"influence on Irdya, and advance the long path that lies ahead for you as the "
"Guardian of Darkness."
msgstr ""
"Entonces, por favor, ayúdanos. Ayúdanos a asaltar la ciudadela. Ayúdanos a "
"arrancar de raíz la maligna influencia de Uria en Irdya y a avanzar en el "
"largo camino que te espera como la Guardiana de la Oscuridad."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:794
msgid ""
"I guess I should be thankful you are not calling me Merthiaal or anything "
"like that."
msgstr ""
"Supongo que debería agradecerte que no me llames Merthiaal ni nada por el "
"estilo."

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:799
msgid ""
"The names of the guardians you know were the names they chose for themselves "
"in the First Cycle. We may not call you by the name of the original Guardian "
"of Darkness unless you choose to adopt her name instead of your own."
msgstr ""
"Los nombres de los guardianes que conoces eran los nombres que eligieron "
"para sí mismos en el Primer Ciclo. No podemos llamarte por el nombre de la "
"Guardiana de la Oscuridad original a menos que elijas adoptar su nombre en "
"lugar del tuyo."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:804
msgid "Is that how it really works? I prefer to keep my current name, then."
msgstr ""
"¿Así es como funciona? Entonces prefiero quedarme con mi nombre actual."

#. [message]: speaker=Irylean
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:813
msgid ""
"Hey, Durvan, did you ever think you would fight at the side of two faerie "
"goddesses against an endless horde of demons, imps, and devout worshipers of "
"an evil demoness?"
msgstr ""
"Oye, Durvan, ¿alguna vez pensaste que pelearías al lado de dos diosas "
"feéricas contra una horda interminable de demonios, diablillos y devotos "
"adoradores de una malvada demonio?"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:818
msgid ""
"No. Well, now that you mention it... this will be quite the story to tell "
"the folks in the Heart Forest. Nobody will ever believe me."
msgstr ""
"No. Bueno, ahora que lo dices... será toda una historia para contarle a la "
"gente del Bosque del Corazón. Nadie me creerá jamás."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:823
msgid "Same..."
msgstr "Lo mismo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:837
msgid ""
"On the bright side, dying and returning to the physical realm as a Guardian "
"is a surprisingly easy way to get rid of all the sweat and filth on me."
msgstr ""
"Visto desde el lado positivo, morir y volver al plano físico como Guardiana "
"es una forma sorprendentemente fácil de librarme de todo el sudor y la mugre "
"que tenía encima."

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:851
msgid "Igor?"
msgstr "¿Igor?"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:856
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr "¿Hm?"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:861
msgid ""
"Have you ever felt like... no matter how hard you try, you can’t even hope "
"to measure up to someone whose company you enjoy?"
msgstr ""
"¿Alguna vez sentiste que... no importa cuánto lo intentes, no puedes ni "
"siquiera acercarte a alguien cuya compañía disfrutas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:866
msgid "Uh, sometimes."
msgstr "Eh... a veces."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:880
msgid ""
"But you end up realizing that friends don’t expect you to magically become "
"something you’re not! Lady Elynia and the scary lich always were way more "
"than me with all those magic powers I don’t understand, but that never "
"stopped them from seeing me as a friend!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero al final te das cuenta de que los amigos no esperan que te conviertas "
"mágicamente en algo que no eres! Lady Elynia y la aterradora liche siempre "
"fueron mucho más que yo con todos esos poderes mágicos que no entiendo, "
"¡pero eso nunca les impidió verme como un amigo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:885
msgid "Right. <i>(sighs)</i> I guess I’ve just got to accept it..."
msgstr "Cierto. <i>(suspira)</i> Supongo que solo tengo que aceptarlo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:909
msgid "Oh, hello again!"
msgstr "¡Oh, hola de nuevo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:914
msgid "Greetings."
msgstr "Saludos."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:919
msgid ""
"I thought something bad may have happened to you back there... You were with "
"us and then disappeared? Why?"
msgstr ""
"Pensé que te había pasado algo malo allá atrás... Estabas con nosotros y "
"luego desapareciste. ¿Por qué?"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:924
msgid ""
"You need not worry about my wellbeing, Anya. I can easily escape from "
"certain danger thanks to my intimate connection to the Aspect of Water. "
"There is a large amount of it around these parts, after all."
msgstr ""
"No necesitas preocuparte por mi bienestar, Anya. Puedo escapar fácilmente de "
"ciertos peligros gracias a mi íntima conexión con el Aspecto del Agua. "
"Después de todo, hay una gran cantidad de ella en esta región."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:929
msgid ""
"Please don’t tell me now that you are the Guardian of Water or some nonsense "
"like that... I cannot take more of this right now."
msgstr ""
"Por favor, no me digas ahora que eres la Guardiana del Agua o alguna "
"tontería así... No puedo soportar más de esto en este momento."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:934
msgid ""
"It would be a sin beyond measure for someone such as I to pretend to be a "
"god in front of one. With that said, all faeriekind creatures are connected "
"to one or two Aspects to some degree. For example, you are connected to both "
"Darkness and Earth as the daughter of a forest faerie."
msgstr ""
"Sería un pecado inconmensurable para alguien como yo fingir ser un dios "
"delante de uno. Dicho esto, todas las criaturas feéricas están conectadas en "
"cierto grado a uno o dos Aspectos. Por ejemplo, tú estás conectada tanto a "
"la Oscuridad como a la Tierra como hija de una feérica del bosque."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:944
msgid ""
"Right, which reminds me I still don’t know how the story of my parents ends. "
"Then again... perhaps I don’t want to know."
msgstr ""
"Cierto, lo que me recuerda que todavía no sé cómo termina la historia de mis "
"padres. Aunque... tal vez no quiero saberlo."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:951
msgid "Did you know I was meant to become the Guardian of Darkness, though?"
msgstr ""
"¿Sabías que estaba destinada a convertirme en la Guardiana de la Oscuridad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:956
msgid ""
"Yes, I did. And I apologize for not revealing that to you — if I had, there "
"is a good chance that you would have made all the wrong decisions."
msgstr ""
"Sí, lo sabía. Y te pido disculpas por no habértelo revelado; si lo hubiera "
"hecho, había una buena posibilidad de que hubieras tomado todas las "
"decisiones equivocadas."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:964
msgid ""
"Meanwhile, Ergea hasn’t apologized for keeping information from me... Which "
"reminds me, we still have a battle to fight. I hope I can count on your help."
msgstr ""
"Por otro lado, Ergea no se ha disculpado por ocultarme información... Lo que "
"me recuerda que aún tenemos una batalla que pelear. Espero poder contar con "
"tu ayuda."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:970
msgid ""
"Meanwhile, Ergea hasn’t apologized for keeping information from me... Well, "
"it doesn’t matter for now. We need to get back to the fight."
msgstr ""
"Por otro lado, Ergea no se ha disculpado por ocultarme información... Bueno, "
"no importa por ahora. Tenemos que volver a la pelea."

#. [message]: speaker=Daeira
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:977
msgid "Certainly."
msgstr "Por supuesto."

#. [set_variables]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1115
msgid ""
"The prophecies were correct! The Dark Lady was reborn, and she has finally "
"come to vanquish the usurper and set us free from his grasp!"
msgstr ""
"¡Las profecías eran correctas! La Dama Oscura ha renacido, y finalmente ha "
"venido a derrotar al usurpador y liberarnos de su control!"

#. [set_variables]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1117
msgid "Rise up, brethren! We are slaves of the Fist no more!"
msgstr "¡Levántense, hermanos! ¡Ya no somos esclavos del Puño!"

#. [set_variables]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1119
msgid "May the Dark Lady guide us to victory over the false god!"
msgstr "¡Que la Dama Oscura nos guíe hacia la victoria sobre el falso dios!"

#. [set_variables]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1121
msgid ""
"Can it be? Rebelling against Uria could be highly disastrous for everyone! "
"But... What else do we have left anymore?"
msgstr ""
"¿Será posible? ¡Rebelarse contra Uria podría ser muy desastroso para todos! "
"Pero... ¿qué más nos queda ahora?"

#. [set_variables]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1128
msgid ""
"We have long awaited this night. Together, we shall forge a new empire from "
"the blood of the usurper and the fakes who dare to adore him!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos esperado mucho tiempo por esta noche. ¡Juntos, forjaremos un nuevo "
"imperio con la sangre del usurpador y los falsos que se atreven a adorarlo!"

#. [set_variables]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1130
msgid "Uria’s time is almost over. I can feel it. Death to the usurper!"
msgstr ""
"¡El tiempo de Uria está casi terminado! ¡Lo siento! ¡Muerte al usurpador!"

#. [set_variables]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1132
msgid "Behold, the Guardian of Darkness in all her godly glory!"
msgstr "¡Contemplen a la Guardiana de la Oscuridad en toda su gloria divina!"

#. [set_variables]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1134
msgid "Let us cleanse this land and restore the true cult of Yechnagoth!"
msgstr ""
"¡Purifiquemos esta tierra y restauremos el verdadero culto a Yechnagoth!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Ba'arth
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1340
msgid ""
"... It is true, then. The Dark Lady has finally arisen and come to reclaim "
"this doomed world... But it is all in vain... all in vain..."
msgstr ""
"... Entonces es cierto. La Dama Oscura finalmente ha resurgido y viene a "
"reclamar este mundo condenado... Pero todo es en vano... todo es en vano..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1494
msgid "The citadel is ours! Now we should be able to find Elynia and—"
msgstr "¡La ciudadela es nuestra! Ahora deberíamos poder encontrar a Elynia y—"

#. [message]: speaker=Irylean
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1505
msgid ""
"I fear that we will have to put that plan on hold, Anya. There are reports "
"of more of those creatures coming from the hives around the citadel. People "
"say they will be here in a matter of minutes."
msgstr ""
"Me temo que tendremos que dejar ese plan en pausa, Anya. Hay informes de más "
"de esas criaturas acercándose desde las colmenas alrededor de la ciudadela. "
"La gente dice que estarán aquí en cuestión de minutos."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1510
msgid ""
"But we have only just won! Are they going to storm their own capital now?"
msgstr "¡Pero acabamos de ganar! ¿Van a asaltar su propia capital ahora?"

#. [message]: speaker=Durvan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1515
msgid ""
"I would not put it past them to attempt to destroy the citadel in an attempt "
"to ensure we cannot find Elynia... assuming she is even alive at this point."
msgstr ""
"No me sorprendería que intentaran destruir la ciudadela para asegurarse de "
"que no podamos encontrar a Elynia... suponiendo que siquiera siga viva a "
"estas alturas."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1520
msgid "Do <b>not</b> say that! Let’s repel those awful creatures, then!"
msgstr "¡<b>No</b> digas eso! ¡Entonces repelamos a esas horribles criaturas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Irylean
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1525
msgid "Easier said than done..."
msgstr "Eso es más fácil decirlo que hacerlo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1530
msgid "Battle goblin, ready to crush those bugs!"
msgstr "¡Duende de batalla, listo para aplastar a esos bichos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1544
msgid ""
"The Storm Sisters are now our prisoners, but we must destroy the last member "
"of the Iron Council if we intend to seize the citadel."
msgstr ""
"Las Hermanas de la Tormenta son ahora nuestras prisioneras, pero debemos "
"destruir al último miembro del Consejo de Hierro si queremos tomar la "
"ciudadela."

#. [message]: speaker=Ergea
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1552
msgid ""
"The last member of the Iron Council is no more, but as long as any of the "
"Storm Sisters still roam about, there shall be no end to our struggles."
msgstr ""
"El último miembro del Consejo de Hierro ha caído, pero mientras alguna de "
"las Hermanas de la Tormenta siga rondando, no habrá fin para nuestras luchas."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/08D_Destiny_part_2.cfg:1711
msgid "The earth rumbles..."
msgstr "La tierra tiembla..."

#. [scenario]: id=Elynia
#. [part]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/storytxt.cfg:418
msgid "Dark Depths"
msgstr "Profundidades Oscuras"

#. [side]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:106
msgid "team_name^Engineer"
msgstr "Ingeniero"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:515
msgid "... We are not really trying to locate Zhangor, are we?"
msgstr "... No estamos intentando localizar a Zhangor, ¿verdad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:520
msgid ""
"Of course we are. It is just taking us a while because he prefers to dwell "
"in a very particular place... a place I also want you to see, before "
"confronting him. I also want to give him a while to realize his mistake in "
"interpreting the Seer’s prophecy."
msgstr ""
"Claro que sí. Solo nos está llevando tiempo porque él prefiere habitar en un "
"lugar muy particular... un lugar que también quiero que veas, antes de "
"enfrentarnos a él. Además, quiero darle un tiempo para que se dé cuenta de "
"su error al interpretar la profecía de la Vidente."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:525
msgid "What mistake?"
msgstr "¿Qué error?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:530
msgid ""
"The Seer said that on the Day of the Longest Night, the Angel of Blood would "
"make a hasty attempt on the life of the New Guardian of Darkness, and fail. "
"She also said that his actions would bring forth his own downfall."
msgstr ""
"La Vidente dijo que en el Día de la Noche más Larga, el Ángel de Sangre "
"intentaría apresuradamente acabar con la vida de la Nueva Guardiana de la "
"Oscuridad, y fracasaría. También dijo que sus acciones provocarían su propia "
"caída."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:535
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Zhangor must have decided to send his beasts after Ergea and your friend "
"first, and then wait in his lair for me to go and challenge him — or "
"alternatively, for Naia to rise up again. It would be a clever plan to "
"subvert the prophecy, if it weren’t for his completely incorrect reading of "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Zhangor decidió enviar a sus bestias contra Ergea y tu amiga primero, y "
"luego esperar en su guarida a que yo fuera a desafiarlo, lo cual sería un "
"curso de acción bastante predecible para mí. O bien, está esperando que Naia "
"resurja para atacarme entonces. Todas sus acciones sugieren que quería "
"subvertir la profecía. Pero ya se enfrentó a la Nueva Guardiana de la "
"Oscuridad y fracasó en matarla... aunque fuera a través de sus esbirros."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:540
msgid ""
"He doesn’t realize that the Guardian in question is that girl, who he "
"already confronted and failed to kill. And you might not realize this, but "
"it has been <i>more than a day</i> already — simply put, the Longest Night "
"will not end until the girl puts an end to her emotional turmoil and learns "
"to control her powers."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:545
msgid "Anya’s powers... So she is the cause for the Longest Night?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:550
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Indeed, she is. I would explain more, but I suspect Zhangor is already aware "
"of our movements. Let’s not keep him waiting longer than strictly necessary, "
"shall we?"
msgstr ""
"Y, lamentablemente, también sospecho que Zhangor ya es consciente de "
"nuestros movimientos. No lo hagamos esperar más tiempo del estrictamente "
"necesario, ¿de acuerdo?"

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:576
msgid "You pick up a curious crystal shard."
msgstr "Recoges un curioso fragmento de cristal."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:659
msgid "Where does that lead to?"
msgstr "¿A dónde lleva eso?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:664
msgid ""
"It’s an alternative path to an elevator shaft that will take us directly to "
"the place I previously mentioned. While I don’t mind stabbing whoever stands "
"in our way, a more discreet approach will get us there faster."
msgstr ""
"Es un camino alternativo hacia un pozo de ascensor que nos llevará "
"directamente al lugar que mencioné antes. Aunque no me importa apuñalar a "
"quien se cruce en nuestro camino, un enfoque más discreto nos llevará allí "
"más rápido."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:681
msgid ""
"Only a fully corporeal unit such as Elyssa or Elynia may activate this "
"touchplate."
msgstr ""
"Solo una unidad completamente corpórea como Elyssa o Elynia puede activar "
"esta placa de presión."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:766
msgid "Nothing happens."
msgstr "No ocurre nada."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:777
msgid ""
"These passages have gone unused for centuries — it’s no wonder that most of "
"their mechanisms have rusted beyond use. But I know a method that never "
"fails..."
msgstr ""
"Estos pasajes han estado sin usarse durante siglos; no es de extrañar que la "
"mayoría de sus mecanismos se hayan oxidado sin remedio. Pero conozco un "
"método que nunca falla..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:783
msgid ""
"These passages have gone unused for centuries — it’s no wonder that most of "
"their mechanisms have rusted beyond use. Just blast the wall down already."
msgstr ""
"Estos pasajes han estado sin usarse durante siglos; no es de extrañar que la "
"mayoría de sus mecanismos se hayan oxidado sin remedio. Vamos, derriba ya la "
"pared."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:833
msgid "Perfect."
msgstr "Perfecto."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:861
msgid "That is not very useful—"
msgstr "Eso no es muy útil—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:870
msgid "Hm, there is a hot current of air coming from another direction now."
msgstr ""
"Hm, ahora hay una corriente de aire caliente que viene de otra dirección."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:896
msgid "Ah. I remember now."
msgstr "Ah. Ahora lo recuerdo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1007
msgid "We need to cross this inconvenient lava trench. Elynia, do your thing."
msgstr "Necesitamos cruzar esta incómoda zanja de lava. Elynia, haz lo tuyo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1012
msgid "My... thing?"
msgstr "¿Mi... cosa?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1017
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You are the Guardian of <i>Earth</i>, dear. You are supposed to be capable "
"of more complicated things than blasting walls and vermin."
msgstr ""
"Eres la Guardiana de la <i>Tierra</i>, querida. Se supone que deberías hacer "
"cosas más complicadas que derribar muros y exterminar alimañas."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1022
msgid ""
"Do you really expect me to know how this works all of a sudden?! I did not "
"ask to be given this role, and all I know is that the pain has not ceased! I "
"cannot think clearly like this!"
msgstr ""
"¿De verdad esperas que sepa cómo funciona esto de repente? ¡Yo no pedí que "
"me dieran este papel, y lo único que sé es que el dolor no ha cesado! ¡No "
"puedo pensar con claridad así!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1031
msgid ""
"I <i>really</i> should just stab you in the chest and toss your useless "
"bloody corpse into the lava."
msgstr ""
"De verdad debería clavarte un puñal en el pecho y arrojar tu inútil y "
"sangriento cadáver a la lava."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1060
msgid "Keep moving."
msgstr "Sigue avanzando."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1105
msgid "Well, this wall is not going to move by itself—"
msgstr "Bueno, este muro no se moverá por sí solo—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1111
msgid "Well, that wall is not going to move by itself—"
msgstr "Bueno, ese muro no se moverá por sí solo—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1145
msgid "I stand corrected. That was very convenient."
msgstr "Me corrijo. Eso fue muy conveniente."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1204
msgid "Of course. A cunning trap by Zhangor, I presume?"
msgstr "Por supuesto. ¿Una astuta trampa de Zhangor, supongo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1238
msgid "The elevator..."
msgstr "El ascensor..."

#. [unit]: id=Engineer Fendyrn, type=Dwarvish Engineer
#. [hidden_unit]: id=Engineer Fendyrn, type=Magnum Suit
#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1277
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1397
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1501
msgid "Engineer Fendyrn"
msgstr "Ingeniero Fendyrn"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1293
msgid "<i>... heh, heh, heh, heh, heh, heh...</i>"
msgstr "<i>... je, je, je, je, je, je...</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1302
msgid "Who is that?"
msgstr "¿Quién es ese?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1311
msgid "Engineer?"
msgstr "¿Ingeniero?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1321
msgid "<i>... hah, hah, hah, hah...</i>"
msgstr "<i>... ja, ja, ja, ja...</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1326
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You lack the required clearance to be around these levels, Engineer. Return "
"to your workshop immediately."
msgstr ""
"No se supone que debas estar en estos niveles, Ingeniero. Regresa a tu "
"taller de inmediato."

#. [message]: speaker=Engineer Fendyrn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1331
msgid ""
"I dinna’ listen tae orders from ye anymore, witch. Yer time as the ‘Warlord’ "
"ended with Lord Zhangor’s arrival."
msgstr ""
"Ya no escucho órdenes tuyas, bruja. Tu tiempo como la ‘Señora de la Guerra’ "
"acabó con la llegada del Lord Zhangor."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1336
msgid ""
"I believe I speak for Zhangor as well when I say that you are not supposed "
"to be here. Return to your workshop immediately, or face the consequences."
msgstr ""
"Creo que también hablo por Zhangor al decir que no deberías estar aquí. "
"Vuelve a tu taller de inmediato o afronta las consecuencias."

#. [message]: speaker=Engineer Fendyrn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1341
msgid ""
"Ye’ll chop me remainin’ leg too, winna ye? Ha, ha, ha, ha. Yer torture "
"methods are as obsolete as the tech’ Argan used tae rebuild yer body."
msgstr ""
"¿También me cortarás la pierna que me queda, no? Ja, ja, ja, ja. Tus métodos "
"de tortura son tan anticuados como la tecno’ que usó Argan pa’ reconstruir "
"tu cuerpo."

#. [message]: speaker=Engineer Fendyrn
#. "Squirming insects" refers to the Shaxthal.
#. "The two of you" refers to Elyssa and Zhangor, not Elyssa and Elynia.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1348
msgid ""
"Zhangor released me a while ago, didna’ ye hear? “Yer free”, he said. “Ye "
"can do anythin’ ye please”, said. And so here I am, ready tae take on the "
"two of ye, and all yer squirmin’ insects."
msgstr ""
"Zhangor me soltó hace un tiempo, ¿no lo oíste? “Eres libre”, dijo. “Podés "
"hacer lo que se te antoje”, dijo. Y aquí estoy, listo pa’ encarar a los dos "
"y a todos vuestros insectos retorciéndose."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1353
msgid "Is this insubordination I hear? This is your last chance."
msgstr "¿Es esto insubordinación lo que oigo? Esta es tu última oportunidad."

#. [message]: speaker=Engineer Fendyrn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1358
msgid "I believe ’tis yer last chance tae <i>run</i>, girl."
msgstr "Creo que esta es tu última chance pa’ <i>huir</i>, muchacha."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1471
msgid "Oh gods... Is that..."
msgstr "Oh, dioses… ¿Es eso…?"

#. [message]: speaker=Engineer Fendyrn
#. The lich is Mal Hekuba.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1477
msgid ""
"Aye. The Soul Hammer is made’a the crystals commissioned by tha’ wretched "
"lich. Lord Zhangor has put many a’them intae good use, elf. But he dinna’ "
"ken ’tis hammer exists, or that it shall be the instrument of me revenge! "
"Perhaps I should’a named her... the Destroyer o’ Gods!"
msgstr ""
"Sí. El Martillo del Alma está hecho de los cristales encargados por ese "
"liche despreciable. Lord Zhangor ha puesto muchos de’ ellos en buen uso, "
"elfa. Pero él no sabe que este martillo existe… ¡ni que será el instrumento "
"de mi venganza! Quizá debería haberlo llamado… ¡el Destructor de Dioses!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1482
msgid ""
"Elynia, this is extremely dangerous. Stay away from this lunatic and his "
"hammer! You, fool... you have absolutely no idea with what kind of powers "
"you are trifling."
msgstr ""
"Elynia, esto es extremadamente peligroso. ¡Aléjate de este lunático y su "
"martillo! Y tú, imbécil… no tienes ni la menor idea del tipo de poderes con "
"los que estás jugando."

#. [message]: speaker=Engineer Fendyrn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1487
msgid "<b>HA, HA, HA, HA, HA, HA, HA, HA!!!</b>"
msgstr "<b>¡JA, JA, JA, JA, JA, JA, JA, JA!</b>"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1501
msgid "Tortured Inventor of Infernal Contraptions"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1509
msgid "Stop the Engineer"
msgstr "Detener al Ingeniero"

#. [event]: id=engineer_backstabbing_hint_handler # wmllint: ignore
#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1556
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1516
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1857
msgid ""
"The power of the Engineer’s hammer allows him to debilitate and destroy the "
"Energy Heart of a Guardian"
msgstr ""
"El poder del martillo del Ingeniero le permite debilitar y destruir el "
"Corazón de Energía de un Guardián"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1517
msgid ""
"Elyssa and Elynia cannot damage the Engineer’s armor suit as it is powered "
"by more replicas of Merthiaal’s heart; they must find another way to stop him"
msgstr ""
"Elyssa y Elynia no pueden dañar el traje blindado del Ingeniero, ya que está "
"alimentado por más réplicas del corazón de Merthiaal; deben encontrar otra "
"forma de detenerlo"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1528
msgid ""
"I have an idea... Malin once mentioned something specific about Galas’ first "
"encounter with your mechanical automatons."
msgstr ""
"Tengo una idea… Malin mencionó una vez algo específico sobre el primer "
"encuentro de Galas con tus autómatas mecánicos."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1533
msgid "And what would that be?"
msgstr "¿Y qué sería?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1538
msgid ""
"They are particularly vulnerable in the neck region. Maybe if we could "
"distract him, you could stab him with your weapon—"
msgstr ""
"Son particularmente vulnerables en la región del cuello. Quizá, si "
"pudiéramos distraerlo, podrías apuñalarlo con tu arma—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1543
msgid ""
"That was already my plan, stupid! Just try to do your part right for once!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ese ya era mi plan, estúpida! ¡Solo intenta hacer bien tu parte por una vez!"

#. [event]: id=engineer_backstabbing_hint_handler # wmllint: ignore
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1548
msgid ""
"Backstab the Engineer using the Claw of Urvatha while he is facing Elynia"
msgstr ""
"Ap stabbed al Ingeniero usando la Garra de Urvatha mientras está de cara a "
"Elynia"

#. [event]: id=engineer_backstabbing_hint_handler # wmllint: ignore
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1555
msgid "You can only backstab the Engineer during your own turns, on offense"
msgstr ""
"Solo puedes apuñalar por la espalda al Ingeniero durante tus propios turnos, "
"en ataque"

#. [message]: speaker=Engineer Fendyrn
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1840
msgid "<b>ACK!</b> What ha’ ye done!!!"
msgstr "<b>¡ARGH!</b> ¡¿Qué has hecho?!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1845
msgid ""
"Oops! It seems your armor suit and fancy hammer are not perfect substitutes "
"for the power of a true Guardian of Darkness!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ups! Parece que tu armadura y tu martillo elegante no son sustitutos "
"perfectos del poder de un verdadero Guardián de la Oscuridad."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1850
msgid "Defeat the Engineer now that he is vulnerable to attacks"
msgstr "Derrota al Ingeniero ahora que es vulnerable a los ataques"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:1938
msgid "Elynia, grab my hand!"
msgstr "¡Elynia, agarra mi mano!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2143
msgid "Unngh..."
msgstr "Ungh..."

#. [event]: id=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2161
msgid ""
"I did not know where I was. The last thing I could recall was the chamber "
"floor collapsing due to the energy released from the dwarf’s fractured "
"hammer."
msgstr ""
"No sabía dónde estaba. Lo último que recordaba era el suelo de la cámara "
"colapsando por la energía liberada del martillo fracturado del enano."

#. [event]: id=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2163
msgid ""
"My neck felt cold and sticky... it was blood. I must have smashed my head "
"during the fall, and yet I was standing there as though my body had healed "
"itself from the otherwise fatal injury.\n"
"\n"
"I glanced at my surroundings..."
msgstr ""
"Mi cuello se sentía frío y pegajoso... era sangre. Debí haberme golpeado la "
"cabeza durante la caída, y aun así estaba de pie como si mi cuerpo se "
"hubiera curado de una herida que de otro modo habría sido fatal.\n"
"\n"
"Eché un vistazo a mi alrededor..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2179
msgid "Elyssa...?"
msgstr "¿Elyssa...?"

#. [event]: id=Elynia
#. Yes, Elynia is describing a literal BSOD (Blue Screen of Death).
#. See: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blue_Screen_of_Death
#. Looks like Norsulan technology isn't perfect either!
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2191
msgid ""
"The demoness was lying on the humid cavern floor, inert as a rock. She did "
"not seem injured, but neither did she draw breath. I did not know at first "
"what to make of the situation.\n"
"\n"
"I laid a hand on her forehead and attempted to peer into her mind to see "
"whether she was still alive. However, all I could see through her frozen "
"eyes was a series of incomprehensible white glyphs on a blue background, "
"interspersed with an alien and yet somehow familiar language. Knowing she "
"was a hybrid lifeform, the evidence I gathered was useless."
msgstr ""
"La demonio yacía en el húmedo suelo de la caverna, inerte como una roca. No "
"parecía herida, pero tampoco respiraba. Al principio no supe qué pensar de "
"la situación.\n"
"\n"
"Posé una mano sobre su frente e intenté asomarme a su mente para ver si "
"seguía con vida. Sin embargo, todo lo que pude ver a través de sus ojos "
"congelados fueron una serie de glifos blancos incomprensibles sobre un fondo "
"azul, intercalados con un lenguaje alienígena y, sin embargo, de algún modo "
"familiar. Sabiendo que era una forma de vida híbrida, la evidencia que reuní "
"era inútil."

#. [event]: id=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2195
msgid ""
"She could be alive... or she could be dead.\n"
"\n"
"And not too far from her was the weapon she called the Claw of Urvatha. My "
"master’s staff, first corrupted by the heart of a Gatekeeper, the artifact "
"we used to call the Ruby of Fire, and now, by the malignant touch of "
"Merthiaal’s successor."
msgstr ""
"Podía estar viva... o podía estar muerta.\n"
"\n"
"Y no muy lejos de ella estaba el arma que llamaba la Garra de Urvatha. El "
"báculo de mi maestro, primero corrompido por el corazón de un Guardián, el "
"artefacto que solíamos llamar el Rubí de Fuego, y ahora, por el toque "
"maligno del sucesor de Merthiaal."

#. [event]: id=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2203
msgid ""
"I felt compelled to grab the weapon and leave the demoness behind... but I "
"had to ponder my possibilities first. She could come back to life the moment "
"I laid my hands on it, and destroy me. Or she could stay as a dormant "
"machine, and I would just abandon her and return to the surface, with Anya "
"and Ergea.\n"
"\n"
"A third alternative then occurred to me. I could grab the Claw, and destroy "
"the creature in her sleep..."
msgstr ""
"Sentí la tentación de tomar el arma y dejar atrás a la demonio... pero "
"primero debía reflexionar sobre mis posibilidades. Podía volver a la vida en "
"el momento en que la tomara y destruirme. O podía seguir como una máquina "
"dormida, y yo simplemente la abandonaría para regresar a la superficie con "
"Anya y Ergea.\n"
"\n"
"Entonces se me ocurrió una tercera alternativa. Podía tomar la Garra y "
"destruir a la criatura mientras dormía..."

#. [event]: id=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2211
msgid ""
"... I spent some amount of time contemplating that tempting alternative.\n"
"\n"
"Suddenly, the thought of becoming a cold-blooded murderer horrified me.\n"
"\n"
"No.\n"
"\n"
"No, I would not give in to such terrifying ideas. No. That was not me. That "
"was not the elf who was raised by Niryone to protect the peoples of Irdya.\n"
"\n"
"No."
msgstr ""
"... Pasé un tiempo contemplando esa tentadora alternativa.\n"
"\n"
"De repente, la idea de convertirme en una asesina a sangre fría me "
"horrorizó.\n"
"\n"
"No.\n"
"\n"
"No, no cedería a pensamientos tan terroríficos. No. Esa no era yo. No era la "
"elfa que fue criada por Niryone para proteger a los pueblos de Irdya.\n"
"\n"
"No."

#. [event]: id=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2233
msgid ""
"Between tears, I could catch a glimpse of light coming from around a corner."
msgstr ""
"Entre lágrimas, pude vislumbrar una luz que provenía de la vuelta de la "
"esquina."

#. [event]: id=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2250
msgid ""
"A conspicuous corridor, leading somewhere brightly illuminated. The walls "
"were decorated with peculiar engravings.\n"
"\n"
"I was compelled to follow. With my captor completely incapacitated to exert "
"any kind of magic control over me, I could once again move with absolute "
"freedom."
msgstr ""
"Un pasillo llamativo, que conducía a un lugar intensamente iluminado. Las "
"paredes estaban decoradas con grabados peculiares.\n"
"\n"
"Me sentí impulsada a seguir. Con mi captora completamente incapacitada para "
"ejercer cualquier tipo de control mágico sobre mí, podía moverme de nuevo "
"con absoluta libertad."

#. [event]: id=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2293
msgid "Explore the place"
msgstr "Explorar el lugar"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2323
msgid ""
"It was not my intention to go back where Elyssa’s inert body laid. I needed "
"to keep exploring the corridor. My curiosity was just too great to resist."
msgstr ""
"No era mi intención regresar al lugar donde yacía el cuerpo inerte de "
"Elyssa. Necesitaba seguir explorando el pasillo. Mi curiosidad era demasiado "
"grande para resistirme."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2393
msgid ""
"The ceiling lights formed a familiar shape on the floor: the sigil of the "
"First Guardian of Earth, Xia’el. Or at least, as it was depicted in Argan’s "
"journal.\n"
"\n"
"An odd sense of comfort suddenly came to me. I felt for once as though I "
"was, finally, at home."
msgstr ""
"Las luces del techo formaban en el suelo una figura familiar: el símbolo del "
"Primer Guardián de la Tierra, Xia’el. O al menos, como estaba representado "
"en el diario de Argan.\n"
"\n"
"De repente, una extraña sensación de consuelo me invadió. Por primera vez "
"sentí que, finalmente, estaba en casa."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2411
msgid ""
"If Elyssa spoke the truth, this was my destiny all along. I was meant to be "
"the Guardian of Earth on Irdya, and I was meant to keep my world and my "
"people from harm; from Elyssa, from Argan, from Zhangor, from Uria...\n"
"\n"
"... From myself.\n"
"\n"
"... And I had failed. I had failed them all. I grew up ignorant of my true "
"purpose, focusing only on mundane problems, selfishly centered on my own "
"needs and desires for the most part. I allowed Irdya’s terrible fate to come "
"to pass: the destruction of many civilizations, the deaths of millions.\n"
"\n"
"Weren’t Guardians created to <i>protect</i> their worlds?"
msgstr ""
"Si Elyssa decía la verdad, ese había sido siempre mi destino. Estaba "
"destinada a ser la Guardiana de la Tierra en Irdya, y a proteger mi mundo y "
"a mi pueblo del daño; de Elyssa, de Argan, de Zhangor, de Uria...\n"
"\n"
"... De mí misma.\n"
"\n"
"... Y había fallado. Había fallado a todos ellos. Crecí ignorando mi "
"verdadero propósito, enfocada solo en problemas mundanos, egoístamente "
"centrada en mis propias necesidades y deseos en su mayoría. Permití que el "
"terrible destino de Irdya se cumpliera: la destrucción de muchas "
"civilizaciones, la muerte de millones.\n"
"\n"
"¿No fueron los Guardianes creados para <i>proteger</i> sus mundos?"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2438
msgid ""
"I let myself collapse on the floor... and cried.\n"
"\n"
"I needed to cry after Galas’ death. I needed to cry after losing Malin. But "
"I resisted the emotion for so long because I did not want anyone to know I "
"was weak inside.\n"
"\n"
"But then, I was at home at last... alone. Nobody would know. So I cried.\n"
"\n"
"I wished Anya could be with me. But she did not know where I was, and I did "
"not even know whether she was still alive. And even if she was... it would "
"only be a matter of time until Zhangor solved the Seer’s riddle and killed "
"the girl."
msgstr ""
"Me dejé caer al suelo... y lloré.\n"
"\n"
"Necesitaba llorar tras la muerte de Galas. Necesitaba llorar tras perder a "
"Malin. Pero resistí la emoción por tanto tiempo porque no quería que nadie "
"supiera que era débil por dentro.\n"
"\n"
"Pero entonces, por fin estaba en casa... sola. Nadie lo sabría. Así que "
"lloré.\n"
"\n"
"Desearía que Anya pudiera estar conmigo. Pero ella no sabía dónde estaba, y "
"yo ni siquiera sabía si seguía viva. Y aunque lo estuviera... solo sería "
"cuestión de tiempo hasta que Zhangor resolviera el acertijo del Vidente y "
"matara a la chica."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2450
msgid "Home..."
msgstr "Casa..."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2456
msgid "There, there."
msgstr "Ahí, ahí."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2462
msgid "You have not failed yet, my love. There are still things left to do."
msgstr "Aún no has fallado, mi amor. Todavía quedan cosas por hacer."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2468
msgid "... A— Argan?"
msgstr "... A— Argan?"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2474
msgid "... Oh, I must have really lost it now."
msgstr "... Oh, creo que realmente he perdido la cabeza."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2480
msgid "I am here. Don’t you feel me?"
msgstr "Estoy aquí. ¿No me sientes?"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2486
msgid "... Is this a dream?"
msgstr "... ¿Es esto un sueño?"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2492
msgid "... Is it?"
msgstr "... ¿Lo es?"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2498
msgid "... I feel you. I feel your warm touch again. But... how?"
msgstr "... Te siento. Siento tu cálido tacto de nuevo. Pero... ¿cómo?"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2500
msgid "Because you wished for my return. All these years..."
msgstr "Porque deseaste mi regreso. Durante todos estos años..."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2502
msgid "... I did."
msgstr "... Lo deseé."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2504
msgid "I missed you, Elynia."
msgstr "Te extrañé, Elynia."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2506
msgid ""
"... I— I—\n"
"\n"
"... I did too.\n"
"\n"
"Oh, Argan..."
msgstr ""
"... Yo— yo—\n"
"\n"
"... Yo también.\n"
"\n"
"Oh, Argan..."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2516
msgid ""
"We don’t have much time left, my love. Irdya is in ruins now, and Zhangor "
"could find us any moment now. You need to get up."
msgstr ""
"No nos queda mucho tiempo, mi amor. Irdya está en ruinas, y Zhangor podría "
"encontrarnos en cualquier momento. Tienes que levantarte."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2518
msgid "Yes..."
msgstr "Sí..."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2556
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I let my lips approach his as we embraced like we had not for an eternity. "
"He felt so delightfully real, I was willing to give in to our carnal urges.\n"
"\n"
"But..."
msgstr ""
"Dejé que mis labios se acercaran a los suyos mientras nos abrazábamos como "
"si no lo hubiéramos hecho en una eternidad. Se sentía tan maravillosamente "
"real que estaba dispuesta a entregarme a nuestros deseos carnales.\n"
"\n"
"Pero..."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2566
msgid "Is there something wrong, my love?"
msgstr "¿Sucede algo, mi amor?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2571
msgid "I... feel... strange."
msgstr "Me... siento... extraña."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2580
msgid "My heart... it hurts..."
msgstr "Mi corazón... duele..."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2585
msgid ""
"That must be because you have spent too much time scurrying around. Just let "
"yourself relax for a moment. We can reminisce about better times together..."
msgstr ""
"Debe ser porque has pasado demasiado tiempo correteando. Solo déjate relajar "
"un momento. Podemos recordar juntos tiempos mejores..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#. Yes, the question mark may seem misplaced, but it's actually intentional
#. as it denotes a different sentence inflection. She is supposed to sound
#. confused.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2599
msgid "You don’t sound like yourself? My head... I—"
msgstr "¿No suenas como tú misma? Mi cabeza... yo—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2604
msgid ""
"My memories have become so hazy... but... I... remember that sword... Elyssa "
"has your sword..."
msgstr ""
"Mis recuerdos están tan borrosos... pero... recuerdo esa espada... Elyssa "
"tiene tu espada..."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2609
msgid "Elynia, please, just..."
msgstr "Elynia, por favor, solo..."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2624
msgid "Hello..."
msgstr "Hola..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2677
msgid "... Zhangor."
msgstr "... Zhangor."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2688
msgid "How..."
msgstr "¿Cómo...?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#. I guess I'm already pushing the censors' limits a lot here?
#. It'd be advisable to keep it subtle in translations too.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2695
msgid ""
"Your act seems pretty cheap in retrospect. I cannot say I am completely "
"disappointed, though; it was <i>absolutely</i> amusing to watch you attempt "
"to—ahem—handle the poor, broken elf. But did you truly think it would work "
"out? Ha ha ha!"
msgstr ""
"Tu acto parece bastante barato en retrospectiva. No puedo decir que esté "
"completamente decepcionada, sin embargo; fue <i>absolutamente</i> divertido "
"verte intentar — ejem — manejar a la pobre y rota elfa. Pero, ¿de verdad "
"pensaste que funcionaría? ¡Ja, ja, ja!"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2700
#, fuzzy
msgid "<i>(metallic voice) I am not precisely here in person, though.</i>"
msgstr "<i>(voz metálica) Sin embargo, no soy exactamente yo mismo.</i>"

#. [unit]: id=Deathbringer, type=Shaxthal Deathbringer Alpha
#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Deathbringer, race=shaxthal, description=
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2745
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Shaxthal_Deathbringer.cfg:6
msgid "Deathbringer"
msgstr "Portador de la muerte"

#. [message]: speaker=Deathbringer
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2777
msgid "But your guess was close enough. Congratulations, Guardian of Darkness."
msgstr ""
"Pero tu suposición estuvo bastante cerca. Felicidades, Guardiana de la "
"Oscuridad."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2782
msgid ""
"So the rumors are true, after all — you go around possessing other creatures "
"using your disgusting body ooze."
msgstr ""
"Así que los rumores son ciertos, después de todo — posees a otras criaturas "
"usando tu asqueroso limo corporal."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2787
msgid "(<i>enraged</i>) You were going to possess me..."
msgstr "(<i>enfurecida</i>) Ibas a poseerme..."

#. [message]: speaker=Deathbringer
#. "Aspect" here refers to the Aspect of Earth, not Elynia's physical appearance.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2793
msgid ""
"Now, now, possessing a Guardian as vulnerable and inexperienced as you could "
"hardly be considered a feat. <i>Consuming</i> you and stealing your aspect, "
"though... would that not be something? Alas, it would seem you both wish to "
"perish instead."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2816
msgid "(<i>enraged</i>) Not if I can kill <b>you</b> first."
msgstr "(<i>enfurecida</i>) No si puedo matarte <b>a ti</b> primero."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2843
msgid "Defeat Zhangor’s Deathbringer"
msgstr "Derrota al Portador de la Muerte de Zhangor"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2850
msgid ""
"The Deathbringer’s spear allows it to destroy the Energy Heart of a Guardian"
msgstr ""
"La lanza del Portador de la Muerte le permite destruir el Corazón de Energía "
"de un Guardián"

#. [event]
#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Deathbringer Alpha, race=shaxthal, description=
#. That's a greek alpha. Translate as it seems more
#. convenient for your target language/font.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2863
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Shaxthal_Deathbringer_Alpha.cfg:8
msgid "Deathbringer α"
msgstr "Portador de la muerte α"

#. [event]
#. That's a greek alpha. Translate as it seems more
#. convenient for your target language/font.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:2866
msgid "The Demon Lord’s Puppet"
msgstr ""

#. [_journeylog_ui_ats_e3s9]
#. As part of the eerie ambience for this section, the JourneyLog UI gets
#. "corrupted" as well, along with other parts of the game interface.
#. This text is a direct quote of IftU S10y - The Fall, in which Elynia
#. introduces the Ka'lian.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3121
msgid ""
"<i>The members of the Ka’lian valued knowledge over all other things\n"
"\n"
"They sought to plunder all the secrets of Irdya for the greater good\n"
"\n"
"In time, this would bring about our downfall</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3470
msgid "Hello?"
msgstr "¿Hola?"

#. [event]
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [case]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3479
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4771
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:2573
msgid "Niryone"
msgstr "Niryone"

#. [message]: speaker=Niryone
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3483
msgid "Back from Filinor’s class early?"
msgstr "¿Volviste temprano de la clase de Filinor?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3502
msgid ""
"He twisted his ankle yesterday morning while hunting with Cerin, so he let "
"us go after a short round of questions."
msgstr ""
"Se torció el tobillo ayer por la mañana mientras cazaba con Cerin, así que "
"nos dejó ir tras una breve ronda de preguntas."

#. [message]: speaker=Niryone
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3507
msgid ""
"Bah. Figures. At least that means we can enjoy a nice midday meal together "
"for a change."
msgstr ""
"Bah. Claro que sí. Al menos eso significa que podemos disfrutar juntos de "
"una buena comida al mediodía para variar."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3518
msgid "Sure, that would be great! I’m starving."
msgstr "¡Claro, sería genial! Estoy hambrienta."

#. [message]: speaker=Niryone
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3531
msgid "Don’t come with me. It’s too dangerous."
msgstr "No vengas conmigo. Es demasiado peligroso."

#. [_journeylog_ui_ats_e3s9]
#. Urvenirdrya is an archaic name for Urvatha (Inferno)
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3575
msgid ""
"Head severed\n"
"\n"
"Eyes blinded\n"
"\n"
"Limbs scattered\n"
"\n"
"Deep beneath Urvenirdrya\n"
"\n"
"I have waited"
msgstr ""

