#. [_journeylog_ui_ats_e3s9]
#. This is a direct quote of Elyssa lifted from UtBS S2
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3606
msgid ""
"<i>I accidentally managed to anger a powerful necromancer a while ago...\n"
"\n"
"It’s a long story\n"
"\n"
"But who are you?\n"
"\n"
"You almost look like elves</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3647
msgid "Niry? Where did you go?"
msgstr "¿Niry? ¿A dónde fuiste?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. IftU S23B callback.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3655
msgid "<i>You are... hurting me...</i>"
msgstr "<i>Me estás... haciendo daño...</i>"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3659
msgid "Final Objective:"
msgstr "Objetivo Final:"

#. [_journeylog_ui_ats_e3s9]
#. This is Elynia's side of an exchange in which Argan
#. is proposing to her. She accepts.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3675
msgid ""
"<i>Argan, are you sure about this?\n"
"\n"
"Tragedy appears to follow me wherever I go\n"
"\n"
"And we may not be able to see each other for long periods of time\n"
"\n"
"I know, but...\n"
"\n"
"Immortality does little to assuage the passage of time\n"
"\n"
"I could never love anyone else as much as I do love you, my Argan\n"
"\n"
"My love...\n"
"\n"
"Yes...\n"
"\n"
"Oh, Argan, my love...\n"
"\n"
"Yes, yes, I would</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [case]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3704
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:2587
msgid "Anlindë"
msgstr "Anlindë"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3706
msgid ""
"<i>Don’t you realize that he will murder them all if you continue this "
"pointless crusade of yours? Just leave them be, please!</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>¿No te das cuenta de que él los matará a todos si continúas con esta "
"cruzada inútil? ¡Déjalos en paz, por favor!</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3713
msgid ""
"<i>Don’t you dare speak in that tone to me, foul priestess! You should be "
"grateful we do not cut your tongue off for your insolence. Guards! Escort "
"her out, now!</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>¡Ni se te ocurra hablarme con ese tono, vil sacerdotisa! Deberías estar "
"agradecida de que no te cortemos la lengua por tu insolencia. ¡Guardias! "
"¡Echadla ahora!</i>"

#. [_journeylog_ui_ats_e3s9]
#. This is Elyssa's voice, in a flashback to her imprisonment prior to
#. dying and being 'rebuilt'.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3766
msgid ""
"<i>Please, let me go\n"
"\n"
"If you let me go I swear will never trouble you again\n"
"\n"
"Please...\n"
"\n"
"Please...\n"
"\n"
"I beg you...\n"
"\n"
"I just want to go...\n"
"\n"
"Please...\n"
"\n"
"I can’t...\n"
"\n"
"I can’t...\n"
"\n"
"I just want to go...</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3790
msgid "The Lady of Light and the Master of Darkness must die!"
msgstr "¡La Dama de la Luz y el Maestro de la Oscuridad deben morir!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3795
msgid "Stop! Why are you doing this?!"
msgstr "¡Alto! ¿Por qué haces esto?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. "Them" = the elvish peoples
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3811
msgid ""
"<i>I do not suppose I can convince you to abandon them now, after so long. "
"Am I right?</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>No creo que pueda convencerte de que los abandones ahora, después de "
"tanto tiempo. ¿Estoy en lo cierto?</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3818
msgid "<i>Of course not.</i>"
msgstr "<i>Por supuesto que no.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3828
msgid "<i>Then... we shall do this. Together.</i>"
msgstr "<i>Entonces... haremos esto. Juntos.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3839
msgid "<i>... Together.</i>"
msgstr "<i>... Juntos.</i>"

#. [_journeylog_ui_ats_e3s9]
#. This is Elynia's voice, again only her side of an exchange
#. with Argan.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3853
msgid ""
"<i>Ever considered returning to your land?\n"
"\n"
"I’m sure there must be a way\n"
"\n"
"From the things you’ve told me, it sounds so beautiful\n"
"\n"
"“Earth”? That’s not very original, is it?\n"
"\n"
"I mean, Irdya is often called that as well\n"
"\n"
"“Naalirdrya”? That’s such a mouthful, my love\n"
"\n"
"“Norsula”? Norsula... Hm, I like that\n"
"\n"
"Well, it’s just...\n"
"\n"
"Sometimes I wish I could leave all this behind\n"
"\n"
"Just you and me\n"
"\n"
"Somewhere where nobody knows us\n"
"\n"
"Free from responsibilities\n"
"\n"
"Forever</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3915
msgid "Do you think our people will ever find peace again, Elynia?"
msgstr ""
"¿Crees que nuestro pueblo alguna vez encontrará la paz de nuevo, Elynia?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3939
msgid "It doesn’t matter now, I guess."
msgstr "Supongo que ya no importa."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3968
msgid "Because I am dead."
msgstr "Porque estoy muerto."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3989
msgid "Previous Objective:"
msgstr "Objetivo Anterior:"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3990
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:3992
msgid ""
"Kill Argan, the Master of Darkness, and put an end to his sinister rule over "
"Irdya"
msgstr ""
"Mata a Argan, el Maestro de la Oscuridad, y pone fin a su siniestro dominio "
"sobre Irdya"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4008
msgid "What is this place... Something feels amiss."
msgstr "¿Qué es este lugar...? Algo se siente extraño."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4053
msgid ""
"Elynia! Oh, I’m so glad I could finally find you... Come with me, this way! "
"Quickly!"
msgstr ""
"¡Elynia! Oh, me alegra tanto haberte encontrado al fin... ¡Ven conmigo, por "
"aquí! ¡Rápido!"

#. [_journeylog_ui_ats_e3s9]
#. This is Elyssa's voice or thoughts -- unclear which one.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4085
msgid ""
"<i>Why...\n"
"\n"
"Why am I...\n"
"\n"
"What did you do to me...\n"
"\n"
"My body...\n"
"\n"
"The intense red sun...\n"
"\n"
"It’s blinding me...\n"
"\n"
"Please make it stop...\n"
"\n"
"Please...\n"
"\n"
"I just want to go...\n"
"\n"
"I just want to die...</i>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4116
msgid ""
"My hair gets so messy with all the wind in this desert. It’s almost tempting "
"to shave it... Do you think I would look too weird if I did that?"
msgstr ""
"Mi cabello se despeina con todo el viento de este desierto. Casi me tienta "
"afeitarlo... ¿Crees que me vería muy raro si lo hiciera?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4127
msgid "Did we... Didn’t we have this conversation already?"
msgstr "¿No habíamos tenido esta conversación ya?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4132
msgid ""
"I’m just concerned that you might not like it if I do that... Your hair is "
"always so fluffy and nice and beautiful..."
msgstr ""
"Solo me preocupa que no te guste si lo hago... Tu cabello siempre está tan "
"esponjoso, lindo y hermoso..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4137
msgid "... All right, that is not something I recall you saying..."
msgstr "... Está bien, eso no recuerdo habértelo escuchado decir..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anya
#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4152
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4163
msgid "You promised..."
msgstr "Lo prometiste..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4217
msgid "I must find Elyssa. She must be here, somewhere..."
msgstr "Debo encontrar a Elyssa. Debe estar aquí, en algún lugar..."

#. [_journeylog_ui_ats_e3s9]
#. This is Zhangor, addressing Elynia and Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4236
msgid ""
"Do you really think you can escape me?\n"
"\n"
"The grasp of Existence permeates all\n"
"\n"
"Your lives\n"
"\n"
"Your aspects\n"
"\n"
"Your souls\n"
"\n"
"They now belong\n"
"\n"
"<big><big>to me</big></big>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. Elyssa speaking here.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4284
msgid "<i>Did you know that this entire land used to be a huge empire?</i>"
msgstr "<i>¿Sabías que toda esta tierra solía ser un gran imperio?</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. Elyssa speaking to Argan here.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4297
msgid ""
"<i>You’re asking too much from me. To confront a goddess who has accrued "
"enough power to wipe out an entire world...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Me pides demasiado. Enfrentar a una diosa que ha acumulado suficiente "
"poder para destruir un mundo entero...</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. Elyssa speaking to Argan here.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4308
msgid "<i>... I understand. </i>"
msgstr "<i>... Lo entiendo. </i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. Callback to IftU S23Bx.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4352
msgid "<i>... you betrayed... me...</i>"
msgstr "<i>... me traicionaste...</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#. Callback to IftU S23Bx.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4404
msgid ""
"Argan! No, no, this can’t be happening, you can’t be doing this, I am trying "
"to heal you, don’t you see? I..."
msgstr ""
"¡Argan! No, no puede estar pasando, no puedes hacer esto, estoy tratando de "
"sanarte, ¿no lo ves? Yo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4423
msgid "Why don’t you say anything? Argan!"
msgstr "¿Por qué no dices nada? ¡Argan!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia2
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4428
msgid "Argan— No..."
msgstr "Argan— No..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4446
msgid "Elyssa?"
msgstr "¿Elyssa?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4457
msgid "YOU KILLED HIM!"
msgstr "¡LO MATASTE!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4466
msgid "Elyssa, I..."
msgstr "Elyssa, yo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4473
msgid "Why— Why do you have to show me this again? WHY?"
msgstr "¿Por qué— por qué tienes que mostrarme esto otra vez? ¿POR QUÉ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4536
msgid "Why couldn’t you <b>save</b> him instead?!"
msgstr "¿Por qué no pudiste <b>salvarlo</b> en su lugar?!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4574
msgid "WHY?!"
msgstr "¿¡POR QUÉ!?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4605
msgid ""
"<i>(metallic voice) You are a disgrace to your sad excuse of a civilization!"
"</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>(voz metálica) ¡Eres una vergüenza para tu triste excusa de civilización!"
"</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4611
msgid "Stop it... please... Zhangor is attempting to control you..."
msgstr "Detente... por favor... Zhangor está intentando controlarte..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4620
msgid "<i>(metallic voice) Nobody can control me!</i>"
msgstr "<i>(voz metálica) ¡Nadie puede controlarme!</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4629
msgid "... please..."
msgstr "... por favor..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4637
msgid "... I know you—"
msgstr "... te conozco—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4646
msgid "... I know you loved Argan too."
msgstr "... sé que también amabas a Argan."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4661
msgid ""
"<i>(metallic voice) ... He wanted you to find me... and guide me... didn’t "
"he...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>(voz metálica) ... Él quería que me encontraras... y me guiaras... ¿no es "
"así?</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4671
msgid "... You... you are not me. Why am I crying?"
msgstr "... Tú... no eres yo. ¿Por qué estoy llorando?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4680
msgid "... Are these... my own tears?"
msgstr "... ¿Son estas... mis propias lágrimas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4685
msgid "<i>(metallic voice) ... Try to remember... that you...</i>"
msgstr "<i>(voz metálica) ... Intenta recordar... que tú...</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4694
msgid "<i>... that I was once...</i>"
msgstr "<i>... que una vez fui...</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4704
msgid "<i>(metallic voice) ... human—</i>"
msgstr "<i>(voz metálica) ... humana—</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4711
msgid "No... no..."
msgstr "No... no..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4716
msgid ""
"<i>(metallic voice) Uria demanded I kill them! It was... it was never my "
"intention... please!</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>(voz metálica) ¡Uria me ordenó matarlos! Nunca fue mi intención... ¡por "
"favor!</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4730
msgid "Zhangor is trying to make us lose control..."
msgstr "Zhangor está intentando hacernos perder el control..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#. This is part of one of Elyssa's lines from IftU scenario 22B.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4736
msgid ""
"<i>(metallic voice) Now that I have failed, there’s no purpose left for me..."
"</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>(voz metálica) Ahora que he fallado, no me queda ningún propósito...</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4744
msgid ""
"... He is trying to take us both at once... using the powers of the "
"Gatekeeper..."
msgstr ""
"... Está intentando llevarnos a los dos a la vez... usando los poderes del "
"Guardián..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4749
msgid ""
"<i>(metallic voice) Why... why did you bring me back to life... WHY?!</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>(voz metálica) ¿Por qué... por qué me trajiste de vuelta a la vida... "
"¿POR QUÉ?!</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. Callback to AtS E3S8A "Interim".
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4758
msgid "<i>... you have allowed others to distort your identity...</i>"
msgstr "<i>... has permitido que otros distorsionen tu identidad...</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. [case]
#. [section]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4763
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:2600
#: After_the_Storm/journey/recap.cfg:12
#: After_the_Storm/macros/character-defines.cfg:27
msgid "Mal Keshar"
msgstr "Mal Keshar"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4773
msgid ""
"<i>... take the Sceptre of Fire... and wield it... against our enemies...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>... toma el Cetro de Fuego... y empuñalo... contra nuestros enemigos...</"
"i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4781
msgid ""
"... He is using the powers of the Gatekeeper of Urvatha to tear into our "
"minds... I should have known that he would try to do this..."
msgstr ""
"... Está usando los poderes del Guardián de Urvatha para desgarrar nuestras "
"mentes... Debí saber que intentaría hacer esto..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4794
msgid "<i>(metallic voice) Elynia, grab my hand!</i>"
msgstr "<i>(voz metálica) ¡Elynia, agarra mi mano!</i>"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4827
msgid ""
"I could barely tell our memories and emotions apart; it was almost as though "
"our minds had merged into one.\n"
"\n"
"Never in my entire life did I imagine I would be forced by an enemy to share "
"the essence of my self with someone who was previously intent on my "
"destruction; someone who must have already peered countless times without "
"consent. And yet, knowing she had unbounded access to the totality of my "
"experiences did not bother me like it normally would.\n"
"\n"
"I did not need to communicate anything with words, and I knew she would know "
"and understand, and I knew she felt the same; for I was brought to an open "
"door, and she offered — no, <i>needed</i> me to come inside.\n"
"\n"
"And thus I found out that behind all the barriers the demoness meticulously "
"built and kept up all these years, concealed within her warped mortal frame, "
"buried deep inside the core of her usurped divinity, lay a young human girl "
"that was just as afraid of our reality as the rest of us."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4835
msgid ""
"I sensed her fear of Uria, and her fear of the many creatures she had "
"tortured and slain, both under the goddess’ command, and of her own "
"volition; her fear of Zhangor; her fear of failure; her fear of ceasing to "
"exist, tethering her to the prolonged torture that became her new unwanted "
"existence.\n"
"\n"
"I saw a life of loneliness given direction and purpose by the search for "
"knowledge; a fire mage wandering the desolate sands amidst the ruins of "
"Wesnoth; an ambush laid by agents of the so-called Guardian of Life.\n"
"\n"
"I felt the gruesome wounds carved into her very soul by those human-looking "
"monsters before Argan rescued her from their senseless cruelty; the intense "
"pain that welcomed her back into the physical realm as she was forcefully "
"remade into an artificial god; the centuries of hiding behind an invisible "
"mask to protect her fragile self from the corruption rooted deep within the "
"energy hearts of our kind; the soul-crushing agony upon finding out that the "
"one person to whom she had entrusted her humanity was gone for good."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4841
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I caught a glimpse of one her nightmares, one in which she is alone "
"wandering an endless void with nothing in sight but a tree above; a broken "
"tree, in flames.\n"
"\n"
"But it was a tree unlike any other I have never seen..."
msgstr ""
"Vi una de sus pesadillas, una en la que ella está sola vagando en un vacío "
"infinito sin nada a la vista excepto un árbol arriba; un árbol roto, en "
"llamas.\n"
"\n"
"Pero era un árbol diferente a cualquier otro que haya visto..."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. Callback to AtS E1S9.3 "The Triad, part 3".
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4853
msgid "<i>Don’t you see? We aren’t that different after all.</i>"
msgstr "<i>¿No lo ves? Después de todo, no somos tan diferentes.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#. Callback to AtS E3S8C "Breakdown".
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4913
msgid "Why... did you not kill me?"
msgstr "¿Por qué... no me mataste?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4922
msgid "Because..."
msgstr "Porque..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4931
msgid "Argan asked me to help you."
msgstr "Argan me pidió que te ayudara."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4938
msgid ""
"I could restrain myself no longer. With tears in my eyes I laughed "
"maniacally like I never had before."
msgstr ""
"Ya no podía contenerme. Con lágrimas en los ojos reí maníacamente como nunca "
"antes."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4940
msgid "Was that my own emotion, or Elyssa’s? Did it actually matter?"
msgstr "¿Era esa mi propia emoción, o la de Elyssa? ¿Realmente importaba?"

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4942
msgid ""
"There was only one thing I knew for sure.\n"
"\n"
"Galas, Anlindë, and Mal Keshar woke me to save Irdya from Uria’s corrupting "
"influence. Their lives were cut short not by Elyssa, but by the broken "
"creature into which Uria turned her."
msgstr ""
"Solo había una cosa que sabía con certeza.\n"
"\n"
"Galas, Anlindë y Mal Keshar me despertaron para salvar Irdya de la "
"influencia corruptora de Uria. Sus vidas fueron truncadas no por Elyssa, "
"sino por la criatura rota en la que Uria la convirtió."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4946
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I gave Ergea a chance because that is what my friends would have done, and "
"she led me to Elyssa.\n"
"\n"
"If fate dictates we join forces in spite of our mutual enmity, then so be it."
msgstr ""
"Le di una oportunidad a Ergea porque eso es lo que mis amigos habrían hecho, "
"y ella me llevó a Elyssa.\n"
"\n"
"Si el destino dicta que unamos fuerzas a pesar de nuestro odio mutuo, que "
"así sea."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4950
msgid ""
"No-one on Irdya will ever see peace again for as long as Zhangor and Uria "
"exist.\n"
"\n"
"No matter the consequences... no matter who is at my side, I will confront "
"those two.\n"
"\n"
"Uria has to be stopped."
msgstr ""
"Nadie en Irdya volverá a ver la paz mientras Zhangor y Uria existan.\n"
"\n"
"No importan las consecuencias... no importa quién esté a mi lado, enfrentaré "
"a esos dos.\n"
"\n"
"Uria debe ser detenida."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/09_Dark_Depths.cfg:4985
msgid "... I give up. You are beyond useless."
msgstr "... Me rindo. Eres más que inútil."

