#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:436
#: After_the_Storm/lua/gui/combo_info_dialog.lua:111
msgid "Attack Combinations"
msgstr "Combinaciones de Ataque"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:460
msgid "Blood?"
msgstr "¿Sangre?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:465
msgid ""
"Yes, more blood. You might want to get used to it — there is a lot of it in "
"the place we are headed towards."
msgstr ""
"Sí, más sangre. Quizás quieras acostumbrarte — hay mucha en el lugar al que "
"nos dirigimos."

#. [event]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:469
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Elyssa can now summon <b>Fire Wraiths</b> on unoccupied tiles adjacent to "
"Elynia regardless of the distance between both."
msgstr ""
"Elyssa ahora puede invocar Espíritus de Fuego junto a Elynia sin importar la "
"distancia entre ambas."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:477
msgid ""
"If we want to have any chance of killing that bastard for good, we must "
"stick together and try to combine our powers and attacks in different ways. "
"Your aspect is undeniably affiliated to the path of Light; mine is Darkness. "
"Perhaps, even without the Union, we may be able to achieve something in some "
"form."
msgstr ""
"Si queremos tener alguna oportunidad de matar a ese bastardo para siempre, "
"debemos permanecer juntas y tratar de combinar nuestros poderes y ataques de "
"distintas formas. Tu aspecto está innegablemente afiliado al camino de la "
"Luz; el mío es la Oscuridad. Quizás, incluso sin la Unión, podamos lograr "
"algo de alguna manera."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:482
msgid "That is why you wanted me by your side, right?"
msgstr "Por eso querías que estuviera a tu lado, ¿verdad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#. "Us" = Argan and Elyssa.
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:488
msgid "Yes. It is my hope that you... will not let us down."
msgstr "Sí. Espero que tú... no nos decepciones."

#. [transient_message]
#: After_the_Storm/episode3/scenarios/10_Blood.cfg:493
msgid ""
"Right click on the map and choose <b>Attack Combinations</b> for information "
"on the possible attack combinations you can use and their effects."
msgstr ""
"Haz clic derecho en el mapa y elige <b>Combinaciones de Ataque</b> para "
"información sobre las posibles combinaciones de ataque que puedes usar y sus "
"efectos."

