"This unit’s resistances to non-arcane damage are increased to 10% or (if "
"already 10% or higher) tripled up to a maximum of 60%, when defending on "
"water, reef, or swamp terrain. It also regenerates 8 HP at the start of "
"every turn when positioned on those terrains, but it will not remove poison "
"from itself."
