msgstr "Este es el árbol de unidades para la campaña “Después de la Tormenta”."

#. [unit_type]: id=Verlissh Control Spire, race=verlissh
#: After_the_Storm/units/alien-verlissh/Control_Spire.cfg:10
msgid "Control Spire"
msgstr "Aguja de Control"

#. [unit_type]: id=Verlissh Control Spire, race=verlissh
#: After_the_Storm/units/alien-verlissh/Control_Spire.cfg:60
msgid "Nobody has ever seen anything like this before."
msgstr "Nadie ha visto algo semejante antes."

#. [unit_type]: id=Errant Executor, race=demon
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Fighter_Errant_Executor.cfg:5
msgid "Errant Executor"
msgstr "Ejecutor Errante"

#. [unit_type]: id=Errant Executor, race=demon
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Fighter_Errant_Executor.cfg:30
msgid ""
"Only the mightiest demons are allowed to serve Uria as her greatest vassals "
"and governors of the various peoples of Inferno. After the fall of the Chaos "
"Emperor, rumors of the presence of these figures of legend on Irdya abound "
"and instill great fear among the ill-equipped armies of the northern lands."
msgstr ""
"Solo los demonios más poderosos tienen permitido servir a Uria como sus "
"mayores vasallos y gobernadores de los diversos pueblos del Infierno. Tras "
"la caída del Emperador del Caos, los rumores sobre la presencia de estas "
"figuras legendarias en Irdya abundan y generan gran temor entre los "
"ejércitos mal equipados de las tierras del norte."

#. [attack]: type=blade
#. [attack]: type=pierce
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Fighter_Errant_Executor.cfg:35
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Fighter_Errant_Executor.cfg:44
msgid "battle axe"
msgstr "hacha de batalla"

#. [attack]: type=cold
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Fighter_Errant_Executor.cfg:53
msgid "infernal tempest"
msgstr "tempestad infernal"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Messenger, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Fighter_Messenger.cfg:6
msgid "female^Demoness Messenger"
msgstr "Mensajera demoníaca"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Messenger, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Fighter_Messenger.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Demons without any remarkable fighting skills who survive to adulthood are "
"often employed for more menial tasks. In spite of their condition as slaves "
"of their lords, messengers who can endure all kinds of hazards and serve "
"with unconditional devotion—even if that may require taking their own lives—"
"are a valuable resource in times of war when communication by magic means "
"may fail or be intercepted by the enemy."
msgstr ""
"Los demonios sin habilidades de combate destacables que sobreviven hasta la "
"edad adulta suelen ser empleados en tareas más serviles. A pesar de su "
"condición de esclavos de sus señores, los mensajeros que pueden soportar "
"todo tipo de peligros y servir con devoción incondicional —aunque ello pueda "
"requerir quitarse la propia vida— son un recurso valioso en tiempos de "
"guerra cuando la comunicación mágica puede fallar o ser interceptada por el "
"enemigo."

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Spelldancer, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Fighter_Spelldancer.cfg:6
msgid "female^Demoness Spelldancer"
msgstr "Hechicera danzante demoníaca"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Spelldancer, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Fighter_Spelldancer.cfg:26
msgid ""
"It is very rare for this demon species at large to dabble in the intricacies "
"of the various types of magic, having adapted their body structure over time "
"for feats of physical strength, much in the same vein as their distant "
"cousins, the Valdemons. The endless wars waged in their homeworld during the "
"Era of Strife have also contributed to a general scarcity of knowledge and "
"those capable of spreading it.\n"
"\n"
"In spite—or perhaps because—of this, the few individuals who attain control "
"of those otherworldly powers not naturally available to them are respected "
"by their people as the great spell-masters they strive to be."
msgstr ""
"Es muy raro que esta especie demoníaca en general se aventure en las "
"complejidades de los distintos tipos de magia, habiendo adaptado su "
"estructura corporal con el tiempo para hazañas de fuerza física, al igual "
"que sus lejanos primos, los valdemonios. Las guerras interminables libradas "
"en su mundo natal durante la Era de los Conflictos también han contribuido a "
"una escasez general de conocimiento y de aquellos capaces de difundirlo.\n"
"\n"
"A pesar de ello —o quizás precisamente por ello—, los pocos individuos que "
"consiguen dominar esos poderes de otro mundo no disponibles de forma natural "
"son respetados por su pueblo como grandes maestros de la hechicería que "
"aspiran a ser."

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Fighter_Spelldancer.cfg:33
msgid "blazing grasp"
msgstr "agarre llameante"

#. [unit_type]: id=Gatekeeper, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Gatekeeper.cfg:6
msgid "female^Gatekeeper"
msgstr "Guardián de la Puerta"

#. [unit_type]: id=Gatekeeper, race=demon, gender=female
#. [unit_type]: id=Guardian of Life Uria, race=demon, gender=female
#. [unit_type]: id=Guardian of Darkness Anya, race=faerie, gender=female
#. [unit_type]: id=Guardian of Earth Aradellys, race=faerie, gender=female
#. [unit_type]: id=Guardian of Earth Elynia, race=faerie, gender=female
#. [unit_type]: id=Boss Shaxthal Warlord Elyssa
#. [unit_type]: id=Guardian of Darkness Elyssa, race=shaxthal, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Gatekeeper.cfg:52
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Guardian_of_Life_Uria.cfg:32
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Dark_Nightshade_Fire_F.cfg:37
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Guardian_of_Earth_Aradellys.cfg:26
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Sylvan_Warden_F.cfg:33
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Warlord_Elyssa_Boss.cfg:28
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Warlord_Elyssa_F.cfg:35
msgid ""
"There is no information available about this class of beings at this time."
msgstr ""
"No hay información disponible sobre esta clase de seres en este momento."

#. [unit_type]: id=Guardian of Life Uria, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Guardian_of_Life_Uria.cfg:6
msgid "female^Guardian of Life"
msgstr "Guardiana de la Vida"

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Guardian_of_Life_Uria.cfg:39
msgid "psychic blast"
msgstr "explosión psíquica"

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Guardian_of_Life_Uria.cfg:51
msgid "breath of thanatos"
msgstr "aliento de Thánatos"

#. [unit_type]: id=Lumeril Glyph Mistress, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Lumeril_Glyph_Mistress.cfg:6
msgid "female^Lumeril Glyph Mistress"
msgstr "Ama de Glifos Lumeril"

#. [unit_type]: id=Lumeril Glyph Mistress, race=demon, gender=female
#. 'Awesome' is used here in the older classical sense of the quality of "inspiring awe".
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Lumeril_Glyph_Mistress.cfg:26
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By combining a meticulous research of history and tradition with an arduous "
"training in the arcane arts, this demon sorceress has attained an unrivaled "
"mastery of the path of Light and the awesome powers it confers upon the "
"devout. Her ability to summon ancient records to shield herself from the "
"nefarious influence of the unenlightened makes her virtually invincible as a "
"foe."
msgstr ""
"Al combinar una meticulosa investigación de la historia y la tradición con "
"un arduo entrenamiento en las artes arcanas, esta hechicera demoníaca ha "
"alcanzado una maestría sin igual en el camino de la Luz y los asombrosos "
"poderes que otorga a los devotos. Su habilidad para invocar los registros de "
"los antiguos para protegerse de la nefasta influencia de los ignorantes la "
"hace prácticamente invencible como enemiga."

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Lumeril_Glyph_Mistress.cfg:32
msgid "hand of agathar"
msgstr "mano de Agathar"

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Lumeril_Glyph_Mistress.cfg:44
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Lumeril_Guard.cfg:33
msgid "lumeril star"
msgstr "estrella lumeril"

#. [unit_type]: id=Lumeril Guard, race=demon
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Lumeril_Guard.cfg:6
msgid "Lumeril Guard"
msgstr "Guardia Lumeril"

#. [unit_type]: id=Lumeril Guard, race=demon
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Lumeril_Guard.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Members of an ancestral race of warriors of light, these demons now serve as "
"Uria’s elite guards and executioners, imparting her justice with their sharp "
"silver axes."
msgstr ""
"Miembros de una raza ancestral de guerreros de la luz, estos demonios ahora "
"sirven como los guardias de élite y verdugos de Uria, impartiendo su "
"justicia con sus afiladas hachas de plata."

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Shapeshifter, race=demon, gender=male,female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Shapeshifter.cfg:6
msgid "Demon Shapeshifter"
msgstr "Cambiante demoníaco"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Shapeshifter, race=demon, gender=male,female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Shapeshifter.cfg:24
msgid ""
"The exceedingly rare Shapeshifters, as their name implies, have the ability "
"to take on the shape of other creatures, and even mimic their powers to a "
"limited extent. On their own, they are easily mistaken for elves or humans. "
"Although they rarely use their powers when not called for, they have "
"developed a peculiar custom of hiding behind personalized, often elaborate "
"masks.\n"
"\n"
"Once known for their remarkably peaceful nature, it was this trait that led "
"to their near-extinction in Inferno following Uria’s rise to power. More "
"powerful and bellicose demon lords have slaughtered or enslaved their kind "
"over time, occasionally using them as specialized assassins. Their "
"androgynous appearance, flexible attributes, and unusual resistance to "
"physical damage have allowed them to survive by blending with other lifeforms"
"—rumored to even include Irdyan creatures, civilized or otherwise—at the "
"cost of bloodline purity and their continuance as a species.\n"
"\n"
"Before their downfall, they had rarely been governed by any demon lords of "
"their own, Zhangor being one of the last successful tyrants to take over. It "
"is currently unclear whether the shapeshifters seen fighting in Irdya after "
"the destruction of the Wesmere hive follow a specific demon lord."
msgstr ""
"Los extremadamente raros Cambiantes, como indica su nombre, poseen la "
"capacidad de adoptar la forma de otras criaturas e incluso imitar sus "
"poderes hasta cierto punto. Por sí solos, pueden confundirse fácilmente con "
"elfos o humanos. Aunque rara vez usan sus poderes sin necesidad, han "
"desarrollado la costumbre peculiar de ocultarse tras máscaras personalizadas "
"y a menudo elaboradas.\n"
"\n"
"Antes conocidos por su naturaleza notablemente pacífica, esta misma cualidad "
"provocó su casi extinción en el Infierno tras el ascenso de Uria al poder. "
"Con el tiempo, demonios más poderosos y belicosos los han masacrado o "
"esclavizado, usándolos ocasionalmente como asesinos especializados. Su "
"apariencia andrógina, atributos flexibles y resistencia inusual al daño "
"físico les han permitido sobrevivir mezclándose con otras formas de vida, se "
"rumorea que incluso con criaturas irdyanas civilizadas o no, a costa de la "
"pureza de su linaje y la continuidad de su especie.\n"
"\n"
"Antes de su caída, rara vez habían estado gobernados por señores demoníacos "
"propios, siendo Zhangor uno de los últimos tiranos exitosos en tomar el "
"control. Actualmente no está claro si los cambiantes vistos combatiendo en "
"Irdya tras la destrucción de la colmena de Wesmere siguen a un demonio en "
"particular."

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Shapeshifter.cfg:45
msgid "curse"
msgstr "maldición"

#. [female]: gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Shapeshifter.cfg:158
msgid "female^Demoness Shapeshifter"
msgstr "Cambiante demoníaca"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Hellbent Tide, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Hellbent_Tide.cfg:6
msgid "female^Demoness Hellbent Tide"
msgstr "Demonia Marea Infernal"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Hellbent Tide, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Hellbent_Tide.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Formerly one of Uria’s closest vassals, the Demon Lord of the Storms is "
"perhaps the youngest demoness besides the undisputed ruler of Inferno "
"herself to rise to power. Descendant of the Great Followers of the Wind, her "
"mastery of this element is unrivaled.\n"
"\n"
"Her rule over the stormkind people is unusual in that she cares for the well-"
"being of their already sparse population. This often requires coping with "
"Uria’s sadistic nature and complying with her commands in order to minimize "
"casualties and secure her trust for less evident purposes."
msgstr ""
"Antaño una de las vasallas más cercanas de Uria, la Señora Demonio de las "
"Tormentas es quizás la demonio más joven, además de la propia gobernante "
"indiscutida del Infierno, en alcanzar el poder. Descendiente de los Grandes "
"Seguidores del Viento, su dominio de este elemento es inigualable.\n"
"\n"
"Su gobierno sobre el pueblo de las tormentas es inusual, ya que se preocupa "
"por el bienestar de su población, ya de por sí escasa. Esto a menudo "
"requiere lidiar con la naturaleza sádica de Uria y cumplir sus órdenes para "
"minimizar las bajas y asegurar su confianza para propósitos menos evidentes."

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Hellbent_Tide.cfg:36
msgid "wind strike"
msgstr "Golpe de viento"

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Hellbent_Tide.cfg:45
msgid "hellbent tide"
msgstr "marea infernal"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Slashing Gale, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Slashing_Gale.cfg:6
msgid "female^Demoness Slashing Gale"
msgstr "Demonio Vendaval Cortante"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Slashing Gale, race=demon, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Slashing_Gale.cfg:29
msgid ""
"Armed with deadly metal claws and the remarkable flight skills of their "
"stormkind brethren, the Storm Sisters are hired assassins working for the "
"ranks of the Fist of Uria, bearing the mask of his order. Their experience "
"with glamour magic—though limited as it is—allows them to sport wings much "
"like those often acquired by real faerie creatures. In spite of their vain "
"nature, they are dangerously competent as a group — it would take a great "
"degree of foolishness to underestimate their prowess in combat, and even "
"more to expect them to play fair."
msgstr ""
"Armadas con garras metálicas mortales y las notables habilidades de vuelo de "
"sus hermanos de las tormentas, las Hermanas de la Tormenta son asesinas a "
"sueldo que trabajan para las filas del Puño de Uria, portando la máscara de "
"su orden. Su experiencia con la magia de glamour —aunque limitada— les "
"permite lucir alas similares a las que a menudo adquieren las criaturas "
"feéricas reales. A pesar de su naturaleza vanidosa, son peligrosamente "
"competentes como grupo: subestimar su destreza en combate requeriría una "
"gran dosis de imprudencia, y aún más esperar que jueguen limpio."

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Slashing_Gale.cfg:47
msgid "wind crush"
msgstr "aplastamiento de viento"

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Slashing_Gale.cfg:59
msgid "heart sight"
msgstr "visión del corazón"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Stormtide, race=demon, gender=male,female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Stormtide.cfg:6
msgid "Demon Stormtide"
msgstr "Demonio Marea de Tormenta"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Stormtide, race=demon, gender=male,female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Stormtide.cfg:28
msgid ""
"On occasion, these aerial demons have been mistaken for faeries and undead "
"spirits of demonkind because of their unusual wings and apparent lack of "
"legs. Formerly unheard of, they can summon strong winds and create great "
"storms for laying waste to forests and villages. When combined with their "
"race’s inherent affinity with fire, the effects can be particularly "
"disastrous."
msgstr ""
"En ocasiones, estos demonios aéreos han sido confundidos con hadas y "
"espíritus no muertos de la especie demoníaca debido a sus alas inusuales y "
"la aparente falta de piernas. Antes desconocidos, pueden invocar fuertes "
"vientos y crear grandes tormentas para devastar bosques y aldeas. Cuando se "
"combina con la afinidad inherente de su raza con el fuego, los efectos "
"pueden ser particularmente desastrosos."

#. [attack]: type=cold
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Stormtide.cfg:42
msgid "stormtide"
msgstr "marea de tormenta"

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Stormtide.cfg:50
msgid "fire storm"
msgstr "tormenta de fuego"

#. [female]: gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/Storm_Stormtide.cfg:127
msgid "female^Demoness Stormtide"
msgstr "Demonia Marea de Tormenta"

#. [unit_type]: id=Blood Core, race=demon, description={_BLOOD_GATEKEEPER_DESCRIPTION}
#. [unit_type]: id=Angel of Blood, race=shaxthal, description={_BLOOD_GATEKEEPER_DESCRIPTION}
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/angel-of-blood/01_blood_core.cfg:5
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/angel-of-blood/10_angel.cfg:13
