#. [variation]
#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/angel-of-blood/30_nightmare.cfg:433
msgid "Crimson Tide"
msgstr "Marea Carmesí"

#: After_the_Storm/units/demons/angel-of-blood/_initial.cfg:8
msgid ""
"While the history of how the War of Wesmere came to happen is only known to "
"a few elves in the present day, there are even fewer people who know about "
"Zhangor’s true origins. The few records left of his rule in Urvatha speak of "
"his achievements as an implacable warlord who led his people into a "
"slaughter of unprecedented proportions, sealing the fate of shapeshifters "
"for the rest of eternity. Some sources claim that it was this — his most "
"shameful defeat — that led him to take the power of the mythical sentinel "
"between worlds and seek to amplify it using the souls of Irdya’s people as "
"sacrifice."
msgstr ""
"Si bien la historia de cómo ocurrió la Guerra de Wesmere solo es conocida "
"por unos pocos elfos en la actualidad, hay aún menos personas que conocen "
"los verdaderos orígenes de Zhangor. Los pocos registros que quedan de su "
"mandato en Urvatha hablan de sus logros como un señor de la guerra "
"implacable que condujo a su pueblo a una masacre de proporciones sin "
"precedentes, sellando el destino de los cambiaformas por toda la eternidad. "
"Algunas fuentes afirman que fue esta — su derrota más vergonzosa — la que lo "
"llevó a tomar el poder del mítico centinela entre mundos y buscar "
"amplificarlo usando las almas del pueblo de Irdya como sacrificio."

#. [female]: gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-quenoth/Archer_Kyara.cfg:8
msgid "female^Quenoth Archer"
msgstr "Arquera de Quenoth"

#. [female]: gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-quenoth/Marskman_Kyara.cfg:8
msgid "female^Quenoth Marskman"
msgstr "Tiradora de Quenoth"

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Acolyte, race=elf, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Acolyte.cfg:5
msgid "female^Elvish Acolyte"
msgstr "Acólita Elfa"

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Acolyte, race=elf, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Acolyte.cfg:21
msgid ""
"A trio of elves originally working as helpers for the mysterious order of "
"the Sylphs discovered by chance new applications for elemental powers. "
"Although they documented their findings for their peers, their powers and "
"skill remained unmatched for their lifetime.\n"
"\n"
"The legend lived on throughout eons, and the reflourishing elves of the "
"Valley of Elynia have found a new need for offensive magic to assert their "
"control over their lands. The ultimate goal of the so-called “acolytes” is "
"to master the fierce power of the elements and resurrect the legend of the "
"Elemental Three."
msgstr ""
"Un trío de elfos que originalmente trabajaban como ayudantes de la "
"misteriosa orden de los Sílfides descubrió por casualidad nuevas "
"aplicaciones para los poderes elementales. Aunque documentaron sus hallazgos "
"para sus pares, sus poderes y habilidades permanecieron sin igual durante su "
"vida.\n"
"\n"
"La leyenda perduró a lo largo de los eones, y los elfos renacidos en el "
"Valle de Elynia han encontrado una nueva necesidad de magia ofensiva para "
"afirmar su control sobre sus tierras. El objetivo final de los llamados "
"“acólitos” es dominar el feroz poder de los elementos y resucitar la leyenda "
"de los Tres Elementales."

#. [unit_type]: id=Anlinde Elvish Avatar, race=elf, gender=female, description=
#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Avatar, race=elf, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Anlinde_Avatar.cfg:6
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Avatar.cfg:5
msgid "female^Elvish Avatar"
msgstr "Avatar Elfa"

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Anlinde_Avatar.cfg:58
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Avatar.cfg:58
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Sylvan_Faerie_Avatar.cfg:55
msgid "ethereal storm"
msgstr "tormenta etérea"

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Ascetic, race=elf, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Ascetic.cfg:5
msgid "female^Elvish Ascetic"
msgstr "Elfa Asceta"

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Ascetic, race=elf, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Ascetic.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Some elves have studied varieties of magic better suited for offensive "
"purposes. Whence their knowledge and mastery of such arts came is not known, "
"and they do not reveal their secrets. All that is known of their training is "
"that they may spend a long time alone in the wilderness, not to appear for "
"years, or in extreme cases, centuries.\n"
"\n"
"For these ascetics, knowledge may be a curse at times, as their people tend "
"to expect from them more that what they can offer without violating their "
"own principles. Nonetheless, they may use their mastery of magic to lend a "
"hand to fate--or to twist it. They possess good knowledge of both offensive "
"and defensive spells. They often also have basic notions of medicine and can "
"cure other creatures from the effects of poison."
msgstr ""
"Algunos elfos han estudiado variedades de magia más adecuadas para fines "
"ofensivos. No se sabe de dónde proviene su conocimiento y dominio de tales "
"artes, y ellos no revelan sus secretos. Todo lo que se sabe de su "
"entrenamiento es que pueden pasar mucho tiempo solos en la naturaleza, sin "
"aparecer durante años, o en casos extremos, siglos.\n"
"\n"
"Para estas ascetas, el conocimiento puede ser a veces una maldición, ya que "
"su pueblo suele esperar de ellos más de lo que pueden ofrecer sin violar sus "
"propios principios. No obstante, pueden usar su dominio de la magia para "
"ayudar al destino —o para torcerlo. Poseen buen conocimiento tanto de "
"hechizos ofensivos como defensivos. A menudo también tienen nociones básicas "
"de medicina y pueden curar a otras criaturas de los efectos del veneno."

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Ascetic.cfg:52
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Mystic.cfg:52
msgid "ethereal zephyr"
msgstr "céfiro etéreo"

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Avatar, race=elf, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Avatar.cfg:23
msgid ""
"The great power attained by some mystics is often dreaded by the enemies of "
"elvenkind. After a long path of learning — often lasting their entire "
"lifetime — these avatars of wind and storm master the natural elements, and "
"are capable of commanding them at their will.\n"
"\n"
"Needless to say, these skills could be used to destroy the elvish "
"civilization. Avatars are thus highly respected, often feared sages of their "
"people. Power is both a gift and a curse — understanding and bearing this "
"great responsibility is perhaps one of the last challenges that must be "
"mastered by these mystics."
msgstr ""
"El gran poder alcanzado por algunos místicos es a menudo temido por los "
"enemigos de los elfos. Después de un largo camino de aprendizaje —que a "
"menudo dura toda su vida— estos avatares del viento y la tormenta dominan "
"los elementos naturales, y son capaces de comandarlos a voluntad.\n"
"\n"
"Ni qué decir tiene que estas habilidades podrían usarse para destruir la "
"civilización élfica. Por ello, los avatares son sabios muy respetados y "
"temidos por su pueblo. El poder es tanto un don como una maldición —"
"comprender y soportar esta gran responsabilidad es quizás uno de los últimos "
"desafíos que deben dominar estos místicos."

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Mystic, race=elf, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Mystic.cfg:5
msgid "female^Elvish Mystic"
msgstr "Elfa Mística"

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Mystic, race=elf, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Mystic.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Experienced mystics are of great value in the new Elvish society. Their "
"great knowledge of history and magic, tolerance, and fair judgement is what "
"is sought for in a leader or advisor. In times of need, they are in charge "
"of assisting their lords with worthy advice or even support on the "
"battlefield. But they have not finished learning yet, and still wander about "
"the world, seeking new questions to answer."
msgstr ""
"Las místicas experimentadas son de gran valor en la nueva sociedad élfica. "
"Su vasto conocimiento de la historia y la magia, su tolerancia y su juicio "
"justo son cualidades buscadas en un líder o consejero. En tiempos de "
"necesidad, asisten a sus señores con consejos valiosos o incluso apoyo en el "
"campo de batalla. Pero aún no han terminado de aprender y continúan vagando "
"por el mundo en busca de nuevas preguntas que responder."

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Spellbinder, race=elf, gender=female, description=
#: After_the_Storm/units/elves-wood/Spellbinder.cfg:6
msgid "female^Elvish Spellbinder"
msgstr "Hechicera elfa"

#. [unit_type]: id=Dusk Faerie, race=faerie, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Dark_Dusk_Faerie.cfg:6
msgid "female^Dusk Faerie"
msgstr "hada del crepúsculo"

#. [unit_type]: id=Dusk Faerie, race=faerie, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Dark_Dusk_Faerie.cfg:32
msgid ""
"In the largest and densest forests of Irdya it is possible to find some of "
"the most elusive and fascinating surface creatures, such as woses and forest "
"faeries. However, a particular kind of faerie beings has always remained "
"relatively unknown by outsiders and denizens of the forests alike.\n"
"\n"
"The mysterious faeries of the darkness hide away from any form of "
"civilization, dwelling in some of the most dangerous locations. Their "
"rumored natural mastery of the shadows often leads the uneducated to liken "
"them to necromancers, even though there is no recorded evidence of any "
"involvement of their kind with such magic."
msgstr ""
"En los bosques más grandes y densos de Irdya es posible encontrar algunas de "
"las criaturas superficiales más esquivas y fascinantes, como los woses y las "
"hadas del bosque. Sin embargo, un tipo particular de seres feéricos siempre "
"ha permanecido relativamente desconocido tanto para forasteros como para los "
"propios habitantes de los bosques.\n"
"\n"
"Las misteriosas hadas de la oscuridad se ocultan de cualquier forma de "
"civilización, habitando en algunos de los lugares más peligrosos. Su "
"supuesta maestría natural sobre las sombras a menudo lleva a los ignorantes "
"a compararlas con nigromantes, aunque no existe evidencia registrada de que "
"su especie se relacione con dicha magia."

#. [unit_type]: id=Night Nymph, race=faerie, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Dark_Night_Nymph.cfg:6
msgid "female^Night Nymph"
msgstr "ninfa nocturna"

#. [unit_type]: id=Night Nymph, race=faerie, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Dark_Night_Nymph.cfg:32
msgid ""
"It is said that the dark faeries’ secluded lives in hazardous environments "
"has led them to lose any kind of empathy towards those who are not of their "
"kind. Many fables revolve around men who were lured into following these "
"beautiful temptresses to their homes, never to be seen ever again."
msgstr ""
"Se dice que la vida solitaria de las hadas oscuras en entornos peligrosos "
"las ha llevado a perder cualquier atisbo de empatía hacia quienes no son de "
"su especie. Muchas fábulas giran en torno a hombres que fueron seducidos por "
"estas bellas tentadoras para seguirlas hasta sus hogares, y jamás se los "
"volvió a ver."

#. [attack]: type=cold
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Dark_Night_Nymph.cfg:53
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Dark_Nightshade_Fire.cfg:61
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Dark_Nightshade_Fire_F.cfg:63
msgid "forest chill"
msgstr "escalofrío del bosque"

#. [unit_type]: id=Nightshade Fire, race=faerie, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Dark_Nightshade_Fire.cfg:6
msgid "female^Nightshade Fire"
msgstr "Fuego de Sombra Nocturna"

#. [unit_type]: id=Nightshade Fire, race=faerie, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Dark_Nightshade_Fire.cfg:37
msgid ""
"Many stories tell of unfortunate young men who wandered into the deep forest "
"at night, and by chance laid their eyes upon a beautiful night nymph. "
"Although a few were sufficiently prudent to immediately flee back to their "
"brightly-lit homes instead of approaching the otherworldly maiden, they were "
"often confronted and abducted in their way out.\n"
"\n"
"Combined with their remarkable mastery of the arcane flame of darkness, the "
"rumored ability of these faeries to teleport between distant places at will "
"would turn them into fearsome enemies — that is, if they were ever to "
"abandon their natural environment."
msgstr ""
"Muchas historias cuentan sobre desafortunados jóvenes que se adentraron en "
"el bosque profundo por la noche y, por casualidad, posaron sus ojos en una "
"hermosa ninfa nocturna. Aunque unos pocos fueron lo suficientemente "
"prudentes como para huir de inmediato a sus hogares bien iluminados en lugar "
"de acercarse a la doncella de otro mundo, a menudo fueron confrontados y "
"secuestrados en su huida.\n"
"\n"
"Combinada con su extraordinario dominio de la llama arcana de la oscuridad, "
"la rumoreada capacidad de estas hadas para teletransportarse entre lugares "
"distantes las convertiría en enemigas temibles… si alguna vez abandonaran su "
"entorno natural."

#. [unit_type]: id=Guardian of Darkness Anya, race=faerie, gender=female
#. [unit_type]: id=Boss Shaxthal Warlord Elyssa
#. [unit_type]: id=Guardian of Darkness Elyssa, race=shaxthal, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Dark_Nightshade_Fire_F.cfg:6
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Warlord_Elyssa_Boss.cfg:23
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Warlord_Elyssa_F.cfg:6
msgid "female^Guardian of Darkness"
msgstr "Guardiana de la Oscuridad"

#. [unit_type]: id=Guardian of Earth Aradellys, race=faerie, gender=female
#. [unit_type]: id=Guardian of Earth Elynia, race=faerie, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Guardian_of_Earth_Aradellys.cfg:6
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Sylvan_Warden_F.cfg:7
msgid "female^Guardian of Earth"
msgstr "Guardiana de la Tierra"

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Guardian_of_Earth_Aradellys.cfg:58
msgid "faerieborn blaze"
msgstr "llamarada de las hadas"

#. [unit_type]: id=Naiad, race=faerie, gender=female
#. [unit_type]: id=Epilogue Cutscene Controller, race=invisible_dummy_race, description=, gender=female, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Naiad.cfg:6
#: After_the_Storm/units/fake/Epilogue_Cutscene_Controller.cfg:83
msgid "female^Naiad"
msgstr "Náyade"

#. [unit_type]: id=Naiad, race=faerie, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Naiad.cfg:27
msgid ""
"While faeries of the deep forest, hamadryads and oreads are best known for "
"how little anyone knows about them, the elusive nature of the water faeries "
"known as “naiads” manages to surpass them all by a large margin.\n"
"\n"
"Even though they are known to share their natural habitat with other sapient "
"river and sea creatures such as merfolk and naga, those have very little "
"additional information to offer. It is thought that naiads possess some form "
"of shapeshifting that enables them to blend into the water and remain "
"undetected by all except those well versed in faerie magic.\n"
"\n"
"The exceedingly few recorded instances of certain naiad encounters suggest "
"that they are solitary nymphs that never make contact with anyone — even "
"faeries — except as messengers of nature in times when the very existence of "
"Irdya is at stake, and even then they leave as suddenly as they appear "
"without ever taking sides in armed conflicts. With that said, some have "
"suggested that they may occasionally take matters into their own hands by "
"causing otherwise unexplained weather occurrences near bodies of water, "
"especially in the open ocean."
msgstr ""
"Aunque las hadas del bosque profundo, las hamadríades y las oréades son "
"famosas por el misterio que las rodea, la naturaleza esquiva de las hadas "
"acuáticas conocidas como «náyades» supera con creces a todas las demás.\n"
"\n"
"Aunque se sabe que comparten su hábitat natural con otras criaturas "
"conscientes de ríos y mares, como las sirenas y los nagas, estas poco pueden "
"aportar sobre ellas. Se cree que las náyades poseen alguna forma de cambio "
"de forma que les permite fundirse con el agua y permanecer indetectables "
"salvo para quienes dominan la magia feérica.\n"
"\n"
"Los poquísimos casos documentados de encuentros con náyades sugieren que son "
"ninfas solitarias que nunca contactan con nadie —ni siquiera con otras hadas"
"— salvo como mensajeras de la naturaleza en épocas en que la misma "
"existencia de Irdya está en juego. Incluso entonces, desaparecen tan "
"repentinamente como aparecen, sin tomar partido en los conflictos armados. "
"Dicho esto, algunos sugieren que a veces toman cartas en el asunto "
"provocando fenómenos meteorológicos inexplicables cerca de masas de agua, "
"especialmente en mar abierto."

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Naiad.cfg:54
msgid "naia touch"
msgstr "toque de náyade"

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Naiad.cfg:67
msgid "tidal wave"
msgstr "ola gigante"

#. [unit_type]: id=Faerie Avatar, race=faerie, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Sylvan_Faerie_Avatar.cfg:6
msgid "female^Faerie Avatar"
msgstr "avatar feérica"

#. [unit_type]: id=Faerie Avatar, race=faerie, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Sylvan_Faerie_Avatar.cfg:23
msgid ""
"This faerie woman of unknown origins is bent on manipulating elvenkind to do "
"Uria’s bidding by impersonating the true Lady of Light and instilling strife "
"among her kind. Not much else is known about her at this time."
msgstr ""
"Esta mujer feérica de orígenes desconocidos está empeñada en manipular al "
"pueblo élfico para cumplir la voluntad de Uria, haciéndose pasar por la "
"verdadera Dama de la Luz y sembrando la discordia entre los suyos. No se "
"sabe mucho más sobre ella en este momento."

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Sylvan_Faerie_Avatar.cfg:31
msgid "arcane touch"
msgstr "toque arcano"

#. [unit_type]: id=Sylvan Warden, race=faerie, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Sylvan_Warden.cfg:6
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Sylvan_Warden_E3.cfg:7
msgid "female^Sylvan Warden"
msgstr "guardiana silvana"

#. [unit_type]: id=Sylvan Warden, race=faerie, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Sylvan_Warden.cfg:26
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Sylvan_Warden_E3.cfg:26
msgid ""
"Elynia’s mastery of faerie magic remains unrivaled on Irdya, even without "
"the legendary power of the Union of Light and Darkness. Always dutiful as "
"the sworn protector of elvenkind and the forests of Irdya, she will do "
"anything to stop those who may threaten her people or upset the delicate "
"balance of nature."
msgstr ""
"La maestría de Elynia sobre la magia feérica sigue siendo inigualable en "
"Irdya, incluso sin el legendario poder de la Unión de la Luz y la Oscuridad. "
"Siempre fiel a su deber como protectora jurada del pueblo élfico y los "
"bosques de Irdya, hará lo que sea necesario para detener a quienes amenacen "
"a su gente o perturben el delicado equilibrio de la naturaleza."

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Sylvan_Warden.cfg:66
#: After_the_Storm/units/faeries/Sylvan_Warden_E3.cfg:69
msgid "mystic fire"
msgstr "fuego místico"

