msgid "Domain Guard"
msgstr "Guardia del Dominio"

#. [unit_type]: id=Epilogue Cutscene Controller, race=invisible_dummy_race, description=, gender=female, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/fake/Epilogue_Cutscene_Controller.cfg:57
msgid "female^Eventide Dancer"
msgstr "Bailarina del Crepúsculo"

#. [unit_type]: id=Aragwaith Seer, race=aragwaith, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Aragwaith_Seer.cfg:6
msgid "female^Seer"
msgstr "Vidente"

#. [unit_type]: id=Aragwaith Seer, race=aragwaith, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Aragwaith_Seer.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Very few humans are born with a gift that allows them to see the world "
"beyond time and space. These rare individuals are usually not skilled in "
"combat, but their special ability makes them highly respected amongst other "
"ranks of magi in civilized countries."
msgstr ""
"Son muy pocos los humanos que nacen con el don de ver el mundo más allá del "
"tiempo y el espacio. Estos raros individuos suelen carecer de habilidad en "
"combate, pero su talento especial los hace altamente respetados entre los "
"demás rangos de magos en los países civilizados."

#. [unit_type]: id=Chaos Gunner, race=human, description=
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Chaos_Gunner.cfg:6
msgid "Chaos Gunner"
msgstr "Artillero del Caos"

#. [attack]: type=pierce
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Chaos_Gunner.cfg:34
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Chaos_Gunner_Marksman.cfg:34
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Chaos_Gunner_Sharpshooter.cfg:35
msgid "gun"
msgstr "pistola"

#. [unit_type]: id=Chaos Marksman, race=human, description=
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Chaos_Gunner_Marksman.cfg:6
msgid "Chaos Marksman"
msgstr "Tirador del Caos"

#. [unit_type]: id=Chaos Sharpshooter, race=human, description=
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Chaos_Gunner_Sharpshooter.cfg:6
msgid "Chaos Sharpshooter"
msgstr "Francotirador del Caos"

#. [unit_type]: id=Chaos Dreadcrafter, race=human
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Chaos_Invoker_Dreadcrafter.cfg:6
msgid "Chaos Dreadcrafter"
msgstr "Artesano Temible del Caos"

#. [unit_type]: id=Chaos Dreadcrafter, race=human
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Chaos_Invoker_Dreadcrafter.cfg:28
msgid ""
"The processes involved in the creation of new biomechanical weaponry, and "
"similar hybrid lifeforms—now at the helm of the very Empire—remain a mystery "
"for outsiders. It is said that a barely known order of Lorekeepers was "
"formed under Mal Zagarn’s supervision to gather the resources and knowledge "
"required to perform this duty."
msgstr ""
"Los procesos involucrados en la creación de nuevas armas biomecánicas y "
"formas de vida híbridas similares — ahora al mando del propio Imperio — "
"siguen siendo un misterio para los forasteros. Se dice que una orden apenas "
"conocida de Guardianes del Saber fue formada bajo la supervisión de Mal "
"Zagarn para reunir los recursos y conocimientos necesarios para cumplir esta "
"tarea."

#. [unit_type]: id=Civilian, race=human, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Civilian.cfg:6
msgid "female^Civilian"
msgstr "Civil"

#. [unit_type]: id=Civilian, race=human, gender=female
#. [unit_type]: id=Messenger, race=human, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Civilian.cfg:19
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Messenger.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Commoners without any kind of combat training, magic abilities or medical "
"expertise are strikingly useless on the battlefield. It would take a great "
"deal of incompetence to send one such person across the marchlands and wild "
"forests of the Far North without an adequately armed escort."
msgstr ""
"Los civiles comunes, sin ningún tipo de entrenamiento en combate, "
"habilidades mágicas o conocimientos médicos, son sorprendentemente inútiles "
"en el campo de batalla. Se necesitaría una gran incompetencia para enviar a "
"una persona así a cruzar las tierras fronterizas y los bosques salvajes del "
"Lejano Norte sin una escolta armada adecuada."

#. [unit_type]: id=Master of Darkness, race=human, description=
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Master_of_Darkness.cfg:6
msgid "Master of Darkness"
msgstr "Maestro de la Oscuridad"

#. [attack]: type=cold
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Master_of_Darkness.cfg:46
msgid "infernal chill"
msgstr "frío infernal"

#. [unit_type]: id=Messenger, race=human, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/humans/Messenger.cfg:6
msgid "female^Messenger"
msgstr "Mensajera"

#. [unit_type]: id=Ixthala Fire Dancer, race=imps
#: After_the_Storm/units/imps/Ixthala_Fire_Dancer.cfg:6
msgid "Ixthala Fire Dancer"
msgstr "Bailarín de fuego de Ixthala"

#. [unit_type]: id=Ixthala Fire Dancer, race=imps
#: After_the_Storm/units/imps/Ixthala_Fire_Dancer.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Coming from the blazing lands of fire and brimstone in Inferno to aid in the "
"invasion of Irdya, these dangerous fire demons are now said to serve one of "
"Uria’s most ruthless commanders. With their flaming swords they are intent "
"on spreading death and destruction throughout the land."
msgstr ""
"Provenientes de las ardientes tierras de fuego y azufre en el Infierno para "
"apoyar la invasión de Irdya, estos peligrosos demonios de fuego sirven ahora "
"a uno de los comandantes más despiadados de Uria. Con sus espadas llameantes "
"están decididos a esparcir muerte y destrucción por toda la tierra."

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: After_the_Storm/units/imps/Ixthala_Fire_Dancer.cfg:27
msgid "flaming sword"
msgstr "espada flamigera"

#. [unit_type]: id=Serpent Messenger, race=imps
#: After_the_Storm/units/imps/Serpent_Messenger.cfg:6
msgid "Serpent Messenger"
msgstr "Mensajero Serpiente"

#. [unit_type]: id=Serpent Messenger, race=imps
#: After_the_Storm/units/imps/Serpent_Messenger.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Legend tells of the mighty serpent god who defied Uria and was shortly "
"defeated by her. In order to set an example for other demon lords who could "
"consider defying or betraying her, his soul was sealed into stone. His "
"followers—once worshipers of the power of light—were turned to the darkness "
"and changed into wretched creatures charged with the mission of spreading "
"fear and panic to dishearten her victims.\n"
"\n"
"Regardless of the veracity of their origins, they can be quite effective "
"against lesser creatures and the weak-willed, whereas brave and experienced "
"warriors find them to be little more than a nuisance on the battlefield."
msgstr ""
"La leyenda habla del poderoso dios serpiente que desafió a Uria y fue "
"rápidamente derrotado por ella. Para dar un ejemplo a otros señores "
"demoníacos que pudieran considerar desafiarla o traicionarla, su alma fue "
"sellada en piedra. Sus seguidores —antaño adoradores del poder de la luz— "
"fueron corrompidos por la oscuridad y transformados en miserables criaturas "
"encargadas de difundir miedo y pánico para desmoralizar a sus víctimas.\n"
"\n"
"Sea cual sea la veracidad de su origen, pueden resultar muy efectivos contra "
"criaturas menores y espíritus débiles, mientras que los guerreros valientes "
"y experimentados los consideran poco más que una molestia en el campo de "
"batalla."

#. [unit_type]: id=Valdemon Basher, race=imps
#: After_the_Storm/units/imps/Valdemon_Basher.cfg:6
msgid "Valdemon Basher"
msgstr "Aplastador Valdemon"

#. [unit_type]: id=Valdemon Basher, race=imps
#: After_the_Storm/units/imps/Valdemon_Basher.cfg:22
msgid ""
"While these behemoths—native to the shores of Inferno—are remarkably dumb, "
"they are quite skilled at using their heads—literally—to knock their "
"opponents out of the way, allowing their smarter allies to trespass their "
"defenses."
msgstr ""
"Aunque estos behemoths —nativos de las costas del Infierno— son notablemente "
"torpes, son bastante hábiles usando sus cabezas —literalmente— para apartar "
"a sus oponentes y permitir que sus aliados más astutos atraviesen las "
"defensas enemigas."

#. [unit_type]: id=Magnum Suit, race=mechanical
#: After_the_Storm/units/mechanical/Magnum_Suit.cfg:6
msgid "Magnum Suit"
msgstr "Armadura Magnum"

#. [unit_type]: id=Magnum Suit, race=mechanical
#: After_the_Storm/units/mechanical/Magnum_Suit.cfg:36
msgid ""
"The many parallels existing between dwarvish and Chaos technology have "
"remained a troubling mystery for centuries. Although claims of lost "
"prototypes and espionage have served well enough to satisfy the most "
"inquisitive minds so far, many still suspected that some other force had to "
"exist behind all that technological advancement."
msgstr ""
"Los numerosos paralelismos entre la tecnología enana y la del Caos han sido "
"un inquietante misterio durante siglos. Aunque las afirmaciones sobre "
"prototipos perdidos y espionaje han bastado para satisfacer a las mentes más "
"inquisitivas hasta ahora, muchos aún sospechaban que alguna otra fuerza "
"debía existir detrás de todo ese avance tecnológico."

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: After_the_Storm/units/mechanical/Magnum_Suit.cfg:47
msgid "soul hammer"
msgstr "martillo de almas"

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: After_the_Storm/units/mechanical/Magnum_Suit.cfg:60
msgid "flamethrower"
msgstr "lanzallamas"

#. [unit_type]: id=Giant Mushroom, race=monster, description=FIXME
#: After_the_Storm/units/monsters/Giant_Mushroom.cfg:5
msgid "Giant Mushroom"
msgstr "Hongo Gigante"

#. [unit_type]: id=Lumeril Glyph, race=monster
#: After_the_Storm/units/monsters/Lumeril_Glyph.cfg:6
msgid "Lumeril Glyph"
msgstr "Glifo Lumeril"

#. [unit_type]: id=Lumeril Glyph, race=monster
#: After_the_Storm/units/monsters/Lumeril_Glyph.cfg:36
msgid ""
"This ethereal projection was created by a powerful demoness, follower of the "
"path of Light. As such, it is invulnerable to physical attacks."
msgstr ""
"Esta proyección etérea fue creada por una poderosa demonesa, seguidora del "
"camino de la Luz. Por ello, es invulnerable a los ataques físicos."

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: After_the_Storm/units/monsters/Lumeril_Glyph.cfg:69
#: After_the_Storm/units/monsters/Lumeril_Glyph.cfg:80
msgid "lightbeam"
msgstr "rayo de luz"

#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Custodian Drone, race=shaxthal
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Drone_Custodian.cfg:6
msgid "Custodian Drone"
msgstr "Dron Custodio"

#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Custodian Drone, race=shaxthal
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Drone_Custodian.cfg:27
msgid ""
"This massive airborne Shaxthal creature was created with the purpose of "
"protecting key locations with its powerful raining fire attack. Combining "
"the strengths of the more generic drones, a formidable foe like this is best "
"approached with extreme caution."
msgstr ""
"Esta enorme criatura aérea Shaxthal fue creada con el propósito de proteger "
"lugares clave con su poderoso ataque de lluvia de fuego. Combinando las "
"fortalezas de los drones más genéricos, un enemigo formidable como este debe "
"ser enfrentado con extrema precaución."

#. [attack]: type=impact
#. [attack]
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Drone_Custodian.cfg:44
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Stormblade_Ivyel.cfg:24
msgid "energy shock"
msgstr "choque de energía"

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Drone_Custodian.cfg:53
msgid "firefly rain"
msgstr "lluvia de luciérnagas"

#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Demolisher Drone, race=shaxthal, description=
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Drone_Demolisher.cfg:6
msgid "Demolisher Drone"
msgstr "Dron Demoledor"

#. [attack]: type=pierce
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Drone_Demolisher.cfg:45
msgid "drill"
msgstr "taladro"

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Drone_Demolisher.cfg:66
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Queen.cfg:51
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Turret.cfg:34
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Turret.cfg:43
msgid "energy burst"
msgstr "ráfaga de energía"

#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Infiltrator, race=shaxthal
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Infiltrator.cfg:9
msgid "female^Infiltrator"
msgstr "Infiltradora"

#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Infiltrator, race=shaxthal
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Infiltrator.cfg:17
msgid ""
"A creature made of flesh and steel, with the power of the arcane flame "
"bestowed upon her and unconditional servitude as her only goal in life, this "
"hybrid Shaxthal being was created and enhanced for the purpose of posing as "
"the elvenkind savior to provide the forces of Uria with new and powerful "
"allies."
msgstr ""
"Una criatura hecha de carne y acero, con el poder de la llama arcana "
"conferido sobre ella y la servidumbre incondicional como su único objetivo "
"en la vida, este ser híbrido Shaxthal fue creado y mejorado con el propósito "
"de hacerse pasar por el salvador de los elfos para proporcionar a las "
"fuerzas de Uria nuevos y poderosos aliados."

#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Hive Queen, race=shaxthal
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Queen.cfg:6
msgid "Hive Queen"
msgstr "Reina de la Colmena"

#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Hive Queen, race=shaxthal
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Queen.cfg:22
msgid ""
"One of the greatest mysteries surrounding Shaxthalkind is their ability to "
"follow orders from the servants of Uria, even though they normally appear to "
"be chiefly insentient, irrational creatures with no ability to understand or "
"communicate with other lifeforms. Following the destruction of the hive in "
"the ruins of Weldyn, it’s been theorized by some that their behavior could "
"be driven by commands from a single controlling entity of their own species."
msgstr ""
"Uno de los mayores misterios que rodean a los Shaxthal es su capacidad para "
"obedecer órdenes de los sirvientes de Uria, aunque normalmente parecen ser "
"criaturas principalmente insensibles e irracionales, sin capacidad para "
"comprender o comunicarse con otras formas de vida. Tras la destrucción de la "
"colmena en las ruinas de Weldyn, algunos han teorizado que su comportamiento "
"podría estar dirigido por las órdenes de una única entidad controladora de "
"su propia especie."

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Shaxthal_Deathbringer.cfg:44
msgid "concussion beam"
msgstr "rayo de conmoción"

#. [attack]
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Stormblade_Ivyel.cfg:20
msgid "weapon^rayblade"
msgstr "espada rayo"

#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Turret, race=shaxthal
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Turret.cfg:6
msgid "Turret"
msgstr "Torreta"

#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Turret, race=shaxthal
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Turret.cfg:29
msgid ""
"It is said that these technological constructs once were living creatures, "
"and in particular, some of the most persistent opponents faced by Uria’s "
"forces on Irdya and Inferno. Whether their former selves remain within their "
"twisted bodies is a mystery, but if it were indeed the case they would "
"unhesitatingly embrace their own destruction."
msgstr ""
"Se dice que estas construcciones tecnológicas alguna vez fueron criaturas "
"vivientes, y en particular, algunos de los oponentes más persistentes que "
"enfrentaron las fuerzas de Uria en Irdya e Inferno. Si sus antiguos seres "
"permanecen dentro de sus cuerpos retorcidos es un misterio, pero de ser así "
"abrazarían sin vacilar su propia destrucción."

#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Warlord Elyssa, race=shaxthal, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Warlord_Elyssa.cfg:5
msgid "female^Shaxthal Warlord"
msgstr "Señora de la Guerra Shaxthal"

#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Warlord Elyssa, race=shaxthal, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Warlord_Elyssa.cfg:34
msgid ""
"Nobody knows for sure what path led her to become what she is now: a "
"creature neither human nor machine. The Chaos Warlord’s human visage and "
"emaciated body belie the fearsome strength and sharpness of mind she has "
"displayed in battle over the centuries. To Uria’s servants — humans or "
"otherwise — her unnatural abilities and great power have earned her a "
"reputation as a demoness, along with the fear and respect normally reserved "
"for a demon lord.\n"
"\n"
"The fate of anyone facing her in combat is already set, and the most they "
"can hope for is a swift and painless death."
msgstr ""
"Nadie sabe con certeza qué camino la llevó a convertirse en lo que es ahora: "
"una criatura que no es ni humana ni máquina. El semblante humano de la "
"Señora de la Guerra del Caos y su cuerpo demacrado ocultan la temible fuerza "
"y agudeza mental que ha demostrado en combate a lo largo de los siglos. Para "
"los sirvientes de Uria —humanos o no—, sus habilidades antinaturales y su "
"gran poder le han otorgado una reputación de demonio, junto con el miedo y "
"respeto que normalmente se reserva a un señor demoníaco.\n"
"\n"
"El destino de cualquiera que se enfrente a ella en combate ya está sellado, "
"y lo mejor que pueden esperar es una muerte rápida y sin dolor."

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Warlord_Elyssa.cfg:53
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Warlord_Narhamoth.cfg:50
msgid "ethereal blast"
msgstr "explosión etérea"

#. [attack]: type=fire
