#. [unit_type]: id=Shaxthal Warlord Narhamoth, race=shaxthal
#: After_the_Storm/units/shaxthal/Warlord_Narhamoth.cfg:33
msgid ""
"In stark contrast with their remarkably savage soldiers and mercenaries, the "
"Chaos Empire’s higher tiers are well defined and disciplined. Commanding the "
"uncivilized human and demonic hordes is no easy task, and the Chaos "
"Lorekeepers use their dominance of magic to intimidate their violent "
"subordinates and keep them under control."
msgstr ""
"En marcado contraste con sus soldados y mercenarios notablemente salvajes, "
"los rangos superiores del Imperio del Caos están bien definidos y "
"disciplinados. Comandar a las hordas humanas y demoníacas incivilizadas no "
"es tarea fácil, y los Guardianes del Caos usan su dominio de la magia para "
"intimidar a sus subordinados violentos y mantenerlos bajo control."

#. [unit_type]: id=Chaos Cardinal Fused, race=undead
#: After_the_Storm/units/undead/Chaos_Cardinal_Fused.cfg:6
msgid "Chaos Cardinal"
msgstr "Cardenal del Caos"

#. [unit_type]: id=Chaos Cardinal Fused, race=undead
#: After_the_Storm/units/undead/Chaos_Cardinal_Fused.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Infused with Yechnagoth’s dark power and bound to the structure housing a "
"replica of her preserved heart, this necromancer knows no limits to his "
"worship of the deities who mandated the construction of the Chaos Empire. "
"Thus he has offered his own soul as a tribute for the Eater of Souls, intent "
"on fulfilling her covenant with Uria by utilizing his own decayed body as a "
"medium.\n"
"\n"
"Even while restricted to watching his minions strike down all undesirable "
"intrusion during his unholy ritual, and even as the corrupting energy of the "
"fallen goddess slowly gnaws at his very soul, he can channel it into a "
"devastating blast capable of ravaging the souls of his helpless targets."
msgstr ""
"Imbuido con el oscuro poder de Yechnagoth y atado a la estructura que "
"alberga una réplica de su corazón preservado, este nigromante no conoce "
"límites en su adoración a las deidades que ordenaron la construcción del "
"Imperio del Caos. Así, ha ofrecido su propia alma como tributo a la "
"Devoradora de Almas, decidido a cumplir su pacto con Uria utilizando su "
"propio cuerpo en descomposición como medio.\n"
"\n"
"Aunque está limitado a observar cómo sus esbirros aniquilan toda intrusión "
"indeseada durante su ritual profano, y aun cuando la energía corruptora de "
"la diosa caída roe lentamente su propia alma, puede canalizarla en una "
"devastadora explosión capaz de arrasar las almas de sus indefensas víctimas."

#. [attack]: type=cold
