#: After_the_Storm/units/undead/Fallen_Faerie.cfg:6
msgid "female^Fallen Faerie"
msgstr "hada caída"

#. [unit_type]: id=Fallen Faerie, race=undead, gender=female
#: After_the_Storm/units/undead/Fallen_Faerie.cfg:40
msgid ""
"The essence of true faeries normally makes it unfeasible for them to be "
"brought back as undead, but this is by no means a feat without precedent.\n"
"\n"
"Much like other creatures resurrected by necromancy they are merely shadows "
"of their former beings, mostly devoid of free will and emotions. They roam "
"about places from their previous memories, seeking to draw energy from the "
"living in a futile attempt to revert the effects of time upon their decayed "
"bodies and spirits. Their former affinity to forests becomes key to their "
"subsistence, but there is little more they can obtain from it."
msgstr ""
"La esencia de las verdaderas hadas normalmente hace inviable que sean "
"resucitadas como no-muertas, pero esto no es un hecho sin precedentes.\n"
"\n"
"Al igual que otras criaturas resucitadas por nigromancia, son meras sombras "
"de sus antiguos seres, en su mayoría carentes de voluntad propia y "
"emociones. Deambulan por lugares de sus recuerdos anteriores, buscando "
"absorber energía de los vivos en un intento vano de revertir los efectos del "
"tiempo sobre sus cuerpos y espíritus decadentes. Su antigua afinidad con los "
"bosques se vuelve clave para su subsistencia, pero poco más pueden obtener "
"de ello."

